NK071(du)002:1: // s+au r+ya tsa n+d+ra s+ya ga r+b+ha n+aa ma m+aa
NK071(du)002:2: ya dz+aa la m+au la s+ya tan+t+ra s+yo pa bri
NK071(du)002:3: t+ti bi ha ra ti sma //
NK071(du)002:7: //  // sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi mchan 'grel nyi zla'i snying po zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:10: // sam pa ra pa r+ya go tra +pa ram pa
NK071(du)002:11: r+ya bi d+y+aa d+ha ro ni rmi t+aa r+g+ho dzi
NK071(du)002:15: // rgyal ba dgongs brgyud rig 'dzin brda yi brgyud //
NK071(du)002:16: sprul pa'i gang zag rim nas rim brgyud dang /
NK071(du)002:19: // na ma s+se ni kah u t+ta ma sh+tsi t+ta
NK071(du)002:20: de bo ma h+aa ka lpa n+aa dwa tsa d+aa
NK071(du)002:23: // yi dam lha dang d+aak+ki tshogs bcas la //
NK071(du)002:24: gnyis med mnyam pa chen pos phyag bagyi'o /
NK071(du)002:27: / de la 'dir theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK071(du)002:29: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi theg pa'i nye lam chen po /
NK071(du)002:30: gsang ba bas kyang ches shin tu gsang ba //
NK071(du)002:31: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nges pa'i
NK071(du)002:32: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'chad pa la gsum
NK071(du)002:33: ste / brjod bya rtogs pa'i yan lag tu mtshan gyi don bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:34: brjod bya nyid gsal bar ston pa rgyud kyi don dngos bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:35: yongs su rdzogs pa 'jug gi don bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:38: phyag gis mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:41: sh+r+ai gu h+ya gar+b+ha ta t+aa bi ni stsa ya ma h+aa tan+t+ra n+aa ma /
NK071(du)002:43: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa sku gsung
NK071(du)002:44: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo 'khor 'das
NK071(du)002:45: thams cad dbyer med pa ni 'khor 'das kun gyi
NK071(du)002:46: dpal de nyid shin tu rtogs par dka' bas gsang
NK071(du)002:47: ba'i ste sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK071(du)002:48: mi khyab pa'o // gnas lugs rdzogsa pa chen po
NK071(du)002:49: dang de'i rjod byed zab cing rgya che ba rnams
NK071(du)002:50: ni snying po yin la de nyid kun khyab bslu
NK071(du)002:51: ba med pa'i chos te 'pho 'gyur med pas de
NK071(du)002:52: kho na nyid don de yang sangs rgyas la yod
NK071(du)002:53: cing sems can la med pa ltar ma yin pas
NK071(du)002:54: rnam par nges pa'i don gyi rgyud chen po'o //
NK071(du)002:55: gzhan yang thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor ni gzhi gsang ba'i snying po //
NK071(du)002:56: de nyid bskyed rdzogs gnyis su med pas nyams su len pa ni lam de kho na nyid /
NK071(du)002:57: mthar thug sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa na 'bras bu gzhi thog tu nges pa'o //
NK071(du)002:58: mdor na snang ba dang stong pa bskyed pa dang
NK071(du)002:59: rdzogs pa 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa
NK071(du)002:60: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin du ye nas sangs
NK071(du)002:61: rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid ston pa'i mtshan yin no
NK071(du)002:63: bdud bzhi dang sgrib pa gnyis bag chags dang bcas
NK071(du)002:64: pa bcom pa ni spangs ba phun sum tshogs pa'o
NK071(du)002:65: // sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i don
NK071(du)002:66: dang ldan pa ni rtogs pa phun sum tshogs pa'o
NK071(du)002:67: // // kha cig bcom pa'i don de nyid dang ldan pas bcom ldan zhes kyang bzhed do //
NK071(du)002:68: 'khor 'das blang dor yod med sogs spros pa'i mtshan
NK071(du)002:69: ma thams cad las 'das pa chos kyi sku las
NK071(du)002:70: ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs sku lhun grub tu 'char
NK071(du)002:71: ba'i don gnyis grub pa'i dpal lhun stug po bkod
NK071(du)002:72: pa'i zhing na 'pho 'gyur med par dus kun tu
NK071(du)002:73: bzhugs shing rang snang ba'i longs spyod chen po rdzogs
NK071(du)002:74: pas bzang po de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK071(du)002:75: de yang dbye na lnga ste /
NK071(du)002:76: kun gyi sngon rol du mngon par byang chub gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)002:77: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs de bzhin nyid rang bzhin kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)002:78: sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo sku gsum 'du
NK071(du)002:79: 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin da lta nyid nas rang
NK071(du)002:80: chas su lhun gyis grub pas ye nas sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:81: pa gzhi'i kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)002:82: lam goms pas thabs shes gnyis med kyi rtogs pa shar ba lam kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)002:83: lam mthar phyin nas gzhi thog tu phyin te sku
NK071(du)002:84: dang ye shes lhun gyis grub pa ni 'bras bu'i
NK071(du)002:86: yul de dag la 'gyur mdzad pa po sgo gsum dang bas phyag byas pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:87: brjod bya nyid gsal bar ston pa rgyud kyi don dngos la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:88: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang las 'char tshul bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:89: de las zhi khro gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'phros tshul bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:90: rgyud dam par gdams nas rjes 'jug la gtad tshul bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:92: chos sku'i ston pa nyid dbyings las ma g.yos par
NK071(du)002:93: lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing du rdo rje dbyings
NK071(du)002:94: kyi dkyil 'khor rang snang bar ji ltar bkod pa'i
NK071(du)002:95: tshul / ston pa nyid rigs lngar bzhengs pa'i thugs
NK071(du)002:96: rang byung gi ye shes gnyis su med pas chos
NK071(du)002:97: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par ched du brjod
NK071(du)002:98: cing thugs rje g.yo ba'i tshul /
NK071(du)002:99: thugs rje rang bzhin chos nyid las ma g.yos bzhin
NK071(du)002:100: du rnam pas 'jig rten na sgron ma bkod de
NK071(du)002:101: chos thams cad gtan la dbab pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:103: phun sum tshogs pa'i gleng gzhi mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:104: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:105: ye shes kyi rang snang bkod par don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:107: phyi rgyud 'byung ba gleng gzhi'i tshul du bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:108: nang ltar bkod pa byang chub sems su bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:109: gsang ba 'od gsal ltar bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:111: e wam m+aa y+aa zhes pa'i sgras go bar bya ste /
NK071(du)002:112: e wam ni dbyings kyi yi ge yin pas de
NK071(du)002:113: las yi ge kun 'byung ba'i phyir 'og nas 'byung
NK071(du)002:114: ba'i tshul 'di skad ces pa snang bar byed do
NK071(du)002:119: 'byung ba sogs yod kyang 'dir 'byung ba bzung ste bshad pa'i dus zhes pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:120: de la 'di skad 'og gi rgyud rgyas pa rnams te chos phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:121: bshad pa'i zhes rgyud sdud pa po nyid ston pa phun sum tshogs par zhal gyis bzhes pa dang /
NK071(du)002:122: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa'ang shugs la bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:123: dus na zhes pas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin dus phun sum tshogs pa bstan la /
NK071(du)002:126: 'khor rnams snang ba de'i tshe gnas kyang yod nges pas 'og miin shugs la bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:128: gnas yul gyi gsang ba dang 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa rnams so //
NK071(du)002:129: ston pa yab yum ni dwangs ma dkar dmar dang ye shes kyi rlung ngo //
NK071(du)002:130: 'khor dga' ba bcu drug gi nyams dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:131: chos bde stong gnyis med kyi ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:132: dus gtsug tor 'khor los bsgyur ba bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i dus na'o //
NK071(du)002:134: gnas snying rin chen zur brgyad pa'i dbus na srog gi rtsa mthing ga /
NK071(du)002:135: shar na chu'i rtsa dkar po /
NK071(du)002:136: lho na sa'i rtsa ser po /
NK071(du)002:137: nub na me'i rtsa dmar po /
NK071(du)002:138: byang na rlung gi rtsa ljang gu rnams kyi nang
NK071(du)002:139: na kun rdzob kyi thig le nyungs 'bru tsam re
NK071(du)002:140: gnas so // ston pa ni rang byung gi ye
NK071(du)002:141: shes 'od lnga so sor ma 'dres pa'i kha dog
NK071(du)002:142: la ye shes lnga'i rang rtsal ma 'gag par bzhugs
NK071(du)002:143: gnas so // pa'o // 'khor ni rtsa dang thig
NK071(du)002:144: le de dag las lus kyi steng 'og kun tu
NK071(du)002:146: dus ni gnas skabs lus dang dbang po'i rten 'brel
NK071(du)002:147: tshang ba dang rang bzhin dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med
NK071(du)002:148: pas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dus so //
NK071(du)002:149: chos ni stong gsal spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:150: gnyis pa de rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:151: ston pa'i ngo bo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:152: de'i dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:154: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu'i de bzhin nyid la
NK071(du)002:155: mnga' brnyes pa de'i tshe sku gzhan bzhi yang rtag
NK071(du)002:156: tu lhun gyis grub cing chos sku'i rjes su byed
NK071(du)002:157: pa mthun pas de bzhin gshegs pa sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)002:158: rgyan gyi 'khor lo yon tan thams cad yang dag
NK071(du)002:159: par rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid ni ma rig pa'i gnyid
NK071(du)002:160: las sangs shing shes bya thams cad la blo gros
NK071(du)002:161: phun sum tshogs pa rgyas pa bdud bzhi ye nas
NK071(du)002:162: bcom pa sogs gong du bstan pa'i yon tan rnams
NK071(du)002:164: gnas dang 'khor la sogs pa gzhan la mi ltos
NK071(du)002:165: par ye shes kyi rang snang nyid du ting nge
NK071(du)002:166: 'dzin gyi sgyu ma'i rol par lhun gyis grub pas
NK071(du)002:167: longs spyod chen po shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba
NK071(du)002:168: la sogs pa phyogs bcu dang 'das pa'i dus su
NK071(du)002:169: byung ba la sogs pa'i dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:170: pa mi 'khrugs pa dang mar me mdzad la sogs
NK071(du)002:171: pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo
NK071(du)002:172: rje'i bdag nyid / chos sku'i phun sum tshogs pa
NK071(du)002:173: ma lus pa thams cad longs sku'i phun sum tshogs
NK071(du)002:174: pa mi lus pa thams cad sprul sku'i phun sum
NK071(du)002:175: tshogs pa lus pa med pa thams cad dang /
NK071(du)002:176: ngo bo so so ma yin zhing dgongs pa tha
NK071(du)002:177: mi dad chos nyid la dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:178: te / ye nas lhun gyis grub cing 'du 'bral med pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:182: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:184: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i zhing khams dang /
NK071(du)002:186: bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:187: dang po lhun stug po bkod pa snang ba thams
NK071(du)002:188: cad kyi mchog de'i gong na gzhan med pas 'og
NK071(du)002:189: min gyi gnas steng dang 'og la sogs pa'i phyogs
NK071(du)002:190: bcu ma yin pas mtha' dang dbus zhes ris su
NK071(du)002:192: 'og gzhi yang rgya khyon gyi tshad dmigs su med
NK071(du)002:193: pa me long lta bu la sogs pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:194: kyi rtsal ma 'gags pas nyon mongs pa lnga gcod
NK071(du)002:195: pa'i rtags su 'od lnga'i 'khor lo rtsib bzhi lte
NK071(du)002:196: ba dang bcas pa ma 'dres par rang gsal ba
NK071(du)002:198: ye shes lnga'i gdangs las 'dod dgu lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:199: pa'i rin po che 'od dang gzi brjid mtha' yas
NK071(du)002:200: pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ltar 'bar ba'i ngo bo
NK071(du)002:201: yon tan dang rgya khyon la sogs pa blos dpag
NK071(du)002:202: par mi nus pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK071(du)002:203: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)002:204: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' bas de'i rgya che
NK071(du)002:205: chung gi tshad phyogs bcur mthar thug pa med pa'i
NK071(du)002:206: phyir yongs su ma chad pa ste nam mkha' dang
NK071(du)002:207: mnyam pa / sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa
NK071(du)002:208: bco brgyad dang zad par dang zil gnon la sogs
NK071(du)002:209: pa'i yon tan dpag tu med par yongs su rgyas
NK071(du)002:210: pa'i phyir dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa me long lta
NK071(du)002:211: bu la sogs pa mthar thug pa'i ye shes bzhi
NK071(du)002:212: sangs rgyas kho na'i chos yin pas lhag pa'i ye
NK071(du)002:213: shes te de dag nyid mtshon pa'i brdar phyogs bzhi
NK071(du)002:214: na shel dang gser dang pad+ma r+aa ga dang mar
NK071(du)002:215: gad las grub pa'i rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis
NK071(du)002:216: mnyam pa / mdzes pa / ye shes thams cad
NK071(du)002:217: kyang ngo bo gcig pa'i brdar dkyil 'khor gcig tu
NK071(du)002:218: mnyam pa / mdzes pa / bstan la / rtsa
NK071(du)002:219: ba'i ye shes lnga las gyes pa'i ye shes lnga
NK071(du)002:220: lnga mtshon pa'i phyir phyogs bzhi'i glo 'bur gyi sgras
NK071(du)002:221: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyi rtsig pa lnga yang
NK071(du)002:222: nang nas rim pa bzhin mthing ga dang /
NK071(du)002:226: dkar po rnams sbrags mar bstan pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:227: gzhal med khang de'i rtse mo ste bum pa zlum
NK071(du)002:228: po ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mtshon pa
NK071(du)002:229: ste sngar smon pa bzhin phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs
NK071(du)002:230: rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad rang
NK071(du)002:231: bzhin so so ma yin zhing ngo bo nyid gcig
NK071(du)002:232: pa'i ye shes chen po dus bzhi kun tu 'khyil
NK071(du)002:233: ba / ye shes re re la'ang lnga lnga ste
NK071(du)002:234: ye shes nyi shu rtsa lnga nas de yang lnga
NK071(du)002:235: tshan du phye bas ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)002:237: zhing dang gzhal yas khang pa'i dbyibs dang kha dog
NK071(du)002:238: la sogs pa'i ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang
NK071(du)002:239: kha dog dang mthun pa rtsa ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK071(du)002:240: nas phyogs bzhi la sogs pa dag tu gzhal yas
NK071(du)002:241: khang grangs med pa thams cad kyi kha dog so
NK071(du)002:242: sor gsal zhing de dag gi dbyibs kyang dbus gru
NK071(du)002:243: bzhi shar zla gam la sogs par dang kha dog
NK071(du)002:244: kyang dkar ser sogs rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye
NK071(du)002:245: brag dang bkod pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas khyad
NK071(du)002:247: nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa'i snang ba'i yon tan las khyad par du spags pa /
NK071(du)002:248: dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs pa'i tshad dpag tu med pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:250: rgyan dang khri'i bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:252: ngo bo ye shes la grub pa rin po che
NK071(du)002:253: sna tshogs kyi gzugs dang kha dog tu snang ba'i
NK071(du)002:254: rang bzhin rtsig pa lnga'i steng na pha gu dang
NK071(du)002:255: de'i steng mda' phyir 'phyar ba'i kha bad kyi gdung
NK071(du)002:256: sna las ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi
NK071(du)002:258: de'i bar bar na nyi zla'i tshar dang dar gyi
NK071(du)002:259: lda ldi dang rnga yab nor bu'i yu ba can
NK071(du)002:261: rtse mo rin po che'i d+r+wa mig gseng ma'i shar bu'i rgyan gyi pu shus mdzes pa dang /
NK071(du)002:262: mi sgrib pa gsal ba'i rgyan can rab tu 'tsher zhing yid du 'ong ba ste /
NK071(du)002:263: pha gu ni ye shes 'gyur ba med pa'i brda' 'o //
NK071(du)002:264: d+r+wa phyed ni sku gsum du 'du 'bral med pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i barda'o //
NK071(du)002:265: mda' yab ni thugs rjes 'gro ba sgrol ba'i barda'o //
NK071(du)002:266: pu shu ni kun gyi bla mar gyur pas mtshungs pa med pa'i barda'o //
NK071(du)002:267: gzhan yang 'dod yon gyi snam bu'i steng na gzhal
NK071(du)002:268: yas khang pa'i phyogs bcu kun tu khyab par 'dod
NK071(du)002:269: yon gyi lha mo lnga lnga'i sprin 'phro bas nang
NK071(du)002:270: gi lha rnams la mchod pa ni yid du 'ong
NK071(du)002:275: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur sprin phung 'khrigs pa rang byung la /
NK071(du)002:276: 'di dag ni 'dod yon thams cad rol pa'i rgyan du shar ba'i brda' 'o //
NK071(du)002:277: phyi nang gi rgyan thams cad rags par ma grub
NK071(du)002:278: cing dwangs bas gcig gis gcig mi sgrib par phyi
NK071(du)002:279: nang zang thal bar gsal ba'i rgyan can bkod mdzes
NK071(du)002:280: shing bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab par lhab lhub
NK071(du)002:281: tu klubs pa ni sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas
NK071(du)002:282: 'od gsal shing yon tan tshad med par mtshon pa'o
NK071(du)002:283: // dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa
NK071(du)002:284: las rnam par thar pa stong pa nyid dang mtshan
NK071(du)002:285: ma med pa dang smon pa med pa dang /
NK071(du)002:286: mngon par 'dus ma byas pa bzhi'i sgo nas kun
NK071(du)002:287: tu bzang po lhun gyis grub pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK071(du)002:288: der 'jug pa mtshon pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK071(du)002:289: gzugs can gzugs la blta ba'i rnam thar dang /
NK071(du)002:290: gzugs can ma yin pa gzugs la lta ba'i rnam thar dang /
NK071(du)002:292: nam mkha' mtha' yas dang rnam shes mtha' yas dang ci yang med pa dang /
NK071(du)002:293: 'du shes med 'du shes med min gyi skye mched kyi rnam thar dang /
NK071(du)002:294: 'gog pa'i rnam thar te rnam par thar pa brgyad
NK071(du)002:295: kyi yon tan thams cad lhun grub tu rdzogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:296: brdar sgo bzhi'i phyi 'gram gnyis na ka ba gnyis
NK071(du)002:297: gnyis te bzhis btegs pa'i sgo steng na rdo rje'i
NK071(du)002:298: gdung bzhi'i steng rta babs bang rim bzhi nyid snam
NK071(du)002:299: phran brgyad dang ldan pa la rin po che'i gdugs
NK071(du)002:300: kyi rtsa bar chos kyi 'khor lo ri dwags gnyis
NK071(du)002:304: dar gyi lda ldi dang kha khyer bzhi bzhi la
NK071(du)002:305: ba dan nyer bzhi gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha'i
NK071(du)002:306: phreng ba khrol ba la sogs pas brgyan zhing /
NK071(du)002:307: spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:308: yin pas phyi dang nang med pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)002:309: yon tan thams cad der ma chud pa med pas
NK071(du)002:310: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK071(du)002:312: theg pa 'og mas nyam ma nga zhing mi 'jigs
NK071(du)002:313: pa bzhi mtshon pa'i phyir dbus su seng ge'i khri
NK071(du)002:314: dang / theg pa 'og mar mi chud pa'i don
NK071(du)002:315: 'dir shong zhing theg la stobs bcu mnga' ba'i brdar
NK071(du)002:316: shar du glang po che'i khri dang /
NK071(du)002:317: gdul bya thams cad myur du grol bar byed cing
NK071(du)002:318: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi la dbang 'byor ba'i
NK071(du)002:319: rtags su lhor cang shes rta'i khri dang /
NK071(du)002:320: snang ba thams cad dbang du byed cing dbang bcu mnga' ba'i brdar nub tu rma bya'i khri dang /
NK071(du)002:321: phrin las sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba 'dul zhing thogs
NK071(du)002:322: pa med pa'i ye shes gsum dang so so yang
NK071(du)002:323: dag par rigs pa bzhis don mdzad pa'i brdar byang
NK071(du)002:324: du nam mkha' lding ste shang shang gi khri dang
NK071(du)002:325: / sems nyid ye nas rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal
NK071(du)002:326: ba'i rang bzhin thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:327: pa mtshon pa'i nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)002:328: nyes pa'i skyon thams cad kyis gos pa med pa
NK071(du)002:329: mtshon pa'i sna tshogs pad+ma ste de dag gi rgyu
NK071(du)002:330: 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i rin po che'i rang bzhin gyi
NK071(du)002:332: de yang khri lnga'i steng na pad+ma dang nyi zlas
NK071(du)002:333: spras pa ni gtso bo rnams kyi gdan yin la
NK071(du)002:334: 'khor la ni so so'i gnas su pad+ma dang nyi
NK071(du)002:336: gnyis pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:337: gtso bo bzhugs tshul dang phyag mtshan thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:338: yab yum so sor bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:339: dang po ni sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin 'gro ba
NK071(du)002:340: thams cad la dus rtag tu gzigs shing rgyab kyis
NK071(du)002:341: mi phyogs pa sku mdun dang rgyab med pa /
NK071(du)002:342: tshom bu'i 'khor thams cad la mdun gyis gzigs pas
NK071(du)002:343: phyogs thams cad du zhal gyi dkyil 'khor thal le
NK071(du)002:344: bar gsal zhing mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa
NK071(du)002:345: / de yang thun mong ma yin pa'i dbang du
NK071(du)002:346: byas nas dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bcu drug gi
NK071(du)002:347: rtsa sems dpa' bcu drug dang /
NK071(du)002:348: de'i yul chos dbyings bcu drug gi sems ma bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mtshan dang /
NK071(du)002:349: sems dpa' bcu drug po re re la'ang ye shes
NK071(du)002:350: lnga'i rtags rigs lnga lnga'i dbu brgyan pa ni dpe
NK071(du)002:351: byad do // yum rnams la dbu rgyan med pa ni chos kyi dbyings mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)002:352: de dag mtshan dper 'jog pa ni 'khor phun sum
NK071(du)002:353: tshogs pas gtso bo rang bzhin yang bkod pa mdzes
NK071(du)002:354: shing phun sum tshogs pa ste me tog gi ze'u
NK071(du)002:355: 'bru dang 'dab mas me tog gi bkod pa mdzes
NK071(du)002:357: thun mong ba ni phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan pa la sogs pa sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan dang /
NK071(du)002:358: sen mo zangs kyi mdog lta bu la sogs pa brgyad cu ni dpe byad do //
NK071(du)002:359: nam mkha'i khams dang gdul bya'i 'jig rten bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du /
NK071(du)002:360: lhun gyis grub pa'i sku gsung thugs mi zad pa
NK071(du)002:361: rgyan gyi 'khor los sna tshogs par kun tu snang
NK071(du)002:362: ba'o // ji ltar snang na chos kyi dbyings spros
NK071(du)002:363: pa dang bral ba'i zhing khams su sku mi zad
NK071(du)002:364: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo chos sku kun bzang yab
NK071(du)002:365: yum zhal phyag gi mtshan ma las 'das pa /
NK071(du)002:366: gsung mi zad pa brjod du med pa dang mnyan du med pa dang ngo bo nyid med pa /
NK071(du)002:367: thugs mi zad pa gtad du spros pa thams cad zhi zhing rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pa'o //
NK071(du)002:368: nam mkha'i khams kyi mtha' klas par rang snang lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing du ni //
NK071(du)002:369: sku mi zad pa longs spyod pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa /
NK071(du)002:370: gsung mi zad pa zhal gyi dkyil 'khor las 'od zer 'phros pas brjod bya'i don ston pa /
NK071(du)002:371: thugs mi zad pa ye shes lnga'i mtshan nyid du bzhugs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:372: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten 'gro ba drug gi gdul zhing nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa rnams su ni /
NK071(du)002:373: sku mi zad pa gang la gang gis 'dul ba sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK071(du)002:374: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang so so skye
NK071(du)002:375: bo dang lha dang klu la sogs pa sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:376: dang / pad+ma dang dpag bsam gyi shing dang gru
NK071(du)002:377: gzigs dang grong dang skyed mos tshal la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:378: sems can la phan bde 'byung ba de dang de'i
NK071(du)002:380: gsung mi zad pa 'gro ba so so'i skad dang /
NK071(du)002:381: pad+ma dang dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs pa las chos kyi gsung sna tshogs par sgrogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:382: thugs mi zad pa ji lta ba ji snyed pa mkhyen pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad par snang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:383: de'ang sangs rgyas rnams rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis
NK071(du)002:384: mi khyab pas don mdzad pa yin pas 'di dang
NK071(du)002:385: 'adi'o zhes blos bsam par nus pa ma yin no
NK071(du)002:386: // thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong
NK071(du)002:387: pa nyid kyi rang bzhin mtshon pa'i zhabs gnyis srid
NK071(du)002:388: zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pa'i brda rtags su mnyam
NK071(du)002:389: pa'i rang bzhin nyon mongs pas mtha' dag brtul cing
NK071(du)002:390: ye shes chen po'i ngo bor zhugs pa nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:391: brdar rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK071(du)002:392: ye shes lnga dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:393: dang drug gi phyag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK071(du)002:394: las gnyis su med pa'i ye shes las dgos 'dod
NK071(du)002:395: thams cad 'byung bas rin po che'i rang bzhin rdo
NK071(du)002:396: rje la sogs pa'i phyag rgya drug la 'od zer
NK071(du)002:397: mu med pa 'bar ba can ni ser sna dang
NK071(du)002:398: 'chal khrims dang khong khro dang le lo dang rnam
NK071(du)002:399: par g.yeng ba dang shes rab 'chal ba dang drug
NK071(du)002:400: 'joms pa'i barda'o // de'ang rdo rje dang rin po
NK071(du)002:401: che dag 'khor lo dang pad+ma dang rgya gram dang
NK071(du)002:402: dril bu ste rigs so so'i rtsa phyag gnyis kyi
NK071(du)002:403: g.yas thams cad rang rang gi phyag mtshan g.yon thams
NK071(du)002:404: cad dril bu ste thugs kar bsnol nas 'dzin pa
NK071(du)002:405: dang gzhan rnams so sor brkyang pa'o //
NK071(du)002:406: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)002:407: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mtshon byed du dbu gsum
NK071(du)002:408: dang ldan pa ste de yang gtso bo'i rtsa zhal
NK071(du)002:410: mi bskyod pa'i rtsa zhal dkar po g.yas mthing g.yon dmar /
NK071(du)002:411: rin 'byung gi rtsa zhal ser po g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK071(du)002:412: 'od dpag med kyi rtsa zhal dmar po g.yas dkar g.yon mthing /
NK071(du)002:413: don grub kyi rtsa zhal ljang gu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ro //
NK071(du)002:415: dbyings ngo bo nyid kyi gtso bo dang /
NK071(du)002:416: rang bzhin tha mi dad pa'i 'khor lo //
NK071(du)002:418: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK071(du)002:419: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs kyi rgyal po mi bskyod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:420: de bzhin gshegs pa tshor ba'i rgyal po rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK071(du)002:421: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du shes kyi rgyal po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK071(du)002:422: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du byed kyi rgyal po don yod grub pa dang lnga'o //
NK071(du)002:423: de dag kun kyang me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:424: 'gyur ba med pas rnam par snang mdzad mthing ga
NK071(du)002:425: dang / chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dri ma
NK071(du)002:426: thams cad dang bral bas mi bskyod pa dkar po
NK071(du)002:427: dang / dang / mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK071(du)002:428: che ba'i yon tan du ma dang ldan pas rin
NK071(du)002:430: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes 'gro ba'i don la
NK071(du)002:431: rjes su chags pas 'od dpag med le brgan dang
NK071(du)002:432: / bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis sems can
NK071(du)002:433: gyi don du sna tshogs su mdzad pas don yod
NK071(du)002:434: grub pa ljang gu'i mdog tu gsal zhing 'od 'tsher
NK071(du)002:435: ba ni rigs lnga ka'i rang bzhin dwangs la bkrag
NK071(du)002:437: de dag gi yum ni longs spyod par bya ba'i
NK071(du)002:438: gzhi dang gtso bo'i yum du gyur pa dang yon
NK071(du)002:439: tan gyi cho rigs btsun pas btsun mo gzhan las
NK071(du)002:440: khyad par du 'phags pas dam pa nam mkha'i rang
NK071(du)002:441: bzhin ni chos nyid yangs shing yon tan gyi go
NK071(du)002:442: 'byed pa la mi sgrib pas gsal bar byed pa'i
NK071(du)002:443: phyir snang ba'i dbyings nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug
NK071(du)002:444: ma dang / sa ni brtan zhing rten du gyur
NK071(du)002:445: pa bzhin du ngo bo'i mi 'gyur zhing yon tan
NK071(du)002:446: gyi rten byed pas sra ba'i dbyings sangs rgyas spyan
NK071(du)002:447: ma dang / ma dang / chu ni gsher la
NK071(du)002:448: skye bo'i gsos su gyur pa ltar 'gro ba'i rgyud
NK071(du)002:449: rlan par byed bas mnyen pa'i dbyings m+aa ma k+ai
NK071(du)002:450: ma dang / ma dang / dang / me ni
NK071(du)002:451: bsreg cing snang ba ltar nyon mongs pa bsreg cing
NK071(du)002:452: shes bya thams cad gsal bar byed pas dro ba'i
NK071(du)002:454: rlung ni bskyod pa dang 'degs pa'i bya ba byed
NK071(du)002:455: pa ltar 'gro ba'i don la thog pa med cing
NK071(du)002:456: nye bar 'tsho ba'i gzhir gyur pas bskyod pa'i dbyings
NK071(du)002:457: dam tshig sgrol ma dang de la sogs pa rigs
NK071(du)002:458: kyi btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad dang thabs dang shes
NK071(du)002:459: rab gnyis su med par gyur nas chos kyi dbyings
NK071(du)002:460: kun tu mtha' yas par longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i
NK071(du)002:463: dper na til gyi gong bu kha phye ba bzhin
NK071(du)002:464: du go 'tshams med par sku dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:465: dkyil 'khor gyis gang nas thams cad kun tu khyab
NK071(du)002:466: par bzhugs so // gnyis pa rang bzhin 'khor dngos
NK071(du)002:467: ni gong du bshad pas de dang 'brel ba'i thugs
NK071(du)002:469: nang gi sems dpa' yab yum /
NK071(du)002:474: gtso bo rigs lnga'i rang bzhin bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:475: de nas sems dpa'i 'khor bshad pa ni ston pa
NK071(du)002:476: nyid byang chub chen po yin pa bzhin du rang
NK071(du)002:477: snang ba'i thugs rje'i ngang las shar ba'i 'khor rnams
NK071(du)002:478: kyang de ltar yin pas byang chub chen po dbyings
NK071(du)002:479: dang ye shes snang ba dang stong pa gnyis su
NK071(du)002:480: med cing 'jig 'bral med pas rdo rje mthong ba
NK071(du)002:482: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos pa ste phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK071(du)002:483: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa ste nam mkha'i snying dang /
NK071(du)002:484: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba ste spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK071(du)002:485: de dag kyang mthong sogs tha ma la dag pas
NK071(du)002:486: khyad par du byung ba'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK071(du)002:487: yul thams cad la 'jug cing thams cad kyang ro
NK071(du)002:488: gcig tu mkhyen pa'i brdar snang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:489: gnyis pa de dag gi yum bzhi ni rim pa
NK071(du)002:490: bzhin du btsun mo mthong bar bya ba ye shes
NK071(du)002:491: kyi snang ba'i yul gzugs te sgeg mo dang /
NK071(du)002:492: mnyan par bya ba phreng ba ma dang /
NK071(du)002:493: bsnam par bya ba glu dbyangs ma dang /
NK071(du)002:494: myong bar bya ba'i rang bzhin gar ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:495: gnyis pa phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:497: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed de byams pa dang /
NK071(du)002:498: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos byed de sgrib pa rnam sel dang /
NK071(du)002:499: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom byed de kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)002:500: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong byed de 'jam dpal dang /
NK071(du)002:501: 'di dag kyang tha mal gyi dbang po las khyad
NK071(du)002:502: par du 'phags pa sangs rgyas kyi spyan sogs sgrib
NK071(du)002:503: pa med pas yul kun la 'jug pa'i rten byed
NK071(du)002:504: pa'i mtshon byed du snang ba yin no //
NK071(du)002:505: gnyis pa de dag gi yum bzhi ni rim pa
NK071(du)002:506: bzhin btsun mo 'das pa ste bdug spos mar snang
NK071(du)002:507: ba dang / da ltar ste me tog mar snang ba dang /
NK071(du)002:508: ma byung ba ste snang gsal mar snang ba dang /
NK071(du)002:509: 'byung bar ma nges pa'i rang bzhin dri chab mar snang ba'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:510: gsum pa sgo ba yab yum la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:512: 'joms pa ste thams cad dang chen po ste shes
NK071(du)002:513: rab kyi rang bzhin rdo rje reg pa bdud rtsi
NK071(du)002:514: 'khyil ba dang / 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg byed rta mchog rol pa dang /
NK071(du)002:515: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg bya stobs po che dang /
NK071(du)002:516: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg shes gshin rje
NK071(du)002:517: gshed dang bzhi ste sangs rgyas kyi ye shes sgrib
NK071(du)002:518: pa med pa don gyi spyi 'dzin pa la mi
NK071(du)002:519: ltos par mngon sumadu gyur cing chags sdang thams cad
NK071(du)002:520: dang bral ba'i mtshon byed du khro bo bzhi sgo
NK071(du)002:521: bar ye shes kyi rtsal las rang snang zhing de
NK071(du)002:525: rnam pa med par rtogs pa'i ye shes bzhi'o //
NK071(du)002:526: gnyis pa de dag gi yum bzhi ni /
NK071(du)002:527: btsun mo rtag par ma yin pa ste lcags kyu ma dang /
NK071(du)002:528: chad par ma yin pa ste zhags pa dang /
NK071(du)002:529: bdag tu ma yin pa ste lcags sgrogs ma dang /
NK071(du)002:530: mtshan mar ma yin pa ste dril bu ma'o //
NK071(du)002:531: de dag kyang ngo bo phyin ci log bzhi spangs
NK071(du)002:532: shing rnam pa tshad med pa bzhi dang bsdu ba'i
NK071(du)002:533: dngos po bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i brda rtags
NK071(du)002:534: su shar ba'o // de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yab yum dang /
NK071(du)002:535: sems dpa' sems ma dang sgo ba yab yum la sogs pa /
NK071(du)002:536: dbus su snang ba bzhin du phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i
NK071(du)002:537: dkyil 'khor rang rang gi tshom bu'i 'khor 'bum phrag
NK071(du)002:538: du mas bskor ba lha'i bkod tshul gyi mang nyung
NK071(du)002:539: dang rnam pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor de lta bu'i
NK071(du)002:540: tshogs nam mkha'i dbyings kun khyab pa brjod kyis mi
NK071(du)002:541: lang ba rnams dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so
NK071(du)002:542: // gsum pa ye shes kyi rang snang bkod pas don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:543: gang bkod pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK071(du)002:544: ji ltar bkod pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:546: gleng gzhi'i bkod pa rgya cher snang bar mdzad pa
NK071(du)002:547: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun
NK071(du)002:548: mo'i tshogs dang rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ngo
NK071(du)002:549: bo gzhan gyi spyod yul du ma gyur pas gsang
NK071(du)002:550: ba'i dkyil 'khor rang snang ba de dag nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:551: gsang ba chen po 'di nyid sku dang gsung dang
NK071(du)002:552: thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las rdo rje las
NK071(du)002:553: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor rang snang ba'i don ston pa'i
NK071(du)002:554: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig 'di dag dgongs pa rang
NK071(du)002:555: shar du sgra tshig la ma ltos par rang phyung
NK071(du)002:556: ngo // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:557: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor de nyid gang gi ngang las bkod pa /
NK071(du)002:559: de nyid gang gi bzhugs gnas yin pa ngos bzung ba'o //
NK071(du)002:561: chos sku skye ba med pa'i dbyings la ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:562: ba'i tshig e longs sku 'gag med kyi snang ba
NK071(du)002:563: la ngo mtshar bas e ma nam mkha'i dbyings dang
NK071(du)002:564: mnyam par sna tshogs su rang snang bas e ma
NK071(du)002:565: ho / chos sku de bzhin nyid kyi dbying nyid
NK071(du)002:566: la dbang bsgyur longs sku ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:567: lhun gyis grub pa ni ston pa nyid kyi bsam
NK071(du)002:568: gyis mi khyab pa'i thugs rje'i ngang las byung ba'o
NK071(du)002:570: de lta bu'i zhing khams lhun stug po bkod par
NK071(du)002:571: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la rang snang ba nyid
NK071(du)002:572: de sangs rgyas kyi ting nge 'dzin rnam par dag
NK071(du)002:573: pa'i gzugs brnyan ye shes kyi sgyu ma rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:574: gyis rnam par dag pa'i ngo bor gsal zhing snang
NK071(du)002:577: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon
NK071(du)002:578: tan dang phrin las rnams nyes pa'i skyon cung zad
NK071(du)002:579: tsam gyi'ang sel med pa yi bdag nyid yon tan
NK071(du)002:580: phun sum tshogs pa yid bzhin rin po che /
NK071(du)002:581: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mnga' thang chen po mi
NK071(du)002:582: zad par ldan pa ye shes rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)002:583: mnga' ba'i rang bzhin rdo rje mchog gi ngo bo
NK071(du)002:584: 'du 'bral med pa dang longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i
NK071(du)002:585: gnas nyid do // zhes sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK071(du)002:586: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)002:587: las rgyud 'byung ba'i lo rgyus dang nges pa sbyin
NK071(du)002:588: pa dang gzhir gyur pa'i gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang
NK071(du)002:590: gnyis pa ston pa nyid rigs lngar bzhengs pa'i thugs
NK071(du)002:591: rang byung gi ye shes gnyis su med pas chos
NK071(du)002:592: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par ched du brjod
NK071(du)002:593: cing thugs rje g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa la gnyis
NK071(du)002:594: te / don gyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba dang /
NK071(du)002:595: de ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rjes g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:597: yab kyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba /
NK071(du)002:598: yum gyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba /
NK071(du)002:599: gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa gleng bslang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:601: dgongs pa gleng bslang ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)002:604: gleng gzhi rnam par bkod pa de nas bcom ldan
NK071(du)002:605: 'das rigs kyi gtso bo'i thugs rang byung gi ye
NK071(du)002:606: shes yul 'byed par byed pa po gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:607: pa'i tshul rdo rje yid yul du ma la 'jug
NK071(du)002:608: pas kun tu ngo bo dbyings las ma g.yos pas
NK071(du)002:609: bzang po / phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams
NK071(du)002:610: cad kyi dgongs pa ma lus pa 'dus pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:611: bzhin gyi sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i tshul dus
NK071(du)002:613: yul rnams chos nyid kyi rang bzhin yin pas btsun
NK071(du)002:614: mo gtan la dbab par bya ba mo snang srid
NK071(du)002:615: kyi chos kun tu ste thams cad kyang ye nas
NK071(du)002:616: dag pas bzang mo la rnam par 'byed pa'i blo
NK071(du)002:618: blo zhugs pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:619: pa ma lus pa thams cad du thugs rang byung
NK071(du)002:620: gi ye shes kun tu bzang po gcig gi rang
NK071(du)002:621: bzhin du ngo bo dbyer med pas nyid la gzhan
NK071(du)002:622: pa'i chos ma gzigs nas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK071(du)002:623: / de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du brjod pa 'di skad du brjod do //
NK071(du)002:625: chos thams cad gdod nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin la ngo mtshar ba'i tshul gyis e ma ho /
NK071(du)002:626: ji ltar na sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad
NK071(du)002:627: kyi rang bzhin ye nas skye ba med par sangs
NK071(du)002:628: rgyas pas sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK071(du)002:629: rje de nyid chos can sna tshogs 'gag med du
NK071(du)002:630: snang bas phung po ste de'i yan lag rnam par
NK071(du)002:631: shes pa'i phung po la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK071(du)002:632: rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags /
NK071(du)002:633: de bzhin du skye mched bcu gnyis dang khams bco
NK071(du)002:634: brgyad po rnams kyi bye brag mang po kun kyang
NK071(du)002:635: / byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du ye nas gnas so //
NK071(du)002:636: 'byung ba lnga yang yum lnga'i ngo bor ye nas
NK071(du)002:637: sangs rgyas pa ste sa chu gnyis ni sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:640: gos dkar mo dang dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK071(du)002:641: nam mkha' ni dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK071(du)002:642: de ltar phyi nang gi 'byung ba rtog tshogs kyis
NK071(du)002:643: bsdus pa'i 'dod pa dang gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i
NK071(du)002:644: srid pa gsum gyi ngo bo ma dag pa ltar
NK071(du)002:645: snang ba de rnams kyang ye nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)002:647: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang mya ngan las 'das
NK071(du)002:648: pa'i chos ma lus pa snang zhing srid pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:650: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin te /
NK071(du)002:651: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i ma dag pa'i chos shig /
NK071(du)002:652: sangs rgyas nyid kyis kyang rdul tsam yang mi brnyes so ste mi rnyed do //
NK071(du)002:653: zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:654: gnyis pa yum gyi dgongs pa chos nyid stong pa'i
NK071(du)002:655: gnas lugs gtso bor gleng bslang ba la'ang gnyis te
NK071(du)002:656: / dgongs pas gleng ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)002:659: blos yul gyi gnas lus brjod pa de nas blo
NK071(du)002:660: la snang ba'i yul rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i btsun
NK071(du)002:661: mo gtan la dbab par bya ba mo rang snang
NK071(du)002:662: ba'i chos kun tu bzang mo /
NK071(du)002:663: yul can rig pa'i ye shes bcom ldan 'das yid
NK071(du)002:664: kun tu bzang po dang yul dang yul can gnyis
NK071(du)002:666: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)002:668: chos nyid la ngo mtshar bar bstan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:669: kye ma'o zhes gsungs nas ji ltar na thams cad
NK071(du)002:670: dang snang du shar bas phyogs bcu stong khams snod
NK071(du)002:671: kyi 'jig rten du snang ba thams cad ye nas
NK071(du)002:672: dben pa ste skye ba med pa nyid dang der
NK071(du)002:673: gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can srid pa gsum ni
NK071(du)002:674: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK071(du)002:675: lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK071(du)002:676: ye shes lnga'i rtsal gzung 'dzin du 'khrul dus dug
NK071(du)002:677: lngar snang bas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bskyed pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:678: snyigs ma lnga nyid kyang ngo bo rang byung gi
NK071(du)002:679: ye shes bde ba chen po dang ldan pa'i gnas
NK071(du)002:681: 'gro ba'i phung po lnga nyid kyang gdod nas mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:682: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs la bzang ngan dang
NK071(du)002:683: blang dor gang du'ang ma grub pas mchog gi snying
NK071(du)002:684: po mnyam pa nyid byang chub kyi rang bzhin yin
NK071(du)002:685: pas / de las gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal te /
NK071(du)002:686: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma dag pa zhes bya
NK071(du)002:687: ba'i chos log pa gcig btsal kyang rgyal bas mi
NK071(du)002:688: brnyes so ste mi rnyed do //
NK071(du)002:689: zhes yum gyis brjod pas thams cad ye nas sangs
NK071(du)002:690: rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to
NK071(du)002:691: // gsum pa gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:692: dgongs pas gleng ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK071(du)002:695: yul nyid yul can gyi ngo bor rig pa'i ye
NK071(du)002:696: shes su rnam par dag pa de nas yab yum
NK071(du)002:697: rig stong gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen pos
NK071(du)002:698: 'khor 'das ye nas mnyam pa nyid du sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:699: pa'i phyir sems kyang sangs rgyas pa'i chos nyid du
NK071(du)002:700: shes par byed pa rang byung gi ye shes su
NK071(du)002:701: ye nas yin pa la yin pa'ii bdag nyid du
NK071(du)002:705: chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar zhing gzhan las
NK071(du)002:706: rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos 'di nyid ni
NK071(du)002:707: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba zab mo'i
NK071(du)002:709: chos nyid gdod ma nas skye ba med pa'i ngang
NK071(du)002:710: las snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK071(du)002:711: cad skyes par snang ba rmi lam dang sgyu ma
NK071(du)002:712: lta bu ste skyes pa ltar snang ba'i dus nyid
NK071(du)002:713: na skye ba med pa'i ngo bo ni chos kyi
NK071(du)002:714: dbyings so // de nyid rtogs pa'i blo chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:716: chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar zhing gzhan las
NK071(du)002:717: rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos 'di nyid ni
NK071(du)002:718: / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba zab mo'i don te /
NK071(du)002:720: ye nas 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid gdangs sna
NK071(du)002:721: tshogs su 'char ba me long gi ngos lta bu
NK071(du)002:722: la chos can gzugs brnyan ltar snang ba thams cad
NK071(du)002:723: 'gag pa ltar snang yang 'gag pa snang dus nyid
NK071(du)002:724: na gnas lugs 'gag pa med pa ni me long
NK071(du)002:725: lta bu'o // de rtogs pa'i blo ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:726: e ma ho chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:727: zhing gzhan las rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos
NK071(du)002:728: 'di nyid ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang
NK071(du)002:731: ye nas gnas pa med pa nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK071(du)002:732: ngang las chos sna tshogs pa thams cad gnas pa
NK071(du)002:733: ltar snang yang gnas pa snang dus nyid na don
NK071(du)002:734: la gnas pa med pa ni mnyam pa nyid do
NK071(du)002:735: // de nyid rtogs pa'i blo ni mnyam nyid ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:736: e ma ho chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:737: zhing gzhan las rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos
NK071(du)002:738: 'di nyid ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang
NK071(du)002:740: gang zhe na sems rang bzhin gyis dag pa dmigs
NK071(du)002:741: pa dang mtshan ma med pa nam mkha' dang rgya
NK071(du)002:742: mtsho dwangs pa'i dkyil lta bu'i ngang las rnam par
NK071(du)002:743: rtog pa sprin nam gzugs brnyan ltar sna tshogs su
NK071(du)002:744: shar ba thams cad dmigs pa ltar snang yang /
NK071(du)002:745: rnam rtog sna tshogs su dmigs pa snang dus nyid
NK071(du)002:746: na gzhi med rtsa ba dang bral bas dmigs pa
NK071(du)002:747: dang mtshan ma rang bzhin gyis med pa ni so
NK071(du)002:748: sor rtogs pa'o // de nyid rtogs pa'i blo la so sor rtog pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)002:749: e ma ho chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:750: zhing gzhan las rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos
NK071(du)002:751: 'di nyid ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang
NK071(du)002:754: chos thams cad gdod ma nas 'gro 'ong med pa
NK071(du)002:755: sprul pa lta bu'i ngang las snang ba dang rig
NK071(du)002:756: pa 'gro ba dang 'ong ba sna tshogs su snang
NK071(du)002:757: yang 'gro 'ong du snang ba nyid na 'gro 'ong
NK071(du)002:758: med par gnas pa ni bya ba grub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:759: de nyid rtog pa'i blo ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:760: de ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas dag pa'i tshul de skad ces brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:761: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang yum btsun mo'i
NK071(du)002:762: tshogs thams cad kyang mnyam pa nyid du ye nas
NK071(du)002:763: gnas pa la mnyes pas khyab par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:764: gnyis pa de nyid ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba la
NK071(du)002:765: thugs rje'i g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa la bzhi ste
NK071(du)002:766: / thugs rje 'jug pa'i yul sems can gyis ma rtogs bar bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:767: mi rtogs pa'i rang bzhin bdag tu bzung nas 'khor bar 'khrul tshul /
NK071(du)002:768: 'khrul bar snang dus nyid nas bcing grol med pa'i don las ma 'das pa /
NK071(du)002:769: de nyid bstan pa'i phyir thugs rje rol pa 'byed pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:772: ji ltar 'jug pa'i yul bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:774: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
NK071(du)002:775: btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad dang bcas pas don 'di
NK071(du)002:776: nyid bstan pa'i phyir ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK071(du)002:778: ma rtogs pa'i sems can gyi tshogs la skyo ba'i
NK071(du)002:779: tshul gyis e ma ho chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:780: gdod ma nas sangs rgyas pa'i don thog ma nyid
NK071(du)002:781: nas ma rtogs pas ye nas 'gro ba thams cad
NK071(du)002:783: snang srid sna tshogs su snang ba la sku gsum
NK071(du)002:784: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid ye nas gnas kyang
NK071(du)002:785: ma dag 'khrul pa'i chos su snang bas rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:786: gyis gsang ba'o // de lta bu'i don de nyid
NK071(du)002:787: gzhan gyis sbas pa lta bu la ma yin par
NK071(du)002:788: snang stong 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid ma rtogs
NK071(du)002:789: pas ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:790: don de yang rang gi sems nyid las gzhan du min pa las shin tu gsang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:793: thugs rje'i rgyu bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:796: dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi chos /
NK071(du)002:797: sku dang zhing khams su snang ba thams cad dang /
NK071(du)002:798: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i chos snod bcud srid gsum
NK071(du)002:799: du snang ba thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK071(du)002:800: ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas
NK071(du)002:801: dbyer med pas rnam par dag pa yin na'ang /
NK071(du)002:802: 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa'i ma rig pa gnyis su 'dzin pa las /
NK071(du)002:803: ngan song gsum lha mi gnyis te 'gro ba lnga'i ris bsam gyis mi khyab par smin pa la /
NK071(du)002:804: rang byung gi thugs rje chen po lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:805: pa sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas
NK071(du)002:806: / slar yang ched du brjod pa 'di skad ces brjod do //
NK071(du)002:808: e ma ho gdod ma'i gnas lugs sems nyid 'od
NK071(du)002:809: gsal ba sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i bde bar
NK071(du)002:811: rkyen rang gi rnam rtog dang des byas pa'i las kyis rmi lam ltar sprul pa'o //
NK071(du)002:812: de'ang lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba sna tshogs pa'i lus dang de dag so so'i longs spyod dang /
NK071(du)002:813: mtho ris la sogs pa'i gnas dang rang rang gi
NK071(du)002:814: bde ba dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa du mar
NK071(du)002:815: snang ba la 'gro ba rnams kyis nga zhes bdag
NK071(du)002:816: tu 'dzin pa dang nga'i yo byad ces pa la
NK071(du)002:817: sogs pa bdag gir byed pas so sor 'dzin pas
NK071(du)002:818: nam yang 'khor ba las grol bar mi 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:819: // gsum pa 'khrul bar snang dus nyid nas bcing grol med par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:820: de ltar 'khor ba bde sdug du mas gdungs kyang
NK071(du)002:821: gnas lugs nam mkha' bzhin du 'ching byed sus kyang
NK071(du)002:822: 'gro ba rnams ma bcings shing bcings pa ltar snang
NK071(du)002:824: bcing bar bya ba 'gro ba dang 'gro ba'i sems nyid kyang yod pa ma yin no //
NK071(du)002:825: glo bur ba'i rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis /
NK071(du)002:826: don med par 'khrul pa bzos pa yin te /
NK071(du)002:827: dper na 'ga' zhig nan tan gyis mdun gyi nam
NK071(du)002:828: mkha' la thag pa zhig byung pa blos byas nas
NK071(du)002:829: de nyid la mdud pa bcing grol du ma 'dor
NK071(du)002:830: zhing byed pa ltar rang gi sems nyid gdod nas
NK071(du)002:831: dag pa nam mkha' lta bu la dgag sgrub gzung
NK071(du)002:832: 'dzin du mar byas pas 'khor ba'i 'khrul pa ltar
NK071(du)002:833: snang ba'o // bzhi pa de nyid bstan pa'i phyir thugs rje 'phros tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:834: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sus kyang
NK071(du)002:835: bcings pa med cing rnam par grol ba med pa'i
NK071(du)002:836: // sems nyid ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:837: zhing khams chen por lhun gyis grub cing yongs su
NK071(du)002:838: rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas kyi gsang ba zab
NK071(du)002:839: // mo'i chos / 'di nyid 'gro ba rnams la
NK071(du)002:840: bstan pa'i phyir thabs kyi rol pa bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:841: khyab pa dang thugs rje chen pos sprul pa dpag
NK071(du)002:842: tu med pa spro ba rnam pa sna tshogs par
NK071(du)002:843: // mo'i chos / mdzad / ces rang snang dag
NK071(du)002:844: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)002:845: nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK071(du)002:846: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsang ba'i snying po de
NK071(du)002:847: kho na nyid nges pa las mya ngan las 'das
NK071(du)002:848: pa don dam pa spros pa thams cad dang bral
NK071(du)002:849: ba rnam par dag pa dang 'khor ba kun rdzob
NK071(du)002:850: kyi byang chub sems gnyis ka yang gdod ma nas
NK071(du)002:851: sangs rgyas pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su
NK071(du)002:852: bskyed pa'i ste dbyer med pa'i gnas lugs bstan pa
NK071(du)002:853: dang ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba rang byung gi thugs
NK071(du)002:854: rje dbyings nas 'phro ba'i rgyu mtshan bstan pa'i le'u
NK071(du)002:856: don gsum pa thugs rje'i rang bzhin chos nyid las
NK071(du)002:857: ma g.yos bzhin 'jig rten du sgron ma bkod pas
NK071(du)002:858: chos thams cad gtan la dbab pa'i tshul la gsum
NK071(du)002:863: gleng bslang ba'i tshul bstan pa de nas rang snang bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK071(du)002:864: rang byung gi thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs
NK071(du)002:865: las rang shar ba zhes bya ba'i rnam par 'phrul
NK071(du)002:866: pa sangs rgyas kyi ye shes nyid yin pas rig
NK071(du)002:867: pa'i skyes bu las dang nyon mongs thams cad bcom
NK071(du)002:868: pas thub pa 'jig rten drug gi 'gro ba so
NK071(du)002:869: sor 'dul bas mi'i thub pa la sogs pa drug
NK071(du)002:870: / rang snang bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon to //
NK071(du)002:872: 'dul ba bzhi'i rnam par 'phrul pa'i tshul spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:873: 'dul yul 'gro ba dang chos kyi rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:874: 'khor 'das sems dang ye shes kyi rang snang don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:879: de ltar thub pa drug 'thon nas kyang 'gro ba'i
NK071(du)002:880: las so sor bsags pa nyid kyi dbang gis 'jig
NK071(du)002:881: rten gyi khams kyang tha dad du snang ste de'ang
NK071(du)002:882: bsdu na mgo 'phred la bstan nas 'gro ba s+n+rel
NK071(du)002:883: gzhi dang gyen dang thur la bstan nas 'gro ba
NK071(du)002:884: yan man gyi 'jig rten zlum po dang gru bzhi
NK071(du)002:885: dang zla gam dang gru gsum dang gzhi phyal ba
NK071(du)002:886: dang steng g.yog med pa ste snod kyi bye brag
NK071(du)002:887: rnam pa mi 'dra ba drug gi rang bzhin gyi
NK071(du)002:888: phyogs bcu kun tu khyab cing de dag gi rnam
NK071(du)002:889: grangs dang dbye ba'i tshad ni mtha' yas shing bde
NK071(du)002:890: sdug dang longs spyod la sogs pa'i rnam pa mu
NK071(du)002:891: med pas khyab pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po
NK071(du)002:893: rang rang gi 'dul byed thub pa chen po bcom
NK071(du)002:894: ldan 'das re res 'dul ba rnams pa bzhi bzhis
NK071(du)002:896: de yang bsod nams kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK071(du)002:897: don thams cad mngon sum du gyur pas 'dul ba dang /
NK071(du)002:901: sku bsod nams chen pos mdzad pa phun sum tshogs pas 'dul ba /
NK071(du)002:902: thugs mngon shes chen pos mngon sum pas 'dul ba /
NK071(du)002:903: bsam gyis mi khyab pa rdzu 'phrul chen pos 'dul ba /
NK071(du)002:904: gsung theg pa ltar ston pa rig pas 'dul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:907: khyim spangs te rab tu byung ba dang /
NK071(du)002:908: 'dod yon spangs nas dka' thub mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:909: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK071(du)002:910: bdud kyi sde dpung btul ba dang /
NK071(du)002:911: dam pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK071(du)002:912: gzhan gyi khengs pa bcom pa'i phyir cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:913: gdul bya skyo ba bskyed pa'i phyir mya ngan las
NK071(du)002:914: 'das pa dang gzhan yang dga' ldan nas 'pho ba
NK071(du)002:915: dang bzo'i gnas la mkhas pa dang /
NK071(du)002:916: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol pa dang byang chub snying
NK071(du)002:917: por gshegs pa la sogs pa sku'i rnam par 'phrul
NK071(du)002:918: pa chen pos 'gro ba tshad med pa smin par
NK071(du)002:919: mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul chen po ston pa'i thub pas
NK071(du)002:920: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'gro ba 'dul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:922: 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen
NK071(du)002:923: pa ste shes bya thams cad mngon sum du gzigs
NK071(du)002:924: pa ni sngon gyi gnas mkhyen pa'i mngon par shes
NK071(du)002:925: pa ste tshe rabs du ma rjes su dran pa
NK071(du)002:926: la dbang bsgyur bas 'gro ba 'dul ba dang /
NK071(du)002:927: gzhan yang 'gro ba rigs lnga'am drug la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:928: gdul bya ma lus pa thams cad kyi rang rang
NK071(du)002:929: gi sems kyi nyon mongs pa dang rnam par rtog
NK071(du)002:930: pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)002:931: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi dgongs rgyud gnyis dus dang
NK071(du)002:932: gnas skabs kun tu tha mi dad par mkhyen pa
NK071(du)002:933: yin pas pha rol gyi sems shes pa'i mngon par
NK071(du)002:934: shes pa dang / ye shes sgrib pa med pa'i
NK071(du)002:935: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis dag pa'i zhing dang ma
NK071(du)002:936: dag pa'i 'jig rten gyi 'gro ba 'chi 'pho ba
NK071(du)002:937: dang skye ba dang rnam par 'phrul ba la sogs
NK071(du)002:938: pa thams cad kun tu gzigs pa mngon par 'du
NK071(du)002:939: byed pa las byung ba lha'i mig gi mngon par
NK071(du)002:940: shes pa dang / shes pa dang / rdzu 'phrul
NK071(du)002:941: gyis snyan gyis 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:942: sgra skad che chung thams cad kun tu gsan pa
NK071(du)002:943: lha'i rna ba'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)002:944: sems can gang la thabs gang gis 'dul ba thams
NK071(du)002:945: cad ston pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi tshogs 'groo ba'i mos
NK071(du)002:946: pa dang mthun par kun tu don spyod pa rdzu
NK071(du)002:947: 'phrul gyi mngon par shes pa dang /
NK071(du)002:948: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa ma lus pa
NK071(du)002:949: dbyings su dag pa'i ye shes zag pa med pa
NK071(du)002:950: mnga' bas mthar phyin kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung
NK071(du)002:951: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i spyod pa
NK071(du)002:952: rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin zag pa zad pa'i mngon par
NK071(du)002:953: shes pa ste mngon shes chen po drug gis 'dul
NK071(du)002:955: gdul bya mtha' yas pa kun tu de'i snang ba
NK071(du)002:956: dang mthun pa'i sku sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK071(du)002:957: dpa' dang nyan rang dang tshangs pa dang brgya byin
NK071(du)002:958: dang 'khor los bsgyur ba la sogs pa bsam gyis
NK071(du)002:959: mi khyab pa ston pa dang /
NK071(du)002:960: 'gro ba'i rgyud tshad med pa kun tu de dag
NK071(du)002:961: gi mos pa dang mthun par 'jug pa'i thugs ji
NK071(du)002:962: ltar bu dang ji snyed pa mkhyen nas don mdzad
NK071(du)002:963: pa'i tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba dang
NK071(du)002:964: / gdul bya'i khams dang mos pa mi 'dra ba'i
NK071(du)002:965: spyod yul kun tu sku dang sku'i cha lugs dang
NK071(du)002:966: zhal gyi dkyil 'khor mi 'dra ba zhi ba dang
NK071(du)002:967: khro bo la sogs pa tha dad pa du mar
NK071(du)002:968: snang zhing skad cig skad cig la rang rang gi
NK071(du)002:969: snang ba dang mthun par zhal bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)002:970: pa bstan nas don byed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:971: 'gro ba'i skal ba ji ltar yod pa kun tu
NK071(du)002:972: sems can so so'i skad dang mthun par chos kyi
NK071(du)002:973: gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa sgrogs par snang ba
NK071(du)002:974: dang ldan pa nam mkha'i mtha' klas par rnam par
NK071(du)002:975: 'phrul ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs med pa
NK071(du)002:976: dag gis phyogs bcur gang la gang 'dul du snang
NK071(du)002:977: bar gyur to // bzhi pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:978: theg pa'i dbye ba gang gi gnyen por gsung tshul /
NK071(du)002:979: de dag gi don bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:981: sprul pa'i sku'i gsung rabs phun sum tshogs pa thams
NK071(du)002:982: cad kyang theg pa lngar bstan pa 'di lta ste
NK071(du)002:983: / sems can rnams 'dul ba'i dbang gis dge bcu
NK071(du)002:984: dang bsam gtan dang gzugs med kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:985: bstan pa lha yi theg pa dang dge ba bcu
NK071(du)002:986: bstan pa mi'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)002:987: bden pa bzhi dang byang chub phyogs kyi chos la
NK071(du)002:988: goms pas dgra bcom pa thob par byed pa nyan
NK071(du)002:990: rten 'brel gyi lam la goms pas yid bzhin bde
NK071(du)002:991: ba mchog gi sar 'gro ba rang byang chub kyi
NK071(du)002:992: theg pa dang / byang chub kyi sems dang bdag
NK071(du)002:993: med pa gnyis pha rol tu phyin pa bcu rnams
NK071(du)002:994: kyis rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon du byed pa byang
NK071(du)002:995: chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)002:996: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor gsum du shes shing lam
NK071(du)002:997: zab mo sgoms pas tshe 'dir grol ba gsang sngags
NK071(du)002:998: bla na med pa'i theg pas 'dul bar mdzad do
NK071(du)002:999: // gnyis pa ni 'gro ba'i rgyud kyi ma rig
NK071(du)002:1000: pa'i rnam par rtog pa las byung ba'i nyon mongs
NK071(du)002:1001: pa 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug cha mnyam pa
NK071(du)002:1002: nyi khri chig stong re yod pas stong phrag brgyad
NK071(du)002:1004: 'dul pa mdo sde mngon pa sde snod gsum cha
NK071(du)002:1005: mnyam pa sngags kyi sde snod rnams la nyi khri
NK071(du)002:1006: chig stong re yod pas chos kyi phung po stong
NK071(du)002:1007: phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi rang byung gi ye shes
NK071(du)002:1008: las 'phros pa'i ston pa rnams kyis gdul bya'i snang
NK071(du)002:1009: ba dang mthun par sngar gsungs so //
NK071(du)002:1010: da lta yang phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i 'jig rten na gsung ngo //
NK071(du)002:1011: ma 'ongs pa na'ang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:1013: chos kyi rnam grangs theg pa lngar gsungs pa de
NK071(du)002:1014: dag thams cad kyang phyi gzung ba rags par 'dod
NK071(du)002:1015: pa tha mal pa'i blo las khyad par du 'phags
NK071(du)002:1016: pas rdul phran cha med don dam pa'i bden par
NK071(du)002:1017: shes pa gzung ba bdag med pa dang nang gi
NK071(du)002:1018: sems kyang skad cig ma ste de yang bdag med
NK071(du)002:1019: par shes pas phung po la bdag tu 'dzin pa'i
NK071(du)002:1020: gnyen por byed pa nyan thos kyi theg pa dang
NK071(du)002:1021: phyi snang ba'i yul rdul phran cha med du'ang don
NK071(du)002:1022: dam par ma grub cing kun rdzob tu rdzing bur
NK071(du)002:1023: shar ba'i gzugs brnyan dang 'dra bar rtogs pas phyi
NK071(du)002:1024: yi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba rdzun par shes
NK071(du)002:1025: shing ma rig pa yod na 'du byed nas rga
NK071(du)002:1026: shi'i bar du 'byung zhing ma rig pa log na
NK071(du)002:1027: na rga shi'i bar du 'khor ba'i 'khor lo ldog
NK071(du)002:1028: par shes nas gang zag gi bdag dang phyi snang
NK071(du)002:1029: ba chos kyi bdag byed po med par rtogs pa
NK071(du)002:1030: ni nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bsgoms
NK071(du)002:1031: pas chos kyi phyed phyi yul la log par 'dzin
NK071(du)002:1032: pa'i gnyen por byed pa rang sangs rgyas kyi theg
NK071(du)002:1033: pa dang / de ltar bdag med pa phyed dang
NK071(du)002:1034: gnyis kyi steng du sgom byed gnyen po'i blo nang
NK071(du)002:1035: chos kyi bdag tu 'dzin pa sems 'khrul pa yul
NK071(du)002:1036: du byed pa las byang chub sems dpas de yang
NK071(du)002:1037: ma grub par rtogs pa'i cha nas khyad par du
NK071(du)002:1038: 'phags par 'dogs pa bdag med gnyis mngon du byed
NK071(du)002:1039: pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1040: rgyu las dkar nag dang las kyi 'bras bu so
NK071(du)002:1041: sor smin pa chud mi za ba ston pa ni
NK071(du)002:1042: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1043: dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i las dang las kyi 'bras bus lus la mi gos /
NK071(du)002:1045: sems la gos su med par sgo gsum ye nas
NK071(du)002:1046: dkyil 'khor gsum du shes pas tha mal gyi snang
NK071(du)002:1047: ba med de gnas lugs ston pa'i mthar thug pa
NK071(du)002:1048: rtogs pa ni bla na med pa gsang sngags kyi
NK071(du)002:1050: gnyis pa gdul yul 'gro ba dang chos kyi rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:1051: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin chos nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1052: chos kyi rang bzhin brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1055: ma rig pas 'khor bar snang tshul /
NK071(du)002:1056: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin chos nyid du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1057: 'khrul snang sems kyi cho 'phrul du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1058: 'khrul rtog gzhi med rtsa bral du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1059: rnam rtog ye shes kyi rol bar bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1061: 'dul ba bzhi'i cho 'phrul bstan pa de nas rang
NK071(du)002:1062: snang gi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis ched
NK071(du)002:1065: phyi nang gi chos ma dag pa snod bcud kyi
NK071(du)002:1066: rnam par snang ba ji snyed pas bsdus pa'i 'jig
NK071(du)002:1067: rten 'khrul pa'i chos 'di dag rmi lam dang 'dra
NK071(du)002:1068: ste / gnas lugs ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo
NK071(du)002:1069: bo ma rig pa'i gnyid thibs po ches non te
NK071(du)002:1070: gnyis su rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis bslad de /
NK071(du)002:1071: phyi rol dkar dmar sna tshogs kyi yul dang nang
NK071(du)002:1072: 'gro ba'i rnam pa tshad med par snang ste 'khrul
NK071(du)002:1073: ba'i rgyu las 'khrul snang gi 'bras bu shing rta'i
NK071(du)002:1074: 'phang lo ltar 'byung ba'i rten 'brel phyi nang gnyis
NK071(du)002:1075: su 'khor te / yul dang snang ba mi mthun
NK071(du)002:1076: pa'i bye brag bde sdug sna tshogs myong zhing 'khor
NK071(du)002:1077: ba'i grong khyer gcig nas gcig tu brgyud cing snang
NK071(du)002:1078: su 'khor te / bar 'gyur ro // gsum pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1079: de ltar snang yang 'khor ba'i rang bzhin ye nas
NK071(du)002:1080: grol ba'i chos nyid mnyam rdzogs chen po las nyams
NK071(du)002:1082: 'khor bar snang dus nyid nas don la ma grub
NK071(du)002:1083: pas yang dag pa'i gnas lugs yin la kun rdzob
NK071(du)002:1084: sgyu ma'i tshul tsam du gnyis su snang ba nyid
NK071(du)002:1085: dpyad na rmi lam gyi snang ba dang rmi ba
NK071(du)002:1086: po rang gi sems gnyis tha dad du ma grub
NK071(du)002:1087: pa bzhin du 'khor mkhan bdag dang 'khor ba bdag
NK071(du)002:1088: gi ba'i yul gzhan med de /
NK071(du)002:1089: des na 'khor bar snang dus rang snang rnam par
NK071(du)002:1090: dag pa'i dbyings nyid du ye nas tshul gcig pas
NK071(du)002:1091: chos sku lhun rdzogs kyi dgongs pa 'khor 'das thams
NK071(du)002:1092: cad la ye khyab chen por phyam gcig go /
NK071(du)002:1094: bdag dang bdag gi bar 'dzin pas rang dang gzhan tha dad pa rnams su blos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)002:1095: log par rtog pa tsam nyid las /
NK071(du)002:1096: don la grub pa med de log par rtog pa
NK071(du)002:1097: de nyid btsal na phra zhing phra ba'i chos su'ang
NK071(du)002:1098: med la de las tha dad pa'i chos nyid zab
NK071(du)002:1099: pa'ang yod pa ma yin te log rtog nyid chos
NK071(du)002:1100: nyid du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:1101: de'ang 'khor ba'i gzung 'dzin du snang ba 'di dag
NK071(du)002:1102: yul log rtog gi snang ba rmi lam lta bu
NK071(du)002:1103: nyid la yul can rang gi log rtog nyid spyod
NK071(du)002:1104: pas / don la sems nyid de bzhin nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:1105: gnas lugs las gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med
NK071(du)002:1106: de 'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur nam mkha'i ngang las ma
NK071(du)002:1107: pas / g.yos pa'am / dgag sgrub kyi rnam rtog sems kyi ngang las ma g.yos pa bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:1109: gzung 'dzin 'khrul par snang ba'i log rtog gi rgyu
NK071(du)002:1110: des bskyed pa'i 'bras bu skad cig snga phyi rim
NK071(du)002:1111: can du 'brel bar snang ba'i rgyun nyid kyang brtags
NK071(du)002:1112: na med do // rig pa'i ngo bo la gzhi
NK071(du)002:1113: dang rtsa ba med pa'i chos dbyings gdod nas dag
NK071(du)002:1114: pa'i gnas lugs su gnas shing sna tshogs su 'char
NK071(du)002:1115: dus nyid na'ang rgyun du med de skad cig ma
NK071(du)002:1116: sil bu'i rang bzhin yin no //
NK071(du)002:1118: ma 'ongs pa ma rnyed da lta'i skad cig ma
NK071(du)002:1119: yang brtags na phyi nang bar gsum na med pas
NK071(du)002:1120: skad cig ma tsam du'ang med pa'i phyir rig pa
NK071(du)002:1121: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i chos dbyings nam mkha'
NK071(du)002:1122: lta bu'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa'i tshul yin
NK071(du)002:1124: snang sems thams cad kyi ngo bo ye nas sangs
NK071(du)002:1125: rgyas pa'i yul gdod ma nas rnam par dag pa'i
NK071(du)002:1126: chos nyid la yul can blo'i rol pa sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:1127: su 'char zhing dbang bsgyur ba thams cad rang snang
NK071(du)002:1128: ba'i ye shes nyid la spyod pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:1129: bdag dang gzhan du 'dzin par byed pa dang dgag
NK071(du)002:1130: sgrub dug lngar shar ba'i rtog pa'i rgyun thams cad
NK071(du)002:1131: ye shes kyi rol pa yin pas ye nas rnam
NK071(du)002:1132: par dag pa bla na med pa'i theg pa'i mchog
NK071(du)002:1133: go / gnyis pa chos kyi rang bzhin brjod du med par bstan pa la drug ste /
NK071(du)002:1134: theg pa bzhis nges par 'byung ba'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'i theg par bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1135: chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa'i cho 'phrul du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1136: ston pa dang bstan pa 'pho 'gyur med kyang gdul
NK071(du)002:1137: bya'i don du gang la gang 'dul du bstan pa
NK071(du)002:1138: / rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po theg pa kun gyi 'phro gzhir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1139: de nyid mdo rgyud kun gyi spyi 'grel du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1140: de thams cad ming tshig btags pa tsam las gnas lugs gang du'ang ma grub par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1142: sngar bstan pa'i theg pa bzhi yis rang rang gi
NK071(du)002:1143: mi mthun phyogs 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal dang theg pa
NK071(du)002:1144: dman pa la sogs pa las nges par 'byung bar
NK071(du)002:1145: byed la / de dag gis nges par 'byung ba'i
NK071(du)002:1146: mthar bla na med pa'i theg pa rang bzhin rdzogs
NK071(du)002:1147: pa chen po dang 'phrad de blang dor rtsol sgrub
NK071(du)002:1148: las 'das pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa'i rang bzhin gcig
NK071(du)002:1149: gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi sar gnas par byed
NK071(du)002:1150: byed la / do // gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1151: gnas lugs kyi don yang dag par rtogs pa'i rnal
NK071(du)002:1152: 'byor pas snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams la
NK071(du)002:1153: rig pas rab tu brtags na /
NK071(du)002:1154: gnas lugs rang bzhin med pa'i ngang las snang lugs
NK071(du)002:1155: rkyen gyi 'char tshul cir yang 'grub pa ni nam
NK071(du)002:1156: mkha'i cho 'phrul dang sgyu ma dang gzugs brnyan la
NK071(du)002:1157: sogs pa'i dpes shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:1159: don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas mthar thug
NK071(du)002:1160: gi bgrod byar gyur pa kun tu bzang po lta
NK071(du)002:1161: bu ni / dus thams cad du sku gsum 'du
NK071(du)002:1162: 'bral med par bzhugs pas mya ngan las yongs su
NK071(du)002:1164: de'i bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa'i chos rnams kyang
NK071(du)002:1165: nub par mi 'gyur te dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med
NK071(du)002:1166: pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:1167: de'i ngang las lhun gyis grub pa'i sprul pa mdzad
NK071(du)002:1168: pa bcu gnyis lta bur 'phros te gnas lugs ma
NK071(du)002:1169: rig pa'i sems can rnams smin cing grol bar mdzad
NK071(du)002:1171: so so'i snang ba mthun pa'i sprul pa'i sku rang
NK071(du)002:1172: byung du byung nas don mdzad pa'i mthar mya ngan
NK071(du)002:1175: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston
NK071(du)002:1176: pa 'dul ba dang lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa
NK071(du)002:1177: gtso bor ston pa mdo sde dang lhag pa shes
NK071(du)002:1178: rab kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa chos mngon
NK071(du)002:1180: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pa lus ngag gi
NK071(du)002:1181: dam tshig gtso bor ston pa k+r+ai ya dang spyod
NK071(du)002:1182: pa bya ba dang lta ba rnal 'byor ltar byed
NK071(du)002:1183: pas sangs rgyas sgrub pa u pa dang lus ngag
NK071(du)002:1184: gi spyod pa grogs tsam las sems kyi sgom pa
NK071(du)002:1185: gtso bor ston pas mchog grub pa'i yo ga dang
NK071(du)002:1186: / thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa
NK071(du)002:1187: sku yi rgyud dang shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa
NK071(du)002:1188: gtso bor ston pa gsung gi rgyud dang rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:1189: gnyis su med par ston pa thugs kyi rgyud /
NK071(du)002:1190: phyogs bcu tshad med pa kun tu dam pa'i chos su rab tu grags pa thams cad /
NK071(du)002:1191: gsang ba'i snying po gnas lugs rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK071(du)002:1192: rang bzhin las 'phros te grub pa'i mtha' dang snying
NK071(du)002:1193: po'i don thams cad kyi mthar thug pa rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:1196: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs rang ba zhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di /
NK071(du)002:1197: sde snod gsum po kun dang rgyud sde drug po kun gyi /
NK071(du)002:1198: 'phro gzhir gyur pas 'byung gnas kyang yin la don
NK071(du)002:1199: gyi snying por gyur pas gtan la nges par 'bebs
NK071(du)002:1200: ba'i gzhi dang dbab bya'i yul du gnas shing 'di
NK071(du)002:1201: nyid de thams cad kyi gtan la 'bebs byed kyang
NK071(du)002:1203: gtan la 'bebs byed theg pa lngar bstan pa dang
NK071(du)002:1204: dbab bya'i yul snang srid 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i
NK071(du)002:1205: chos rnams thams cad don la grub pa med pas
NK071(du)002:1206: ming du btags pa tsam mo //
NK071(du)002:1207: sus btags na lha dang bcas pa'i ston pas snang
NK071(du)002:1208: tsam ma 'gag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa'i don
NK071(du)002:1209: dang mthun pa'i phyogs su mdzad de /
NK071(du)002:1210: 'khor 'das dang phung khams skye mched ces pa la
NK071(du)002:1211: sogs pa'i ming dang tshig tu btags nas bstan to
NK071(du)002:1212: // dgos pa ni don gyi gnas lugs blos rtogs par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:1213: de ltar ming tshig tu btags nas ston pa'i dus
NK071(du)002:1214: nyid na ming tshig la dngos po dang mtshan cung
NK071(du)002:1215: zad kyang med ces brjod par mdzad do //
NK071(du)002:1216: gsum pa 'khor 'das sems dang ye shes kyi rang snang du don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:1217: rang snang du ston pa'i rgyu brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1218: ji ltar bstan pa dngos so //
NK071(du)002:1220: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin brjod pa de nas
NK071(du)002:1221: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang shes rab gnyis
NK071(du)002:1222: su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyis gsang
NK071(du)002:1223: ba sems dang ye shes rang snang bar ston pa
NK071(du)002:1224: 'di nyid sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan
NK071(du)002:1225: dang 'phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)002:1227: sems can gyi 'khrul snang sems kyi rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1228: sangs rgyas kyi zhing snang ye shes kyi rang snang du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1230: thams cad rang snang yin pas ngo mtshar ba bstan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:1232: nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga /
NK071(du)002:1233: des rgyu byas te 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na 'khrul
NK071(du)002:1234: snang sna tshogs pa'i srid pa khams gsum gyi rtsa
NK071(du)002:1235: bar gyur ba'i nyes dmigs thams cad ni nga dang
NK071(du)002:1236: bdag tu rtog pa las 'phros te /
NK071(du)002:1237: 'khor bar 'khrul dus na lha la sogs pa'i 'gro
NK071(du)002:1238: ba rgyud drug so so'i snang ba la skye ba
NK071(du)002:1239: dang srog gi dbang po 'gag pas 'chi ba dang
NK071(du)002:1240: rang rang gi lus dang bdud rtsi dang bu ram
NK071(du)002:1241: shing la sogs pa'i longs spyod sna tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:1242: so so'i yul du snang ba'i gnas dang 'chi 'pho
NK071(du)002:1243: ba dang ltung ba la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal gyi
NK071(du)002:1244: 'khrul 'khor dang la sogs pa bde ba dang bar
NK071(du)002:1245: ma'i snang ba dang dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang
NK071(du)002:1246: ba thams cad 'gro ba so so'i ma rig pas
NK071(du)002:1247: bskyed pa'i log rtog bag chags 'khrul ba'i sems kyi
NK071(du)002:1248: rang snang rmi lam lta bu nyid las phyi rol
NK071(du)002:1249: du don gzhan du grub pa ni ci yang med
NK071(du)002:1251: chos thams cad rnam pa kun gyi mchog dang ldan
NK071(du)002:1252: pa'i stong nyid 'khor 'das ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK071(du)002:1253: rang bzhin gang zag dang chos kyi bdag med pa
NK071(du)002:1254: ye nas mkhyen pa so so rang gi rig pa
NK071(du)002:1255: la mnga' brnyes pa'i thugs rang byung gi ye shes
NK071(du)002:1256: te / de la snang ba'i chos rnams la phyi
NK071(du)002:1257: gzung ba'i yul gzhan du dmigs par bya ba dang
NK071(du)002:1258: nang 'dzin pa'i sems bdag tu dmigs par byed pa
NK071(du)002:1259: gnyis su med par ye shes kyi dran pas dbang
NK071(du)002:1261: de ltar dbang bsgyur ba'i chos kyang gzhan las 'phags
NK071(du)002:1262: pas ngo mtshar zhing rmad du byung ba'i sku gsum
NK071(du)002:1263: dang ye shes chen po'i gsung theg par snang ba
NK071(du)002:1264: dang / thugs mkhyen pa gnyis dang yon tan tshad
NK071(du)002:1265: med pa dang phrin las lhun gyis grub pa dang
NK071(du)002:1266: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:1267: yang sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang snang
NK071(du)002:1268: dang / las / gzhan na med de ye shes
NK071(du)002:1269: de nyid de ltar so sor snang ba yin no
NK071(du)002:1270: dang / las / // zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i rgyud kyi tshig tu'o //
NK071(du)002:1271: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:1272: de ltar thugs rje chen po las 'phros pa'i thub
NK071(du)002:1273: pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa theg pa
NK071(du)002:1275: rang snang bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:1276: kyis gsungs pa yang rang bzhin brjod du med cing
NK071(du)002:1277: sems dang ye shes kyi snang bar bstan pa de
NK071(du)002:1278: dag tu 'dus par gtso bo gdod ma'i de bzhin
NK071(du)002:1279: gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK071(du)002:1280: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po brjod du med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1281: don de kho na nyid nges pa las 'khor 'das
NK071(du)002:1282: kyi chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1283: ngo bo gdod ma nyid nas dag pa'i chos nyid
NK071(du)002:1284: du gtan la phab pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1286: // spyi don gnyis pa de las zhi khro gnyis kyi
NK071(du)002:1287: dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'phro ba'i tshul bstan pa la
NK071(du)002:1288: gnyis te / zhi ba lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1289: khro bo mngon par 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1291: gzhi dkyil 'khor bskyed cing dbang bskur ba /
NK071(du)002:1292: lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa /
NK071(du)002:1293: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin la bstod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1295: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1296: dbang bskur ba'i thabs bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1298: rgyu'i yi ge sprin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1299: de las byung ba ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa //
NK071(du)002:1300: de gsal bar byed pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1302: yi ge sprin gyi dkyil 'khor dgod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1303: de ltar sgrub pa'i rim pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1309: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang las thugs rje 'phros
NK071(du)002:1310: te chos thams cad gtan la dbab pa'i don gsungs
NK071(du)002:1311: pa de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:1312: pa thams cad yi ge sgyu 'phrul gyi rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:1313: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don gyi dgongs pa gcig
NK071(du)002:1314: tu gyur nas / chos thams cad dbyer med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1315: mnyam pa chen po'i tshul sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK071(du)002:1316: phrin las chen po'i rang bzhin rdo rje'i dbyings su
NK071(du)002:1317: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yi ge'i
NK071(du)002:1318: ngo bor ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:1319: las dgongs pa mi g.yo bar chos nyid mnyam rdzogs
NK071(du)002:1320: chen po'i don bstan pa'i phyir chos thams cad don
NK071(du)002:1321: la grub pa med pa'i ming tsam du gdod ma
NK071(du)002:1322: nyid nas gnas pa'i rang bzhin yi ge phreng ba'i
NK071(du)002:1324: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)002:1326: yi ge 'khor lo'i rang bzhin spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1327: lha dang sbyar te bye brag so sor bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:1328: de gnyis ka'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:1330: yi ge ji ltar sgom pa'i tshul /
NK071(du)002:1331: yi ge'i sprin ji ltar spros pa'i tshul /
NK071(du)002:1332: yi ge'i rang bzhin ji ltar bshad pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:1337: bskyed pa'i rim pa dang sbyar te ji ltar sgom tshul /
NK071(du)002:1338: rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang sbyar te ji ltar sgom
NK071(du)002:1339: tshul de'i las tshogs dang sbyar te ji ltar bsgom
NK071(du)002:1340: pa'i tshul lo // dang po ni /
NK071(du)002:1341: skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed pa dang stong pa nyid
NK071(du)002:1342: du bsam pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang zla ba'i steng
NK071(du)002:1343: du ah rab tu brtan zhing mi g.yo bar gyur
NK071(du)002:1344: pa'i rang bzhin dri ma med pa'i a dkar po
NK071(du)002:1346: nyung 'bru brgyar gshags pa'i tshad tsam gyi shin tu
NK071(du)002:1347: phra ba'i a dkar po grangs med pa rnams spro
NK071(du)002:1348: bas / phyogs bcu yi 'jig rten gyi khams thams
NK071(du)002:1349: cad yongs su gang bar byas pa'i 'od zer gyis
NK071(du)002:1350: snang srid thams cad a'i rnam par gsal bar gyur
NK071(du)002:1351: bas / nas / de thams cad slar rtsa ba'i
NK071(du)002:1352: a nyid la bsdus shing thim par gyur kyang a
NK071(du)002:1353: nyid de nyid sngon bas cher 'phel ba'am chung ngur
NK071(du)002:1354: 'grib pa med par bstan pa'i ngang la dar cig
NK071(du)002:1356: de nas rtsa ba'i a de las ming gi yi
NK071(du)002:1357: ge ka la sogs pa sum cu rtsa bzhi'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:1358: dang sgra'i yi ge dbyangs yig rnams phyogs bcur 'phros
NK071(du)002:1359: pa'i 'od kyis sems can thams cad yi ge'i rnam
NK071(du)002:1360: par gsal cing 'od zer gyi phung po gcig tu
NK071(du)002:1362: slar 'dus a la thim yang 'phros pa la sogs
NK071(du)002:1363: pa'i spro zhing bsdu ba'ang snga ma de kho na
NK071(du)002:1364: bzhin no // de nas slar yang pad+ma'i dbus su
NK071(du)002:1365: nyi ma dang zla ba'i steng na a dang k+shahyi
NK071(du)002:1366: mthar rim pa bzhin sa bon rnams bkod pa lhar
NK071(du)002:1367: bzhin no // bskyed pa'o // de ni bskyed pa'i rim pa rgyu'i yi ge'i sprin no //
NK071(du)002:1369: rang nyid lhar gsal ba'i thugs kar pad zla'i steng
NK071(du)002:1370: na a rab tu brtan pa dkar po las a
NK071(du)002:1371: grangs med pa 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams
NK071(du)002:1372: cad gang nas sems can thams cad a'i rnam par
NK071(du)002:1373: gyur pa slar 'dus snying ga'i a la thim pas
NK071(du)002:1374: 'phel 'grib med pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag go
NK071(du)002:1375: / de nas yang mtha' bskor gyi yi ge dang
NK071(du)002:1376: a las ming gi yi ge'i tshogs de kho na
NK071(du)002:1377: bzhin 'phros pa slar 'dus 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:1378: pa'i chos nyid 'phel 'grib med pa'i ngang la mnyam
NK071(du)002:1379: / par bzhag go / de ni rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i yi ge sprin no //
NK071(du)002:1381: zhi ba dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po
NK071(du)002:1382: la a dang ming gi yi ge rnams dkar po
NK071(du)002:1383: dang ser po dang dmar po dang mthing nag tu
NK071(du)002:1384: spros te / nad gdon zhi ba dang /
NK071(du)002:1385: tshe dang bsod nams rgyas pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1386: bsgrub bya bkug cing dbang du bya ba dang /
NK071(du)002:1387: gdug pa can tshar bcad pa'i las byas nas mthar
NK071(du)002:1388: 'phel 'grib med pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag go
NK071(du)002:1389: / rgyas par ni le'u lnga pa bzhin te de
NK071(du)002:1390: ni las sna tshogs sgrub pa'i yi ge sprin no
NK071(du)002:1391: / // gnyis pa de'i phan yon bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1392: sgom tshul 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku
NK071(du)002:1393: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rdo rje kun tu
NK071(du)002:1394: bzang po'i dngos grub phun sum tshogs pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:1395: kyi rang bzhin ji ltar 'dod pa thams cad brtan
NK071(du)002:1396: par 'byung ba'i ye shes kyi rgyu yin no //
NK071(du)002:1397: gnyis pa yi ge sprin ji ltar spros pa'i tshul la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:1399: ngo mtshar gyi ltas khyad par can snang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:1401: +aahyi ge rnams kyi 'byung gnas te 'phro gzhi yin
NK071(du)002:1402: pas khongs nas 'byung ba'i rang bzhin du 'phros te
NK071(du)002:1403: / dper na 'byung ba las gyur pa'i gzugs thams
NK071(du)002:1404: cad 'byung ba chen po'i rnam par skye ba bzhin
NK071(du)002:1405: yi ge thams cad kyang a'i rnam par skye ste
NK071(du)002:1406: ngag gi gzhi ma ni ah'o /
NK071(du)002:1407: de yang ngag gi 'du byed kyi dbang gis a de nyid bkugs pa ni i /
