NK071(du)002:1408: smad pa ni u ste rtsa ba gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:1409: de las a dang i sbyar bas e /
NK071(du)002:1410: a dang u sbyar bas o /
NK071(du)002:1413: de re re la'ang ring thung gi dbye bas sgra'i yi ge bcu bzhi dang /
NK071(du)002:1415: rnam par bcad pa ahste bcu drug tu 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:1416: de'ang ma'i sgra de nyid mgul pa'i gnas dang 'phrad pa las ka /
NK071(du)002:1417: de nyid cung zad zhum zhing spyi bo'i gnas dang 'phrad pa las kha /
NK071(du)002:1418: de nyid cung zad zhum pa las ga /
NK071(du)002:1419: de khog sbubs kyi gnas dang phrad pa las g+ha /
NK071(du)002:1420: de sna dang phrad pa las nga ste sangs rgyas kyi mgul gyi bum pal 'thon pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1422: rnams ni a de nyid rkan gyi dbus dang lce'i
NK071(du)002:1423: dkyil phrad pa las byung bas ljags las byung ba'o
NK071(du)002:1425: rnams ni a de nyid lce'i rtse mor nye ba
NK071(du)002:1426: rkan gyi mthar phrad pa las byung bas ljags kyi
NK071(du)002:1429: rnams ni a de nyid lce'i rtse mo dang so
NK071(du)002:1430: 'phrad pa las byung bas ljags kyi rtse mo dang
NK071(du)002:1433: rnams ni a de nyid mchu dang 'phrad pa las byung bas mchu las 'thon te /
NK071(du)002:1434: de dag gi nang tshan gyi bye brag ni ka la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:1437: k+shahste yi ge lhag ma dgu las ya dang sa rkan gyi sde /
NK071(du)002:1442: k+shahmagula ba dang spyi bo'i char gtogs pas de dag las byung yang /
NK071(du)002:1443: 'phro tshul ni smin ma las ya /
NK071(du)002:1455: dbu'i gtsug tor las o oo rnams 'thon to //
NK071(du)002:1457: yi ge 'di dag sku gsung thugs las phyung bas /
NK071(du)002:1458: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa thams
NK071(du)002:1459: cad du yi ge sprin gyi snang ba chen pos
NK071(du)002:1460: shar mtho na nub dma' nub mtho na shar dma'
NK071(du)002:1461: lho mtho na byang dma' byang mtho na lho dma'
NK071(du)002:1462: / mtha' mtho na dbus dma' dbus mtho na mtha'
NK071(du)002:1463: dma' ba'i tshul gyis rnam par 'gyur ba rnam pa
NK071(du)002:1464: drug tu chung ngur g.yos pas snang ba thams cad
NK071(du)002:1465: gzugs brnyan gyi rang bzhin du dag par byas /
NK071(du)002:1466: 'bring du rab tu g.yos pas stong pa thams cad ye shes kyi rang bzhin du gsal bar byas /
NK071(du)002:1467: chen po'i tshul gyis kun tu rab tu g.yos nas
NK071(du)002:1468: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK071(du)002:1469: ngang du 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ming gi
NK071(du)002:1470: mtshan nyid btags pa tsam du gyur to //
NK071(du)002:1471: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa mchog tu dgyes nas
NK071(du)002:1472: ho zhes mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du bzhad do
NK071(du)002:1473: / gsum pa yi ge'i rang bzhin ji ltar gsung ba'i tshul la drug ste /
NK071(du)002:1474: yi ge gsung ba'i rgyu brjod pa /
NK071(du)002:1475: skye ba med pa'i yi ge'i 'khor lor sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:1476: kyi dgongs pa thams cad 'dus pas chos kyi skur
NK071(du)002:1477: bstan pa / yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis a'i
NK071(du)002:1478: rang bzhin du 'dus pas yi ge mngon rdzogs longs
NK071(du)002:1479: spyod rdzogs pa'i skur sangs rgyas par bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1480: yi ge nyid kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas
NK071(du)002:1481: rol pa sna tshogs su 'char ba'i phyir sprul pa'i
NK071(du)002:1482: skur bstan pa / de nyid du rgyal ba'i dgongs
NK071(du)002:1483: pa 'dus pas dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i brjod
NK071(du)002:1484: skur bstan pa / tshul bstan pa / sems nyid
NK071(du)002:1485: snang stong gnyis su med par yi ge'i sgra don
NK071(du)002:1486: skur bstan pa / tshul bstan pa / bshad pa'o // dang po ni /
NK071(du)002:1487: yi ge'i sprin spros pa de nas de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:1488: pa thams cad kyis yi ge sprin gyi ched du
NK071(du)002:1491: yi ge a ni snang ba'i cha tsam ma dor
NK071(du)002:1492: bas stong pa dang dngos po dang mtshan ma med
NK071(du)002:1493: pas mi stong gi mtha' dang bral bas de gnyis
NK071(du)002:1494: kyi rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'o zhes pa'i dbu
NK071(du)002:1495: ma'ang dmigs su yod pa ma yin te ltos pa'i
NK071(du)002:1496: dbang gis bzhag pa'i snang ba dang stong pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:1498: de ltar chos thams cad ming tsam las smra bsam
NK071(du)002:1499: spros brjod kyi ngo bor ma grub pa ni sangs
NK071(du)002:1500: rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa ste /
NK071(du)002:1501: de nyid yi ge 'phreng ba nyid kyi ngang la gnas pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:1503: yi ge thams cad kyi 'byung khungs a nyid yi
NK071(du)002:1504: ge'i rnam pa sna tshogs par snang ba'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:1505: / ka la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su /
NK071(du)002:1506: k+aa l+ai dang a li'i sgra yi ming gis brjod pa thams cad bsdus pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1507: ye nas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i rgyal
NK071(du)002:1508: po a skye ba med pa chos kyi skur sangs
NK071(du)002:1509: rgyas pas na a sangs rgyas pa bzhin du de'i
NK071(du)002:1510: ngang las 'phros pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)002:1511: po de nyid kyang sangs rgyas par nges te ngo
NK071(du)002:1512: bo gcig gi rol pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:1513: don la a ni kun tu bzang mo'i dbyings so //
NK071(du)002:1514: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni de'i ngang las 'phros pa'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK071(du)002:1515: de'i rang bzhin ni yi ge longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bstan pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:1517: ngo bo chos skur gnas pas e ma ho rang
NK071(du)002:1518: bzhin longs skur snang bas ngo mtshar thugs rje sprul
NK071(du)002:1519: skur shar bas ya mtshan pa'i don gyi /
NK071(du)002:1520: yi ge sprin gyi 'khor lo rdzu 'phrul chen po
NK071(du)002:1521: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rang bzhin bzhi bcu rtsa
NK071(du)002:1522: gnyis kyi steng du mgo tsheg shad gsum bsnan pas
NK071(du)002:1523: / bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i tsheg rnams ni ming dang /
NK071(du)002:1524: tshig rnams ma lus pa 'dzin pa'i gnas yin pas /
NK071(du)002:1525: de las theg pa'i chos sna tshogs pa'i don chen po smra zhing gzhan la ston pa'i rgyu'o //
NK071(du)002:1526: rags pa'i dngos por grub pa med pa yi ge'i
NK071(du)002:1527: rang bzhin rang gi sems nyid 'od gsal ba ste
NK071(du)002:1528: / gang zag dang chos kyi bdag med cing spros
NK071(du)002:1529: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i chos nyid ye
NK071(du)002:1530: gdod ma nyid nas dngos po dang mtshan ma'i chos
NK071(du)002:1532: snang ba'i rang bzhin chu zla ltar gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:1533: pa'i tshul gyis sangs rgyas kyi sku dang sems can
NK071(du)002:1534: gyi rtsa gnas 'khor lo rnams na yi ge de
NK071(du)002:1535: dag gi dbyibs a seng ge 'gyings ba lta bu
NK071(du)002:1536: dang ka ba dan rtsegs pa lta bu la sogs
NK071(du)002:1537: par gnas pa dang kha dog kyang +aa li rnams
NK071(du)002:1538: dmar po k+aa li rnams dkar po'i rang bzhin dang
NK071(du)002:1539: sangs rgyas kyi gnas skabs na yi ge'i sprin kha
NK071(du)002:1540: dog dang dbyibs dang ming dang tshig gi tshogs kyi
NK071(du)002:1541: / rnam par 'phrul pa'i rol pa cir yang sprul
NK071(du)002:1542: cing 'gro ba'i skal pa dang mthun par chos ston
NK071(du)002:1543: / par mdzad do // lnga pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1544: phyogs bcu dus bzhir snga phyi da ltar 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)002:1545: sangs rgyas thams cad kyii gsang bar rang byung gi
NK071(du)002:1546: ye shes sems dpa'i sku'i dkyil 'khor ni sku'i sku
NK071(du)002:1548: re re la'ang yon tan phrin las gnyis bsnan nas lnga lngar phye bas bco lnga /
NK071(du)002:1549: de bzhin du gsung dang thugs la'ang bco lnga bco
NK071(du)002:1550: lnga ste rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga
NK071(du)002:1551: po de nyid / yi ge mgo nas mjug k+sha la thug gi bar du rdzogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1553: sems nyid skye ba med pa yi ge'i don du bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1554: skye ba med pa nyid kyi ngang las yi ger snang bas yon tan lhun gyis grub tshul /
NK071(du)002:1555: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i yi ge gang gis bris shing bkod pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:1557: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba de nyid rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i yi ge ste /
NK071(du)002:1558: yi ge de nyid la dngos po dang mtshan mar grub pa yod pa ma yin no //
NK071(du)002:1560: sems nyid dmigs su med pa don dam pa'i yi
NK071(du)002:1561: ge de nyid 'od gsal ba'i khams sna tshogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:1562: phyir / rten byed pa'i sku yi 'khor lo chen
NK071(du)002:1563: po brda spros pa'i gsung gi 'khor lo chen po
NK071(du)002:1564: mnyam par 'jog pa thugs kyi 'khor lo chen po
NK071(du)002:1565: thams cad mkhyen pas yon tan gyi 'khor lo chen
NK071(du)002:1566: phyir / po / thogs pa med pas phrin las kyi 'khor lo chen po ste /
NK071(du)002:1567: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad
NK071(du)002:1568: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo de ni yon tan phun
NK071(du)002:1569: sum tshogs pa ye nas lhun gyis grub pas ngo
NK071(du)002:1570: mtshar gyi mchog / sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK071(du)002:1571: med pa'i dgongs pa ya mtshan gyi cho 'phrul chen
NK071(du)002:1572: po rang la snang bar byed pas rab tu 'gugs
NK071(du)002:1573: mtshar gyi mchog / pa'o // gsum pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1574: de ltar snang ba'i yi ge de nyid sems nyid
NK071(du)002:1575: ye nas dag pa chos kyi dbyings 'gyur ba med
NK071(du)002:1576: pa'i ngang la ye shes lhun gyis grub pa bya
NK071(du)002:1577: rtsol med pa'i dbyings kyis ye nas bris pa ste
NK071(du)002:1578: / gtan du 'pho 'gyur med pa'i chos nyid rang
NK071(du)002:1579: bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba la yi ge zhes bya
NK071(du)002:1580: ba'i don du btags pa ni gsar du byas pa'am
NK071(du)002:1581: byung ba ma yin pa de phyir lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:1582: pa'i yi ge sprin du gnas par brjod do //
NK071(du)002:1583: gnyis pa lha dang sbyar te bye brag so sor bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:1584: yi ge gsum gyi don spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1585: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi don bye brag tu bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1586: de dag gi don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:1588: yi ge'i mgo ber ka ris ni thugs rdo rje
NK071(du)002:1589: mtshon byed glegs bam thams cad la 'jug pa'i sgor
NK071(du)002:1590: gyur pas ma nor ba'i lam yin te shing rta'i
NK071(du)002:1592: tig ni gsung rdo rje mtshon byed shes rab mtha'
NK071(du)002:1593: gnyis la mi gnas pa dngos po rnams ming du
NK071(du)002:1594: so sor grub cing smra ba'o //
NK071(du)002:1595: shad ni sku rdo rje thabs kyi cho 'phrul chen
NK071(du)002:1596: po yi ge rnams ma 'dres par tshigs su gcod
NK071(du)002:1598: dbyings rigs lnga yab yum dang bcas pa'i yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1599: nang sems sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1600: phyi sems sgo ma dang bcas pa'i yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1601: ye shes thub pa dang bcas pa'i yi ge //
NK071(du)002:1602: sgo skyong khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1604: dbyings kun tu bzang mo'i yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1605: rigs lnga yab kyi yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1606: rigs lnga yum gyi yi ge'o //
NK071(du)002:1608: a ni chos thams cad skye ba med pa'i de
NK071(du)002:1609: bzhin nyid kun tu bzang mo'i ngo bo nyid shes
NK071(du)002:1610: rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1612: tha ni rnam par shes pa'i de bzhin nyid khong
NK071(du)002:1613: du chud pa'i sgo ste thabs snang ba'i sgyu ma
NK071(du)002:1614: sna tshogs su 'phrul pa'i ngo bo dbyings las ma
NK071(du)002:1615: skyes pas de bzhin nyid rnam par shes pa'i rdo
NK071(du)002:1616: rje thugs rnam snang gi sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1617: ta ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid khong du chud
NK071(du)002:1618: pa'i thabs snang ba'i sgyu ma sna tshogs su 'phrul
NK071(du)002:1619: pa mi bskyod pa'i sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1620: da ni tshor ba'i de bzhin nyid khong du chud
NK071(du)002:1621: pa'i thabs kyi sgyu ma sna tshogs su 'phrul pa
NK071(du)002:1622: yid bzhin rin chen 'byung ldan gyi sa bon nyid
NK071(du)002:1623: do // d+ha ni 'du shes kyi de bzhin nyid
NK071(du)002:1624: khong du chud pa'i thabs kyi sgyu ma sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:1625: su 'phrul pa 'od dpag med kyi sa bon rnam
NK071(du)002:1627: na ni 'du byed kyi de bzhin nyid rtogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:1628: rang bzhin dus kun tu sgyu 'phrul don yod grub
NK071(du)002:1631: tha ni thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa
NK071(du)002:1632: nam mkha'i rang bzhin zung du 'brel ba'i dra ba
NK071(du)002:1633: mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa nam mkha' dbyings
NK071(du)002:1634: kyi dbang phyug ma'i sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1635: ta ni shes rab kyi dra ba rab tu brtan pa sangs rgyas spyan gyis sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1636: da ni ye shes kyi dra ba 'od zer lham me ba gos dkar mo'i sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1637: d+ha ni chos nyid kyi dra bas 'khril ba m+aa ma k+ai'i sa bon nyid do //
NK071(du)002:1638: na ni de bzhin nyid kyi dra bas kun tu
NK071(du)002:1639: mdzes pa dam tshig sgrol ma'i sa bon 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:1640: // gnyis pa nang sems sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:1641: rnam par shes pa'i sems dpa' bzhi dang thugs kyi sgo ba'i yi ge /
NK071(du)002:1642: yul gyis sems bzhi dang sku'i sgo ba'i yi ge'o //
NK071(du)002:1644: ka ni spyan gyi thugs mig gi rnam par shes
NK071(du)002:1645: pa dbyings su dag pa nyid kyi mchog sa'i snying
NK071(du)002:1646: po'i yi ge'o // kha ni snyan gyi thugs rna
NK071(du)002:1647: ba'i rnam par shes pa dbyings su dag pa nyid
NK071(du)002:1648: kyi mchog phyag na rdo rje'o //
NK071(du)002:1649: ga ni shangs kyi thugs sna'i rnam par shes pa
NK071(du)002:1650: dbyings su dag pa nyid kyi mchog nam mkha'i snying
NK071(du)002:1651: po'o // g+ha ni ljags kyi thugs lce'i rnam par
NK071(du)002:1652: shes pa dbyings su dag pa nyid kyi mchog spyan
NK071(du)002:1653: po'o // ras gzigs so // nga ni dbang shes
NK071(du)002:1654: de dag gi 'dzin pa thugs kyang 'jig par byed
NK071(du)002:1655: pa dang sgo gsum gyi zhen pa dag pa'i sgo
NK071(du)002:1656: ba gshin rje gshed yin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1658: tsa ni spyan gyi sku yi mchog gzugs rnam par dag pa rdo rje sgeg pa mo'o //
NK071(du)002:1659: tsha ni snyan gyi sku yi mchog sgra rnam par dag pa glu ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1660: dza ni shangs kyi sku yi mchog dri rnam par dag pa phreng ba ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1661: dz+ha ni ljags kyi sku yi mchog ro rnam par dag pa gar ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1662: nya ni sku yang 'jig par byed pa yul rnams
NK071(du)002:1663: dang sgo gsum la zhen byed du 'dzin pa dag
NK071(du)002:1664: pa'i sku'i sgo ba stobs po che bstan pa'o /
NK071(du)002:1665: gsum pa phyi sems sgo ba dang bcas pa'i yi ge la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:1666: dbang po'i sems dpa' bzhi sgo ba dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)002:1667: dus kyi sems ma bzhi sgo ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1669: pa ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog mig gi dbang po gnas su dag pa byams pa'i yi ge'o //
NK071(du)002:1670: pha ni snyan gyi gsung gi mchog rna ba'i dbang
NK071(du)002:1671: po gnas su dag pa sgrib pa rnam par sel
NK071(du)002:1672: ba'o // ba ni shangs kyi gsung gi mchog sna'i
NK071(du)002:1673: dbang bo gnas su dag pa kun tu bzang po'o
NK071(du)002:1674: ba'o // // b+ha ni ljags kyi gsung gi mchog
NK071(du)002:1675: lce'i dbang po gnas su dag pa 'jam dbyangs so
NK071(du)002:1676: ba'o // // // ma ni gsung yang 'jig par
NK071(du)002:1677: byed pa de dag la bdag tu 'dzin pa dang
NK071(du)002:1678: sgo gsum gyi zhen yul dag pa rta mgrin no
NK071(du)002:1680: ya ni 'das pa'i chos rnams skye ba rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid bdug spos ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1681: wa ni da ltar gnas pa rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid me tog ma yin no //
NK071(du)002:1682: ra ni ma 'ongs pa na 'jig pa rnam par dag pa ste chos nyid snang gsal ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1683: la ni dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK071(du)002:1684: su rang snang ba'i stong pa rnam par dag pa'i
NK071(du)002:1686: sha ni rtag pa rnam par dag pa ste lcags kyu ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1687: sha ni chad pa rnam par dag pas yod pa ma yin pa zhags pa ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1688: sa ni chos thams cad rtag chad kyi mtha' dang bral zhing bdag med pa lcags sgrog ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1689: ha ni dngos po dang mtshan ma med pa nyid kyi phyir dril bu ma'o //
NK071(du)002:1690: bzhi pa ye shes thub drug dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK071(du)002:1691: k+sha ni chos nyid zad pa'i sgo ste rang snang
NK071(du)002:1692: gi ye shes rnam par dag pa thugs kyi thugs
NK071(du)002:1693: te kun tu bzang po yab kyi yi ge'o //
NK071(du)002:1694: i ni 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho'i rdul phra
NK071(du)002:1695: ba snyed kyi lha yi 'jig rten rnams yongs su
NK071(du)002:1697: de bzhin du thams cad la sbyar te +ai ni
NK071(du)002:1698: rdul snyed lha ma yin rnams la lha min gyi
NK071(du)002:1699: thub pa dang / u ni rdul snyed mi rnams su mi'i thub pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1700: +au ni rdul snyed byol song rnams la byol song gi thub pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1701: e ni rdul snyed yi dwags rnams su yi dwags kyi thub pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1702: ee ni rdul snyed dmyal ba rnams su dmyal ba'i thub pas 'dul ba'i yi ge'o //
NK071(du)002:1703: lnga pa sgo skyong khro bo dang bcas pa'i yi ge ni /
NK071(du)002:1704: o ni mtshan ma thams cad dang sgo gsum gyi
NK071(du)002:1705: spros pa mtha' dag 'jig par byed cing cho 'phrul
NK071(du)002:1706: chen por ston pa bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1707: oo ni gzung 'dzin thams cad zhig pa yin te
NK071(du)002:1708: zhi ba'i gdangs ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin khro bor
NK071(du)002:1709: snang ba'o // de'ang bin+d+hu chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK071(du)002:1710: zla tshes me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK071(du)002:1711: khog pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK071(du)002:1712: n+aa da so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK071(du)002:1713: rang bzhin bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:1714: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sa
NK071(du)002:1715: bon +amo ye shes lnga ldan las 'phros pa yin
NK071(du)002:1716: no // gsum pa de dag gi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:1717: de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sprin 'dis /
NK071(du)002:1718: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs ye shes kyi 'phreng ba thams cad bsdus so //
NK071(du)002:1719: zhes pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis ched du brjod do //
NK071(du)002:1720: de ltar yi ge'i sprin de nyid sku dang ye
NK071(du)002:1721: shes 'du 'bral med pa'i ngo bor ye nas gnas
NK071(du)002:1722: pa la ngo mtshar ba'i tshul gyis /
NK071(du)002:1724: gsum pa de gnyis ka'i don bsdu ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:1725: tshul ji ltar byung ba dang /
NK071(du)002:1728: yi ge rgyas par bshad pa de nas rang snang
NK071(du)002:1729: ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang rang
NK071(du)002:1730: bzhin gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid
NK071(du)002:1731: kyi snying po yi ge sprin gyi gsang ba'i 'di
NK071(du)002:1732: nyid / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku
NK071(du)002:1733: dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las
NK071(du)002:1736: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin la sngags pa'i phyir a ho zhes bzhag nas /
NK071(du)002:1737: thabs rang byung gi thugs rje chen po dang shes
NK071(du)002:1738: rab mtha' gnyis las 'das pa'i rang bzhin gyi ngang
NK071(du)002:1739: las ston pa nyid lhag pa'i ye shes gdul bya'i
NK071(du)002:1740: don la rab tu dgyes nas thugs rje'i sprin phung
NK071(du)002:1741: byang chub kyi sems phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu mi
NK071(du)002:1743: ye nas mnga' ba'i 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu
NK071(du)002:1744: rtsa gnyis la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po smin
NK071(du)002:1745: pa las sprul pa'i sku 'phro bas 'gro ba'i don
NK071(du)002:1746: lhun gyis grub par 'byung ba'i rgyu ngo mtshar ba'i
NK071(du)002:1747: yi ge k+aa li la sogs pa ming tshogs bzhi
NK071(du)002:1748: bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba de nyid /
NK071(du)002:1749: rgyu rkyen gyis gsar du 'dus ma byas pa nyid
NK071(du)002:1750: kyi ngo bo lhun gyis grub pa'i chos ye nas
NK071(du)002:1751: gnas pa'i ngang las 'gro ba'i don du rang byung
NK071(du)002:1752: gi thugs rje snang bas 'dus byas pa ltar 'khor
NK071(du)002:1753: lo bkod pa ngo bo la 'pho 'gyur med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1754: don gyis gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje sku gsung
NK071(du)002:1755: thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor lnga bcu
NK071(du)002:1756: rtsa lnga la sogs pa 'byin pa'i rang bzhin dkyil
NK071(du)002:1757: 'khor 'phrul cing snang bar byed pa'i dam tshig chen
NK071(du)002:1758: po las / dus rtag tu 'da' bar mi mdzad
NK071(du)002:1759: cing yi ge 'khor lo las rang byung gi ye
NK071(du)002:1760: shes shar ba'i tshe rang snang gi dkyil 'khor dang
NK071(du)002:1761: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dkyil 'khor phyogs bcur 'phro ba
NK071(du)002:1762: thams cad rang dbang med par 'char ba ni rgyu
NK071(du)002:1763: yi ge sprin dang rkyen ye shes dang gdul bya'i
NK071(du)002:1764: snang ba 'tshogs pa'i mthu chen po las snang ba
NK071(du)002:1765: po las / yin no // de la ngo mtshar bas ho zhes bzhad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1766: de ni sangs rgyas las spros tshul ltar bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1767: gzhan du na yi ge 'khor lo lus la gnas
NK071(du)002:1768: tshul dang lam sgom tshul ltar bshad pa gnyis las
NK071(du)002:1770: lus can kun gyi lus la thabs dang shes rab
NK071(du)002:1771: thig le dkar dmar gnyis su med par dgyes pa'i
NK071(du)002:1772: sprin gyi khams byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni rgyu
NK071(du)002:1773: kun rdzob kyi rang bzhin snum dang sdong bu lta
NK071(du)002:1774: bur rtsa 'khor lo bzhi'i dbus dang 'dab ma la
NK071(du)002:1775: gnas pa'i dwangs ma mar me ltar 'od gsal ba
NK071(du)002:1776: nyid yi ge'i gzugs su snang ba ste /
NK071(du)002:1777: de nyid 'bras bu rgyal ba smin cing grub par
NK071(du)002:1778: byed pas ngo mtshar ba'i ming tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa
NK071(du)002:1779: gnyis te / rang bzhin ye nas gnas pas 'dus
NK071(du)002:1780: ma byas pa'i chos nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngang las
NK071(du)002:1781: gnyis te / / lam goms par byed pa'i 'dus
NK071(du)002:1782: byas thabs la mkhas pa'i rang bzhin dang shes rab
NK071(du)002:1783: zung du 'brel ba'i rdo rjes sku dang ye shes
NK071(du)002:1784: kyi sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mngon du
NK071(du)002:1785: 'byin pa'i dam tshig chen po las 'da' bar mi
NK071(du)002:1786: mdzad pa ni gzhi'i yi ge nyid lam gyi rkyen
NK071(du)002:1787: gyis lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar byed pa rten
NK071(du)002:1788: cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i dbang gis rgyu rkyen tshogs
NK071(du)002:1789: pa'i nus mthu 'byung rung du gzhi la da lta
NK071(du)002:1790: nas yod pa ni ngo mtshar che ho zhes bstan
NK071(du)002:1791: gnyis te / / pa'o // yang lam sgom tshul dang sbyar na gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:1792: grol lam dang sbyar ba ni thabs byang chub tu
NK071(du)002:1793: sems bskyed pa dang shes rab de bzhin nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:1794: ting nge 'dzin dang dgyes sprin kun snang dang byang
NK071(du)002:1795: chub sems tshogs rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin rnams bsgoms nas
NK071(du)002:1796: / yi ge sprin gyi 'khor lo sngar bstan pa
NK071(du)002:1797: bzhin bsgoms pas 'bras bu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor smin
NK071(du)002:1798: grub 'byung bas ngo mtshar gyi ming tshogs bzhi bcu
NK071(du)002:1799: rtsa gnyis kyis 'dus ma byas chos sku dang /
NK071(du)002:1800: 'dus byas gzugs sku'i rdo rje gnyis su med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1801: dkyil 'khor dam pa 'byin pa'i dam tshig las 'das
NK071(du)002:1803: rten 'brel gyis dbang med rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i mthu
NK071(du)002:1804: ste gzugs brnyan dang sgyu ma'i snang ba bzhin 'byung
NK071(du)002:1805: ba ni ngo mtshar che ho zhes pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1806: thabs lam ltar na thabs yab kyi zla ba dang
NK071(du)002:1807: shes rab yum gyi nyi ma gnyis su med par
NK071(du)002:1808: 'dres pa'i dgyes sprin dga' ba bzhi'i ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)002:1809: ni khams byang chub kyi sems kyi tshogs 'khor lo
NK071(du)002:1810: bzhir bab pa las byung ba'i bde stong gnyis su
NK071(du)002:1811: med pa bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu rgyal ba smin cing
NK071(du)002:1812: grub par byed pa ngo mtshar che ba ming tshogs
NK071(du)002:1813: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ngo bo de yang 'dus
NK071(du)002:1814: ma byas pa'i ye shes bzhi po nyid bsrubs pa
NK071(du)002:1815: dang 'gengs pa dang 'grems pa la sogs pas 'dus
NK071(du)002:1816: byas pa'i dbang gis thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK071(du)002:1817: rdo rje'i don du gnas pas dkyil 'khor dam pa
NK071(du)002:1818: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa 'byin pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)002:1819: las 'da' bar mi mdzad pa ni ye shes de
NK071(du)002:1820: bsgoms pas dbang med du 'byung ba rgyu rkyen yab
NK071(du)002:1821: yum gyi rten 'brel tshogs pa'i mthu chen pos grub
NK071(du)002:1822: pa yin te ngo mtshar che ho zhes pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1823: don de nyid ye shes kyi bdag nyid gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK071(du)002:1824: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:1825: chos thams cad yi ge'i sprin du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:1826: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor dang snang ba'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:1827: pa thams cad ngo bor rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK071(du)002:1828: dag pas tha mi dad par yi ge'i 'khor lor
NK071(du)002:1829: gyur to // ye nas gsang ba'i snying po yi
NK071(du)002:1830: ge phreng ba'i chos nyid de kho na nyid nges
NK071(du)002:1831: pa las lhun gyis grub pa yi ge 'phreng ba'i
NK071(du)002:1832: 'khor lo chen po bkod pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o
NK071(du)002:1834: don gnyis pa de ltar sgrub pa'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:1839: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yi ge'i rol par
NK071(du)002:1840: bstan pa de nas yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin bkod
NK071(du)002:1841: pa las / thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:1842: pa'i sgyu 'phrul sgrub pa'i rim pa rnam par 'phro
NK071(du)002:1845: gang sgrub pa dngos grub kyi rim pa /
NK071(du)002:1846: gang gis bsgrubs pa yi ge'i sprin gyi rang bzhin /
NK071(du)002:1847: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs dngos so //
NK071(du)002:1849: ye nas dag pa'i sems nyid dngos grub kyi rtsa bar bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1850: de las grub pa mchog gi dngos grub /
NK071(du)002:1851: de'i yan lag thun mong gi dngos grub /
NK071(du)002:1854: gzhi dang rtsa ba med pa'i nam mkha' lta bu'i sems nyid ni /
NK071(du)002:1855: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin no //
NK071(du)002:1856: de'ang shel gong gcig las rkyen tha dad kyis me
NK071(du)002:1857: dang chu 'byung ba ltar gzung 'dzin byas ma byas
NK071(du)002:1858: dang rig ma rig gis sems nyid gcig la 'khor
NK071(du)002:1859: 'das su snang yang don la gnyis su yod pa
NK071(du)002:1860: ma yin no // de'i phyir ye nas dag pa'i
NK071(du)002:1861: sems nyid 'od gsal ba yi ge'i rang bzhin du
NK071(du)002:1862: ye nas shar te snang la rang bzhin med par
NK071(du)002:1863: ma yin no // yod do // yi ge'i rang
NK071(du)002:1864: bzhin gyi sems nyid ni rtogs na don gnyis 'byor
NK071(du)002:1865: bas brgyan pa'i char rgyun dngos su 'bab cing ma
NK071(du)002:1866: rtogs na yang 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i gzhir ye nas
NK071(du)002:1867: grub pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen gyi
NK071(du)002:1868: ma yin no // yod do // sprin yin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1869: sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngang na rang byung lhun
NK071(du)002:1870: gyis grub pas sgyu 'phrul gyi dkyil 'khor yi ge'i
NK071(du)002:1871: gzugs su snang ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ngo
NK071(du)002:1872: bor / spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK071(du)002:1873: shes rab dra ba'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas mngon
NK071(du)002:1874: par rdzogs pa'i chos nyid du grub zin pas na
NK071(du)002:1875: bor / / de nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi rim
NK071(du)002:1876: pas nyams su blang ba'i tshe phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK071(du)002:1877: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rigs dang dgongs pa gcig
NK071(du)002:1879: dkyil 'khor thams cad yongs su 'grub par 'gyur te
NK071(du)002:1880: dkyil 'khor gyi rtsa ba yi ge sprin nyid phyin
NK071(du)002:1881: ci ma log par nyams su blangs pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:1883: ye shes grub pa'i rtags su las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:1884: phung po lnga gnas su dag pa'i rtags su 'byung ba lnga'i zad par grub pa'i tshul bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:1885: rnam shes brgyad dbyings su dag pa'i rtags su grub pa brgyad ji ltar thob pa'i tshul brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1887: me long lta bu'i ye shes grub pa na dug
NK071(du)002:1888: thams cad kyang 'gro ba'i gsos sman gyi bdud rtsir
NK071(du)002:1890: des bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad thams cad sel zhing bde legs su byed do //
NK071(du)002:1891: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes grub pa'i tshe lha
NK071(du)002:1892: dang mi'i longs spyod las 'das pa nam mkha' mdzod
NK071(du)002:1893: kyi longs spyod lhun grub tu 'byung zhing re ba
NK071(du)002:1894: rdzogs pa dang / chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes
NK071(du)002:1895: grub pa'i tshe ngan song gi 'gro ba rnams kyi
NK071(du)002:1896: rgyud sbyong zhing mtho ris kyi bde ba la 'god
NK071(du)002:1897: rdzogs pa dang / par byed do // so sor
NK071(du)002:1898: rtog pa dang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes grub
NK071(du)002:1899: pa'i tshe snang ba nyid mi snang bar byed cing
NK071(du)002:1900: rdzogs pa dang / par byed do // / mi
NK071(du)002:1901: snang ba'ang snang bar ston pa sogs ci yang gzhan
NK071(du)002:1902: du 'gyur ba'i cho 'phrul 'grub pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:1904: gzugs kyi phung po gnas su dag pas zad par
NK071(du)002:1905: sa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa de'i tshe nam mkha'
NK071(du)002:1906: 'ang rdo rje'i sa gzhi ltar sra bar byin gyis
NK071(du)002:1908: tshor ba'i phung po gnas su dag pa na me'i
NK071(du)002:1909: ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob pas lus la me
NK071(du)002:1910: 'bar nas sems can dmyal ba'i me yang 'tshig cing
NK071(du)002:1911: sdug bsngal las thar bar byed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:1912: 'du shes kyi phung po gnas su dag pas chu'i
NK071(du)002:1913: ting nge 'dzin la dbang thob ste snang ba thams
NK071(du)002:1915: sa la 'dzul ba dang thams cad chu klong gcig
NK071(du)002:1916: tu 'bab pa ston pa'ang me la bya ba de
NK071(du)002:1917: bzhin te gzhan gyi sdug bsngal sel bar byed pa
NK071(du)002:1918: yin no // 'du byed kyi phung po gnas su
NK071(du)002:1919: dag pas rlung gi ting nge 'dzin la mnga' brnyes
NK071(du)002:1920: pa'i tshe 'jig rten gyi khams 'di ni rdul phran
NK071(du)002:1921: du 'thor ba'i cho 'phrul 'gyed cing sems can la
NK071(du)002:1923: rnam shes rnam par shes pa'i phung po gnas su
NK071(du)002:1924: dag pas nam mkha'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i tshe
NK071(du)002:1925: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad stongs shing nyi ma
NK071(du)002:1926: dang zla ba yang sa la ltung bar 'gyur ba'i
NK071(du)002:1929: kun gzhi'i rnam shes la sogs brgyad dag cing rig
NK071(du)002:1930: pa'i ye shes la dbang thob pa'i tshe sgrub bya
NK071(du)002:1931: rang gi mdun du dgug pa dang yul gzhan du
NK071(du)002:1932: btang ba bskrad pa dang chom rkun sogs bcing ba
NK071(du)002:1933: dang byad dang gdon las dgrol ba dang /
NK071(du)002:1934: dug la sogs pa gso ba dang dgra bgegs bsad
NK071(du)002:1935: pa dang pha rol gyi sde 'pham par byed pa
NK071(du)002:1936: dang rang gi sde rgyal ba'i las thams cad /
NK071(du)002:1937: yi ge sprin gyi ting nge 'dzin 'di yis byed par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:1938: bzhi pa de dag grub pa'i dpe ni ting nge
NK071(du)002:1939: 'dzin grub pa'i dngos grub de nyid gdod nas dag
NK071(du)002:1940: pa'i ye shes rang snang du shar ba'i cho 'phrul
NK071(du)002:1941: phyi rol du snang ba'i gzugs brnyan yin no //
NK071(du)002:1942: de'ang ming dang tshig gis mtshon pas yi ge +aa
NK071(du)002:1943: li dang ka li'i phreng ba so so'i gzugs tha
NK071(du)002:1944: dad dang kha dog dang 'od zer sogs las so
NK071(du)002:1945: so'i rjes su 'gro ba can goms pas ting nge
NK071(du)002:1946: 'dzin de'i 'bras bu yid la bsam pa bzhin gyis
NK071(du)002:1947: grub pa ni / dper na mun pa la snang
NK071(du)002:1948: ba byung ba ji ltar de bzhin du gang 'dod
NK071(du)002:1949: pa thams cad mthong ba dang /
NK071(du)002:1950: phyi nang gi dug rnams ma spangs par bdud rtsir 'gyur ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu dang /
NK071(du)002:1951: mi 'dod pa rnams rang sar zhi ba gsos sman gyi tshul dang 'dra bar shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:1952: gnyis pa gang gis bsgrub pa yi ge sprin gyi rang bzhin la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:1953: gang zag gang gis bsgrubs pa dang ngo bor gang sgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1955: yul khyad par can gang la brten na thar pa'i
NK071(du)002:1956: lam ston pa rdo rje slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:1957: gyi lha rnams mchod pa la brtson pa ni yi
NK071(du)002:1958: ge 'grub pa'i yan lag dang po'o //
NK071(du)002:1959: lha dang yi ge'i sgom pa'i mngon par rtogs pa gsal zhing ma yengs pa ni gnyis pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1960: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig la gnas pa ni gsum pa'o //
NK071(du)002:1961: sngags bzlas pa'ang ha cang myur ba dang bul ba
NK071(du)002:1962: dang chad pa dang lhag pa dang sgra che ba
NK071(du)002:1963: dang chung ba rnams spangs te dag pa ni bzhi
NK071(du)002:1964: pa dang phyag rgya la chos dang las dang dam
NK071(du)002:1965: tshig dang phyag rgya chen po rnams /
NK071(du)002:1966: de dag gi yan lag ma nyams par don ji
NK071(du)002:1967: lta ba bzhin shes shing 'ching bar byed pa ni
NK071(du)002:1968: lnga pa'o // de dag gi yan lag tu bsgrub
NK071(du)002:1969: pa'i gnas dang dus dang yo byad dang ldan pas
NK071(du)002:1971: de dag dang mi ldan pa'i gang zag gis 'di
NK071(du)002:1972: bsgrub kyang don med cing brlag par yang 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:1973: lnga pa'o // 'di nyid // // gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)002:1974: 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da lta ba'i dus gsum gyi rgyal bas thugs su chud pa'i /
NK071(du)002:1975: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni yi ge 'khor lo yin pas na /
NK071(du)002:1976: de'i ngo bo rin po che ltar 'dod dgu lhun
NK071(du)002:1977: grub tu 'byung ba'i phyir zad pa'i dus med de
NK071(du)002:1978: yid bzhin gyi mdzod dam par gyur ba'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:1979: // de'ang chos sku nam mkha' lta bu 'phel ba
NK071(du)002:1980: med cing longs sku 'ja' tshon lta bu 'grib pa
NK071(du)002:1981: med pa'i ngang nas sprul sku sna tshogs su 'phro
NK071(du)002:1983: chos sku dngos po med pa'i rang las gzugs sku
NK071(du)002:1984: gnyis kyi dngos po'i sprin las 'gro ba'i don du
NK071(du)002:1985: mdzad pa'i phrin las sna tshogs su rnam par 'byung
NK071(du)002:1986: zhing lhun gyis grub pa'i rol par 'gyur ba ni
NK071(du)002:1987: yi ge sprin gyi ngo bo yin no //
NK071(du)002:1988: gsum pa ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs dngos bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:1990: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:1991: mnyam par bzhag pa gcig tu don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:1993: bskyed pa'i rim pa yi ge sprin du snang bas
NK071(du)002:1994: mtshon nas snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK071(du)002:1995: dngos por snang dus nyid na chos rnams kyi de
NK071(du)002:1996: kho na nyid ni dngos po med par ye nas
NK071(du)002:1997: rnam par dag pa'i rdzogs rim du shes par bya
NK071(du)002:1998: zhing bskyed rim snang la ngos bzung med pa'i ngang
NK071(du)002:1999: nas las dang mthun pa'i yi ge spro bsdu rtogs
NK071(du)002:2000: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la yang dang yang du rtsal
NK071(du)002:2001: sbyangs zhing rig pa la dbang bsgyur ba'i rol pa
NK071(du)002:2002: ni yi ge 'khor lo'i ting nge 'dzin yin no
NK071(du)002:2004: shes rab chos kyi sku stong pa nyid bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK071(du)002:2005: thabs gzugs kyi sku snang ba nyid bsdom pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK071(du)002:2007: dmigs su med pa'i don la gdams tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2008: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2010: gang zag gang gis chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:2011: dmigs pa dang mtshan ma med par mi shes pa
NK071(du)002:2012: / de yis chos kyi dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i gnas lugs mi shes pas /
NK071(du)002:2013: rgyu mtshan de yi phyir sems la snang ba'i gzung
NK071(du)002:2014: yul dngos po sna tshogs rmi lam lta bu 'di
NK071(du)002:2015: dag gzhig cing dpyad na phyi nang gang du'ang grub
NK071(du)002:2016: pa med pa nam mkha' lta bur gnas pa dang
NK071(du)002:2017: / de rtogs byed kyi shes pa kha dog dang
NK071(du)002:2018: dngos po med pa la brtags na phyi nang gang
NK071(du)002:2019: du'ang mi rnyes pas 'dzin pa ngo bo nyid med
NK071(du)002:2020: pa de'i tshe sems dang sems la snang ba las
NK071(du)002:2021: gzhan pa'i chos shig dmigs su med pas /
NK071(du)002:2022: gzung 'dzin du zhen pa'i 'khrul rtog 'jig pa'i tshul
NK071(du)002:2023: brtags pas chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin dmigs su
NK071(du)002:2024: med pa'i de kho na nyid shes par gyis shig
NK071(du)002:2026: ye nas gzhi dang rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu ni /
NK071(du)002:2027: dngos po dang mtshan ma gang du'ang ma grub pas
NK071(du)002:2028: 'di la pho dang mo zhes gdags pa ma yin
NK071(du)002:2029: la ma ning zhes kyang dmigs su yod pa min
NK071(du)002:2030: zhing / mtshan med kyang ma yin la rgyal po
NK071(du)002:2031: la sogs pa'i rigs brgyud du gtogs pa min zhing
NK071(du)002:2032: zhing / / dkar po la sogs pa'i kha dog tu grub pa ma yin /
NK071(du)002:2033: gru bzhi la sogs pa'i dbyibs su grub pa'ang ma yin /
NK071(du)002:2034: sems nyid 'di sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang sems can
NK071(du)002:2035: gyi gnas su dmigs pa ma yin zhing mdor na
NK071(du)002:2036: gang yang min te 'phags pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)002:2037: rgyal po las / sems ni dmigs med bsam du yod ma yin //
NK071(du)002:2038: rang bzhin dag cing ngo bo nyid kyis stong //
NK071(du)002:2039: ye nas bdag med chos nyid zab mo ste //
NK071(du)002:2040: nam mkha' bzhin du zab zhi spros dang bral //
NK071(du)002:2042: de lta bu'i sems nyid ni chos nyid de bzhin
NK071(du)002:2043: nyid kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes te
NK071(du)002:2044: / thabs kyi phyag rgya thams cad dang shes rab
NK071(du)002:2045: zab mo kun gyi rgyu byed pas phun sum tshogs
NK071(du)002:2046: pa thams cad 'grub pa'i dbyings yin no //
NK071(du)002:2047: gnyis pa thabs gzugs snang bsgoms pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:2048: bskyed rdzogs lha'i ting nge 'dzin du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2049: snang srid kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgyar bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2051: rang gi sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i yi ge thabs
NK071(du)002:2052: kyi rang bzhin du snang ba las thabs byung 'od
NK071(du)002:2053: zer gyi rtse las yi ge 'thon pa dang de
NK071(du)002:2054: yang grangs med par 'phro bas thabs bsam yas shing
NK071(du)002:2056: de yongs su gyur ba las don la tha dad
NK071(du)002:2057: pa gzhan du yod pa min pa las tha dad
NK071(du)002:2058: pa'i rnam pa snod gzhal yas khang dang bcud lha
NK071(du)002:2059: dang lha mo'i rol bar bsgom zhing /
NK071(du)002:2060: de ltar bsgom pa'i dus na nang rang nyid lha
NK071(du)002:2061: dang yi ger snang ba'i 'phro 'du dang nang gi
NK071(du)002:2062: phyi rol gyi rnam pa sems kyis bskyed pa'i gzhal
NK071(du)002:2064: spro bsdu'i gzhi sangs rgyas dang sems can du blos
NK071(du)002:2065: bkod pa rnams kyi dkyil 'khor grangs med bsam yas
NK071(du)002:2066: su bsgom pa'i 'phro 'du yang rang snang gi ye
NK071(du)002:2067: shes bkod pa'i rol pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2068: sems nyid gdod nas dag pas sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:2069: bzhin gang la'ang 'jigs pa med pa gnas lugs don
NK071(du)002:2070: gyi kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgya'i mchog gis btab
NK071(du)002:2071: pa'i phyir ro // bskyed pa'i rim pa'ang rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:2072: med pa'i rdzogs rim du lhun gyis grub pas de'i
NK071(du)002:2073: ngang la mnyam par bzhag cing spros pa med pa'i
NK071(du)002:2076: 'od gsal ba'i sems nyid yi ger snang ba'i thabs
NK071(du)002:2077: las rang gi de kho na nyid yul sems su
NK071(du)002:2078: snang ba'i thabs byung zhing snang srid sna tshogs su
NK071(du)002:2079: snang ba'i thabs bsam yas su shar ba de dag
NK071(du)002:2080: kyang don tha dad du yod pa min pa la
NK071(du)002:2081: / tha dad pa'i rnam pa sna tshogs su snang ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2082: nang gi sems dang nang gi phyi rol dkar dmar
NK071(du)002:2083: sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos kyi dkyil 'khor bsam
NK071(du)002:2084: yas ye shes kyi rol par shar bas 'jigs med
NK071(du)002:2085: kun tu bzang po ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyag
NK071(du)002:2086: rgya'i mchog gis rgyas btab pa zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)002:2087: yang thabs yi ge 'khor lo las thabs byung 'phro
NK071(du)002:2088: 'du byed pa'i yi ge'i thabs bsam yas 'phro ba
NK071(du)002:2089: yang / sems las tha dad min pa blos 'phro
NK071(du)002:2090: sa 'phro yul tha dad pa'i chos su byed cing
NK071(du)002:2091: nang rang gi sems dang nang gi phyi rol sems
NK071(du)002:2092: la snang ba'i chos thams cad yi ger gyur pa'i
NK071(du)002:2093: 'phro 'dus dbang bsgyur ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye
NK071(du)002:2094: shes kyi rol pa bsgom pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2095: 'jig med kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgya'i mchog yin no //
NK071(du)002:2096: zhes yi ge bsgom pa la'ang sbyar ro //
NK071(du)002:2097: gsum pa mnyam par bzhag pa gcig tu don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2098: de ltar yi ge phreng ba rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor
NK071(du)002:2099: pa gang gis glang chen chang gis myos pa dang
NK071(du)002:2100: 'dra ba'i sems las su mi rung ba bdag tu
NK071(du)002:2101: lta ba'i gnas la rten 'cha' zhing mtshan mar 'dzin
NK071(du)002:2102: pa'i chang gis myos pas 'khor bar rgyu zhing sdug
NK071(du)002:2104: gnas lugs kyi don la zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi
NK071(du)002:2105: tshul du mnyam par bzhag pas dngos po dang mtshan
NK071(du)002:2106: mar 'dzin pa'i blo btul nas su /
NK071(du)002:2107: bskyed rdzogs yan lag sngags dang phyag rgya rab tu brtan zhing gom par byas na /
NK071(du)002:2108: dngos grub ya mtshan chen po kun tu bzang po nyid thob par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:2109: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2110: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin yi ge'i sprin du gnas so zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:2111: de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang po nyid yi
NK071(du)002:2112: ge 'khor lo las dngos grub phun sum tshogs pa
NK071(du)002:2113: lhun grub tu 'byung ba'i gzigs mos mnyes par gyur
NK071(du)002:2114: to // yi ge sprin gyi 'khor lo gsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:2115: snying po dngos grub thams cad 'byung ba'i de kho
NK071(du)002:2116: na nyid nges pa las yi ge sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK071(du)002:2117: ba bsgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam grangs bstan
NK071(du)002:2120: // don gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:2121: dbyings ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2122: de'i yan lag sngags dang phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2124: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i rgyu brjod pa dang de las 'phros pa dkyil 'khor nyid bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2126: yi ge sprin gyi dkyil 'khor bkod pa de nas
NK071(du)002:2127: rang snang gi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:2128: rang bzhin gcig dang du ma med pa'i bdag nyid
NK071(du)002:2129: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba thams
NK071(du)002:2130: cad kyis / gdul bya'i 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad la rnam par gzigs nas /
NK071(du)002:2131: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi che ba'i dkyil 'khor dbyung bar bzhed nas /
NK071(du)002:2132: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)002:2134: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:2135: lam ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:2136: 'bras bu ye shes chen po'i dkyil 'khor du don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2138: phyi rol sa chu me rlung nang du gzugs tshor
NK071(du)002:2139: ba 'du shes 'du byed gsang bar gti mug nga
NK071(du)002:2140: rgyal 'dod chags phrag dog bzhi ni ye nas chos
NK071(du)002:2141: kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid so sor rtog pa bya
NK071(du)002:2142: ba grub pa'i ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas
NK071(du)002:2143: phyogs bzhi dang zhe sdang nam mkha' rnam shes gsum
NK071(du)002:2144: ni me long lta bu'i ye shes su gnas pas
NK071(du)002:2146: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga dang phung po lnga yab dang /
NK071(du)002:2147: dug lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gnas pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:2148: 'khor bsam yas par snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)002:2149: thams cad ye nas rang snang du lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:2150: pa ni / rdzogs pa chen po ste de nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK071(du)002:2151: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun spang blang dang dgag
NK071(du)002:2152: sgrub med par rang byung ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:2154: bla ma rong pas ni rdzogs pa chen po'i don
NK071(du)002:2155: rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas kun 'byung gi chos su
NK071(du)002:2156: grags pa thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:2157: chen por spyod cig ces gsungs /
NK071(du)002:2159: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dngos dang /
NK071(du)002:2160: de'i grub pa 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:2162: rten gzhal yas khang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)002:2169: ye shes bzhis ma rig pa gcod par mtshon pa'i
NK071(du)002:2170: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa de nyid kyang spros pa
NK071(du)002:2171: dang bral ba'i ye shes su mtshon pa'i phyir mu
NK071(du)002:2172: khyud dkar po zlum po dang bcas shing /
NK071(du)002:2173: de'i phyi rol du tshad med pa bzhi'i mtshon byed
NK071(du)002:2174: gru chad bzhis brgyan pa ye shes la rgya chad
NK071(du)002:2175: dang phyogs ltung med par mtshon pa'i bar khyams phyogs
NK071(du)002:2177: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su gzhal yas
NK071(du)002:2178: khang de'i rnam pa kun tu gru bzhi pa rnam
NK071(du)002:2179: par thar pa bzhi mtshon pa'i sgo khyud dang ldan
NK071(du)002:2180: pa / des mtshon te rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2182: byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum bcu rtsa bdun la
NK071(du)002:2183: sogs pa mtshon pa'i phyir gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la
NK071(du)002:2184: sogs pa rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin du
NK071(du)002:2185: gtibs pa / de mdzes par byed pa lha'i gnas
NK071(du)002:2186: kyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i so so'i gdan gyi dkyil
NK071(du)002:2187: 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2189: mi 'jigs pa bzhi la sogs pa'i mtshon byed du
NK071(du)002:2190: seng ge dang glang chen dang rta dang khyung dang
NK071(du)002:2191: / nam mkha'i lding gi dbang po rnams kyis btegs pa'i khri chen po la /
NK071(du)002:2192: shes rab nyi ma thabs zla ba skyon gyis ma
NK071(du)002:2193: gos pa pad+ma de dag las 'dod dgu 'byung bas
NK071(du)002:2194: rin po che zhes smos so //
NK071(du)002:2195: de'ang rigs lnga la lnga brtsegs gdangs kyi kun bzang yab yum la bzhi brtsegs /
NK071(du)002:2196: sems dpa' rnams la sum brtsegs /
NK071(du)002:2197: thub pa drug la pad+ma'i gdan re re dang /
NK071(du)002:2198: sgo ba rnams la nyi ma re re rkyang par bshad do //
NK071(du)002:2199: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la drug las dang po ji ltar 'byung ba'i tshul ni //
NK071(du)002:2200: gdan de dag la kun bzang yab yum dang rigs
NK071(du)002:2201: lnga yab yum rnams ni rgyal po'i tshul te don
NK071(du)002:2202: gnyis lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa'i dkyil mo krung
NK071(du)002:2203: dang sems dpa' yab yum rnams blon po'i tshul gyis
NK071(du)002:2204: 'khor du bkod pas sems dpa'i dkyil krung gi tshul
NK071(du)002:2205: dang / sgo ba rnams ni dmag dpon gyi tshul
NK071(du)002:2206: du bgegs dang log 'dren tshar gcod pas zhal phyir
NK071(du)002:2207: gzigs shing gyad kyi dor thabs su bzhugs la thub
NK071(du)002:2208: pa rnams ni rang rang gi 'gro ba'i gtso ba'i
NK071(du)002:2209: gzugs su snang bas rgyal phran gyi rnam pas mi
NK071(du)002:2211: gnyis pa gnas gang du lha gang bzhugs pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2212: dbus kyi 'khor lo de'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhis
NK071(du)002:2213: rnam snang la sogs pa rgyal po yab lnga dang
NK071(du)002:2214: rgyal mo yum lnga dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2215: gtso bo'i g.yas shar lho nas gzung ste rtsibs mchan
NK071(du)002:2216: bzhir mthong ba sa'i snying po dang thos pa phyag
NK071(du)002:2217: na rdo rje dang snom pa nam mkha'i snying po
NK071(du)002:2218: dang myong ba spyan ras gzigs dang btsun mo'i rang
NK071(du)002:2219: bzhin sgeg pa ma dang phreng ba ma dang glu
NK071(du)002:2220: ma dang gar ma'i tshogs su bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2221: shar lho'i la sogs pa'i gru chad bzhi la ni mthong byed byams pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2222: thos byed sgrib pa rnams sel dang /
NK071(du)002:2223: snom byed kun tu bzang po dang myong byed 'jam dpal rnams /
NK071(du)002:2224: btsun mo'i rang bzhin bdug pa ma dang me tog
NK071(du)002:2225: ma dang mar me ma dang dri chab ma'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:2227: bar khyams la ni lha la sogs pa'i thub pa drug po rnams dang /
NK071(du)002:2228: gtso bo'i thugs ka'i mdun dang rgyab tu zhal phyogs
NK071(du)002:2229: pa'i tshul gyis byed pa po kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)002:2231: bya ba mo kun tu bzang mo gdangs kyi 'char
NK071(du)002:2232: gzhi gnyis po dag ni gnas par bstan te de
NK071(du)002:2233: gnyis las dkyil 'khor kun 'char bar mtshon pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:2234: ro // shar la sogs pa'i sgo khyud bzhi la
NK071(du)002:2235: bdud bzhi 'joms pa khro bo gshin rje gshed stobs
NK071(du)002:2236: po che rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil pa bzhi ni
NK071(du)002:2237: ro // / btsun mo'i rang bzhin lcags kyu ma
NK071(du)002:2238: zhags pa ma lcags sgrog ma dril bu ma bzhi'i
NK071(du)002:2239: tshogs dang ldan par gar dgu'i rol pas gnas so
NK071(du)002:2240: ro // / // gsum pa phyag mtshan gang 'dzin pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2241: thugs rnam pa snang mdzad stong pa nyid dang snying
NK071(du)002:2242: rje gnyis su med pa'i brdar rtsa ba'i phyag g.yas
NK071(du)002:2243: kyi dang po rdo rje dang mi bskyod pas nyon
NK071(du)002:2244: mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod cing chos kyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)002:2245: bskor ba'i brdar 'khor lo dang rin chen 'byung ldan
NK071(du)002:2246: 'gro ba'i re ba skong zhing yon tan lhun gyis
NK071(du)002:2247: grub pa'i brdar rin po che dang /
NK071(du)002:2248: 'od dpag med 'dod chags dbyings su dag cing so
NK071(du)002:2249: sor rtog pas 'gro ba la dgongs pa'i brdar pad+ma
NK071(du)002:2250: dang don yod grub pa phrin las bzhis 'gro ba'i
NK071(du)002:2251: nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i brdar ral gri dang rtsa
NK071(du)002:2252: phyag g.yon rnams na dril bu 'od 'bar bas yum
NK071(du)002:2253: la 'khyud pa'o // gtso bo'i phyag mtshan ni rdo rje me long las /
NK071(du)002:2255: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK071(du)002:2257: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes /
NK071(du)002:2258: dang po thugs dang g.yon 'khyud pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2259: zhes gsungs pas mi bskyod pa la sogs pa bzhi yang shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:2260: yum rnams ni g.yas yab dang mthun zhing g.yon dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2261: de'ang yab rnams ni zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang yum rnams ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma'o //
NK071(du)002:2262: sems dpa' rnams kyi phyag mtshan ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan /
NK071(du)002:2263: ces pas 'jam dpal ni nyom mongs pa spangs pa ut+pala /
NK071(du)002:2264: byams pa ni nyon mongs pa'i tsha gdung sel bas klu shing /
NK071(du)002:2265: sa'i snying po ye shes kyi myu gu bskrun pas rin po che'i myu gu /
NK071(du)002:2266: phyag na rdo rjes sdug bsngal 'joms pas rdo rje /
NK071(du)002:2267: nam mkha'i snying po nyon mongs ba'i rgyun gcod pas ral gri //
NK071(du)002:2268: spyan ras gzigs nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pas pad+ma /
NK071(du)002:2269: sgrib pa rnams sel sems can la chos ston pas rin po'i che'i sgrom bu /
NK071(du)002:2270: kun tu bzang po sems can gyi re ba bskong bas rin po che'i snye ma'o //
NK071(du)002:2271: de dag gi yum rnams ni mdzes tshul du mnyes pa'i yo byad 'dzin par byed do //
NK071(du)002:2272: rdo rje sgeg mo ni gzugs thams cad de bzhin
NK071(du)002:2273: nyid kyi ngo bor ston pas rdo rje'i khu tshur
NK071(du)002:2274: dkur brten pa'am me long 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:2275: phreng ba ma thabs dang shes rab mi 'bral bar mtshon pas rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK071(du)002:2276: glu ma chos kyi sgra sgrogs pas pi wam /
NK071(du)002:2277: gar ma gdul bya la dga' ba bskyed pas gar
NK071(du)002:2278: bsgyur ba'i phyag na rdo rje dril bu 'khrol ba'o
NK071(du)002:2279: // bdug spos ma ni tshul khrims kyi dris tshim par byed pas spos khang /
NK071(du)002:2280: me tog ma byang chub kyi yan lag mtshon pas me tog gi za ma tog /
NK071(du)002:2281: mar me mas ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bas mar me /
NK071(du)002:2282: dri chab mas bag chags kyi dri ma 'khru bas dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2284: brgya byin lha rnams la chos kyi sdom bzhi ston pas pi wam /
NK071(du)002:2285: thag bzang ris lha ma yin rnams 'thab rtsod kyis 'dul bas go mtshon /
NK071(du)002:2286: sh+aakya thub pa mi rnams la dge bcu ston pas mkhar gsil dang lhung bzed /
NK071(du)002:2287: seng ge rab brtan byol song glen lkugs kyi mdud pa 'grol bas po ti /
NK071(du)002:2288: kha 'bar de ba yi dwags kyi bkres skom sel bas rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK071(du)002:2289: a wa glang mgo dmyal ba'i nyes dmigs ston pas me chu bsnams pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2290: kun tu bzang po yab yum ni dbyings chos kyi
NK071(du)002:2291: sku spros pa dang bral bar mtshon pas phyag mtshan
NK071(du)002:2292: med do // sgo ba bzhi ni 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms pas gshin rje gshed thod dbyug /
NK071(du)002:2293: phung po'i bdud 'joms pas stobs chen rdo rje /
NK071(du)002:2294: nyon mongs pa'i bdud 'joms pas rta mgrin thod sbrul /
NK071(du)002:2295: lha'i bu'i bdud 'joms pas bdud rtsi 'khyil pa rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2296: yum bzhi ni bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang tshad
NK071(du)002:2297: med pa bzhi mtshon byed du lcags kyu zhags pa
NK071(du)002:2298: lcags sgrog dril bu rnams 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2299: bzhi pa sku mdog ji ltar snang ba ni rigs kyi sku mdog nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK071(du)002:2300: sna tshogs kyi sku mdog bcu bdun las dang po //
NK071(du)002:2301: thugs kyi rigs chos nyid mi 'gyur ba mtshon pa'i
NK071(du)002:2302: phyir rnam snang yab yum kun bzang yab yum lha
NK071(du)002:2303: ma yin gyi thub pa dang lnga ni mthing kha
NK071(du)002:2304: dang sku'i rig rnams skyon gyis ma gos par mtshon
NK071(du)002:2305: pa'i phyir mi bskyod pa yab yum //
NK071(du)002:2306: sa snying yab yum lha'i thub pa rnams dkar po
NK071(du)002:2307: dang yon tan gyi rigs rnams che ba'i yon tan
NK071(du)002:2308: mtshon pa'i phyir rin 'byung yab yum nam snying yab
NK071(du)002:2309: yum mi'i thub pa rnams ser po dang gsung gi
NK071(du)002:2310: rigs rnams thugs rjes 'gro ba la chags pa mtshon
NK071(du)002:2311: pa'i phyir 'od dpag med yab yum spyan ras gzigs
NK071(du)002:2312: yab yum yi dwags kyi thub pa rnams le brgan
NK071(du)002:2313: te dmar po dang phrin las kyi rigs rnams las
NK071(du)002:2314: sna tshogs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir don grub yab yum
NK071(du)002:2315: phyag rdor yab yum dud 'gro'i thub pa rnams ljang
NK071(du)002:2316: gu'o la sogs kyis bsdus ba sna tshogs pa'i mdog
NK071(du)002:2317: can ni phrin las dang yon tan du mas 'gro
NK071(du)002:2318: ba 'dul ba'i phyir byams pa yab yum dkar ser
NK071(du)002:2319: / sgrib pa rnam sel yab yum dmar ser //
NK071(du)002:2320: kun bzang yab yum dmar ljang /
NK071(du)002:2322: gshin rje gshed yab yum smug nag stobs chen yab yum ser nag rta mgrin yab yum dmar nag /
NK071(du)002:2323: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum ljang nag dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha'o //
NK071(du)002:2324: lnga pa tshul ji ltar bzhugs pa ni //
NK071(du)002:2325: lha de dag kyang skye ba gnas su dag pas
NK071(du)002:2326: sku mnyen pa dang na ba gnas su dag pas
NK071(du)002:2327: sku skabs phyed cing rim par 'tshams pas lcug pa
NK071(du)002:2328: dang 'chi ba gnas su dag pas sku lhod por
NK071(du)002:2329: ma gyur par 'khril bag chags shing rab tu ldem
NK071(du)002:2330: pa dang / rga ba gnas su dag pas sku
NK071(du)002:2331: 'jam shing gzhon sha chags pa'i ngang tshul can no
NK071(du)002:2332: pa dang / // de lnga ni ngo bo'i yon tan yin la /
NK071(du)002:2333: rnam pa'i yon tan ni mtshan dpa'i mdzes pa'i sku
NK071(du)002:2334: dri ma med pas kha dog shin tu gsal ba
NK071(du)002:2335: dang gsal ba dang zad par rdzogs pas sku bkrag
NK071(du)002:2336: rab tu 'tsher ba'i mdangs can dang brjid cing yid
NK071(du)002:2337: du 'ong ba'i sku lhun stug pa dang 'gro ba
NK071(du)002:2338: zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi brjid chen po dang ldan
NK071(du)002:2339: pa'o // drug pa 'od zer ji ltar 'phro ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2340: sku de dag gi gnas chen po drug dang ba
NK071(du)002:2341: spu'i bu ga thams cad nas kyang 'od zer bye
NK071(du)002:2342: ba khrag khrig grangs med pa phyogs bcur 'phro bas
NK071(du)002:2343: 'od zer gyi tshogs chen po snang bar gyur pa'o
NK071(du)002:2344: // sgo ba yab yum ni bskal pa'i me dpung
NK071(du)002:2345: ltar 'bar ba'i klong na me'i 'phreng bas phyogs bcur
NK071(du)002:2346: 'khyil ba ste rngam pa'i cha byad can no //
NK071(du)002:2347: de lta bu'i snang bas nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi /
NK071(du)002:2348: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor grangs dang tshad bsam
NK071(du)002:2349: yas shing rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par bsgoms pa
NK071(du)002:2350: ni chos kyi dbyings ltar rgya che zhing ye shes
NK071(du)002:2351: dam pa'i ngo bo gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2352: gnyis pa de'i grub pa 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)002:2354: de las phrin las mdzad tshul /
NK071(du)002:2356: ngo mtshar ltas kyi snang tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:2357: dang po ni chos kyi sku yi rang bzhin phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub ni /
NK071(du)002:2358: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos kyang sku gzhan gyi 'char gzhi byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2359: de'i ngang nas sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa
NK071(du)002:2360: las yang dag par thar ba'i gzugs mtshan dang dpe
NK071(du)002:2361: byad phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa'i longs spyod rdzogs
NK071(du)002:2362: pa'i sku dang / de'i thugs rje las 'gro ba ma lus pa 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:2363: de dag gi bsam pa dang mthun par byas pa'i sku ni sna tshogs su ston par mdzad do //
NK071(du)002:2365: dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin du phrin las snang ba'i dpe dang /
NK071(du)002:2366: gdul bya'i don du phrin las snang ba'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:2368: de ltar sprul pa sna tshogs gdul bya la ston
NK071(du)002:2369: pa nyid sgyu ma dang mig yor ltar snang dus
NK071(du)002:2370: nyid nas ngos bzung med pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)002:2371: tshul de nyid kyang chos kyi dbyings las g.yos pa med la /
NK071(du)002:2372: de ltar ma g.yos bzhin du 'gro ba'i snang ngor
NK071(du)002:2373: sprul pa'i sku sna tshogs pa'i rnam pa so sor
NK071(du)002:2374: snang ba / de tshe rgyal po dang bram ze
NK071(du)002:2375: la sogs pa dang zhi ba dang khro bo la
NK071(du)002:2376: sogs pa rnam pa mi mthun pa'i sku sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:2377: snang ba / pa dag / gdul bya so so
NK071(du)002:2378: la rang rang gi ris dang 'dra bar snang ba
NK071(du)002:2379: snang ba / pa dag / ni / chos sku de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos kyang /
NK071(du)002:2380: 'gro ba rang rang gi skal ba dang sngon gyi
NK071(du)002:2381: las 'phro'i dbang gis rang bzhin dang 'gro 'dul dang
NK071(du)002:2382: sna tshogs sprul sku la sogs par so sor snang
NK071(du)002:2383: ba ste / dper na me long gis ngos la
NK071(du)002:2384: byad ma 'phos kyang de'i rnam pa snang ba dang
NK071(du)002:2385: chu snod du nam mkha'i zla ba ma 'phos kyang
NK071(du)002:2386: chu zla snang ba bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:2388: 'gro drug phal la snang tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2389: lhun stug po bkod par sku gsum 'du 'bral med
NK071(du)002:2390: pa'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa de yi tshe
NK071(du)002:2391: lha la sogs pa'i 'gro ba drug po thams cad
NK071(du)002:2392: la / de dag gi rgyud kyi sdig pa spong
NK071(du)002:2393: ba'i gzugs brgya byin la sogs pa'i thub pa rnams
NK071(du)002:2394: su snang bar bstan nas sgrib pa sbyong ba la
NK071(du)002:2396: gnyis pa nyan thos la snang tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2397: nyan thos kyi rigs can rnams la dgra bcom pa'i
NK071(du)002:2398: gzugs su bstan nas bden pa bzhi'i don rtogs pa
NK071(du)002:2400: gsum pa rang rgyal la snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2401: rang rgyal gyi rigs can rnams la bse ru lta
NK071(du)002:2402: bu'i tshul gyis rten 'brel gyi chos brda'i sgo nas
NK071(du)002:2404: bzhi pa theg pa chen po pa la snang tshul ni //
NK071(du)002:2405: de dag las gzhan yang theg pa mchog gi rigs can rnams la dbang po'i rim pa bzhin /
NK071(du)002:2406: sa bcu'i sems dpa' rnams la gnas dbang phyug chen
NK071(du)002:2407: po'i 'og min bla na med pa'i gnas gzugs kyi
NK071(du)002:2408: khams las khyad par du 'phags pa'i mchog tu /
NK071(du)002:2409: ston pa nyid sku ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi tshul du bzhugs pa la /
NK071(du)002:2410: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la /
NK071(du)002:2411: sngar 'gro ba tha dad la snang ba'i sprul pa'i
NK071(du)002:2412: skus chos rnams tshig tu ston par snang ba de
NK071(du)002:2413: bzhin du longs sku'i ston pa nyid chos rnams gsung
NK071(du)002:2415: sku snang ba'i ngo bo de yis theg pa mchog
NK071(du)002:2416: gi chos rnams 'khor gyi blo la mjal bar ston
NK071(du)002:2417: to // gsum pa de las 'gro ba grol tshul gnyis /
NK071(du)002:2418: rgyu lam gyi sgrib pa sbyang ba dang /
NK071(du)002:2419: 'bras bu sku dang sa mchog thob tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:2422: gdong la me long bstan pa'i tshe rang gi byad
NK071(du)002:2423: snang ba'i tshul gyis dri ma mthong ba bzhin tu
NK071(du)002:2424: slar byad dngos kyi dri mas gos pa'i mdog ngan
NK071(du)002:2425: pa thams cad 'khru zhing sel ba ltar /
NK071(du)002:2427: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor gyis dpe de
NK071(du)002:2428: bzhin du ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK071(du)002:2429: bltas pa na / byang chub la sgrib pa yi
NK071(du)002:2430: dri ma che 'bring phra rags dang bcas pa gting
NK071(du)002:2431: dpag dka' zhing tshad med pa rnams me long nang
NK071(du)002:2432: du dri ma snang ba bzhin du sku la snang
NK071(du)002:2433: bltas pa na / ngo // de nas dri ma dag stobs kyis sa bcu rim gyis 'byang zhing /
NK071(du)002:2434: bla na med pa'i byang chub yang dag par thob bo //
NK071(du)002:2436: lhun stug po bkod par sku dang ye shes rdzogs tshul spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:2437: de la sa'i rdzogs tshul bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:2438: sku lnga lhun gyis grub tshul du don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2440: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i thob tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2441: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:2442: chos kyi sku ni blos dpag tu med cing tshig
NK071(du)002:2443: gis brjod du med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK071(du)002:2444: de nyid kyi ngang las longs sku ni rtag tu
NK071(du)002:2445: lhun gyis grub par bzhugs pas zad pa med pa'i
NK071(du)002:2446: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i gter du
NK071(du)002:2447: bzhugs so de'i ngang las gdul bya'i don du sprul
NK071(du)002:2448: pa'i sku bye ba khrag khrig dpag tu med cing
NK071(du)002:2449: bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phro bar byed do //
NK071(du)002:2450: gnyis pa rang snang lhun grub kyis chen por bzhugs tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2451: de ltar snang sa'i longs sku de yang mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs shing /
NK071(du)002:2452: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rang snang
NK071(du)002:2453: ba'i spyod yul kun tu sku dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:2454: man+dala ste dkyil 'khor du snang bas nyid las bzang
NK071(du)002:2455: ngan med pa'i rang bzhin du lhun gyis grub cing
NK071(du)002:2456: phun sum tshogs pa thams cad rang snang ba'i bsod
NK071(du)002:2458: gang du'ang 'dzin pa mi mnga' ba'i ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:2459: tshogs te tshogs chen gnyis kyang rang snang de nyid
NK071(du)002:2460: du lhun gyis rdzogs par rol pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2461: gnyis pa sa'i rdzogs tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2462: thabs sprul pa sku'i sa kun tu 'od dang shes
NK071(du)002:2463: rab rang snang dag pa longs spyod rdzogs pa pad+ma
NK071(du)002:2464: can gyi sa dang gnyis su med pa sa yi
NK071(du)002:2465: mchog / 'khor lo tshogs chen chos kyi sku'i sa'o //
NK071(du)002:2466: sa'i rnam grangs dang yon tan gyi chos de dag
NK071(du)002:2467: la sogs pa tshad med cing bsam yas kyi mchog
NK071(du)002:2469: gsum pa sku lnga lhun gyis grub tshul du don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2470: de ltar de dag thob pa'i tshe sku lnga yang
NK071(du)002:2471: lhun grub tu thob pas na dang po chos kyi
NK071(du)002:2472: sku spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba ni 'gyur ba
NK071(du)002:2473: med pa'i yongs grub ste skye shi med pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:2475: de'i ngang las longs skur shar ba'i byin rlabs las
NK071(du)002:2476: rang byung ba nyon mongs par gyur ba'i sems can
NK071(du)002:2477: kun gyi zhing du gang la gang 'tshams pa'i sprul
NK071(du)002:2478: skur gnas te don mdzad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2479: sprul sku'i 'char gzhi de nyid yon tan gyi tshogs
NK071(du)002:2480: zad mi shes pa'i rang bzhin lhun stug po bkod
NK071(du)002:2481: pa'i longs spyod kun gyi gter du 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2482: de ltar sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:2483: ni gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje dang rig pa'i
NK071(du)002:2484: ye shes chen po 'dzin pa'i phyir mi 'gyur rdo
NK071(du)002:2485: rje'i sku'o // chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:2486: chen por dbyer med cing mnyam pa'i rang bzhin du
NK071(du)002:2487: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni ji lta ba
NK071(du)002:2489: chos can thams cad ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'i ye
NK071(du)002:2490: shes ni ji snyed par mngon par byang chub pa'i
NK071(du)002:2491: sku'o // de dag kyang rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i
NK071(du)002:2492: sku ste g.yung drung gi sku ni de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:2493: pa'i rigs me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi sku'o
NK071(du)002:2494: sku'o // // longs spyod zad mi shes pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:2495: nyid rdo rje rig pa 'dzin pa'i sku ni rdo
NK071(du)002:2496: rje'i rigs te chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:2497: sku'o // // sku'o // thams cad dbyer med mnyam
NK071(du)002:2498: pa'i sku ni rin chen rigs te mnyam nyid ye
NK071(du)002:2499: sku'o // // sku'o // shes kyi sku'o // thams
NK071(du)002:2500: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi sku ni pad+ma'i rigs
NK071(du)002:2501: te so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi sku'o //
NK071(du)002:2502: nyon mongs kun gyi zhing du gnas pa ni sprul
NK071(du)002:2503: pa ste las kyi rigs bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK071(du)002:2504: shes kyi sku'o // sa thob pa de tshe sku
NK071(du)002:2505: lnga po kun kyang rdzogs par thob pa yin te
NK071(du)002:2506: shes kyi sku'o // / 'bras bu'i sa dang sku
NK071(du)002:2507: dang ye shes rnams chas dbye ba las snga phyi
NK071(du)002:2508: shes kyi sku'o // / med do // bzhi pa
NK071(du)002:2509: ngo mtshar ltas kyi snang tshul ni zhes brjod pas
NK071(du)002:2510: shes kyi sku'o // / med do // / gdul
NK071(du)002:2511: bya'i 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu re re zhing
NK071(du)002:2512: grangs mtha' yas shing dbyings mu med pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:2513: du rnam par 'phrul pa'i dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:2514: khyab brjod kyis mi lang ba phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:2515: thams cad kyi zhing gi rdul phra rab kyi grangs
NK071(du)002:2516: ci snyed dang mnyam pa de snyed du gsal bar
NK071(du)002:2517: shes kyi sku'o // / med do // / gyur
NK071(du)002:2518: to // gsum pa 'bras bu ye shes chen po'i
NK071(du)002:2519: dkyil 'khor gcig tu don bsdu ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:2520: tshul ji ltar gsungs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2523: thams cad dkyil 'khor du gsal ba de nas rang
NK071(du)002:2524: snang ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK071(du)002:2525: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag
NK071(du)002:2526: las de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi gsang ba 'di
NK071(du)002:2527: nyid kyi gsang ba 'di nyid sku dang gsung dang
NK071(du)002:2528: thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las rdo rje las
NK071(du)002:2529: phyung ngo // gnyis pa ni ting nge 'dzin rang
NK071(du)002:2530: snang ba'i dkyil 'khor ngo mtshar ba'i rol pa dbyings
NK071(du)002:2531: las ma g.yos par bstan pa'i phyir a ho zhes
NK071(du)002:2532: phyung ngo // bzhad pa'o // de'ang dmigs par bya
NK071(du)002:2533: ba'i yul chos rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa
NK071(du)002:2534: dang dmigs par byed pa'i blo glo bur kun brtags
NK071(du)002:2535: kyis rnam par dag pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2536: de gnyis ka'i ngo bo gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK071(du)002:2537: shes tsam du'ang mi dmigs pa ni don dam pa'i
NK071(du)002:2538: rang bzhin blos dpag tu med cing bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:2539: khyab pa gzhi rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:2540: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum sngon du 'gro bas
NK071(du)002:2541: bskyed pa lha'i rang bzhin chu'i zla ba ltar bsgom
NK071(du)002:2542: pa'i ye shes rang rig pa'i dkyil 'khor rnam pa
NK071(du)002:2543: sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba bsgoms pa'i rjes
NK071(du)002:2544: la / 'khor ba'i rang bzhin chos nyid du mnyam
NK071(du)002:2545: pa nyid dang mya ngan las 'das pa dmigs pa
NK071(du)002:2546: nye bar zhi bas mi mnyam pa'i ngo bo kun
NK071(du)002:2547: la ye nas dag pa'i de bzhin nyid khyab bya
NK071(du)002:2548: khyab byed med pa'i rang bzhin chos nyid rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:2549: chen pos khyab pa'i dbyings de bzhin nyid bskyed rdzogs
NK071(du)002:2550: tsam du'ang 'dzin pa med par mnyam par bzhag pa
NK071(du)002:2551: la / ni / lam bskyed rdzogs bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:2552: de ltar nyams su blangs pa'i mtha' 'bras bu gzhi
NK071(du)002:2553: thog tu phyin pa de'i tshe ye nas snang la
NK071(du)002:2554: kun tu 'od gsal ba'i longs sku 'gag pa med
NK071(du)002:2555: pa'i ngang las sna tshogs sprul pa sku'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:2556: rnam par spros nas 'gro ba'i don gnyis lhun gyis
NK071(du)002:2558: de ltar snang ba nyid nas rang bzhin spros pa med pa ni chos kyi sku ste /
NK071(du)002:2559: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos nyid ngo mtshar bar bstan pas ho /
NK071(du)002:2560: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK071(du)002:2561: de bzhin du gzhi lam 'bras bu re re zhing
NK071(du)002:2562: yang gnas te dmigs bya yul dmigs byed blo de
NK071(du)002:2563: gnyis ka'i rang bzhin ye nas dmigs pa med pa'i
NK071(du)002:2564: sems nyid dpag tu med cing bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)002:2566: ye shes rang rig gi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod
NK071(du)002:2567: kyis mi lang ba ye nas gnas pa de yang
NK071(du)002:2568: chos nyid mnyam pa dang chos can tha dad mi
NK071(du)002:2569: mnyam pa kun la khyab pa'i rang bzhin mnyam pa
NK071(du)002:2570: nyid ni khyab pa chen po'i dbyings te /
NK071(du)002:2571: ye nas kun gsal gyi dkyil 'khor lhun grub chen
NK071(du)002:2572: po 'gro ba kun la 'phro yang spros pa med
NK071(du)002:2573: pa'i rang bzhin ngo mtshar ro //
NK071(du)002:2575: lam ltar na dmigs bya ting nge 'dzin /
NK071(du)002:2576: dmigs byed rang gi blo de gnyis ka'i ngo bo
NK071(du)002:2577: mi dmigs pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:2578: dang / kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin snying rje tshad med pa dang /
NK071(du)002:2579: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin snying rje'i ngang las sems nyid
NK071(du)002:2580: bsam gyis mi khyab pa yi ge'i rang bzhin a
NK071(du)002:2581: la sogs pa'i ngo bo las ye shes rang rig
NK071(du)002:2582: gi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba
NK071(du)002:2583: bsgoms nas / de thams cad sems nyid du mnyam
NK071(du)002:2584: pas stong pa dang rnam pa tha dad bskyed pas
NK071(du)002:2585: mi mnyam par snang ba dang de nyid kyi ngo
NK071(du)002:2586: bo ma skyes pas kun khyab khyab med khyab pa'i
NK071(du)002:2587: bsgoms nas / dbyings / ye nas kun gsal gyi ngang nas /
NK071(du)002:2588: dkyil 'khor gyi spro bsdu mang po rnam par 'phro
NK071(du)002:2589: yang don la spros pa med pa'i ngang du shes
NK071(du)002:2590: pa'o // 'bras bu ltar na dbyings dmigs bya dmigs
NK071(du)002:2591: byed dmigs pa med cing dpag med bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:2592: khyab pa chos sku'i ngang las /
NK071(du)002:2593: rang snang ye shes rig pa'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:2594: brjod kyis mi lang bar gsal ba rnams kyi ngo
NK071(du)002:2596: bkod pa dang rnam pa mi mnyam pa kun la
NK071(du)002:2597: khyab pa'i chos nyid khyab bya khyab byed khyab pa
NK071(du)002:2598: med pa'i dbyings ye nas kun gsal longs spyod rdzogs
NK071(du)002:2599: pa sku las / sprul sku'i dkyil 'khor 'phro yang
NK071(du)002:2600: chu zla ltar ma 'phos par dbyings de nyid la
NK071(du)002:2601: spros pa med pas sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i
NK071(du)002:2602: chos nyid ngo mtshar bar bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2603: ting nge 'dzin gsang ba'i snying po rang snang ba'i
NK071(du)002:2604: de kho na nyid nges pa las rang bzhin ting
NK071(du)002:2605: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste drug
NK071(du)002:2607: don gnyis pa de'i yan lag sngags dang phyag rgya'i
NK071(du)002:2608: dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te
NK071(du)002:2609: / gsung gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)002:2610: sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2612: gsung gi dkyil 'khor 'byung ba'i rgyu brjod pa /
NK071(du)002:2613: gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor dngos bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:2614: rang bzhin gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2616: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas
NK071(du)002:2617: de'i yan lag sngags kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:2618: de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa
NK071(du)002:2619: thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje
NK071(du)002:2620: las gsang sngags 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK071(du)002:2625: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sngags /
NK071(du)002:2626: brten pa lha bskyed pa'i sngags /
NK071(du)002:2627: phrin las yongs su rdzogs pa'i sngags /
NK071(du)002:2628: ngo mtshar gyi ltas ji ltar snang ba'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:2630: b+h+r+aum zhes pa rnam snang dang //
NK071(du)002:2634: gtsug tor 'khor los bsgyur ba'i sa bon du gyur
NK071(du)002:2635: pa las 'dir gzhi tshad med pa ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:2636: 'khor lo'i steng du gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sa
NK071(du)002:2637: bon dang / bi shwa sna tshogs te 'khor 'das kyi chos su snang ba thams cad /
NK071(du)002:2638: bi shwa d+d+he rang bzhin gyis dag pa ste chos
NK071(du)002:2639: dbyings spros pa dang bral ba de nyid sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:2640: kyi bzhugs gnas su bstan pas 'dir des mtshon byed
NK071(du)002:2643: dang po rigs lnga yab yum gyi sngags la h+aum
NK071(du)002:2644: la sogs pa ni rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i
NK071(du)002:2646: gzhan rnams rang bzhin mtshon par ngo bo'i sngags so //
NK071(du)002:2647: de las h+aum sa bon dang badz+ra rdo rje d+h+rika ni de 'dzin pas na mi bskyod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2648: dzi na dzika ni spros pa dang mi dge ba
NK071(du)002:2649: las rnam par rgyal bas rnam pa snang mdzad do
NK071(du)002:2651: 'gro ba la 'dod dgu sbyin pas rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK071(du)002:2652: a ro lika ni gdul bya la rjes su chags pas 'od dpag med do //
NK071(du)002:2653: ha pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika ni gdul bya'i don du shes rab sna tshogs 'chang bas don yod grub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2654: m+au d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai ni rang bzhin gyis dag pa dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK071(du)002:2655: l+aam d+ae sha ra ti ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi blon mo ste sangs rgyas spyan ma'o //
NK071(du)002:2656: m+aam mo ha ra ti ni sems can bdag gir byed pa m+aa ma k+ai'o //
NK071(du)002:2657: p+y+aam r+aa ga ra ti ni nyes pa'i dri mas ma gos pas gos dkar mo'o //
NK071(du)002:2658: t+aam badz+ra ra ti ni sems can 'khor ba las sgrol bas sgrol ma'o //
NK071(du)002:2659: gnyis pa thugs kyi sems dpa' yab yum gyi sngags
NK071(du)002:2660: la rtsa ba dang rang bzhin gyi sngags sngar dang
NK071(du)002:2661: 'dra bas k+sh+aim hi r+aa dza yahs dang mig ltar
NK071(du)002:2662: sems can gyi don byed pas rgyal po'o //
NK071(du)002:2663: t+r+aam +aa gar+b+ha yahdagosa 'dod thams cad 'byung ba'i snying por gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2664: hri ha h+aum pad+ma pa da mahchagasa pa med cing
NK071(du)002:2665: gdul bya'i yid 'phrog pas pad+ma lta bu'i zhal mnga'
NK071(du)002:2666: ba'o // dzim ku ru p+aa na h+r+aihrdo rje lta bus sems can gyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2667: h+aum l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam ni sgeg pa'i
NK071(du)002:2668: nyams dang ldan pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dam
NK071(du)002:2670: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hohni gzugs dang ting
NK071(du)002:2671: nge 'dzin gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dam tshig
NK071(du)002:2673: h+r+ai g+ai ti r+aa go&a ham ni glu dbyangs snyan
NK071(du)002:2674: po lta bus sems can la rjes su chags pa
NK071(du)002:2675: yin no // an+ri ti r+aa ga y+aa mi ni
NK071(du)002:2676: gar bsgyur ba lta bu'i phrin las kyis sems can
NK071(du)002:2677: la rjes su chags par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:2678: gsum pa gsung gi sems dpa'i yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:2679: mee d+h+aa ra ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)002:2680: byams pas sems can rjes su 'dzin pa'i gzhi tshugs shig pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2681: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)002:2682: 'thug pa'am sbyangs bar dka' ba'i sgrib pa sel ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2683: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)002:2684: 'khor 'das gnyis la mi gnas pa'i rang bzhin kun tu bzang po'i rgyal po'o //
NK071(du)002:2685: mum sh+ri am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)002:2686: gnyis su mi gnas pa'i dpal sems can la rjes su chags pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2687: dzahd+hu p+pe pra be sha tshul khrims kyi bdug spos gdul bya'i rgyud la 'jug pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2688: h'u push+pe a be sh+aa byang chub kyi me tog rgyas pa'i char gdul bya'i rgyud la 'bebs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2689: bam di pa su khi n+ai ye shes kyi sgron mes ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2690: hohgan+d+he tsit+ta bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyis gdul bya'i rgyud tshims par byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2691: bzhi pa sgo ba yab yum gyi sngags ni h+aum bzhi sngar ltar sa bon dang /
NK071(du)002:2692: mjug gi phata rnams ni gdug pa can 'thor ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2693: h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata 'chi bdag gshin rje'i gzugs 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2694: h+aum big+h+nan+ta krita phata lha'i bu'i bdud mthar byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2695: h+aum pad+m+aan+ta krita phata 'khor ba'i 'dam gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2696: h+aum pra dz+ny+aan+ta krita phata nyon mongs pa'i bdud 'joms pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2697: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa
NK071(du)002:2698: ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata ni rdo rje'i gzung
NK071(du)002:2699: ma chen mo khro mo dbang phyug 'bar ma chen
NK071(du)002:2700: mo'o // ma h+aa rat+na ni rin po che d+ha
NK071(du)002:2701: ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai
NK071(du)002:2702: mo'o // h+aum phata / ma h+aa pad+ma ni skad
NK071(du)002:2703: sor bzhag d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai
NK071(du)002:2705: ma h+aa karma ni phrin las d+ha ro ma h+aa
NK071(du)002:2706: kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata gzhan
NK071(du)002:2708: lnga pa kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi sngags la /
NK071(du)002:2709: khams gsum sems can gyi rgyud dag pa ye shes gsum mtshon pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2710: h+aum h+aum h+aum dang badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum ni sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:2711: thams cad kyi thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin can no
NK071(du)002:2712: // sgo gsum dang dug gsum skye ba med pa mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:2713: a a a dang badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ahni
NK071(du)002:2714: rdo rje kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin du dag
NK071(du)002:2715: pa'o // drug pa thub pa drug gi sngags la
NK071(du)002:2716: rnams sngags kyi tshogs byin gyis brlabs pa ye shes
NK071(du)002:2718: mu ne rnams ni thub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2719: s+w+aa h+aa rnams ni gzhi tshugs shig pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2720: mu ni krem s+w+aa h+aa lha min gyi snying po /
NK071(du)002:2723: mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa dud 'gro'i snying po /
NK071(du)002:2724: mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa yi dwags kyi snying po /
NK071(du)002:2725: mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa lha'i snying po /
NK071(du)002:2726: mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa dmyal ba'i snying po /
NK071(du)002:2727: gnyis pa phrin las yongs su rdzogs pa'i sngags la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:2728: dang po spyan drangs shing bstim pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:2729: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan tshur byon tshur byon bcom ldan 'das /
NK071(du)002:2730: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni k+aa dri sh+ya hoh thugs
NK071(du)002:2731: rje chen po dang ldan pa thugs rjes gzigs la
NK071(du)002:2732: / sa ma ya s+t+aam dam tshig la nos shig /
NK071(du)002:2736: dril bus dbang du byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2737: gnyis pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:2738: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:2745: yi ge bkram pa 'di dag ni /
NK071(du)002:2746: yi ge btu ba'i gzhi yin pas badz+ra sa ma ya +amo /
NK071(du)002:2747: ni sku'i dam tshig gis skur bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2749: gsung gi dam tshig gis gsung du bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2750: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK071(du)002:2751: thugs kyi dam tshig gis thugs su bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2752: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK071(du)002:2753: yon tan gyi dam tshig gis yon tan chu bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2754: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK071(du)002:2755: phrin las kyi dam tshig gis phrin las su bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2756: gsum pa dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2757: ye shes rgyal po zhes bcom ldan 'das la bos
NK071(du)002:2758: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK071(du)002:2759: thugs // yon tan phrin las rmad po che /
