NK071(du)002:2761: de la dus da lta nyid du ni mnyam par sbyor bas /
NK071(du)002:2762: lha'i sku gsung thugs phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK071(du)002:2763: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum gis sku'i dam tshig dus la bab par bskul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2764: badz+ra sa ma ya stam gyis gsung gi dam tshig dus la bab par bskul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2765: badz+ra sa ma ya ho zhes pas thugs kyi dam tshig dus la bab pas bskul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2766: dzahmh'u bam hohzhesa gnyis su med par bsre zhing brtan par byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2767: bzhi pa ngo mtshar gyi ltas ji ltar snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2770: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du sngags kyi sgra chen pos khyab par grags so //
NK071(du)002:2771: des sems can gyi rgyud kun smin par byas pas rab tu grags so //
NK071(du)002:2772: grol bar byas pas kun tu grags so //
NK071(du)002:2773: yang sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi gsang sngags kyi sgra dang /
NK071(du)002:2775: zer kun tu 'phros pa'i snang ba chen po la yang shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:2776: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i sngags la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:2777: ji ltar gsung ba'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)002:2778: dbang bskur ba'i sngags dngos so //
NK071(du)002:2780: bskyed pa'i sngags bstan pa de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK071(du)002:2781: yid byed pa po rdo rje kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)002:2782: dang / chos bya ba mo rdo rje kun tu
NK071(du)002:2783: bzang mo gnyis su med pa'i gsung gi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:2785: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK071(du)002:2786: bdag nyid chen po kun tu bzang pos sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:2787: thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK071(du)002:2788: kyi bdag nyid dngos grub chen po'i ye shes dang
NK071(du)002:2789: gzi byin phun sum tshogs pa thams cad bsdu bar
NK071(du)002:2790: zhes bya ba gsang sngags kyi tshig 'di nyid ston
NK071(du)002:2791: pa yab yum gyi sku dang gsung dang thugs gnyis
NK071(du)002:2792: su med pa'i rdo rje thabs dang shes rab zung
NK071(du)002:2793: du 'brel ba'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las rang shar
NK071(du)002:2794: du phyung ba'o // gnyis pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:2795: dang po dri ma 'khrud pa ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK071(du)002:2796: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa
NK071(du)002:2797: ba +aat+ma konya ham ni stong pa nyid kyi ye
NK071(du)002:2798: shes chen po rdo rje'i ngo ba nyid kyi bdag
NK071(du)002:2800: de bzhin du sbyar te ma h+aa +aa dar+sha me
NK071(du)002:2801: long lta bu dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aa
NK071(du)002:2802: t+ma ko&a ham / ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha
NK071(du)002:2803: n+aa so sor rtog pa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa
NK071(du)002:2805: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa mnyam pa nyid dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)002:2806: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aana bya ba nan tan dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)002:2807: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i don ni skabs 'dir rang
NK071(du)002:2808: rang gi rigs bdag gang yin pa mtshon gang ba
NK071(du)002:2809: res dbu brgyan par bya ba yin no //
NK071(du)002:2810: gnyis pa nus pa 'jug pa rigs lngas byin gyis brlabs pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:2811: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)002:2812: ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku rdo rje'i rang bzhin nga yin no /
NK071(du)002:2814: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa b+aa ka badz+ra gsung rdo rje swa b+h+aa ba a t+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)002:2815: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra thugs rdo rje swa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)002:2816: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa
NK071(du)002:2817: ga na badz+ra yon tan rdo rje swa b+h+aa ba
NK071(du)002:2818: +aat+ma ko&aham / sarba t+aa th+aa ga ta ma h+aa
NK071(du)002:2819: p+au dza badz+ra phrin las rdo rje swa b+h+aa ba
NK071(du)002:2820: +aat+ma ko&aham / +aat+ma ko&aham / de dag gis lha
NK071(du)002:2821: thams cad kyi gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa lnga
NK071(du)002:2823: pa de las byung ba'i byin rlabs kyi snang tshul
NK071(du)002:2824: +aat+ma ko&aham / +aat+ma ko&aham / bskyed pa'o // ni / zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:2825: byin rlabs gdul bya'i lus ngag yid gsum la gnyis su med par thim par gyur /
NK071(du)002:2826: des nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gsal bar gyur /
NK071(du)002:2827: des phung khams skye mched thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'od 'bar gyur to //
NK071(du)002:2828: gsum pa rang bzhin gtan la dbab pa la lnga /
NK071(du)002:2829: gsung gi ngo bo brjod du med pa /
NK071(du)002:2830: ra nga bzhin bsam gyis mi khyabapa /
NK071(du)002:2831: gnas lugs gdod ma nas dag pa /
NK071(du)002:2832: snang lugs mchog tu gyur pa /
NK071(du)002:2833: yin lugs dbyings las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2835: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK071(du)002:2836: mi khyab pa'i don ni khyad par du 'phags pa'i
NK071(du)002:2837: phyir / e ma ho ngo mtshar zhing ya mtshan rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos ni /
NK071(du)002:2838: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo dam pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2839: ji ltar ngo mtshar ba'i tshul ni gsung gi ngo
NK071(du)002:2840: bo de nyid brjod pa'i sgra dang chos kyi ming
NK071(du)002:2842: bzhin du 'gro ba'i snang ba dang mthun par gsung
NK071(du)002:2843: dbyangs phun sum tshogs pa sna tshogs pa'i sgra skad
NK071(du)002:2844: tshad med pa rnams gsal bar 'byung bas ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:2846: sangs rgyas kyi gsung gcig dbyangs kyi yan lag drug
NK071(du)002:2847: cus brgyan pa'i dkyil 'khor de las kyang yan lag
NK071(du)002:2848: ni 'jig rten drug gis phyi bas rnam grangs bsam
NK071(du)002:2849: gyis mi khyab pa'i zhing khams kun tu khyab cing
NK071(du)002:2850: sems can so so'i sgra skad dang ming tshig so
NK071(du)002:2851: sor snang ba dang mthun par grags shing go bar
NK071(du)002:2852: mdzad do // sgra skad de dag thams cad kyang
NK071(du)002:2853: gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog brjod du med pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:2856: rgyud thams cad kyi mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa las /
NK071(du)002:2857: 'gro ba la phan bde dpag tu med pa dang
NK071(du)002:2858: ldan pa'i rgyu chos kyi sgra dbyangs yin pas gsung
NK071(du)002:2860: chos thams cad gdod nas dri mas ma gos pa'i
NK071(du)002:2861: chos nyid pad+ma lta bu'i ngang du ye nas gyur
NK071(du)002:2862: bas na / rnam par grol ba thar pa'i lam
NK071(du)002:2863: theg pa'i sgra skad dang 'dod chags la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:2864: dbang gis srid par sbyong ba 'khor ba'i sgra /
NK071(du)002:2865: sna tshogs pa ji skad brjod pa thams cad kyang
NK071(du)002:2866: grags stong skye ba med pa'i chos nyid las ma
NK071(du)002:2867: 'das pas gsung gi mchog ste brjod du med pa'i
NK071(du)002:2868: rang bzhin ye nas dag pa'i ngo bo nyid do
NK071(du)002:2869: // de'ang thar lam theg pa mtho dman gyi sgra skad thams cad dang /
NK071(du)002:2870: phyin ci log ngan 'gro gsum la sogs pa sems
NK071(du)002:2871: can ma lus pa thams cad kyi sgra skad kyang
NK071(du)002:2872: / grags stong skye ba med pa'i ngo bo ye
NK071(du)002:2873: nas byang chub pa'i gnas lugs bzang ngan gnyis su
NK071(du)002:2874: med pa'i rdo rje sangs rgyas kyi gsung brjod du
NK071(du)002:2877: gsung gi ngo bo brjod du med par bsdus pa
NK071(du)002:2878: de nyid kyi ngang las phyogs bcur sprul pa du
NK071(du)002:2879: mas chos kyi rnam grangs dpag tu med pa'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:2880: rnam par grags shing go bar mdzad do //
NK071(du)002:2881: chos kyi sgra grags pa de nyid ye nas ma
NK071(du)002:2882: chags pa'i ngang du gdul bya'i snang ba dang mthun
NK071(du)002:2883: par gsungs kyang / gsung ba nyid kyi dus na ngo bo brjod du med la /
NK071(du)002:2884: brjod du med pa'i gnas lugs de nyid brjod pa sna tshogs pa'i sgra /
NK071(du)002:2885: gdul bya kun la mthun par grags shing don so sor mjal ba nyid /
NK071(du)002:2886: dper na sgra'i dbyings rjod byed gcig de bzhin nyid sbrid sangs zhes pa la /
NK071(du)002:2887: la la dug gis sbrid pa sangs par go /
NK071(du)002:2888: la las 'dug stangs nyes pas sbrid pa sangs par go /
NK071(du)002:2889: la las rigs sngags kyis sbrid pa las sangs par go la la sogs pa bzhin du /
NK071(du)002:2890: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gcig gi sgra yis sems
NK071(du)002:2891: can so so'i bsam pa dang mthun pa'i chos so
NK071(du)002:2892: sor go ba / de ni gsung mchog dam pa
NK071(du)002:2893: sgra skad du snang ba thams cad kyi rgyal po
NK071(du)002:2894: sor go ba / yin no // lnga pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:2895: dang po theg pa so sor snang yang ngo bor gsung ba med par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2896: theg pa mtho dman bsam yas par snang ba dag kyang /
NK071(du)002:2897: chos nyid de bzhin nyid las gzhan du ci yang ma gsungs te /
NK071(du)002:2898: gdul bya'i snang ngor 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pas
NK071(du)002:2899: chos kyi rnam grangs su so sor thos pa de
NK071(du)002:2900: yang / theg pa lnga'i sgron ma rnams par bkod
NK071(du)002:2901: pa ji ltar bar de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab
NK071(du)002:2902: yan lag bcu gnyis la sogs pa kun brjod pa
NK071(du)002:2904: de bzhin nyid kyi gnas lugs kyis gzhal na sangs rgyas mthar thug chos kyi sku yin pas /
NK071(du)002:2905: des chos kyi rnam grangs cung zad kyang gsungs pa med do //
NK071(du)002:2906: gnyis pa thugs rje'i ngang las gsung gi rdo rje 'gro ba la snang tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:2907: brjod bya'i don yi ge med pa'i gnas lugs dang
NK071(du)002:2908: rjod byed kyi tshig tu snang ba bde bar gshegs
NK071(du)002:2909: pa'i rigs pa'i gsung 'gro bas thos pa de yang
NK071(du)002:2910: ljags kyi rtse mor sgra tshig rang mtshan par ma
NK071(du)002:2911: phyung yang / rgyal ba'i thugs rje gsung rang byung gi byin rlabs kyis /
NK071(du)002:2912: gdul ba'i 'gro ba la tshig don sna tshogs mos pa dang mthun par so sor gsal lo //
NK071(du)002:2913: gsum pa gsungs pa med kyang gsung bar snang ba'i dpe ni /
NK071(du)002:2914: de ltar sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang sems can
NK071(du)002:2915: gyi mos pa las snang ba'i chos kyi tshig don
NK071(du)002:2916: gdul bya'i rna ba la gsal ba de nyid gdod
NK071(du)002:2917: nas ma skyes pas gsung gi rdo rje'i mchog dam
NK071(du)002:2918: pa yin la / brjod pa med pa gdul bya
NK071(du)002:2919: la snang ba'i chos gyi de bzhin nyid gsung gi
NK071(du)002:2921: dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang
NK071(du)002:2922: rang snang ba ste dper na brag ca'i sgra de
NK071(du)002:2923: skyes bu dang brag dang de'i bar gang na'ang med
NK071(du)002:2924: bzhin du rkyen gyis ji skad brjod pa'i rnam pa
NK071(du)002:2926: gsung gsang ba'i snying po brjod du med pa las
NK071(du)002:2927: mos pa dang mthun par snang ba 'byung ba'i de
NK071(du)002:2928: kho na nyid nges pa las gsung gi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:2929: 'dus pa dang lha so so'i gsang sngags kyi rang
NK071(du)002:2930: bzhin bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2932: // don gnyis pa sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor dgod pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:2933: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i tshul mdor bstan pa dang //
NK071(du)002:2934: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:2936: gsung sngags kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)002:2937: lus kyi yan lag mgo la sogs pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:2938: lha'i dkyil 'khor du rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par
NK071(du)002:2939: byin gyis rlobs pa zhes bya ba 'di ched du
NK071(du)002:2940: brjod do // gnyis pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:2941: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:2942: lam mngon par sgrub bya'i phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa //
NK071(du)002:2943: 'bras bu ye shes mchog gi phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:2945: phung po khams dang skye mched kyis bsdus pa snang
NK071(du)002:2946: srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sku dang ye
NK071(du)002:2947: shes 'du 'bral med pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i ngo
NK071(du)002:2948: bo ye nas mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i
NK071(du)002:2949: bdag nyid me dang tsha ba ltar gnas pas chos
NK071(du)002:2950: thams cad kun tu bzang po byang chub mchog gi
NK071(du)002:2951: phyag rgya ye nas btab pa ste gnas lugs rang
NK071(du)002:2952: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de nyid la gsang
NK071(du)002:2953: ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa yi
NK071(du)002:2954: rgyal po / chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'i snying
NK071(du)002:2955: po'i phyag rgya btab pa na rang bzhin mnyam rdzogs
NK071(du)002:2956: chen po de las mi 'da' zhing nam yang 'pho
NK071(du)002:2957: 'gyur med pa'i ngang las gzhan du 'da' daka'o //
NK071(du)002:2960: de las byung ba spyi'i phyag rgya /
NK071(du)002:2961: de las 'phros pa lha so so'i phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:2963: spyir mgo ni de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK071(du)002:2964: lag pa g.yas mi bskyod pa /
NK071(du)002:2967: g.yas don yod grub pa'i ngo bor brjod cing /
NK071(du)002:2973: mathe'u chung las kyi rigs so //
NK071(du)002:2974: skabs 'dir rdo rje'i thal mo phyag rgya'i rgyu yin pas de nyid brjod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2975: lag pa g.yas mi bskyod pa'i sor mo lnga'i rtse
NK071(du)002:2976: la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor sran zlum tsam lnga'i steng
NK071(du)002:2977: du h+aum s+w+aa +aamm h+aa ste thabs kyi yi ge
NK071(du)002:2978: lnga dang / g.yon rin chen 'byung ldan gyi sor
NK071(du)002:2979: mo lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor sran ma'i g+aa'u
NK071(du)002:2980: tsam lnga'i steng du mum l+aam mum p+aam t+aam ste
NK071(du)002:2981: shes rab yum gyi yi ge lnga bkod de /
NK071(du)002:2982: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo lnga dang g.yon gyi
NK071(du)002:2983: sor mo lnga gnyis zung du sbyar te so sor
NK071(du)002:2984: sprad pa las / rdo rje'i thal mo sbyar bas
NK071(du)002:2985: lha so so'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu yin no
NK071(du)002:2986: sprad pa las / // de yang rang nyid lhar
NK071(du)002:2987: sgom pa sgyu ma 'ja' tshon lta bu ni phyag
NK071(du)002:2988: sprad pa las / // rgya chen po'o // phyag
NK071(du)002:2989: gi sor mo la yig 'bru sgom pa ni chos
NK071(du)002:2990: sprad pa las / // rgya chen po'o // kyi
NK071(du)002:2991: phyag rgya / de las rdo rje la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:2992: phyag mtshan sgom pa ni dam tshig gi phyag rgya
NK071(du)002:2993: sprad pa las / // rgya chen po'o // kyi
NK071(du)002:2994: phyag rgya / / de las g.yas g.yon bsgyur ba
NK071(du)002:2995: dang 'khyud pa ni las kyi phyag rgya yin no
NK071(du)002:2996: sprad pa las / // rgya chen po'o // kyi phyag rgya / / // gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)002:2997: g.yas kyi mdzub mo'i bsam pa de dang g.yon gyi
NK071(du)002:2998: gung mo'i m+aum bsam pa de gnyis rtse sbyar te
NK071(du)002:2999: / lhag ma g.yas g.yon gyi h+aum dang lam s+w+aa
NK071(du)002:3000: dang mam +aahdang p+y+aam ha dang tam te yi ge
NK071(du)002:3001: 'bru brgyad so sor bsnol nas rtse mo sprad pa
NK071(du)002:3002: / ni / rigs lnga'i rgyal ba kun dang ngo bo mnyam pa nyid du sbyor ba'i /
NK071(du)002:3003: dngos grub bde ba chen po tshe 'di nyid la sbyin par byed pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:3005: dang po rig lnga yab yum gyi phyag rgya las
NK071(du)002:3006: bdag nyid gtso bo'i skur bsgom pa phyag rgya chen
NK071(du)002:3007: po 'di'i ngang las g.yas rdo rje khu tshur gyi
NK071(du)002:3008: h'u las gzhan pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi nang du
NK071(du)002:3009: sbas nas gung mo bsgreng ba'i rgyab thugs kar bkan
NK071(du)002:3010: pa ni bcing ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:3011: gung mo h'u gi ngo bo bsgreng ba'i rtse mor
NK071(du)002:3012: nyi ma'i dbus su h+aum bsam pa ni bsam pa
NK071(du)002:3014: h+aum de nyid 'od du zhu ba las rdo rje
NK071(du)002:3015: rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gyur pa
NK071(du)002:3016: ni bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:3017: lag pa rdo rje'i khu tshur du byas nas zla
NK071(du)002:3018: ba'i steng gi yi ge nang du brtul cing dpa'
NK071(du)002:3019: bo 'bru lnga sbas te rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK071(du)002:3020: dril bu gsil zhing yum la 'khyud de 'khril ba'i
NK071(du)002:3021: tshul gyis yum gyi chos barla g.yon pa snang ba
NK071(du)002:3022: mtha' yas kyi steng du dril bu bzhag pas dku
NK071(du)002:3023: la brten pa ni yab kyis yum la mchod pa
NK071(du)002:3024: ste de nyid bca' ba las kyi phyag rgyar bshad
NK071(du)002:3025: do // de nas phyag rgya g.yon phyogs su bkrol
NK071(du)002:3026: te phyag mtshan yum gyi thugs kar thim pas mnyes
NK071(du)002:3027: par bsams shing h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika brjod pa ni brjod
NK071(du)002:3029: yum gyi phyag rgya yang bdag rdo rje dbyings phyug mar sgom pa ni phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK071(du)002:3030: de'i ngang la g.yon rdo rje khu tshur gyi zla
NK071(du)002:3031: ba'i mam las gzhan pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi nang
NK071(du)002:3032: du sbas nas gung mo thugs kar bkan pa ni
NK071(du)002:3033: dam tshig go / gung mo nyid m+aum gyi sgras
NK071(du)002:3034: brjod pa sgreng ba'i rtse mor zla ba'i steng du
NK071(du)002:3035: m+aum las dril gsil 'bar bar bsam pa ni bsam
NK071(du)002:3037: phyag g.yas nyi ma la dpa' bo 'bru lnga yab
NK071(du)002:3038: kyi barla g.yas pa'i steng du bzhag pa ni las
NK071(du)002:3040: yum gyi dbu yab la cung zad btud de zhal
NK071(du)002:3041: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal la blta ba
NK071(du)002:3042: ni bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:3043: de nas phyag rgya g.yon phyogs su bkrol te m+aum
NK071(du)002:3044: d+h+aa tu shwa ri brjod nas phyag mtshan yab kyi
NK071(du)002:3045: thugs kar thim par bsam pa ni brjod pa chos
NK071(du)002:3046: kyi phyag rgya'o // de'ang don rtags ni ye shes
NK071(du)002:3047: lnga'i mtshon byed du rdo rje dang 'khor lo la
NK071(du)002:3048: kyi phyag rgya'o // sogs pa'o // rnam pa de
NK071(du)002:3049: kho na bzhin gzhan rnams la'ang rgyas par sbyar ro
NK071(du)002:3050: kyi phyag rgya'o // sogs pa'o // // mi bskyod
NK071(du)002:3051: pa yab yum ni rang nyid der gsal ba'i ngang
NK071(du)002:3052: las g.yas rdo rje khu tshur gyi las gzhan pa'i
NK071(du)002:3053: yi ge 'bru bzhi nang du sbas nas mdzub mo
NK071(du)002:3054: bsgreng ba'i rgyab thugs kar bkan zhing /
NK071(du)002:3055: mdzub mo sgreng ba'i rtse mor 'od du zhu ba
NK071(du)002:3056: las 'khor lo 'od 'bar ba rtsi bzhir bsam zhing
NK071(du)002:3057: / g.yon rdo rje khu tshur gyi zla ba'i steng
NK071(du)002:3058: gi yi ge nang du btul te dpa' mo 'bru
NK071(du)002:3059: lnga sbas pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis dril bu
NK071(du)002:3061: yum la 'khyud cing 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon
NK071(du)002:3062: pa'i ste du bzhag pa ni chos la brten pa'o
NK071(du)002:3063: // g.yon pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi nang du sbas nas 'dzub mo'i rgyab thugs kar bkan te /
NK071(du)002:3064: l+aam sgreng ba'i rtse mor l+aam zhu ba las dril
NK071(du)002:3065: bu gsil cing 'od 'bar ba thugs kar bkan la
NK071(du)002:3066: / g.yas pa nyi ma la gnas pa'i yi ge
NK071(du)002:3067: 'bru lnga nang du bsdus nas las su 'khril ba
NK071(du)002:3068: ste yab kyi barla g.yas pa'i steng du bzhag cing
NK071(du)002:3069: yab la cung zad zhal phyogs pas btud de 'dzum
NK071(du)002:3071: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yub ni rang nyid der
NK071(du)002:3072: gsal ba'i yab kyi g.yas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi
NK071(du)002:3073: nang du sbas nas mthe bong thugs kar bkan zhing
NK071(du)002:3074: / s+w+aam sgreng ba'i rtse mor de zhu ba las rin chen 'od 'bar ba bsam la /
NK071(du)002:3075: g.yon gyi zla ba la gnas pa'i yi ge brtul
NK071(du)002:3076: te 'bru lnga sbas pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK071(du)002:3077: dril bu gsil ba 'dzin zhing yum la 'khyud nas
NK071(du)002:3078: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon
NK071(du)002:3079: pa'i steng du bzhag pa ni chos la brten pa'o
NK071(du)002:3080: // g.yon pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi nang du sbas nas mthe bong thugs kar bkan zhing /
NK071(du)002:3081: mthe bong m+aam sgreng ba'i rtse mor m+aam las dril
NK071(du)002:3082: gsil 'od 'bar ba bskyed de thugs kar bzung la
NK071(du)002:3083: / g.yas kyi nyi ma la gnas pa'i yi ge
NK071(du)002:3084: 'bru lnga nang du bsdus nas yab kyi barla g.yas
NK071(du)002:3085: pa'i steng du bzhag pa ni las su 'khril ba'o
NK071(du)002:3086: / // rnam 'gyur de nyid kyis yab la btud
NK071(du)002:3087: de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba ni yum gyi
NK071(du)002:3088: / // phyag rgya'o // 'od dpag med yab yum ni //
NK071(du)002:3089: der gsal ba'i ngang las yab kyi g.yas pa'i yi
NK071(du)002:3090: ge 'bru bzhi nang du sbas nas srin lag gi
NK071(du)002:3092: srin lag am sgreng ba'i rtse mor am zhu ba
NK071(du)002:3093: las pad+ma 'bar ba bsams te thugs kar phyag rgya
NK071(du)002:3094: bcas la g.yon gyi zla ba'i yi ge brtul cing
NK071(du)002:3095: 'bru lnga nang du sbas pa'i khu tshur gyi dril
NK071(du)002:3097: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos
NK071(du)002:3098: snang ba mtha' yas kyi steng du dril bu dku
NK071(du)002:3099: la brten pa'o // g.yon pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi
NK071(du)002:3100: nang du sbas nas srin lag gi rgyab thugs kar
NK071(du)002:3101: la brten pa'o // bkan zhing / srin lag pyam
NK071(du)002:3102: sgreng ba'i rtse mor pyam las dril gsil 'bar bar
NK071(du)002:3103: bsams pa thugs kar bzung la /
NK071(du)002:3104: g.yas kyi nyi ma la gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru
NK071(du)002:3105: lnga nang du bsdus te barla g.yas pa'i steng du
NK071(du)002:3106: bzhag pa ni las su 'khril bas yab la btud
NK071(du)002:3107: de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba'o //
NK071(du)002:3108: don grub yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)002:3109: der gsal bas g.yas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi nang
NK071(du)002:3110: du sbas nas mathe'u chung gi rgyab thugs kar bkan
NK071(du)002:3111: zhing / mathe'u chung h+aam sgreng ba'i rtse mor ha
NK071(du)002:3112: la ral gri 'bar bar bsams te thugs kar bzung
NK071(du)002:3113: zhing / la / g.yon gyi zla ba'i yi ge
NK071(du)002:3114: brtul cing 'bru lnga nang du sbas nas dril bu
NK071(du)002:3115: zhing / la / gsil zhing / yum la 'khril
NK071(du)002:3116: ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa'i steng du dril bu
NK071(du)002:3117: bzhag pa ni chos la brten pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3118: yang g.yon pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi sbas nas mathe'u chung gi rgyab thugs kar bkan zhing /
NK071(du)002:3119: mathe'u chung t+aam sgreng ba'i rtse mor tam las dril gsil 'bar ba thugs kar bzung la /
NK071(du)002:3120: g.yas kyi nyi ma gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru lnga
NK071(du)002:3121: nang du bsdus nas yab kyi barla g.yas pa'i steng
NK071(du)002:3122: du bzhag pa ni las su 'khril ba yin pas
NK071(du)002:3123: / yab la btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta ba'o //
NK071(du)002:3124: gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag
NK071(du)002:3125: rgya ni gong dang mtshungs pa las khyad par du
NK071(du)002:3126: rang rang gi sa bon las phyag mtshan du gyur
NK071(du)002:3127: pa'i tshul gyis yab kyi phyag g.yas kyis thugs kar
NK071(du)002:3128: 'dzin cing yum gyis phyag g.yon gyis thugs kar 'dzin
NK071(du)002:3129: la / yab kyi g.yon pas yum gyi barla g.yon pa'i chos la brtan cing /
NK071(du)002:3130: yum gyi g.yas pas yab kyi barla g.yas pa las la 'khril ba'o //
NK071(du)002:3131: de'ang m+aum las ut+pala mee las klu shing la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK071(du)002:3132: k+sham las rin chen gyi myu gu tra las ral gri 'od 'bar ba //
NK071(du)002:3136: h+aum las rin chen snye ma ste yab kyi phyag mtshan no //
NK071(du)002:3137: h+aum las gzugs mdzes par mtshon pa'i me long dang tra las rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK071(du)002:3138: h+r+ai las pi wam dang a las gar mkhan mchog
NK071(du)002:3139: nyid de rdo rje rtse gsum pa khyer nas spyi
NK071(du)002:3141: dza las me tog gi 'phreng ba dang h+aum las spos mchod ma spos kyi khang bu dang /
NK071(du)002:3142: bam las mar me dang ho las byug pa la
NK071(du)002:3143: sogs pa'i dung chos te yum gyi phyag mtshan no
NK071(du)002:3144: // yum gyi g.yas kyi yab kyi las te barla
NK071(du)002:3145: g.yas pa la 'khril zhing yab kyi g.yon pas yum
NK071(du)002:3146: gyi barla g.yon pa chos la brten cing /
NK071(du)002:3147: yab kyi dbu rnams yum la cung zad 'phyo zhing
NK071(du)002:3148: yum rnams yab la 'dud pa'i tshul du gnas pa
NK071(du)002:3149: ni / gong gi phyag rgya chen po bzhin du /
NK071(du)002:3150: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med pa chos kyi
NK071(du)002:3151: dbyings spros bral bde ba chen po nyid kyi ngang
NK071(du)002:3152: du 'khril ba'o // gsum pa sgo ba yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)002:3153: dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhi'i khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)002:3154: h+aum bzhi las n+ri mgo gdengs ba dang rdo rje rtse lnga pas gnon pa'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)002:3155: thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa chen po bsnams pas gnon pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3156: rdo rje rgya gram las kyis gnon pa ste g.yas
NK071(du)002:3157: pa bzhis phyar zhing g.yon pa bzhis yum la bsdigs
NK071(du)002:3158: mdzub kyi tshul du 'khyud pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3159: yum gyi phyag rgya ni phata bzhi las lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta ho //
NK071(du)002:3160: g.yon gyis bzungs nas g.yas rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK071(du)002:3161: yab la 'khyud pa ste sgo bzhir gnas pa sgo
NK071(du)002:3162: ba yab yum de dag kyang /
NK071(du)002:3163: yum gyis yab la 'dud cing yab kyis yum la
NK071(du)002:3164: dbu 'byo ba'i tshul gyis gnyis med du 'khril ba
NK071(du)002:3166: bzhi pa thub pa drug gi phyag rgya ni gdul bya'i dbang gis sna tshogs te /
NK071(du)002:3167: gcig tu nges pa dang grangs dang tshad med kyang /
NK071(du)002:3168: de dag gi rigs mdor bsdus na phyag rgya drug tu bstan pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:3169: gang zhe na rdo rje las /
NK071(du)002:3170: pi wam go cha gseg par sgrom //
NK071(du)002:3171: po ti me chur shes par bya /
NK071(du)002:3173: sa bon drug las phyag rgya de dag thugs kar 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3174: de dag la yum med pas thabs dang shes rab
NK071(du)002:3175: zung du ma 'brel lam snyam na yum ni gang
NK071(du)002:3176: du'ang dmigs pa med pa chos kyi dbyings spros pa'i
NK071(du)002:3178: lnga pa kun ba zangayaba yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)002:3179: kun tu bzang po phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag gi mthil
NK071(du)002:3180: las gdangs kyi 'char gzhir bstan pa'i phyir ye shes
NK071(du)002:3181: lnga'i 'od zer 'phro zhing zhabs rdo rje'i skyil krung
NK071(du)002:3182: mdzad pa'o // de'i yum du 'gyur ba kun tu
NK071(du)002:3183: bzang mo ni phyag rgya mnyam rdzogs te yab dang
NK071(du)002:3184: mtshungs shing zhabs gnyis pad+ma'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'o
NK071(du)002:3185: mdzad pa'o // // de ltar so so'i phyag rgya
NK071(du)002:3186: bstan pas gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te rigs
NK071(du)002:3187: so sor bsgrub pa na lha de dag gi phyag
NK071(du)002:3188: rgya yang phyogs gcig tu rdo rje la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:3189: rigs de'i phyag mtshan du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3190: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa lnga po'i phyag rgya sngar bstan pa de nyid dam /
NK071(du)002:3191: yang na rdo rje'i thal mo sbyar ba'i nyid tsam yang bcad par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3192: gsum pa 'bras bu ye shes kyi phyag rgyar don bsdu ba la gsum /
NK071(du)002:3193: rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi phyag rgya spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:3194: gnas skabs snang byed kyi phyag rgya bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:3195: mthar thug 'bras bu'i phyag rgyas 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3197: sems nyid gdod nas dag pa'i ngo bo phyag rgya
NK071(du)002:3198: chen po'i ngang las gang shar gyi rtog pa ye
NK071(du)002:3199: shes chen po'i tshogs mchog tu ye nas gnas pa
NK071(du)002:3201: de nyi bla ma'i drin gyis rtogs nas thabs gang
NK071(du)002:3202: snang gi yul dang shes rab 'dzin med du shar
NK071(du)002:3203: ba'i rig pa rang grol phyogs gcig tu ldan par
NK071(du)002:3205: lus ma bskyod yan lag ma bsgul yang 'gro 'dug dang spyod lam thams cad kun /
NK071(du)002:3206: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas shing 'dus pas /
NK071(du)002:3207: bcos ma'i phyag rgya bcing du med pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3209: dang po sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor spro ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3210: sngar phyag rgya spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin goms pa
NK071(du)002:3211: las de'i rtsal gong nas gong du sbyong ba'i phyir
NK071(du)002:3212: lus kyi yan lag la lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)002:3213: dang ldan par byas nas rtogs pa sogs dbyung ba
NK071(du)002:3214: ste de yang bdag nyid rnam snang yab yum du
NK071(du)002:3215: gsal ba las / yab kyi spyi bo mgrin pa
NK071(du)002:3216: snying ga lte ba gsang gnas rnams su mi bskyod
NK071(du)002:3217: pa 'od dpag med rnam snang rin chen 'byung ldan
NK071(du)002:3219: mig dang rna ba dang sna bug dang lce zur
NK071(du)002:3220: g.yas pa bzhi la sa'i snying po phyag rgya rdo
NK071(du)002:3221: rje nam mkha'i snying po spyan ras gzigs te thugs
NK071(du)002:3223: de bzhin du g.yon pa bzhi la byams pa sgrib
NK071(du)002:3224: sel kun bzang 'jam dpal te gsung gi sems dpa'
NK071(du)002:3225: bzhi'o // lag pa g.yas la gshin rje mthar byed /
NK071(du)002:3226: g.yon la shes rab mthar byed /
NK071(du)002:3227: rkang pa g.yon pa pad+ma mthar byed /
NK071(du)002:3228: g.yas la bges mthar byed de sgo ba bzhi'o //
NK071(du)002:3229: spyi gtsug mgrin pa ro stod lte ba gsang gnas
NK071(du)002:3230: rkang mthil drug ste lha nyi shu rtsa gsum mo
NK071(du)002:3231: // yum gyi spyi bo mgrin pa snying ga lte
NK071(du)002:3232: ba gsang gnas lngar sangs rgyas spyan gos dkar mo
NK071(du)002:3233: dbyings phyug ma m+aa ma k+ai sgrol ma ste yum
NK071(du)002:3234: // lnga'o // mig rna ba sna bug lce zur
NK071(du)002:3235: g.yon la rim pa bzhin sgeg mo phreng ma glu
NK071(du)002:3236: ma gar ma ste yul gyi lha mo bzhi'o //
NK071(du)002:3237: de bzhin du g.yas bzhi la bdug spos me tog
NK071(du)002:3238: mar me dri chab ma ste dus kyi lha mo
NK071(du)002:3239: bzhi'o // lag pa g.yon la lcags kyu g.yas la zhags pa /
NK071(du)002:3240: rkang pa g.yas la lcags sgrogs g.yon la dril bu ma ste sgo ma bzhi'o //
NK071(du)002:3241: de ltar yum la lha bcu bdun te /
NK071(du)002:3242: bsdoms pas bzhi bcu ni thabs lha ste rags pa
NK071(du)002:3243: dang phyi na gnas pas de skad ces brtags so
NK071(du)002:3244: // de'i steng du rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis
NK071(du)002:3245: te bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po de rnams la bslab
NK071(du)002:3246: // po / kun bzang yab yum ni rtsa ba'i lha nyid du bsdus so //
NK071(du)002:3247: gnyis pa sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor spro ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3248: bzhi bcu po de nyid kyi thugs kar rang dang
NK071(du)002:3249: 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'i re re gnas pa
NK071(du)002:3250: ni yan lag spros pa'i bdag nyid nang na gnas
NK071(du)002:3251: pa dang phra ba'i phyir shes rab kyi lha ste
NK071(du)002:3252: bzhi bcu'o // thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)002:3253: smos kyang rtsa ba'i yab yum gnyis las gzhan bzhi
NK071(du)002:3254: bcu po la sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3255: lha gsum gsum 'phro bar 'gyur bas brgya nyi shu
NK071(du)002:3256: bzhi bcu'o // dang / de re re la dbu
NK071(du)002:3257: rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga yod pas drug brgya sku
NK071(du)002:3258: gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha gsum yod pas
NK071(du)002:3259: sum brgya drug cu shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu
NK071(du)002:3260: po bsnan pas sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor te
NK071(du)002:3262: gsum pa sangs rgyas nyi khri chig stong gi dkyil 'khor gsal ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3263: sangs rgyas stong po de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog
NK071(du)002:3264: rnams snang yab yum dag gis mtshon pa rgyal ba
NK071(du)002:3265: rigs bzhi dang rgyal mchog kun tu bzang po la
NK071(du)002:3266: yang de bzhin du brtsis pas stong ste stong phrag
NK071(du)002:3267: drug go / de bzhin du sems dpa' yab yum
NK071(du)002:3268: cha brgyad dang sgo ba yab yum cha bzhi ste
NK071(du)002:3269: bcu gnyis la stong phrag bcu gnyis dang drug gi
NK071(du)002:3270: 'od 'phro 'bar ba ni thub pa drug ste yum
NK071(du)002:3271: med pas nyi khri chig stong sum brgya dang bcu
NK071(du)002:3272: gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3273: nyi khri bzhi stong du 'dod pa ni thub pa drug la yum yod par rlom pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:3274: bzhi pa sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dkyil 'khor la bslab pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3275: tshul de la sogs te sangs rgyas re re'ang nyi
NK071(du)002:3276: khri chig stong du bskyed pa lta bu bsam gyis
NK071(du)002:3277: mi khyab pa'i dkyil 'khor la bslab par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3278: bla ma rong pa ni phyag rgya chen po'i bdag
NK071(du)002:3279: nyid gcig la lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi yan
NK071(du)002:3280: lag dang ldan pas de nyid yan lag spro ba
NK071(du)002:3281: dag ste / de dag re re'ang sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya dang ldan pas /
NK071(du)002:3283: de lta bu dang ldan pa des phyag rgya ji
NK071(du)002:3284: snyed 'phro zhing sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ji ltar
NK071(du)002:3287: gtso bo la ji ltar ldan pa de bzhin du
NK071(du)002:3288: yan lag gi lha rnams la yang ldan par brtsis
NK071(du)002:3289: na phyag rgya brgya nyi shu 'byung bas /
NK071(du)002:3290: bcu gnyis drug gi 'od 'phro 'bar zhes 'chad do //
NK071(du)002:3291: snang byed kyi lha 'di rnams rnal 'byor snga ma
NK071(du)002:3292: goms stobs kyis 'bras bur bzhag la tshogs sgrub tu
NK071(du)002:3293: tshe dbang thob par byed pa'i rgyu yin pas lam
NK071(du)002:3294: du'ang bzhag go / gsum pa mthar thug gi phyag rgyas 'gro don mdzad pa'i tshul la lnga las /
NK071(du)002:3295: dang po gdul bya'i don du sna tshogs su ston pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:3296: lam du de ltar bsgoms pas sangs rgyas pa na
NK071(du)002:3297: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi yi sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK071(du)002:3298: khams bsam yas su gdul bya dpag tu med pa
NK071(du)002:3299: 'dul ba'i phyag rgya'i don rnams sangs rgyas dang 'khor
NK071(du)002:3300: los sgyur ba la sogs pa'i sku so sor ston
NK071(du)002:3302: gnyis pa bstan pa bzhin snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:3303: theg pa mtho ba sngags dang pha rol tu phyin
NK071(du)002:3304: pa dman pa nyan rang la sogs pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:3305: dang / lta spyod phyin ci log mu stegs byed rnams dang so so skye bo bsam yas dang /
NK071(du)002:3306: gdul bya zhi ba lha la sogs pa dang khro
NK071(du)002:3307: ba'i rang bzhin bdud dang gshin rje la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3308: tshogs chen po thams cad la /
NK071(du)002:3309: gang la gang 'dul so sor snang zhing mos pa dang mthun par byas te kun tu snang ngo //
NK071(du)002:3310: gsum pa sna tshogs su snang yang gcig las ma g.yos pa'i dpe ni /
NK071(du)002:3311: dper na zlos gar mkhan nyid gcig po de las
NK071(du)002:3312: g.yas rkyang g.yon bskum dang zhi khro du mar snang
NK071(du)002:3314: ye shes kyi lus ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:3315: gcig la dmigs pa'i tshul gyis ched du ma bkod
NK071(du)002:3316: kyang 'gro ba'i snang ba dang mthun par sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:3317: lhun grub tu thugs rjes ston par byed do //
NK071(du)002:3318: bzhi pa gdul bya'i dbang gis phyag rgya'i grangs ma nges par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3319: mdor na byang chub mchog dang bdud 'dul ba la sogs pa'i phyag rgya thams cad ni /
NK071(du)002:3320: 'di kho na'o zhes mtha' gcig tu brjod du med de /
NK071(du)002:3321: thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang gis gnyis dang sku
NK071(du)002:3322: gsung thugs kyis gsum du rnam par 'phro bar byed
NK071(du)002:3323: do // lus bskyod pa dang yan lag phyag rgyar 'gyur ba'ang de bzhin de /
NK071(du)002:3324: lnga pa gnas lugs phyag rgya chen por thams cad 'du ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3325: mdor na lus sgul ba dang yan lag bskyod pa thams cad kun /
NK071(du)002:3326: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas te /
NK071(du)002:3327: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i chos nyid du
NK071(du)002:3328: gnas pa nyid kyis 'di ni ma dag pa'i phyag
NK071(du)002:3329: rgya dang chos so zhes rdul tsam yang mi gnas
NK071(du)002:3330: shing gnas pa'ang min te lus lha ngag sngags sems
NK071(du)002:3331: chos nyid kyi phyag rgya'am dkyil 'khor du gnas pa'i
NK071(du)002:3332: phyir ro // de skad ces sgrib gnyis ma lus
NK071(du)002:3333: pa dag cing mkhyen rab phun sum tshogs pa mnga'
NK071(du)002:3334: ba'i mchog sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po nyid kyis
NK071(du)002:3336: ye shes kyi phyag rgya mchog tu gsang ba'i snying
NK071(du)002:3337: po chos nyid don gyi gnas lugs de kho na
NK071(du)002:3338: nyid nges pa las lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag
NK071(du)002:3339: thams cad ye nas dag pa'i dkyil 'khor du byin
NK071(du)002:3340: gyis brlabs nas rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya spros pa'i
NK071(du)002:3343: // don gsum pa de nyid gsal bar byed pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te //
NK071(du)002:3344: dkyil 'khor gsung tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3345: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3347: sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas de
NK071(du)002:3348: bzhin gshegs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:3349: kyis 'gro ba'i don la dgyes pa chen pos /
NK071(du)002:3350: kun tu bzang po nyid rdo rje gsang ba'i dam
NK071(du)002:3351: tshig gi dkyil 'khor bkod de dbang bskur ba'i rim
NK071(du)002:3352: pa la snyoms par zhugs pa ste yum dang lhan
NK071(du)002:3353: cig phyogs nas / ched du brjod pa 'di skad ces brjod do //
NK071(du)002:3355: dbang po rab mchog gi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba /
NK071(du)002:3356: dman pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba /
NK071(du)002:3357: gang du dbang bskur ba'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:3359: yum gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang yab kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK071(du)002:3361: dkyil 'khor dgod cing sbyin sreg bya ba /
NK071(du)002:3362: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i mchod pa 'bul ba /
NK071(du)002:3371: dang po gnas gang du dkyil 'khor dgod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3372: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde ba chen po ni shes
NK071(du)002:3373: shing rig par dka' bas shin tu phra ba'i don
NK071(du)002:3374: yin la / de nyid tshe 'dir mchog sgrub pa
NK071(du)002:3375: la med du mi rung ba'i dam tshig gi mchog
NK071(du)002:3376: yin la / yin pas na / de gang las
NK071(du)002:3377: skye zhing 'dzin pa phyag rgya mtshan ldan bde ba
NK071(du)002:3378: chen po'i lus rgyas pa'i phyag mthil yum mkha' rnam
NK071(du)002:3379: par dag pa nyid du dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:3380: yin la / yin pas na / gnas so //
NK071(du)002:3381: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni bde ba chen
NK071(du)002:3382: po gnyis su med pa'i ye shes sangs rgyas thams
NK071(du)002:3383: cad kyi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de nyid
NK071(du)002:3384: yin la / yin pas na / gnas so //
NK071(du)002:3385: / sor gyi tshad ni dga' ba dang mchog dga'
NK071(du)002:3386: dang dga' bral gyi dga' ba dang lhan cig skyes
NK071(du)002:3387: pa'i dga' ba bzhi yi tshad du bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3388: gsum pa thig gdab pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3389: gnas de'i rgyud sbyong ba ste de'ang 'bru lnga ste
NK071(du)002:3390: skye ba'i sa bon dug lnga ye shes su gnas
NK071(du)002:3391: pa dang spos lnga ste de dag nyid gnas su
NK071(du)002:3392: dag pa'i ye shes lnga dang rin chen lnga ni
NK071(du)002:3393: phung po lnga'o // snying po lnga ni sku lnga dang sman lnga ni rigs lnga dang /
NK071(du)002:3394: bdud rtsi lnga ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK071(du)002:3395: las lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i sems nyid rnam par
NK071(du)002:3396: dag cing 'od gsal ba ste de dag de ltar
NK071(du)002:3397: yin pa la yin par shes pas thams cad sangs
NK071(du)002:3398: rgyas pa'i rang bzhin rab tu shes par mnyam par
NK071(du)002:3399: byas la / de ltar rig pas yum gyi rgyud
NK071(du)002:3400: ye shes chen por gsal ba'i tshangs thig gi mchog
NK071(du)002:3402: bzhi pa ji ltar bri ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3403: yum mkha'i rang bzhin gzhal yas khang gi rnam par gnas pa de nyid gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK071(du)002:3404: dbus su lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi ngo bo nang rtsal bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3405: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)002:3406: de'i phyi rol gyi dbyibs gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi pa'i rnam pa can gyi /
NK071(du)002:3407: bar 'khyams pad+ma'i sgo khyud ldan pa la de ltar gsal bar bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3408: lnga pa mtshan ma dgod pa ni lha'i gnas der
NK071(du)002:3409: snyigs ma dkar dmar gyi ngo bo mtshon pa sen
NK071(du)002:3410: zlum tsam gyi nyi zla la /
NK071(du)002:3411: sran ma'i ga'u phyed pa tsa na'i 'bru tsam gyi pad+ma'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK071(du)002:3412: shin tu dwangs ma yungs 'bru tsam gyi ngo bo yi ge h+aum du gsal ba las /
NK071(du)002:3413: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i phyag rgya rdo rje
NK071(du)002:3414: til 'bru tsam du bri ba ste gsal gdab po
NK071(du)002:3416: phyag rgya'i g.yon phyogs su tshogs dang mchod pas brgyan
NK071(du)002:3417: par bya ba yang kha dog bsgyur ba'i gos bcos
NK071(du)002:3418: bu'i rnam dar dang ras ni sna tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:3419: dbu rgyan dang mgul rgyan la sogs pa'i rgyan sna
NK071(du)002:3420: tshogs dang do shal dang dra phyed la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:3421: 'i 'phreng ba sna tshogs dang ja dang chang la
NK071(du)002:3422: sogs pa'i btung ba sna tshogs dang sha dang thud
NK071(du)002:3423: dang phrum la sogs pa'i bro bas bskor zhing /
NK071(du)002:3424: shin tu snyan pa'i glu dang bstod pa'i tshig dang
NK071(du)002:3425: bcas pa'i skye bo'i rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i
NK071(du)002:3426: gar dang dung dang cha lang dang pi wang dang
NK071(du)002:3427: gling bu dang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3428: rol mo yi / sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)002:3429: pa'i tshogs kyis rab tu mchod cing gzhan yang mchod
NK071(du)002:3430: pa'i rkyen du gyur ba'i yum dang yid 'jo bar
NK071(du)002:3431: byed pa'i dga' ma dang na tshod gzhon nur gyur
NK071(du)002:3433: rol pa'i dga' ba bskyed pa dang reg bya'i dga' ba bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3434: mig gi dga' ba bskyed pa ste rnam pa gsum
NK071(du)002:3435: po ji ltar 'dod pa'i las bzhin mchod pas brgyan
NK071(du)002:3436: par bya'o // skabs 'di'i mchod pa'i gtso bo ni /
NK071(du)002:3437: bde ba ster bar byed pa'i yum phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi yul rnams yin par bzhed do //
NK071(du)002:3438: gnyis pa sbyin sreg gi las la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3439: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3440: khro bo'i sbyin sreg bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3442: las bzhi'i rim pas thab khung gi dbyibs kyang zlum
NK071(du)002:3443: po la sogs pa dang kha dog kyang dkar po
NK071(du)002:3444: la sogs pa so so'i mtshan nyid tshang ba dang
NK071(du)002:3445: ldan par / me lha'i rang bzhin mchod sbyin gsol
NK071(du)002:3446: ba'i zhal du gyur pa'i lto bar 'jig rten las
NK071(du)002:3447: 'das pa'i me lha bos te spyan drangs la zho
NK071(du)002:3448: zan dang mar khu la sogs pa bza' btung bro
NK071(du)002:3449: ba'i tshogs rnams kyis mchod cing /
NK071(du)002:3450: zhi ba la til rgyas pa la rin po che
NK071(du)002:3451: la sogs pa las bzhi'i mchod pa so so'i sngags
NK071(du)002:3452: dang ting nge 'dzin gyis rab tu sbyin par bya'o
NK071(du)002:3454: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg ji lta bar khro bo'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:3455: 'khor du yang thab dang lha'i mtshan nyid la sogs
NK071(du)002:3456: pa de bzhin du byas te /
NK071(du)002:3457: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i gnad shin tu phra
NK071(du)002:3458: zhing zab mo rnams la sbyangs pa yi rnal 'byor
NK071(du)002:3459: pas / lha'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas dag la'ang cho
NK071(du)002:3460: ga'i rim pa de bzhin du sbyin sreg gis mnyes
NK071(du)002:3461: pas / par bya'o // de'ang lha gang gis dkyil
NK071(du)002:3462: 'khor la las gang gis sbyin sreg ji ltar byed
NK071(du)002:3463: pa'i tshul rnams ni gnas skabs dang sbyar ba'i rang
NK071(du)002:3464: gi rig pas legs par dpag pa tsam du bya'o
NK071(du)002:3465: pas / par bya'o // // gnyis pa snang la
NK071(du)002:3466: rang bzhin med pa'i mchod pa 'bul ba la gnyis
NK071(du)002:3467: pas / par bya'o // // / ting nge 'dzin yid kyis mchod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3468: gsang ba bde ba chen po'i mchod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3470: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mchod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3471: de'i rdzogs rim don dam pa ye shes kyi mchod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3473: dang po ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod sprin bkod pa ni //
NK071(du)002:3474: dkyil 'khor la yid sprul gyis ji ltar mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK071(du)002:3475: rang gi sems kyi bkod pa'i yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i sprin phung 'khrig pa'i tshogs kyis /
NK071(du)002:3476: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK071(du)002:3477: rgyan stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams lta bur b+h+r+aum gyis gsal gdab bo //
NK071(du)002:3478: de'ang rgyan dang bkod pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:3479: khyab cing mnyen pa 'jam zhing reg na bde ba
NK071(du)002:3480: yi / sna tshogs rin po che yis gzhi khod snyoms pa las /
NK071(du)002:3481: rin po che sna tshogs kyis mig mngas ris su
NK071(du)002:3482: mdzes par bris shing lha'i nor bu sna tshogs kyi
NK071(du)002:3483: tshom bus rab tu brgyan pas phyogs kun tu 'khyim
NK071(du)002:3485: t+r+aam las 'dod dgu kun 'byung ba'i rin chen sna
NK071(du)002:3486: bdun gyi phung po 'od zer gyi d+r+wa ba 'bar
NK071(du)002:3487: ba'i ri bo lhun stug pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3488: kham las mtsho dang ldeng ka la sogs pa kha
NK071(du)002:3489: dog mdzes shing dbyibs legs ba'i rdzing bu ro bro
NK071(du)002:3490: ba'i mchog bsil ba la sogs pa'i yan lag brgyad
NK071(du)002:3491: ldan gyi chus yongs su gang ba me tog gis
NK071(du)002:3492: khebs shing bya skad snyan par sgrogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3493: b+h+r+aum las rin chen gyi khang pa dbyibs dang kha
NK071(du)002:3494: dog dang bkod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pas brgyan
NK071(du)002:3495: pa rab tu mang po dang /
NK071(du)002:3496: am las skyed mos tshal gyi gzhir rin po che'i
NK071(du)002:3497: rgyan phreng dang lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing ljon pa'i
NK071(du)002:3498: tshal gos dang nor bu sna tshogs kyis dra bas
NK071(du)002:3499: dpyangs pa dang / h+r+aihls sgra skad thams cad glu
NK071(du)002:3500: dbyangs snyan pa dang bstod pa dang shis pa brjod
NK071(du)002:3501: pa la sogs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra rang
NK071(du)002:3502: dpyangs pa dang / byung ba dang / am las
NK071(du)002:3503: gos kyi rnam pa dang mchod pa'i yo byad bla
NK071(du)002:3504: bre dang rgyal mtshan dang stod g.yogs la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3505: na bza' sna tshogs dang rin po che'i gdugs dang
NK071(du)002:3506: dpyangs pa dang / byung ba dang / / t+r+aam
NK071(du)002:3507: las dbu rgyan dang mgul rgyan dang do shal dang
NK071(du)002:3508: dpung rgyan dang se mo do la sogs pa rgyan
NK071(du)002:3509: gyi bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3510: o las ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa'i bza' ba
NK071(du)002:3511: sna tshogs dang bdud rtsi'i btung ba'i mchog rnams dang
NK071(du)002:3512: / h+aum las sems can thams cad kyi lus dang
NK071(du)002:3513: rang rang la ji ltar 'os pa gos dang rgyan
NK071(du)002:3514: la sogs pas mdzes par brgyan pa yi /
NK071(du)002:3515: lha dang lha mo rdul phra ba snyed kyi grangs dang mnyam pa thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)002:3516: rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar dang rol mo'i
NK071(du)002:3517: glu dbyangs la sogs pa bsam yas kyis mnyes par
NK071(du)002:3518: byed pa'o // de lta bu'i mchod pa'i sprin gyis
NK071(du)002:3519: phyogs bcu'i nam mkha'i khams ji snyed pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:3521: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings kyis
NK071(du)002:3522: bsdus pa gzhi lam 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du gyur
NK071(du)002:3523: to cog kun la mchod sprin de dag gis re
NK071(du)002:3525: gnyis pa tshul ji ltar 'bul ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3526: skal ldan rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i khyad par gyis /
NK071(du)002:3527: rim gyis sam yang na cig car du //
NK071(du)002:3528: rgya che ba chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par sbyong zhing 'bul lo //
NK071(du)002:3529: gnyis pa de'i rdzogs rim don dam ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3530: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa la dngos zhen spang
NK071(du)002:3531: ba'i phyir mchod sprin de dag kyang rang gi sems
NK071(du)002:3532: tsam las gang du'ang grub pa med la /
NK071(du)002:3533: sems de yang nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin gang
NK071(du)002:3534: la'ang mi gnas shing spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang
NK071(du)002:3535: bral ba'i ngang la mchod bya mchod byed mchod pa
NK071(du)002:3536: gsum ka'i ngo bo ma grub pa'i tshul gyis mchod
NK071(du)002:3537: pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom mo //
NK071(du)002:3538: gnyis pa gsang ba chen po'i mchod pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3539: thabs bde ba chen po'i mchod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:3540: shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3545: las kyi phyag rgya shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:3546: gsal bar ldan ma'am de dang mi ldan na rnal
NK071(du)002:3547: 'byor pas lhar bskyed cing mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab
NK071(du)002:3548: pa la sogs pa'i tshogs byin gyis brlabs la /
NK071(du)002:3549: pad+ma'i rtser yungs 'bru tsam gyi dwangs ma dkar dmar dkyil 'khor du bskyed de /
NK071(du)002:3550: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten thams cad 'phags pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis yungs 'brur gzhugs pa'i tshul du /
NK071(du)002:3551: dbyings nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dpag tu med pa
NK071(du)002:3552: pad+ma'i khyams su spyan drangs shing bstiim la sbyor ba'i
NK071(du)002:3553: brdas bskul te rol pa'i bde bas mchod par bya'o
NK071(du)002:3554: // de'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mnyes nas dngos
NK071(du)002:3555: grub chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)002:3556: mchog gi go 'phang thob par bsam mo //
NK071(du)002:3557: gnyis pa de'i phan yon la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3560: dang po la gnyis las sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes
NK071(du)002:3561: pa ni bde ba'i bdag nyid chen po de yis
NK071(du)002:3562: yum mkha'i dkyil 'khor la mchod pa yis /
NK071(du)002:3563: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad mnyes par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:3564: yang bdag nyid chen po rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:3565: la rol pa'i bde bas mchod pa yis khams dang
NK071(du)002:3566: skye mched ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK071(du)002:3567: bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa'i lha rnams mnyes par
NK071(du)002:3568: 'gyur ro // yang yab kyis yum yum gyis yab
NK071(du)002:3569: la bdag nyid chen po'i mchod rdzas des mchod pas
NK071(du)002:3570: thabs dang shes rab kyi lha rnams mnyes par 'gyur
NK071(du)002:3571: ba ste phyi nang gsang ba gsum du shes par
NK071(du)002:3572: 'gyur ro // bya'o // gnyis pa 'gro ba thams cad tshim pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3573: de ltar bde ba'i rol pas lus snang ba'i grong
NK071(du)002:3574: khyer 'dod pa'i srid pa ngag phyed snang gi grong
NK071(du)002:3575: khyer gzugs kyi srid pa yid mi snang ba'i grong
NK071(du)002:3576: khyer gzugs med pa'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK071(du)002:3577: tshor ba dang rtog tshogs kyi 'gro ba thams cad
NK071(du)002:3578: la / ye shes chen po'i dga' ba bzhi dang
NK071(du)002:3579: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid bzhi dang spros pa
NK071(du)002:3580: dang bral ba'i 'od gsal chen pos khyab par 'gyur
NK071(du)002:3581: la / ro // gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3582: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin brtan pa yis /
NK071(du)002:3583: de'i 'bras bu phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)002:3584: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mnyes shing /
NK071(du)002:3585: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams la thugs rjes gzigs pa'i ye shes dam pa mngon du 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:3586: yang na sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor phung
NK071(du)002:3587: po khams dang skye mched lhar gsal ba mthar thug
NK071(du)002:3588: pa dang sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor
NK071(du)002:3589: mngon du gyur pa zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3590: gnyis pa shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3591: de ltar yab yum gnyis su med par snyoms par zhugs pas nyon mongs pa'i 'dzin zhen dang /
NK071(du)002:3592: tha mal gyi rnam rtog rang sar dag par bya
NK071(du)002:3593: ba'i phyir rang dang yum gyi lus dang ngag dang
NK071(du)002:3594: sems dang bde bas mtshon pa'i phyi nang gi chos
NK071(du)002:3596: gzung ba'i yul gang na'ang mi gnas shing 'dzin pa'i sems gang du'ang mi dmigs te /
NK071(du)002:3597: med bzhin du snang ba mig yor lta bu'i tshul du gnyis su med par sbyor ba yis /
NK071(du)002:3598: dbyings skye ba med pa'i nam mkha' la ni sems
NK071(du)002:3599: nyid 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes nam mkha' bsgom
NK071(du)002:3600: zhing dbyer med pa'i chos nyid don gyi ngo bor
NK071(du)002:3601: mnyam par bzhag cing rol par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3602: gsum pa 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i tshul la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3606: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug pa ni de bzhin nyid
NK071(du)002:3607: kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa nas bzung ste cho
NK071(du)002:3608: ga'i sngon du bya dgos pa kun byas nas tshogs
NK071(du)002:3609: dang rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug rdo rje slob dpon
NK071(du)002:3610: nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi rig pas dkyil 'khor la
NK071(du)002:3612: slob ma 'jug pa ni slob dpon zhugs pa de
NK071(du)002:3613: nas slob ma rnams 'jug pa'i chos bcu bdun gyis
NK071(du)002:3615: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3617: blos rim pa dang sbyar nas dbang bskur ba dngos so //
NK071(du)002:3619: dang po yon 'bul ba dngos ni /
NK071(du)002:3620: 'jug pa'i chos rnams sngon du song ba de nas
NK071(du)002:3621: rigs kyi bu skal ba mchog dang ldan pa des
NK071(du)002:3622: bla ma la rgyal srid yul 'khor dang bcas pa
NK071(du)002:3623: dang ni rang gi lus dang /
NK071(du)002:3624: bu dang chung ma dang nor gyi dbyig gser dngul la sogs pa'i rin po che sna tshogs te /
NK071(du)002:3625: de rnams kyi gnyis gnyis yod na rab tu gces
NK071(du)002:3626: shos de dang mdor na rang gis yid la 'thad
NK071(du)002:3627: pa'i dngos po rnams dbul lo //
NK071(du)002:3628: gnyis pa phan yon ni rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug
NK071(du)002:3629: rdo rje slob dpon la 'dod pa'i longs spyod rnam
NK071(du)002:3631: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin na /
NK071(du)002:3632: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor yi dam gyi lha mchod pa lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK071(du)002:3633: des dam tshig dang sdom pa nyams pa'i nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur ba kho na'o //
NK071(du)002:3634: gnyis pa blo'i rim pa dang sbyar nas dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK071(du)002:3635: dad pa dang brtson pa'i brtul zhugs rab tu rtogs pa'i skal yod par shes na /
NK071(du)002:3636: de la phan pa'i dbang bcu dang nus pa'i dbang lnga'o //
NK071(du)002:3637: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya zhing /
NK071(du)002:3638: slob dpon gyis lhag pa'i snying rjes slob ma'i rgyud chud ma zos par gzung bar bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3639: gal te skal ba med na mi sbyin pa'am phan
NK071(du)002:3640: dbang tsam bskur gyis nus dbang mi sbyin te nyes
NK071(du)002:3641: pa chen por 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:3642: gnyis pa yab kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba ni //
NK071(du)002:3643: yum gyi dkyil 'khor du gsang ba dang shes rab
NK071(du)002:3644: ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba de las gzhan pa'i
NK071(du)002:3645: tshul yab kyi rdo rje'i rtse las dbang blang bar
NK071(du)002:3646: bstan pa ni / yang na yab kyi thal mo mnyam bzhag gi tshul gyis rab tu bsnol nas /
NK071(du)002:3647: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i rang bzhin du gsal
NK071(du)002:3648: te ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)002:3650: gu ya badz+ra gyi dkyil 'khor mdzub gang ba'i tshad du yang /
NK071(du)002:3651: bde ba'i thabs la mkhas pas dbang bskur ba'i cho
NK071(du)002:3652: ga ji bzhin du dwangs mas bu la dbang bskur
NK071(du)002:3653: bar bya'o // gnyis pa dman pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur tshul la gsum //
NK071(du)002:3660: chen po bri ba'i cho ga'o //
NK071(du)002:3663: sa'i cho ga ni rab mchog gi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba las tshul gzhan /
NK071(du)002:3664: yang na sa gzhi sa'i cho gas rab tu mnyam pa la bri'o //
NK071(du)002:3665: de'ang sngar ma dag pa'i sa gzhi phyis dag par
NK071(du)002:3666: byed pa ma yin te ye nas sa sbyangs zin
NK071(du)002:3667: pas phyis gsal 'debs pa'i tshul gyis sbyong ba yin
NK071(du)002:3668: no // gnyis pa bri ba dngos ni /
NK071(du)002:3669: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chung ngu'i khru gang gi tshad du bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3670: chung ngu'i 'bring yang na lus gang gi tshad du ste 'dam gang ngo //
NK071(du)002:3671: chung ngu'i chen po yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad tsam la /
NK071(du)002:3672: mi rus la sogs pa'i phur bu ni dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:3673: gyi dbus su 'gying phur sor bzhi la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:3674: dang cha dbye ba'i don du ras bal lam pad+ma'i
NK071(du)002:3675: rgyus pa'am dur khrod kyi skra la sogs pa'i srad
NK071(du)002:3676: bu khrun du dkyiil 'khor nyis 'gyur yod pa dang
NK071(du)002:3677: rigs tha dad pa mtshon pa'i don du kha dog
NK071(du)002:3678: ma 'dres pa'i tshon gyi phye ma lnga la sogs
NK071(du)002:3679: pa dang / las sgrub pa'i don gos dang rgyan
NK071(du)002:3680: bzang po'i mdzes pa'i yid du 'ong ba'i grogs las
NK071(du)002:3681: kyi phyag rgya lo bcu drug lon pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3682: srad bu'i sna nas grogs des bzung la ye shes
NK071(du)002:3683: dang las kyi thig gnyis gdab pa'i cho ga phun
NK071(du)002:3684: sum tshogs pa / dkyil 'khor gyi las la mkhas
NK071(du)002:3685: par ldan pa chen po rdo rje slob dpon gyis
NK071(du)002:3686: lus sems ma yengs par rab tu bsgrims te bya'o
NK071(du)002:3687: sum tshogs pa / // gnyis pa 'bring la 'bring
NK071(du)002:3688: gi chung ngu yang na khru ni bcu drug pa
NK071(du)002:3690: khru nyi shu pa'am 'bring gi chen po khru nyi
NK071(du)002:3692: de la snga ma bzhin thig gdab par bya ste
NK071(du)002:3693: thig tshon la rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rnam pa lnga
NK071(du)002:3694: po rnams bsgom zhing zhu ba las byung ba'i ye
NK071(du)002:3695: shes lnga'i thig tshon du bsams te thig gdab cing
NK071(du)002:3696: tshon bkye nas lha'i gnas so sor sku tsag li
NK071(du)002:3697: sogs dang gsung yig 'bru dang thugs phyag mtshan rdo
NK071(du)002:3698: rje la sogs pa'i mtshan ma dang ldan pa'i gzugs
NK071(du)002:3699: kyang lha so so'i gnas su dgod par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:3701: chen po'i chung ngu yang na rgyang grags gcig gam chen po'i 'bring dpag tshad dam /
NK071(du)002:3702: chen po'i chen po nam mkha' dbyings ni bsam yas
NK071(du)002:3703: par ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor dngos su sprul
NK071(du)002:3704: pa'am sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor rigs sna tshogs pa
NK071(du)002:3706: sems can gyi rgyud la sku lnga ye shes lnga'i
NK071(du)002:3707: rang ye gdod ma nas gnas kyang ma rig pas
NK071(du)002:3708: bsgribs nas ma mthong ba'i rmongs pa rnams la bstan
NK071(du)002:3709: pa'i phyir tshon gyi kha dog kyang dkar po lta
NK071(du)002:3710: bu re re la'ang dkar ser dkar dmar dkar ljang
NK071(du)002:3711: dkar sngo dkar po nyid dang sngar phye ba bzhin
NK071(du)002:3712: du gzhan bzhi la phye bas nyi shu rtsa lnga'am
NK071(du)002:3713: / yang na dkar ser dmar ljang mthig ga lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya /
NK071(du)002:3714: ji ltar bri ba ni mthong ba brgyud pa'i lag
NK071(du)002:3715: len rnam par bzhag pas rgyas 'bring bsdus pa la
NK071(du)002:3716: sogs pa'i rnam bzhag ni skabs 'dir 'dul ba'i cho
NK071(du)002:3717: ga ste de'i lugs bzhin du dagye'o //
NK071(du)002:3718: de'ang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa
NK071(du)002:3719: gsum ni gang zag gi blo dang 'byor bas phye
NK071(du)002:3720: ba ste 'khor los bsgyur ba sogs la dpag tshad
NK071(du)002:3722: phal pa'i 'byor pa mchog la 'bring po dang /
NK071(du)002:3723: gzhan la chung ngu gsungs shing chen po'i chen po
NK071(du)002:3724: ni slob ma mchog la 'phags pa'i bla mas dbang
NK071(du)002:3725: bskur ba'i blo yi rim pas che ba yin no
NK071(du)002:3726: // gzhung gsum po'ang ma 'khrugs par bshad do //
NK071(du)002:3727: chung ngu'i skabs su thig gi rim pa gsungs shing /
NK071(du)002:3728: 'bring gi skabs su thig tshon byin gyis brlabs te bri ba la mtshan ma dgod thabs gsungs la /
NK071(du)002:3729: rgyas pa'i skabs su tshon dgye ba'i rim pas bri thabs rdzogs par gsungs pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:3730: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:3733: gnyis su med par bstim pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3735: sems bskyed pa dang de bzhin nyid la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3736: ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo mtha' yas pa'i mchog
NK071(du)002:3737: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mthas gtug pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK071(du)002:3738: pa'i nang du / lha so so'i gnas su rang
NK071(du)002:3739: rang gi yi ge tha la sogs pa'am tshon gyi
NK071(du)002:3740: thig le sku mdog dang mthun pa'i gdan nam h+aum
NK071(du)002:3741: dang mum la sogs pa snying po 'am rdo rje
NK071(du)002:3742: dang 'khor lo la sogs pa phyag rgya'am gang yang
NK071(du)002:3743: rung ba las lha so so'i sku gsung thugs yongs
NK071(du)002:3744: su rdzogs pa dang ldan par bskyed pa ni rdul
NK071(du)002:3745: tshon gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:3746: dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs pa ste de'i dngos
NK071(du)002:3747: grub ya mtshan pa gnas skabs thun mong gi las
NK071(du)002:3748: bzhi dang rmad po che mthar thug lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:3749: 'grub par 'gyur ba ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dam
NK071(du)002:3751: sa dang shing la sogs pa las sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar byas pa yang /
NK071(du)002:3752: gdul bya'i skal ba dang mthun par rnam par grol
NK071(du)002:3753: ba'i rim pa byang chub gsum so sor thob par
NK071(du)002:3754: 'gyur na / rnam par dag pa'i ye shes te ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyangs pas /
NK071(du)002:3755: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal ba la
NK071(du)002:3756: sangs rgyas 'grub pa smos ci dgos te sems 'di
NK071(du)002:3757: nyid gdod nas sangs rgyas yin pa la gsal btab
NK071(du)002:3758: pa tsam gyis 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:3759: gnyis pa spyan drangs ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3760: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag nyid che ste gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK071(du)002:3761: gang du'ang mi dmigs shing spros pa thams cad dang
NK071(du)002:3762: bral ba ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor chos sku'i ngang
NK071(du)002:3763: las / ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor ji ltar 'dod pa thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK071(du)002:3764: gnyis pa gnyis su med par bstim pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3765: bskyed pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gzhi
NK071(du)002:3766: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis po
NK071(du)002:3767: de rang snang gi ngo bo dbyer med du gnas
NK071(du)002:3768: te rang bzhin dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK071(du)002:3769: bskyed pa ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs
NK071(du)002:3770: pa de nyid 'jug cing bstim pa'i mtshan nyid kyis
NK071(du)002:3771: de gnyis chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin du mnyam
NK071(du)002:3772: par sbyor bas / phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun nas 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)002:3773: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sngon gyi smon lam gyis
NK071(du)002:3774: bsnyen par mdzad pa'i 'bras bu phrin las kyi dkyil
NK071(du)002:3775: 'khor de nyid thugs rjes byon nas dam tshig pa'i
NK071(du)002:3776: dkyil 'khor la rab tu rdzogs par 'jug cing nye
NK071(du)002:3777: ba'i sras su dgongs par gyur pa'i phyir spyan drangs
NK071(du)002:3778: te bstim pa ni dam tshig gi mchog yin no
NK071(du)002:3779: // gsum pa dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la gsum /
NK071(du)002:3780: dngos grub sems las byung ba'i 'thad pa dgod pa /
NK071(du)002:3781: de nyid ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:3782: thabs des grub pa'i 'bras bu brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3784: dang po dpe ni lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing dang
NK071(du)002:3785: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang gzhan
NK071(du)002:3786: yang phyi rol gyi dngos por snang ba las 'dod
NK071(du)002:3787: dgu 'byung ba kun la ya mtshan dang yon tan
NK071(du)002:3789: de dag sems la ma ltos par phyi rol na
NK071(du)002:3790: bden ba'i rdzas gang yang yod pa ma yin te
NK071(du)002:3791: / rang gi sems kun gzhi la gnas pa'i bsod
NK071(du)002:3792: nams kyi rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu brtan pa
NK071(du)002:3793: nyid kyi snang ba der smin cing rkyen de dag
NK071(du)002:3794: dang 'phrad nas 'dod dgu 'byung bar snang ba yin
NK071(du)002:3795: / no // gnyis pa don ni de bzhin du
NK071(du)002:3796: sems nyid don gyi gnas lugs la sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)002:3797: yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor ngo mtshar ba'i
NK071(du)002:3798: cho 'phrul ya mtshan rmad kyi chos dang gnas skabs
NK071(du)002:3799: kyi dngos grub phrin las bzhi la sogs pa thob
NK071(du)002:3800: / no // pa rnams kyang / bdag gis phar
NK071(du)002:3801: bsgrod nas de'i steng du phyin pa 'am phyogs gzhan
NK071(du)002:3802: zhig na yod pa'i tshur bkug nas 'ong ba ma
NK071(du)002:3803: / no // pa rnams kyang / yin te /
NK071(du)002:3804: 'di ltar phyi snod gzhal yas khang nang bcud lha
NK071(du)002:3805: dang lha mo rang nyid rgyal ba'i skur gsal ba
NK071(du)002:3806: la sogs pa'i thabs la brten pa'i shes rab spros
NK071(du)002:3807: pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba la goms pa
NK071(du)002:3808: / no // pa rnams kyang / yin te /
NK071(du)002:3809: nyid kyis / bskyed rdzogs de lta bu yi ngang
NK071(du)002:3810: du ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor lhun grub tu 'byung
NK071(du)002:3811: / no // pa rnams kyang / yin te /
NK071(du)002:3812: nyid kyis / ba yin no // de'ang rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:3813: spros pa dang bral ba'i shes rab chos kyi dbyings
NK071(du)002:3814: kyi de bzhin nyid chos sku'i ngang las /
NK071(du)002:3815: thabs kyi phyag rgyar lhun stug po bkod par gzugs
NK071(du)002:3816: sku'i dkyil 'khor rang snang du bkod pa ni lhun
NK071(du)002:3817: gyis grub pa'i ye shes kyi rol par gyur pa'i
NK071(du)002:3818: phyir / chos sku'i ye shes la ni gzugs sku'i ye shes rol ba'i ngang las /
NK071(du)002:3819: gdul bya'i 'jig rten du snang ba dang mthun par
NK071(du)002:3820: sprul pa'i sku'i ye shes rol pa nyid kyang de
NK071(du)002:3821: las ma g.yos bzhin du snang ba chu zla dang
NK071(du)002:3823: gsum pa des gzhan don 'byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:3824: sems can gyi mos pa dang mthun par rgyal ba
NK071(du)002:3825: mngon sum du 'byung zhing 'gro ba sdug bsngal las
NK071(du)002:3826: skyob pa dang / lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:3827: snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i byin rlabs las sa bcu'i
NK071(du)002:3828: sems dpa' la rang bzhin sprul sku rigs lnga'i sangs
NK071(du)002:3829: rgyas su ston pa'am thugs rje dang 'gro ba'i rang
NK071(du)002:3830: sems bsod nams goms pa'i mthu las nor bu dang
NK071(du)002:3831: dpag bsam shing gi dpe de bzhin te /
NK071(du)002:3832: bden par ma grub bzhin du sprul pa'i sku'i 'gro
NK071(du)002:3833: don gyi bya ba byed nus pa'i tshul ni thugs
NK071(du)002:3834: rje'i gzi byin gyis phrin las kyi rol pa rang
NK071(du)002:3836: de nyid ye shes kyi sgyu ma sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)002:3837: rdo rje yi rang bzhiin can chos thams cad la
NK071(du)002:3838: mnga' dbang bsgyur bas btsan po'i mchog go /
NK071(du)002:3839: gnyis pa de nyid ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:3840: lam ma nor bar ston pa bla ma dge ba'i
NK071(du)002:3841: bshes gnyen gyis zin pa de las zab mo'i dbang
NK071(du)002:3842: thob pa dam tshig dang sdom pa la gnas pa
NK071(du)002:3843: bsgrub pa'i man ngag la mkhas pa brtson 'grus phun
NK071(du)002:3844: sum tshogs pas bsgrub nus pa ste /
NK071(du)002:3845: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i cho ga lnga ni rdzogs par byas shing /
NK071(du)002:3846: bsgrub pa'i gnas bar chad med cing yid dang mthun
NK071(du)002:3847: pa grogs mtshan nyid tshang zhing skal ba bzang ba
NK071(du)002:3848: 'tsho ba'i yo byad mtha' gnyis su ma lhung zhing
NK071(du)002:3849: log 'tsho med pa dngos grub kyi rdzas tshang zhing
NK071(du)002:3850: nyams pa med pa dam tshig gi rdzas tshogs shing
NK071(du)002:3852: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i mthun rkyen gyi yo byad lnga ni yongs su rdzogs par ldan zhing /
NK071(du)002:3857: 'phro 'du'i de kho na nyid de sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas /
NK071(du)002:3858: spyir lta ba dang dam tshig ma nyams shing bye
NK071(du)002:3859: brag tu bsgrub pa'i mthun rkyen tshogs pa las ma
NK071(du)002:3860: nyams par sgrub pa la 'jug par dang zhugs nas
NK071(du)002:3861: sgrub pa la nyid mtshan gnyid dang snyoms las spangs
NK071(du)002:3862: te rab tu brtson na myur du 'grub cing mi
NK071(du)002:3864: gsum pa thabs des grub pa'i 'bras bu brjod pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:3865: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK071(du)002:3867: dbang po dang brtson pa rab kyis zhag ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK071(du)002:3868: 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis sam tha mas zla
NK071(du)002:3869: ba bcu bzhi'am shin tu rtul pos kyang zla ba
NK071(du)002:3870: bcu drug gis / tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rigs kyi dam pa 'grub bo //
NK071(du)002:3871: tshe dbang thob pa de nyid kyi rten la tshe
NK071(du)002:3872: bcu drug mthud pa'i lo grangs sam dus na sangs
NK071(du)002:3873: rgyas te skye ba bcu drug tshun chad kyis /
NK071(du)002:3874: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa de ni thob po //
NK071(du)002:3875: gnyis pa mthar thugs kyi 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la gsum /
NK071(du)002:3876: lhun stug po bkod par rang snang sku dang ye shes su grub tshul /
NK071(du)002:3877: de nyid dbyings chos sku'i zhing na nang gsal spros pa dang bral bar bzhugs tshul /
NK071(du)002:3878: slar yang gdul bya'i 'jig rten du sprul skur 'char tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:3880: dang po mngon par byang chub pa'i tshul ni //
NK071(du)002:3881: dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sems nyid sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:3882: pa'i ye shes spros pa med pa'i thig le grub
NK071(du)002:3883: pas bsal med pa de nyid la /
NK071(du)002:3884: glo bur kun brtags pa'i dri ma rang sar dag
NK071(du)002:3885: pas zad pa dang skye ba med pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:3886: brnyes te dbyings der gnyis su med par chu la
NK071(du)002:3887: chu bzhag pa lta bu'i ye shes ro gcig tu
NK071(du)002:3888: gyur pa'i thig le nyid snang ba ni mngon par
NK071(du)002:3889: byang chub pa dang mi 'gyur rdo rje dang zhi
NK071(du)002:3890: ba chos sku dang gsal ba longs sku dang ye
NK071(du)002:3891: shes sprul pa'i sku lngar lhun gyis grub pas bsam
NK071(du)002:3892: gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa'i mchog /
NK071(du)002:3893: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:3894: kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin dang gnyis
NK071(du)002:3895: su med par mngon par rdzogs par byang chub pa'i
NK071(du)002:3896: mchog gi dngos grub brnyes pa zhes bya'o /
NK071(du)002:3897: gnyis pa zhing khams ji ltar snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:3898: de'i tshe lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams rang
NK071(du)002:3899: bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing chos kyi dbyings dang
NK071(du)002:3900: nam mkha'i mtha' klas par khyab pas bsam yas pa'i
NK071(du)002:3901: ngang de nas / rgya tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK071(du)002:3902: gzhi tshad med pa ye shes kyi 'khor lo la
NK071(du)002:3903: brten cing rgyan gyi rnam pa yang 'khor lo'i rgyan
NK071(du)002:3904: dang 'dod yon phun sum tshogs pa phyogs bcur 'khrigs
NK071(du)002:3905: pa'i rol mo'i tshogs chen po dang /
NK071(du)002:3906: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha'i mthas khyab par snang
NK071(du)002:3907: ba 'od gsal lhun gyis grub pa ma lus pa
NK071(du)002:3908: bsam yas kun gyi rang bzhin /
NK071(du)002:3909: ye shes kyi gzigs pa dag pa'i yul du mthong
NK071(du)002:3910: nas longs spyod chen po'i gzhir mngon sum du nye
NK071(du)002:3912: brjod pa med cing ris su ma chad pas rgya
NK071(du)002:3913: chen po'i gsung yi ge tshogs chen las 'gro ba'i
NK071(du)002:3914: don lhun gyis grub par 'byung ba'ang /
NK071(du)002:3915: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ye nas sangs
NK071(du)002:3916: rgyas pa la lam ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:3917: zab mos gsal btab pas 'bras bu gdod ma'i gnas
NK071(du)002:3918: lugs su byang chub pa rnams dbyer med pa ni
NK071(du)002:3919: rang bzhin mthun pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rang
NK071(du)002:3920: snang ba'o // gnyis pa de nyid dbyings chos sku'i
NK071(du)002:3921: zhing nang gsal spros pa dang bral bar bzhugs tshul
NK071(du)002:3922: snang ba'o // ni / de ltar snang ba'i zhing
NK071(du)002:3923: khams kyang gnam gang gi zla ba ltar dbyings chos
NK071(du)002:3924: sku'i zhing du thim pas phyi rol du snang char
NK071(du)002:3925: med la nang gsal du mkhyen char ma 'gags pa
NK071(du)002:3926: ni rang bzhiin gcig dang du mar bral ba yi
NK071(du)002:3927: snang ba'o // ni / chos sku // mtha' dang
NK071(du)002:3928: dbus med pa'i de bzhin nyid spros pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:3929: zhi ba'i dbyings na phyir snang thim par bzhugs pa'i
NK071(du)002:3931: sangs rgyas kyis kyang phan tshun mi gzigs te /
NK071(du)002:3932: shin tu phra ba'i rang byung gi ye shes de
NK071(du)002:3933: nyid gang du'ang gnas pa med par zhi ba'i dbyings
NK071(du)002:3934: na snang ba ste gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:3935: gsum pa slar yang gdul bya'i 'jig rten du sprul sku'i 'char tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:3936: de nas gdul bya'i 'jig rten du lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:3937: pa'i phrin las kyis gang la gang 'dul du rig
NK071(du)002:3938: pa'i ye shes sprul pa'i skur mngon par snang ba
NK071(du)002:3939: ste / de'ang thugs rje rig pa'i ye shes de
NK071(du)002:3940: nyid phyin ci log gi log par rtog pas kun
NK071(du)002:3941: nas brtags pa'i ngo bo sgrib gnyis bag chags dang
NK071(du)002:3942: bcas pa ma lus pa thams cad rnam par dag
NK071(du)002:3943: ste / cing / shes bya ma lus pa mkhyen
NK071(du)002:3944: pa'i ye shes phyogs bcur rgyas te ye shes de
NK071(du)002:3945: yang dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i chos sku yon
NK071(du)002:3946: tan gyi gter las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:3947: rtog pa med bzhin du 'gro don lhun grub tu
NK071(du)002:3948: 'byung ste yul gdul bya'i 'jig rten dang yul thams
NK071(du)002:3949: cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis ye nas lhun gyis
NK071(du)002:3950: grub pa'i thugs rje chen pos yul yul can du
NK071(du)002:3951: 'brel bas na / ma dag pa 'gro ba drug
NK071(du)002:3952: gi 'jig rten du dus gsum po thams cad du
NK071(du)002:3953: ye shes kyi spyan gyis gzigs shing lha la sogs
NK071(du)002:3954: pa'i gnas ris sems can gyis khyab pa ma lus
NK071(du)002:3955: pa de dag tu thub drug la sogs pa'i sprul
NK071(du)002:3956: pa tshad med pa so sor snang ba dang mthun
NK071(du)002:3957: par snang zhing don mdzad pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:3958: gsum pa gang du dbang bskur ba'i don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:3959: sngar bstan pa'i mchog dbang bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor la ni /
NK071(du)002:3960: yab yum stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor kha dog lnga pa /
NK071(du)002:3961: byas te slob ma dang ldan rnams rab tu zhugs na /
NK071(du)002:3962: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin dngos grub yid du 'ong
NK071(du)002:3963: ba sngon gzhan gyis thob pa dang mnyam par thob
NK071(du)002:3964: par 'gyur ro // de ltar skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes chen po de /
NK071(du)002:3965: don du gnyer na tshe 'di nyid la dngos grub
NK071(du)002:3966: chen po nye bar 'byung ba yi rang bzhin las
NK071(du)002:3967: bzhi dang tshe dbang thob pa'i rten des mchog gi
NK071(du)002:3968: dngos grub ya mtshan chen po sangs rgyas nyid 'byung
NK071(du)002:3969: bar nges so // de las gzhan chos dang bla
NK071(du)002:3970: ma la dad pa med cing rtsa ba dang yan
NK071(du)002:3971: lag gi dam tshig nyams pas bsgrub na phung bar
NK071(du)002:3972: bar nges so // 'gyur ro // zhes de bzhin
NK071(du)002:3973: gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas ched du
NK071(du)002:3974: bar nges so // 'gyur ro // brjod do //
NK071(du)002:3975: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gnas
NK071(du)002:3976: lugs gsang ba'i snying po don gyi ye shes de
NK071(du)002:3977: kho na nyid nges pa las ye nas grub pa'i
NK071(du)002:3978: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo rdo rje mtshon byed gzugs
NK071(du)002:3979: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i mchog tu gsang
NK071(du)002:3980: ba'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dam tshig gi le'u
NK071(du)002:3981: bar nges so // 'gyur ro // brjod do // ste dgu pa'o // //
NK071(du)002:3982: don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i thabs bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:3983: dbang bskur ba la 'jug pa'i tshul mdor bstan pa dang de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:3985: dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas bcom ldan 'das zag
NK071(du)002:3986: pa med pa'i bde bas dgyes pa chen po kun
NK071(du)002:3987: tu bzang po yab yum khams gsum chos kyi rgyal
NK071(du)002:3988: po ru dbang bskur ba slob ma'i rgyud la sbyin
NK071(du)002:3989: pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK071(du)002:3990: zhugs nas dbang bskur ba'i ched du brjod pa 'di
NK071(du)002:3991: brjod do // de'ang dbang gi don la a b+hi
NK071(du)002:3992: she ka ta zhes zer zhing de'i don yang nus
NK071(du)002:3993: pa 'jug par byed pa ste 'jig rten rgyal sar
NK071(du)002:3994: 'don pa la rig byed kyi bum pas dbang bskur
NK071(du)002:3995: nas yul khams la dbang ba'i nus pa 'jug pa
NK071(du)002:3996: dang 'dra bar rang gzhan gyi don byed pa'i nus
NK071(du)002:3997: pa 'jug pa ste rgyal po sbyin pa zhes bya'o
NK071(du)002:3998: brjod do // // yang a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgras ye
NK071(du)002:3999: shes kyis bgos shing sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud
NK071(du)002:4002: nus pa'i dbang dang phan pa'i dbang dang /
NK071(du)002:4005: zab dbang spyir bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4006: sngar bstan pa bzhin lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed cing bdag nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4007: slob ma 'jug pa dang phan dbang dang nus dbang
NK071(du)002:4008: bskur la gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs te yum shes
NK071(du)002:4009: rab dang yab yum thabs kyi phyag rgya snyoms par
NK071(du)002:4010: zhugs pa las / yab kyi byang sems bde ba'i
NK071(du)002:4011: rang bzhin yi ge h+aum gi 'bru tshogs su gsal
NK071(du)002:4012: zhugs pa las / ba'i rgyun / rdo rje'i lam nas phyung ste yum gyi pad+mara 'khyil ba /
NK071(du)002:4013: slob ma'i lce rtse nas khor bar bstim zhing gtso
NK071(du)002:4014: bo'i dkyil 'khor 'phro 'dus byin rlabs bsdus te slob
NK071(du)002:4015: ma'i snying gar bsgyur zhing gsang sngags brjod do //
NK071(du)002:4016: gnyis pa nus dbang bye brag tu bshad pa la lnga las /
NK071(du)002:4017: dang po nyan pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4018: slob ma rin chen 'byung ldan du gsal ba'i nyan
NK071(du)002:4019: byed rna ba gnyis kyi nang du b+h+r+aum las 'khor
NK071(du)002:4020: lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i dbus su t+r+aam las lha'i gzhal
NK071(du)002:4021: yas su / gsal ba'i rna ba'i dbang po sgra
NK071(du)002:4022: la nyan nus su 'dzin pa'i thig le shin tu
NK071(du)002:4023: dwangs ba'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa de /
NK071(du)002:4024: yi ge t+r+aam zung lnga ya bcu h+aum bzhi dzahh+aum
NK071(du)002:4025: bam hohdang bcas gsung gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog gi
NK071(du)002:4026: yi ge rnams 'od du zhu ba las /
NK071(du)002:4027: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bskyed
NK071(du)002:4028: la bla mas ye shes pa de kho na 'dra
NK071(du)002:4029: ba spro ste slob ma'i rna bar thim pas nyan
NK071(du)002:4030: pa'i sgrib pa dag nas lha dang bcas pa 'od
NK071(du)002:4031: du zhu ba las rin chen 'byung ldan du bsam
NK071(du)002:4032: la dam tshig bsgrag cing rjes gnang sbyin pa de
NK071(du)002:4033: ni / t+r+aam zhes mgo 'dren par byas nas gsang
NK071(du)002:4034: ba ma h+aa gsang chen a nu gsang mchog gang
NK071(du)002:4035: yin rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga ste
NK071(du)002:4037: k+r+ai ya u pa yo ga la sogs pa phyi
NK071(du)002:4038: thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa'i gsang ba kun la'ang
NK071(du)002:4040: slob dpon gyi dbang ma thob pa de srid du
NK071(du)002:4041: gsang ba'i don nyid rang gi rgyud la goms 'dris
NK071(du)002:4042: su byed cing brtag pa las /
NK071(du)002:4043: gang zag gzhan dang yul dus gzhan du smra bar bya ba min no //
NK071(du)002:4044: gnyis pa bsgom pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4045: gsal ba'i 'khor lo'i snying gzhal yas khang du bskyed pa'i gnas su /
NK071(du)002:4046: dran gzhi gsal ba'i rten byed pa'i dwangs ma nyungs 'bru tsam gyi thig le'i ngo bo nyid /
NK071(du)002:4047: gtso bo'i sa bon yi ge h+aum gi 'phreng ba'i tshogs mchog 'od du zhu ba las /
NK071(du)002:4048: thugs kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal btab ste
NK071(du)002:4049: ye shes pa 'phro zhing thim pas yid kyi sgrib
NK071(du)002:4050: pa sbyangs te 'od du zhu ba lhar gyur bas
NK071(du)002:4052: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i sras po chen po zhes slob ma la bos nas /
NK071(du)002:4053: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rdo
NK071(du)002:4054: rje lus lha ngag sngags sems chos nyid zab mo'i
NK071(du)002:4056: de'i ngang las rgyal ba thams cad mnyes pa'i mchod
NK071(du)002:4057: pa sgrub pa dang phyi nang gsang ba bde ba
NK071(du)002:4059: 'bras bu rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i go 'phang thob par gyis shig /
NK071(du)002:4060: gsum pa phrin las kyi dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4061: lag pa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su /
NK071(du)002:4062: reg shes gsal ba'i rten byed pa'i thig le dwangs ba'i ngo bo nyid /
NK071(du)002:4063: ham gi phyag rgyas tshogs mchog yi ge'i rang bzhin du gyur pa las /
NK071(du)002:4064: phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bskyed la ye
NK071(du)002:4065: shes pa 'phro zhing thim pa zhu ba las don
NK071(du)002:4066: grub yab yum du gyur pa la rjes gnang sbyin
NK071(du)002:4067: pa ni / rigs kyi bu khyod ni de ring
NK071(du)002:4068: nyid nas rdo rje las te don yod grub pa
