NK071(du)002:4069: pa ni / yin gyis / sems can gyi don
NK071(du)002:4070: dang sangs rgyas mchod pa dang rang gi sgrub pa'i
NK071(du)002:4071: las rnams ma lus pa kun gyis shig /
NK071(du)002:4072: des sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i rnam sprul
NK071(du)002:4073: gyi pho nya mang po'i tshogs tshur 'du bas dngos
NK071(du)002:4074: grub ster zhing phar 'phro bas phrin las bsgrub pa'i
NK071(du)002:4075: rang bzhin du gyur pa kun gyis /
NK071(du)002:4076: khyod kyi dgos pa thams cad byed pa yin zhes pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4077: bzhi pa 'chad pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4078: tshig smra bar byed pa lce'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su /
NK071(du)002:4079: ro 'dzin lce'i dbang po dwangs shing gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid /
NK071(du)002:4080: yi ge h+r+aih yi rang bzhin zung lnga'i phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog 'od du zhu ba las /
NK071(du)002:4081: snang ba mtha' yas gsung chos kyi rigs kyi 'khor
NK071(du)002:4082: lo gsal ba la ye shes pa spro zhing thim
NK071(du)002:4083: pa zhu ba las 'od dpag med du bskyed la
NK071(du)002:4085: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos kyi bdud rtsi bla na med pa rnams kyis /
NK071(du)002:4086: theg pa so so gang dang gang la dad pa
NK071(du)002:4087: dang ldan pa'i skyes bu de dang chos bstan pas
NK071(du)002:4089: dbang po rab la gsang chen rmad du byung ba'i
NK071(du)002:4090: theg pa 'bring la rgyu'i theg pa chen po tha
NK071(du)002:4091: ma'i blo can la nyan rang dang lha mi'i theg
NK071(du)002:4092: pa / dbang po'i rim pa dang mthun par chos
NK071(du)002:4093: kyi gsang ba so sor bsgrags kyis dman pa'i gang
NK071(du)002:4094: zag la chen po'i chos dang /
NK071(du)002:4095: chen po la dman pa'i chos la sogs pa 'chol
NK071(du)002:4096: bar bsgrags pa'i tshul gzhan du bya ba min te
NK071(du)002:4097: don du mi 'gyur ba dang chos spong pa'i las
NK071(du)002:4099: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi
NK071(du)002:4100: ting nge 'dzin ni mgo la sogs pa yan lag
NK071(du)002:4101: lnga ni 'gro 'dug dang phyag rgya dang yul la
NK071(du)002:4102: lta zhing bsgul bskyod byed pas bskyod chen 'khor lo'i
NK071(du)002:4103: gzhal yas su / lus kyi dbang po dwangs shing
NK071(du)002:4104: gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:4105: gzhal yas su / pa / lag pa g.yas kyi
NK071(du)002:4106: dpung mgor h+aum mgo la lag pa g.yon la s+w+aa
NK071(du)002:4107: rkang pa g.yon la +aam g.yas la h+aa rnams 'od
NK071(du)002:4109: rigs lnga so so'i dkyil 'khor lnga dang phyi rol
NK071(du)002:4110: du bsrung ba'i 'khor lo khro bo bcu'i 'phreng ba
NK071(du)002:4112: rjes su gnang ba ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK071(du)002:4113: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rdo rje che ste /
NK071(du)002:4114: 'khor 'das thams cad la ye nas khyab pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:4115: bzhin rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed
NK071(du)002:4116: pa po dpal kun tu bzang po khyod yin pas
NK071(du)002:4117: / rigs kyi bu 'di la mchog gi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4118: dngos grub kun gyi sbyin pa dam pa sbyod pa
NK071(du)002:4120: gsum pa dbang dang mi ldan pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4121: sgo gsum yo byad dang bcas pas gsang sngags kyi slob dpon manya sa par ma byas shing /
NK071(du)002:4122: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang rnams rgyud la thob par ma byas par /
NK071(du)002:4123: gsang sngags nyan pa la sogs pa la rtsom pa rnams /
NK071(du)002:4124: tshe 'dir bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub med cing
NK071(du)002:4125: phyi ma ngan song du sdug bsngal myong bas brlag
NK071(du)002:4126: par 'gyur te chos zab mo la dbang zos pa'i
NK071(du)002:4127: phyir ro // gnyis pa phan pa'i dbang ni slob
NK071(du)002:4128: ma lha'i bdag nyid du gsal ba la rin po
NK071(du)002:4129: che'i dbu rgyan bcings ba ni khams gsum chos kyi
NK071(du)002:4130: rgyal por dbang bskur te rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye
NK071(du)002:4131: shes lngar gsal zhing phyir mi ldog par mtshon pa'o
NK071(du)002:4132: phyir ro // / cod pan ste dar dpyangs kyis
NK071(du)002:4133: sgrib pa gnyis dag cing thabs dang shes rab zung
NK071(du)002:4135: me tog gi 'phreng ba yis ni las dang bag
NK071(du)002:4136: chags dag cing byang chub yan lag gi tshogs thob
NK071(du)002:4138: de gsum ka dbu rgyan gyi dbang ste sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab tu 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)002:4139: go cha ni nyon mongs pa'i mtshon gyis mi tshugs shing bdud kyi rgyu 'dul bar mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4140: rgyal mtshan ni 'khor ba'i rgyu kun nas ldang ba'i
NK071(du)002:4141: cha dang bcas pa dag cing mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK071(du)002:4142: las rnam par rgyal ba mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4143: rdo rje la sogs pa rigs lnga'i phyag rgya ni
NK071(du)002:4144: nyon mongs pa lnga gnas su dag cing ye shes
NK071(du)002:4145: lnga thugs su chud par mtshon pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4146: gdugs ni nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba skyob cing thugs rjes 'gro ba skyob pa mtshon pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4147: 'di gsum gzhan don phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK071(du)002:4148: bum pa ni nyon mongs pa'i dri ma 'khrud cing
NK071(du)002:4149: rigs lnga'i nus pa 'jog pa ste zag pa med
NK071(du)002:4151: bza' ba dang btung ba ni 'khor 'das kyi rgud
NK071(du)002:4152: pa dang bral nas bsam gtan gyi ros rgyas par
NK071(du)002:4153: mtshon pa dang / 'di gsum ni rang don phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK071(du)002:4154: nyi ma zla ba chus sha chen gyi dwangs ma
NK071(du)002:4155: ste snying po lnga yis dbang bskur na phung po
NK071(du)002:4156: lnga yab lnga 'byung ba lnga nyon mongs pa lnga
NK071(du)002:4157: ye shes lngar dag cing dbyer med par mtshon pa'o
NK071(du)002:4158: // 'di ni 'khor 'das gnyis su med pa ston pa'i dbang ngo //
NK071(du)002:4159: gsum pa dbang thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:4160: de ltar nus pa dang phan pa'i dbang rnams rdzogs
NK071(du)002:4161: par thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad rigs kyi bu
NK071(du)002:4162: khyod rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i sras su gyur
NK071(du)002:4163: cing / ngan song dang de'i sdug bsngal thams cad med pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4164: 'dir yang tshe ring zhing nor dang 'byor pa dang
NK071(du)002:4165: dbang phyug dam pa'i bde ba phun sum tshogs pa
NK071(du)002:4166: dang / phyi ma la'ang gnas skabs mtho ris dang
NK071(du)002:4167: mthar thug thar pa'i bdag po sangs rgyas thob par
NK071(du)002:4169: thugs kyi ye shes mchog tu gsang ba'i snying po
NK071(du)002:4170: phun sum tshogs pa zab mo de kho na nyid
NK071(du)002:4171: nges pa las sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab tu dbang
NK071(du)002:4172: bskur ba'i ye shes sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o
NK071(du)002:4174: // // spyi don gnyis pa lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:4175: tha mal gyi mngon zhen bzlog pa bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4176: snying po'i don la 'jug pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4178: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4179: de'i yan lag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4185: gzhi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba de nas lam
NK071(du)002:4186: bskyed pa'i rim pa thabs snang ba'i dngos po lam
NK071(du)002:4187: du slong ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thabs kyi
NK071(du)002:4188: rol pas dgyes pa chen po kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)002:4189: nyid thabs snang ba'i sgyu 'phrul 'dod yon lnga la
NK071(du)002:4190: sogs pa 'khor ba'i chos nyon mongs pa'i rnam par
NK071(du)002:4191: snang ba rnams shes rab stong pa'i rang bzhin du
NK071(du)002:4192: gnas pas dra ba'i ngo bo chos thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:4193: gnas lugs sam rgyal po 'dod yon dang nyon mongs
NK071(du)002:4194: pa ma spangs par snang dus nyid nas ye shes
NK071(du)002:4195: chen por dbang bsgyur ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK071(du)002:4197: thams cad thar lam du bstan pa'i ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)002:4199: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor shes par bya ba dang /
NK071(du)002:4200: lam thabs dang shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor nyams su blang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:4202: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK071(du)002:4203: ye nas stong pa'i ngang las byung bar rgyu gcig
NK071(du)002:4204: pa dang de ltar stong pa'i ngang las dang por
NK071(du)002:4205: byung ba ma zad lta snang dus nyid nas kyang
NK071(du)002:4206: yig 'bru a'i tshul du rang bzhin gyis ma skyes
NK071(du)002:4207: pa'i ngo bor snang stong gnyis su med par gnas
NK071(du)002:4208: te snang ba ni stong pa ni +aahganyisa su med
NK071(du)002:4209: pa ni h+aum gi rang bzhin du gnas pas snang
NK071(du)002:4210: bzhin du stong stong bzhin du snang snang ba dang
NK071(du)002:4211: stong pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor gnas so
NK071(du)002:4212: // me'i rang bzhin tsha bas byin gyis brlab pa
NK071(du)002:4213: ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas dkyil
NK071(du)002:4214: 'khor gyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas par byin gyis
NK071(du)002:4215: brlabs pas ma dag pa med cing dag pa 'ba'
NK071(du)002:4216: zhig gi tshul du gnas te stong pa chos sku
NK071(du)002:4217: snang ba longs sku sna tshogs su snang ba sprul
NK071(du)002:4218: pa'i sku'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir dang de ltar
NK071(du)002:4219: gnas pa'i rang bzhin rnams kyang dus gzhan nam lkog
NK071(du)002:4220: tu gyur pa la sogs pa ma yin par snang
NK071(du)002:4221: dus 'di nyid nas phyi snang ba yum nang phung
NK071(du)002:4222: po yab rtog tshogs lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i
NK071(du)002:4223: ngo bo mngon sum bar snang zhing snang dus nyid
NK071(du)002:4224: nas mnyam pa nyid kyi rang bzhin gyi las mi
NK071(du)002:4225: g.yo ba'i dgongs pa ston pa yin te /
NK071(du)002:4226: de'ang gzhi'i gnas lugs de rang gi bsod nams dang /
NK071(du)002:4227: bla ma dam pas thugs rjes byin gyis brlabs pa
NK071(du)002:4228: la brten nas phyin ci ma log par rab tu
NK071(du)002:4229: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yis /
NK071(du)002:4230: chos thams cad ye nas mngon par rdzogs par byang
NK071(du)002:4231: chub pa'i rgyal po che de ltar rtogs pa na
NK071(du)002:4232: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams la spong len
NK071(du)002:4233: med par byams gcig ye shes kyi rol bar 'char
NK071(du)002:4234: bas gsang chen don gyi gnas lugs so //
NK071(du)002:4235: de ni dbyings de bzhin du nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4236: bskyed rim ltar na rgyu gcig pa ting nge 'dzin gsum dang /
NK071(du)002:4237: yig 'bru lha so so'i snying po bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4238: byin gyis brlab pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4239: mngon sum pa de'i ngang la lhan cig pa'i rdzogs
NK071(du)002:4240: pa sgom par rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi
NK071(du)002:4241: yis chos thams cad shes par byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4243: rgyu gcig pa 'khor 'das sems su gcig pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4244: yig 'bru'i tshul skye ba med pa'i ngang du rtogs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4245: byin gyis brlabs pa de ltar mnyam par 'jog pa
NK071(du)002:4246: thugs rdo rje'i ngo bo gnyis su med par gyur
NK071(du)002:4247: ba'o // mngon sum pa so so rang gi rig
NK071(du)002:4248: pa'i ye shes kyis bsgom pa las rtogs pa ste
NK071(du)002:4250: rgya mtsho dwangs ba'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK071(du)002:4251: sgra rten yid la byed min pa /
NK071(du)002:4252: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral bar //
NK071(du)002:4253: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul bas //
NK071(du)002:4254: nges par gding du gang byas pa //
NK071(du)002:4255: thos bsam brtan pa'i lta mthar phyin /
NK071(du)002:4258: rgyu gcig pa bskyed rdzogs pa bden gnyis su gcig
NK071(du)002:4259: pa dang de'i ngo bo rtag chad las 'das pa
NK071(du)002:4260: yi ge sprin du gnas pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4261: dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngang las bskyed rdzogs su rang snang bar byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4262: de nyid rig pas thag chod cing mi 'gal bar
NK071(du)002:4263: mngon sum du rtogs nas nyin mtshan du brtson pa
NK071(du)002:4265: rtogs pa yang ni rnam pa bzhir //
NK071(du)002:4266: rnal 'byor nang pa bzhed pa ste //
NK071(du)002:4267: rgyu gcig pa dang yi ge'i tshul //
NK071(du)002:4268: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum las //
NK071(du)002:4269: rdzogs chen don la 'jug gyur te //
NK071(du)002:4270: rgyu ni bden gnyis cig char du //
NK071(du)002:4271: gcig pas gcig pa'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK071(du)002:4272: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK071(du)002:4273: chos kun rang bzhin rtogs pa dang //
NK071(du)002:4274: skye med dbyings kyi byin brlabs las //
NK071(du)002:4275: chos kun snang bar shes pa dang //
NK071(du)002:4276: de lta bu yi rang bzhin te //
NK071(du)002:4277: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK071(du)002:4278: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK071(du)002:4279: rnal 'byor sa la sleb pa yin //
NK071(du)002:4282: cir snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK071(du)002:4284: gang sgrub thabs kyi yan lag go /
NK071(du)002:4286: snang sems gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4287: sbyor grol gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4291: rol pa gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:4293: dang po zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du shes par bya ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4294: lus kyi yan lag dang mig la sogs pa'i dbang
NK071(du)002:4295: po dang de dag gi rnam par shes pa'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:4297: tha mal gyi rnam smin rang mtshan pa min par
NK071(du)002:4298: ste ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du shes par bya
NK071(du)002:4299: zhing de'i mtshon byed du yab lnga sems dpa' brgyad
NK071(du)002:4300: sgo ba bzhi thub pa drug dang bcas pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:4301: bzhin me long nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar med bzhin
NK071(du)002:4302: snang ba'i rigs lnga longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4304: gnyis pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du shes par bya ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4305: yang na 'dul bya'i dbang ngam rang gi mos pa'i dbang gis khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4306: gnyis pa yum gyi dkyil 'khor la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:4307: dang po zhi ba'i yul du shes par bya ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4308: snang srid skye 'gros bsdus pa'i gzugs dang sgra dang
NK071(du)002:4309: dri dang ro dang reg bya la sogs pa ste
NK071(du)002:4310: chos dang 'byung ba lngar snang ba thams cad rnam
NK071(du)002:4311: pa de dag tu smin par m+aum du ste gnyis
NK071(du)002:4312: su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid du
NK071(du)002:4313: shes par bya zhing de'i mtshon byed sgom bzhi sems
NK071(du)002:4314: ma brgyad yum lnga'i rnam pa ste snang la ngos
NK071(du)002:4315: bzung med pa yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom
NK071(du)002:4316: par bya'o // gnyis pa khro bo'i yum du gsal ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4317: yang na gdul bya'i dbang ngam rang gi mos pa'i dbang gis khro mo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom mo //
NK071(du)002:4318: gsum pa rol pa gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK071(du)002:4319: lus la bgo ba'i gos dang 'dogs pa'i rgyan dang
NK071(du)002:4320: bza' ba dang btung ba dang ngag gi glu dang
NK071(du)002:4322: lus kyi rnam 'gyur rkang bro dang lag pa'i gar
NK071(du)002:4323: dang nye bar spyod pa'i yo byad kyi tshogs kyi
NK071(du)002:4325: snang stong ngam yab yum gnyis su med pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:4326: bzhin h+aum bde ba chen po'i chos nyid du shes
NK071(du)002:4327: pas chags zhen med pa tshogs kyi yo byad rmi
NK071(du)002:4328: lam ltar bden med kyi ngang nas lha mo drug
NK071(du)002:4329: gi rang bzhin du rab tu spyad na /
NK071(du)002:4330: 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ngo
NK071(du)002:4331: mtshar ba'i rang bzhin 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor phung khams
NK071(du)002:4332: skye mched na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes
NK071(du)002:4333: pas myur du byang chub 'grub pa'i phan yon rlabs
NK071(du)002:4334: po che thob par byed do //
NK071(du)002:4335: gnyis pa sbyor sgrol gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor la gsum /
NK071(du)002:4336: sbyor ba gnas su dag pa bde chen byang chub mchog gi dkyil 'khor /
NK071(du)002:4337: sgrol ba gnas su dag pa thabs chen gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK071(du)002:4338: sbyor sgrol nyes pas mi gos pa ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:4340: dang po yul gang la sbyar ba ni bcu gnyis
NK071(du)002:4341: ma thugs kyi gsang yum lha mo bcu drug ma
NK071(du)002:4342: gsung gi gsang yum klu mo nyi shu ma sku'i
NK071(du)002:4343: gsang yum rigs ngan mo rnams kyi bzang ngan bye
NK071(du)002:4344: brag so sor dbye nas ngan pa dor te bzang
NK071(du)002:4345: ba bsten pa'am yang na mi dbye ba gang rung
NK071(du)002:4347: tshul ji lta bus sbyar na ni lha gcig la'ang
NK071(du)002:4348: bsnyen sgrub bzhis brten pa ltar 'dir yang phyag rgya'i
NK071(du)002:4349: rgyud sbyong zhing byang chub kyi sems rgyas par byed
NK071(du)002:4350: pas bsnyen pa dang 'du shes dag pas lta ba
NK071(du)002:4351: dang reg pa la sogs pa ni nye ba'i bsnyen
NK071(du)002:4352: pa dang / lhar gsal bas 'khyud pa la sogs
NK071(du)002:4353: pa ni sgrub pa dang gnyis su med par rol
NK071(du)002:4354: bas 'khor lo bzhi nas gsang bar 'bebs pa ni
NK071(du)002:4355: sgrub pa chen po yi rim pa bzhi yi ye
NK071(du)002:4357: ngo bo gang sbyor ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4358: de nas yum gyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK071(du)002:4359: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems nyungs 'bru
NK071(du)002:4360: tsam gyi rten bsam pa la bde ba chen po'i
NK071(du)002:4361: rang bzhin / thugs kyi dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)002:4362: tshom bus brgyan pa spro zhing bskyed la ye shes
NK071(du)002:4363: pa dbyings nas spyan drangs shing bstim ste /
NK071(du)002:4364: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sprin tshogs ma lus pa thams cad la rol ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK071(du)002:4365: dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad dgyes pa mnyam pa'i
NK071(du)002:4366: mchog gi sbyin pas so sor bstim zhing tshim par
NK071(du)002:4367: phul bas gnyis med bde ba chen po'i dngos grub
NK071(du)002:4368: thob par bsam nas byang chub kyi sems pad+mora 'khyil
NK071(du)002:4370: dngos grub ji ltar byung ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4371: de ltar sgrub pa'i mkha' gsang gi nyi ma dang zla ba'i snying po de /
NK071(du)002:4372: rtsa 'khor lo bzhi'i dkyil 'khor du gsar pa rdo
NK071(du)002:4373: rje nor bu'i lce yis blang ste mas rim gyis
NK071(du)002:4374: dgang nas lus kyi gnas thams cad la khyab par
NK071(du)002:4375: dgram shing ye shes su la bazla'o //
NK071(du)002:4377: rdzu 'phrul gyis nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang chos
NK071(du)002:4378: thams cad mngon sum du gsal bar rtogs pa dang
NK071(du)002:4379: ting nge 'dzin dang ye shes kyi 'od zer 'bar
NK071(du)002:4380: bas sa lam gyi khyad par gong mar bgrod pa
NK071(du)002:4381: dang tshe la dbang thob pas rdo rje'i sku brnyes
NK071(du)002:4382: pa sogs las te gnas skabs thun mong gi grub
NK071(du)002:4383: pa brgyad dang / mthar thug kun tu bzang po'i
NK071(du)002:4384: sa mchog yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:4385: pa brgyad dang / // gnyis pa sgrol ba gnas
NK071(du)002:4386: su dag pa thabs chen gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la
NK071(du)002:4387: pa brgyad dang / // gsum las / gang bsgral
NK071(du)002:4388: ba'i yul ni zhing gyur mchog lha mi dang mchog
NK071(du)002:4389: phran ngan song gi 'gro ba dbye na zhing bcu
NK071(du)002:4390: po rnams sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang 'bras bu la
NK071(du)002:4391: gnas pas de dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir bsgral
NK071(du)002:4392: pa brgyad dang / // gsum las / lo // ji ltar bsgral ba'i thabs ni /
NK071(du)002:4393: rnal 'byor pa rab ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol la /
NK071(du)002:4394: 'bring ting nge 'dzin dang sngags dang phyag rgyas sgrol zhing /
NK071(du)002:4395: tha mas de dag gi steng du brub khung dang
NK071(du)002:4396: ling+ga la sogs pa rdzas dngos su bsags te gzugs
NK071(du)002:4397: brnyan dang bcas pas sgrol zhing /
NK071(du)002:4398: de'ang dkyil 'khor gyi lho nub tu brub khung ro
NK071(du)002:4399: sol gyis byugs pa e gru gsum 'bar ba'i nang
NK071(du)002:4400: du ma las nyi ma dang a las zla ba'i
NK071(du)002:4401: dkyil du ling+ga ming rus dang bcas pa sgrol ba'i
NK071(du)002:4402: las la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pas bzhag te ting
NK071(du)002:4405: rang bzhin gyis sgrol ba'i lta ba la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4406: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba'i sgom pa la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4407: dbang po yul dus kyis sgrol ba'i spyod pa la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4408: thabs chen gsang bas sgrol ba'i gdams ngag la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4409: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol pa'i sgom pa la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4410: dbang po yul dus kyis sgrol ba'i spyod pa la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4411: thabs chen gsang bas sgrol ba'i gdams ngag la mkhas pa /
NK071(du)002:4412: mngon spyod zab mos sgrol ba'i mdzad spyod la mkhas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4413: de nas bdag nyid dpa' bo chen po yab yum
NK071(du)002:4414: gyi ngo bor bskyed la gdug pa can bsgral bar
NK071(du)002:4415: bya'o snyam pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas lag pa'i
NK071(du)002:4416: sor mo bcu la dpa' bo 'bru lnga'am sgrol ging
NK071(du)002:4417: bcu'i sa bon h+aum bcu las ging pho bcur bskyed
NK071(du)002:4418: pa'i bar du zangs gri'am phur pa 'dril cing lag
NK071(du)002:4419: gi 'du byed ling+ga'i snying la gzir bas sha khrag
NK071(du)002:4420: dum bur gtubs te dkyil 'khor la mchod par bsgom
NK071(du)002:4421: mo // rnam par shes pa h+aum du gyur pas
NK071(du)002:4422: las dang bag chags thams cad rnam par dag cing
NK071(du)002:4423: mo // / h+aum de nyid rim gyis zla tshes
NK071(du)002:4424: kyi dbyings su thim nas zla tshes me long lta
NK071(du)002:4425: bu'i ye shes yongs su gyur pa las thugs kyi
NK071(du)002:4426: phyag rgyar mtshon pa'i rdo rje 'od 'bar ba zhig
NK071(du)002:4427: mo // / tu gyur / de las rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4428: sems dpa'i skur gyur cing 'od zer rab tu 'phro
NK071(du)002:4430: de'i gtsug tu 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal ba'i
NK071(du)002:4431: rtags kun tu bzang po tshon gang ba cig bsgom
NK071(du)002:4432: ste / rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyi steng du zla
NK071(du)002:4433: ba'i gdan la bzhag nas phata kyi sgras 'og min
NK071(du)002:4434: ste / du 'phangs / de bzhiin gshegs pa'i zhal du zhugs /
NK071(du)002:4435: yum gyi mkha' rdo rje sems dpar bskyed de de
NK071(du)002:4436: bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su byas nas sems can gyi
NK071(du)002:4438: de ltar bsgral ba'i phan yon ni sdig pa can
NK071(du)002:4439: mngon spyod kyis bsgral ba 'di ni theg pa gzhan
NK071(du)002:4440: las ngo mtshar ba rdo rje theg pa'i gsang chen
NK071(du)002:4441: sdig can ngan 'gro las thar pa'i thabs khyad par
NK071(du)002:4442: du 'phags pa'o // gsum pa sbyor sgrol gyi nyes
NK071(du)002:4443: pas mi gos pa ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4444: du 'phags pa'o // ni / don dam par chos
NK071(du)002:4445: thams cad kyi gnas lugs ye nas skye ba med
NK071(du)002:4447: kun rdzob snang tsam nyid na rang bzhin med bzhin
NK071(du)002:4448: du rkyen gyis sna tshogs su snang ba sgyu mar
NK071(du)002:4449: snang ba dang ngos bzung med par mig yor gyi
NK071(du)002:4451: sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang
NK071(du)002:4452: byed dus nyid nas las sogs byed gyi bya ba
NK071(du)002:4453: rang mtshan pa rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med
NK071(du)002:4454: do // gnyis pa rol pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:4455: kun tu bzang po'i tshogs mchod mdor bstan pa dang //
NK071(du)002:4456: dkyil 'khor so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o /
NK071(du)002:4458: rang bzhin shes par bya ba ni phyi snod kyi
NK071(du)002:4459: 'jig rten 'byung ba lnga'i ngo bo yum lnga'i rang
NK071(du)002:4460: bzhin du dag cing nang bcud kyi sems can phung
NK071(du)002:4461: po lngas bsdus pa yab lngar dag la rang rang
NK071(du)002:4462: gi rgyud kyi dbang po dang rnam par shes pa
NK071(du)002:4463: dang de dag gi yul rnams sems dpa' dang sems
NK071(du)002:4464: ma dang sgo ba yab yum du ye nas rnam
NK071(du)002:4466: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad don dam
NK071(du)002:4467: par ma skyes pa mnyam zhing kun rdzob tu sgyu
NK071(du)002:4468: ma lta bur mnyam pa gnyis dang phung po lnga
NK071(du)002:4469: sangs rgyas su mnyam pa dang rnam shes brgyad ye
NK071(du)002:4470: shes su mnyam pa ste lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis
NK071(du)002:4471: kyis / thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4472: ye nas kun tu bzang po'i zhing khams nyid do
NK071(du)002:4473: kyis / // gang gis shes par bya ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4474: de ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin du rtogs
NK071(du)002:4475: pas chos nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor la dbang thob
NK071(du)002:4476: pa'i tshe sgo gsum gyi byed spyod ci byas kyang
NK071(du)002:4477: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen gnyis su
NK071(du)002:4478: gyur nas / de yang sngar bstan pa bzhin sngags
NK071(du)002:4479: kyi yan lag lnga ma nyams shing yo byad lnga
NK071(du)002:4481: cho ga lnga po rdzogs par shes pa yi /
NK071(du)002:4482: rnal 'byor pas dus khyad par can la sogs par
NK071(du)002:4483: dur khrod la sogs pa'i gnas su rten gang zag
NK071(du)002:4484: tshogs kyi yo byad rnams yongs su tshogs pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:4485: 'khor gyis mnyes par byas te bsgrubs na 'bras bu
NK071(du)002:4486: gnas skabs rig 'dzin gsum dang phrin las bzhi mthar
NK071(du)002:4487: thug nges par legs pa'i dgos pa byang chub 'grub
NK071(du)002:4488: par 'gyur ro // gnyis pa dkyil 'khor so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:4489: rten dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK071(du)002:4490: de ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4494: dang po la gsum tshom bu lnga pa /
NK071(du)002:4498: rigs lnga dang yum lnga gnyis su med pa yi sbyor ba yis //
NK071(du)002:4499: tshom bu lnga yi lha rtsa ba lnga las yab
NK071(du)002:4500: yum bcu rigs bzhi po re re'ang bcu bcu ste
NK071(du)002:4502: phyi rol du srung ba'i 'khor lo khog pa stong
NK071(du)002:4503: pa phyogs mtshams steng 'og gnyis te rtsibs bcu la
NK071(du)002:4504: h+aum ka ra la sogs pa'i khro bo bcu dang
NK071(du)002:4505: rdo rje sgra 'byin ma la sogs pa'i khro mo
NK071(du)002:4506: bcu / bar chad bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom mo //
NK071(du)002:4507: de yang dbus su gtso bo yab yum kun tu
NK071(du)002:4508: bzang po'i rang bzhin la sems dpa' rdo rje rin
NK071(du)002:4509: chen rdo rje chos kyi rdo rje las kyi rdo
NK071(du)002:4510: rje bzhi'i yum / brtan ma rdo rje 'bar ba
NK071(du)002:4511: rdo rje sdud ma rdo rje bskyod ma rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4513: shar du mi bskyod pa yab yum la rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4514: sems dpa' rdo rje chags pa rdo rje legs pa
NK071(du)002:4515: bzhi'i yum / sgeg mo bdug pa lcags kyu rdo rje sgrol ma'o //
NK071(du)002:4516: lhor rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum la rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4517: rin chen rdo rje gzi brjid rdo rje rgyal mtshan
NK071(du)002:4518: rdo rje bzhad pa bzhi'i yum /
NK071(du)002:4519: phreng ba ma me tog ma zhags pa ma rdo rje bde ma'o //
NK071(du)002:4520: nub tu 'od dpag med yab yum la rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4521: chos rdo rje 'khor lo rdo rje smra ba bzhi'i
NK071(du)002:4522: yum / glu ma mar me ma lcags sgrogs ma rdo rje gsal bkra ma'o //
NK071(du)002:4523: byang du don yod grub pa yab yum la rdo
NK071(du)002:4524: rje las rdo rje srung ba rdo rje gnod sbyin
NK071(du)002:4525: rdo rje khu tshur bzhi'i yum /
NK071(du)002:4526: gar ma dri chab ma dril bu ma rdo rje 'beb ma'o //
NK071(du)002:4527: de ltar lnga bcu'i phyi rol du khro bo bcu
NK071(du)002:4528: yum dang bcas pas lha bdun cu ni tshom bu
NK071(du)002:4529: lnga pa'o // gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK071(du)002:4530: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK071(du)002:4531: pad+ma'i rigs te re re'ang yab yum bcu bcu'i rang
NK071(du)002:4532: bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi lha sum cu'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4533: gyi mthar khro bo'i tshogs te sgo ba yab yum
NK071(du)002:4535: tshom bu gsum gyi lha rnams bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4536: gsum pa tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor ni rigs
NK071(du)002:4537: thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid kun tu bzang po'i
NK071(du)002:4538: rigs te rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi gtso
NK071(du)002:4539: bo rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang bzhin ni de
NK071(du)002:4540: bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor rigs lngar phye ba'i thugs
NK071(du)002:4541: kyi thugs te gtso bo rnam snang mthing gas brgyan
NK071(du)002:4542: pa ni thugs kyi mchog lha bcu'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK071(du)002:4543: mthar sgo ba yab yum brgyad kyi khro bo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:4545: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha bco brgyad po rnams bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4546: gnyis pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK071(du)002:4547: khro bo rigs lnga dang khro mo kro ti shwa ri lnga'i tshogs chen po dang /
NK071(du)002:4548: de dag gi bya ba sgrub pa'i pho nya gnas
NK071(du)002:4549: kyi ma mo brgyad dang phyag brnyan yum gyi phra
NK071(du)002:4550: men brgyad dang bka' nyan ye shes kyi sgo ma
NK071(du)002:4552: ci bgyis las byed dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa'i tshogs rnams kyis /
NK071(du)002:4553: mthar thug mchog gi dngos grub dang gnas skabs las rnams rdzogs par byed do //
NK071(du)002:4554: gnyis pa de ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa bzhi /
NK071(du)002:4558: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4560: gang zag gang gis bsgrub pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4561: sems nyid rnal ma'i don la blo chos nyid du
NK071(du)002:4562: 'byor ba de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK071(du)002:4563: rmad du byung ba'i sngags kyi tshig don 'chang ba
NK071(du)002:4564: rnams kyis bsgrub par bya ba'i mchog thun mong gi
NK071(du)002:4565: dngos grub ni / chos thams cad ye nas mnyam
NK071(du)002:4566: pa nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du
NK071(du)002:4567: lhun gyis grub cing dbyer med pa phyogs bral 'dzin
NK071(du)002:4568: zhen med pa'i ngang du gnas shing /
NK071(du)002:4569: blang dor med par spyad pas ci la yang thogs pa med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK071(du)002:4570: chos thams cad ye nas ngo bo gcig cing dbyer med pa rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas bsgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4572: thugs rdo rje'i rigs su rigs thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor 'dus pas /
NK071(du)002:4573: lha dang gzhal yas khang pa thams cad ye shes
NK071(du)002:4574: kyi 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar ba rab
NK071(du)002:4575: tu bsgom zhing / 'dod yon thams cad la zhen
NK071(du)002:4576: chags med par lha la lha mchod pa'i tshul gyis
NK071(du)002:4578: de'i 'bras bu sems nyid gnyis su med pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:4579: skur gyur nas lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya chen
NK071(du)002:4581: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4582: snga ma las yang na sku mi bskyod pa gsung
NK071(du)002:4583: 'od dpag med thugs rnam par snang mdzad kyi dkyil
NK071(du)002:4584: 'khor nyid de / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dkyil
NK071(du)002:4585: 'khor ma lus pa bsdu na sku gsung thugs su
NK071(du)002:4587: de bsgrub pa'i bskyed rdzogs kyi ting nge 'dzin lha'i
NK071(du)002:4588: rnam pa gsal zhing mtshan dang dpe byad du 'bar
NK071(du)002:4589: ba'i 'od zer 'phro bas sems can gyi don byed
NK071(du)002:4590: pa bsgom pa'o // 'dod yon thams cad yum du
NK071(du)002:4591: bsam pa yab kyis rol pas gnyis su med pa'i
NK071(du)002:4592: chos dbyings kyi ngang du thim par bsam mo //
NK071(du)002:4593: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub mchog thob par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:4594: de las gdul bya'i don du lha'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK071(du)002:4595: lus pa yon tan gyi dpal 'bar ba grub cing
NK071(du)002:4596: / sems can gyi nyon mongs dang sdug bsngal ma lus pa sel bar byed la /
NK071(du)002:4597: sems can de dag rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas su bkod pa'i phrin las byed do //
NK071(du)002:4598: gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:4599: gang zag gang gis tshul ji ltar bsgrub pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4600: sngags 'chang ba'i rnal 'byor pas dngos grub yang dag pa ni rgyud ma thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:4601: yab yum thabs dang shes rab tu gsal zhing ting
NK071(du)002:4602: nge 'dzin gsum la sogs pa'i cho ga thams cad
NK071(du)002:4603: kyis / tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor lnga dang phyi rol du khro 'phreng bsgom mo //
NK071(du)002:4604: 'dod yon la chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni /
NK071(du)002:4605: lha la lha thim pa'i tshul gyis mchod bya mchod byed gnyis su med par bstim par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4606: 'bras bu dngos grub mchog gi snying po lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin 'grub bo //
NK071(du)002:4607: bzhi pa rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa
NK071(du)002:4608: la'ang gnyis las gang zag gang gis ji ltar bsgrub
NK071(du)002:4609: pa ni / rnal 'byor pa yab thabs dang yum shes rab kyi rang bzhin nyid kyis /
NK071(du)002:4610: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dang lnga'i yum du bsgom zhing /
NK071(du)002:4611: dbang po dang rtog tshogs sems dpa' dang sems ma
NK071(du)002:4612: sgo ba yab yum dang bcas pa nyid du bsgom
NK071(du)002:4613: par bya'o // lha de dag kyang 'od zer gyi tshogs rnam pa mang po phyogs bcur 'phro ba'o //
NK071(du)002:4614: gsum pa gang sgrub thabs kyi yan lag la bzhi las /
NK071(du)002:4615: gang sgrub pa ting nge 'dzin gyi yan lag ni /
NK071(du)002:4616: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor du bsgrub pa'i tshe phyi
NK071(du)002:4617: nang gi lus dang longs spyod la sogs pa spyad
NK071(du)002:4619: spyod byed bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi rol pas so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang /
NK071(du)002:4620: ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam pa skabs su gang bab
NK071(du)002:4621: rnams phyin ci ma log pa yang dag par so
NK071(du)002:4622: sor gsal zhing ma 'dres pa shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4623: ji ltar sgrub pa mthun pa'i yan lag ni /
NK071(du)002:4624: bsgrub pa'i gnas mtshan nyid tshang zhing bar chad med
NK071(du)002:4625: pa dang nye bar mkho ba'i longs spyod mtha' gnyis
NK071(du)002:4626: su ma lhung zhing ci bde bar yod pa dang
NK071(du)002:4627: / des mtshon nas sgrub pa'i grogs su gyur pa'i
NK071(du)002:4628: yo byad dang rten dang dam rdzas la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:4629: mthun pa'i rkyen rnams ma nyams par tshang zhing sgrub
NK071(du)002:4630: pa'i blo ni rkyen gzhan gyis mi 'phrogs shing mtha'
NK071(du)002:4631: gcig tu tshugs pa'i zhe bcad rab dang ldan pa'i
NK071(du)002:4632: / rnal 'byor pas / sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i
NK071(du)002:4633: dang por dam bca' ji ltar nos pa bzhin du
NK071(du)002:4635: sgrub dus su de las gzhan pa'i bya ba la
NK071(du)002:4636: brtson pa dang rtags dang mtshan ma ngan pa'am rtags
NK071(du)002:4637: ma byung bas sgyid lugs pa dang ngas mi 'grub
NK071(du)002:4638: snyam du bdag nyid brnyas pa'i le lo rnams dang
NK071(du)002:4639: sos dal dang dus su mi sgrub cing lus ngag
NK071(du)002:4640: cha babs su byed pa'i sgyid snyoms la lus pa
NK071(du)002:4642: sngags dang ting nge 'dzin sogs la yin nam ma
NK071(du)002:4643: yin 'bras bu 'byung ngam mi 'byung snyam pa la
NK071(du)002:4644: sogs pa'i the tshom med par yin nges snyam pa'i
NK071(du)002:4646: gang bsgrub kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK071(du)002:4647: rdo rje gsang mchog sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral
NK071(du)002:4648: med pa'i chos sku dam pa 'thob par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:4649: // nam gyi tshe sgrub pa dus kyi yan lag ni /
NK071(du)002:4650: sgrub pa'i zhag ni le'u dgu par zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK071(du)002:4651: zhes pa sogs dang sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i tshes grangs dang gza' skar la sogs pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4653: dus ni yar ngo'i brgyad la brtsams //
NK071(du)002:4654: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK071(du)002:4655: byang chub spyod pa ched spyod pas //
NK071(du)002:4656: gsang mchog dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK071(du)002:4657: gza' skar shis pa'ang blang bar bya //
NK071(du)002:4658: zhes smos pa bzhin du bshad par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4659: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4660: chos thams cad kun tu bzang po'i rol par ye
NK071(du)002:4661: nas dag pas thams cad la spangs blang med par
NK071(du)002:4662: spyod par bya'o zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o
NK071(du)002:4663: // zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ched du gleng ngo //
NK071(du)002:4664: tshul 'dis ni thams cad rang snang du bstan te
NK071(du)002:4665: rang snang rang gi sems nyid gnyis su med pa
NK071(du)002:4666: rol pa rmi lam dang 'dra bar ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)002:4667: kyis ma skyes par bstan to //
NK071(du)002:4668: chos nyid gsang ba'i snying po gang snang ye shes
NK071(du)002:4669: kyi rol pa de kho na nyid nges pa las
NK071(du)002:4670: rnal 'byor pa lta spyod mthun pa kun 'dus pa
NK071(du)002:4671: dang de rnams kyis 'byor pa'i yo byad bde bar
NK071(du)002:4672: spyod pa dang / de'i dus su yi dam gyi lha dang /
NK071(du)002:4673: mkha' 'gro dam can 'du bar byed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:4674: zhen 'dzin med pa'i sgo nas rgyud la tshogs gnyis
NK071(du)002:4675: rdzogs par byed pas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u
NK071(du)002:4678: // don gnyis pa de'i yan lag bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:4683: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa de nas de bzhin
NK071(du)002:4684: gshegs pa chos thams cad gnyis su med par rol
NK071(du)002:4685: pa'i dgyes pa chen po kun tu bzang pos snang
NK071(du)002:4686: srid kyi chos thams cad ye shes kyi rol mo'i
NK071(du)002:4687: sprin 'dod dgu lhun rdzogs su 'byung ba'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:4688: nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa kun tu rnam par spros
NK071(du)002:4689: te / sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang 'gro ba drug
NK071(du)002:4690: gi spyod yul thams cad du longs spyod chen pos
NK071(du)002:4691: 'byor pa'i rgyan rang rang gi snang ba dang mthun
NK071(du)002:4692: par bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK071(du)002:4693: nas ston pa nyid kyis rang snang dag pa'i 'khor
NK071(du)002:4694: bkod pa na bskul zhing zhu ba po'i rnam pa
NK071(du)002:4695: med par ched du brjod pa 'di dag rang byung
NK071(du)002:4696: te / du brjod do // gnyis pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:4697: tshogs kyi ting nge 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:4698: tshogs bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:4699: tshogs kyi rten dkyil 'khor kun 'dus pa chen po'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:4704: chos thams cad ye shes kyi rol pa sgyu 'phrul
NK071(du)002:4705: d+r+wa ba'i rang bzhin yab yum zung du 'brel bas
NK071(du)002:4707: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa nyid
NK071(du)002:4708: blos gsal gdab cing goms par byas pa'i don brtan
NK071(du)002:4709: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phro 'dus mchog dang thun
NK071(du)002:4711: gnyis pa lnga las bro gar gyi gyi ting nge
NK071(du)002:4712: 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa la gnyis las ting
NK071(du)002:4713: nge 'dzin ni lus kyi mgo la sogs pa yan
NK071(du)002:4714: lag lnga rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed cing sa
NK071(du)002:4715: gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin la gnas khang lha'i gzhal
NK071(du)002:4716: yas khang mdzes pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam
NK071(du)002:4717: par dag par mos par byas te rkang pa'i bro
NK071(du)002:4718: dang lag pa'i gar gyi phyag rgya rnam pa sna
NK071(du)002:4719: tshogs pa'i 'du 'phro lha'i phyag rgya chen po yis
NK071(du)002:4720: mchod par bya'o // phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:4721: sa la 'dzul lam ri brag rnams la thogs pa
NK071(du)002:4722: med pas sa 'og gi phyag rgya klu mo rnams
NK071(du)002:4724: steng gi lam nam mkhar yad bya bzhin du 'gro
NK071(du)002:4725: bar 'gyur zhing lha dang lha ma yin la sogs
NK071(du)002:4727: gnyis pa klu'i phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4728: rang gi lkog mar h+r+aihbakoda la ngag gi gdangs glu
NK071(du)002:4729: snyan po dang de'i tshig bstod pa la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:4730: sgra yi phyag rgyas ni dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams
NK071(du)002:4732: gsung mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo gcig gis
NK071(du)002:4733: go bar nus pa'i chos kyi dung zhes bya ba'i
NK071(du)002:4735: gsum pa rgyan dang gos kyi phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:4736: ting nge 'dzin ni t+r+aa las dbu rgyan la sogs pa rnams rin po cher gsal zhing /
NK071(du)002:4737: a las gos rnams lha'i gos dang zhi khro'i cha
NK071(du)002:4738: lugs su byin gyis rlabs te rin po che dang
NK071(du)002:4739: rus pa la sogs pa'i rgyan dang stod g.yogs dang
NK071(du)002:4740: smad dkris la sogs pa'i bgo ba'i rigs rnams la
NK071(du)002:4741: mchod pa'i phyag rgya yis longs spyod do //
NK071(du)002:4743: gnas skabs su 'od dang gzi brjid sred med kyi
NK071(du)002:4744: bus kyang mi shigs pa'i go cha sra ba'i gos
NK071(du)002:4745: su gyur cig mthar thug mtshan dang dpe byad kyis
NK071(du)002:4746: 'bar ba'i 'khor los bsgyur ba byang chub sems dpa'
NK071(du)002:4747: rnams kyi rgyal po phyir rgol gang gis kyang thub
NK071(du)002:4748: pa med pa'i sangs rgyas nyid 'grub bo //
NK071(du)002:4749: bzhi pa bza' btung gi phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:4751: kham las bza' btung bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs te
NK071(du)002:4752: nya dang sha la sogs pa'i bza' ba dang ja
NK071(du)002:4753: dang chang la sogs pa'i btung ba'i phyag rgyas ni
NK071(du)002:4754: phyi nang gi lha mchod par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4756: rang gi lus 'dod dgur bsgyur ba yid bzhin gyi
NK071(du)002:4757: nor bu lta bu'i sku dang gsung ro bro ba'i
NK071(du)002:4758: mchog gang la longs spyod pa de dag ro brgya
NK071(du)002:4759: dang ldan pa'i bdud rtsi ru 'grub bo //
NK071(du)002:4760: lnga pa sbyor sgrol gyi phyag rgya'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:4761: yab yum lhar gsal ba'i mkha' gsang du dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:4762: spyan drangs te +aa li bde ba chen po'i mchod
NK071(du)002:4763: pa dang zhing dang zhing phran gyi sha khrag bdud
NK071(du)002:4764: rtsir gyur pas mchod pa k+aa li sgrol ba'i phyag
NK071(du)002:4766: phan yon ni sbyor bas zag pa med pa'i ting
NK071(du)002:4767: nge 'dzin la sogs pa mchog dang thun mong gi
NK071(du)002:4768: dngos grub thams cad dang sgrol bas gdug pa can
NK071(du)002:4769: tshar bcad de rang bzhin gyi gnod pa zhi ba
NK071(du)002:4770: dang / pha rol thar pa la sogs pa'i phrin
NK071(du)002:4771: las rlabs po che thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:4772: dang / // gnyis pa tshogs bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:4774: des grub pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu /
NK071(du)002:4775: de mthar thug pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK071(du)002:4778: chos thams cad rtogs pa bzhi'i tshul gyis ye nas
NK071(du)002:4779: sangs rgyas par shes pa'i mtshan nyid kyis lta ba
NK071(du)002:4780: phun sum tshogs pa'i gnas lugs rgyud la 'byor pa'i
NK071(du)002:4781: gzungs ni 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi smin par byed
NK071(du)002:4782: pa'i rgyu yin zhing shes nas sgrub pa la 'jug
NK071(du)002:4783: pa'i mtshan nyid bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel du 'byor ba'i
NK071(du)002:4784: gzungs ni / 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhir smin par
NK071(du)002:4785: byed pa'i rkyen te de ltar rgyu dang rkyen la
NK071(du)002:4786: goms shing 'dris par byas pas nus mthu khyad par
NK071(du)002:4787: can du gang gyur pa de ni /
NK071(du)002:4788: rgyu sa bon drung po rkyen chu lud kyis bran
NK071(du)002:4789: pas 'bras bu myu gu nas ston thog gi bar
NK071(du)002:4790: du 'byung ba bzhin rnam par smin pa nas lhun
NK071(du)002:4791: gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi bar du 'byung ngo
NK071(du)002:4792: / gnyis pa des grub pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:4793: de lta bu'i rig 'dzin rnams ni rgyal ba skyed
NK071(du)002:4794: par byed pa'i zhing yang yin la phyogs bcu'i sangs
NK071(du)002:4795: rgyas kyi zhing du grags shing lung bstan pa'ang 'thob
NK071(du)002:4796: po // gnyis pa des grub pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:4797: 'gro ba gang gis bsdus pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4798: rig 'dzin de dag las kha cig gling bzhi'i mi
NK071(du)002:4799: dang 'dod pa'i lha dang gzugs kyi tshangs pa la
NK071(du)002:4800: sogs pa yi / gnas su skye ba rnam par dag pa 'dzin mod kyi /
NK071(du)002:4801: khyad par du sa bcu la gnas par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK071(du)002:4802: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu po kun tu rdzogs
NK071(du)002:4803: par rgyud la thob pa'i phyir zhes rgyu'i sas bsdus
NK071(du)002:4804: tshul dang / 'bras bu'i sas bsdus tshul bshad na //
NK071(du)002:4805: lhun grub de khyad par gyis bcu gsum rdo rje
NK071(du)002:4806: 'dzin pa la gnas par 'gyur ba yin te 'bras
NK071(du)002:4807: bu mthar thug gi sgrub byed rgyu'i pha rol tu
NK071(du)002:4808: phyin pa bcu po kun tu rdzogs pa'i phyir zhes
NK071(du)002:4809: so // phyir mi ldog khyad par gyis sa bsdus
NK071(du)002:4810: tshul du bshad pa rig 'dzin bzhi po thams cad
NK071(du)002:4811: 'bras bu'i rig 'dzin la gnas par nges pas khyad
NK071(du)002:4812: par gyi sa la gnas par 'gyur ba yin te
NK071(du)002:4813: sa de nyid grub pa'i ngo bo rgyu dang 'bras
NK071(du)002:4814: bu'i pha rol tu phyin pa kun tu rdzogs par
NK071(du)002:4815: bsgrub pa'i rim pa dper na lcags kyus zin pa'i
NK071(du)002:4816: nya skam sar 'don pa bzhin ces pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4817: gsum pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni /
NK071(du)002:4818: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa ni thabs mthar
NK071(du)002:4819: phyin pa rnam par 'phrul pa'i sprul pa dang phrin
NK071(du)002:4820: las kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba bcu gcig kun tu
NK071(du)002:4821: 'od sprul sku'i sa dang shes rab dang thabs kyi
NK071(du)002:4822: mchog zung du 'brel ba mthar thug pa bcu gnyis
NK071(du)002:4823: ma chags pa pad+ma can lhun stug bkod pa'i zhing
NK071(du)002:4824: khams rtsol med du rang snang ba'i sa dang /
NK071(du)002:4825: shes rab mchog gi sa longs sprul gnyis chos sku'i
NK071(du)002:4826: gzhi la mya ngan las 'das pa de'i dbyings su
NK071(du)002:4827: thim pa'i gzhir gyur pa'i mchog tu gyur pa'i lhun
NK071(du)002:4828: grub rin po che'i sbubs chos kyi sku spros pa
NK071(du)002:4829: thams cad dang bral ba'i zhing khams gdod ma'i kun
NK071(du)002:4831: de ltar gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi sa yi
NK071(du)002:4832: khyad par rab tu dga' ba la sogs pa bcu
NK071(du)002:4833: dang kun tu 'od la sogs pa gsum ni /
NK071(du)002:4834: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i khyad par gyis phye ba ste
NK071(du)002:4835: btsal ba med par rang bzhin lhun gyis rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:4836: ni mthar thug gi thob bya'o //
NK071(du)002:4837: gsum pa tshogs kyi rten dkyil 'khor kun 'dus pa chen pos don bsdu ba la gsum /
NK071(du)002:4838: kun tu bzang po'i bskyed rdzogs bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:4840: phra mo'i nyes pas mi gos pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4845: ting nge 'dzin gsum sngon du song bas nam mkha'
NK071(du)002:4846: yi dkyil rab tu dwangs ba'i dbyings ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:4847: gzhal yas khang 'od dang bcas pa'i nang na nyi
NK071(du)002:4849: ye shes rgyal po kun tu bzang po stangs dpyal
NK071(du)002:4850: gnyis zung du sbyor bas rdo rje'i dkyil krung mnyam
NK071(du)002:4851: bzhag dang bcas pa'i sku las 'od zer du ma
NK071(du)002:4853: de ltar bsgom pas rgya ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun /
NK071(du)002:4854: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur te lha'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:4855: 'khor thams cad kyang sku gsung thugs dang dbyings rang
NK071(du)002:4856: bzhin gyis dag pa gcig tu 'du ba'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:4858: 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi dang shar la sogs pa'i phyogs bcu gang nas kyang /
NK071(du)002:4859: sems las logs su gyur pa'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhig rnyed par mi 'gyur te /
NK071(du)002:4860: sems kyi rang bzhin ji ltar gnas pa de nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te /
NK071(du)002:4861: sangs rgyas sems kyi rang bzhin las gzhan med pas yum dus gzhan nas ma 'tshol zhig /
NK071(du)002:4862: gnyis pa tshul des dkyil 'khor kun grub pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4863: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po gcig gi bskyed rdzogs la rab tu sbyor bas /
NK071(du)002:4864: de las 'phros pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams
NK071(du)002:4865: cad 'grub par 'gyur te nyi zla grub pa na
NK071(du)002:4866: de'i 'od zer ma lus pa thams cad 'grub pa
NK071(du)002:4867: bzhin no // gsum pa nyes pa phra mos mi gos pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4868: thams cad sems kyi rang bzhin du shes pas spangs
NK071(du)002:4869: blang gnyis su med pa de lta bu'i don rtogs
NK071(du)002:4870: na rdzogs rim la dbang 'byor bas bskyed rim gyi
NK071(du)002:4871: cho ga phra mo rnams la lhag gam ma tshang
NK071(du)002:4872: na yang / cho ga'i yan lag nyams pa'i skyon
NK071(du)002:4873: nyid dag ste dngos grub la bsgrib pa'i nyes pa
NK071(du)002:4874: na yang / med do / gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:4875: de skad ces rang snang dag pa'i 'khor la ched
NK071(du)002:4876: du brjod pas ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo'i sprin
NK071(du)002:4877: gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur
NK071(du)002:4878: to // thabs kyi rol pa mchog tu gsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:4879: snying po snang bcas tshogs kyi de kho na nyid
NK071(du)002:4880: nges pa las lam bsod nams dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:4881: tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4883: // don gnyis pa snying po'i don la 'jug pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:4888: lam bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa de nas rdzogs
NK071(du)002:4889: pa'i rim pa bstan pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)002:4890: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo
NK071(du)002:4891: rje'i dkyil 'khor thams cad gcig tu bsdus nas gnas
NK071(du)002:4892: pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang po ye shes bla
NK071(du)002:4893: na med pa'i dgyes pa chen pos rol ste /
NK071(du)002:4894: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK071(du)002:4895: ye nas rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK071(du)002:4896: dam tshig ni snod du ma gyur pa rnams la
NK071(du)002:4897: shin tu gsang ba'i rang bzhin de kho na nyid
NK071(du)002:4898: kyi snying po sprin skal ba mchog dang ldan pa
NK071(du)002:4899: rnams la bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK071(du)002:4900: zhugs nas man ngag gi dam pa'i ched du brjod
NK071(du)002:4903: don gsang ba rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas tshul spyir bstan pa dang //
NK071(du)002:4904: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4907: spyir theg pa so so'i don mthar thug rang rang gi ston byed slob dpon la rag las shing /
NK071(du)002:4908: khyad par du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don
NK071(du)002:4909: mthar thug pa rgyud lung gi gzhung tshig la gab
NK071(du)002:4910: cing sbas pa rnams bla ma'i thugs la gnas pas
NK071(du)002:4911: gdams ngag 'dod pas bla ma mnyes par bya ba
NK071(du)002:4912: la thug go / de'ang theg pa bsam gyis mi
NK071(du)002:4913: khyab cing brjod pa las 'das pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK071(du)002:4914: zhing dang sems can gyi gnas ris grangs med pa
NK071(du)002:4915: na yod pas ma nges mod kyi /
NK071(du)002:4916: da lta'i skal pa bzang po 'di dang mi mjed
NK071(du)002:4917: kyi 'jig rten 'dir dman pa dang mchog dang phyin
NK071(du)002:4918: ci log gi theg pa dang gzhung lugs kyi tshul
NK071(du)002:4919: byung ba rnams / re zhig mdor bsdu na brgyad las //
NK071(du)002:4920: dang po yang dag pa'i don ma rtogs pa dang
NK071(du)002:4921: ni grub pa'i mtha' la ma zhugs pa'i skye bo
NK071(du)002:4922: phal pa ste legs pa tsam zhig don du gnyer
NK071(du)002:4923: bas bde 'gro sgrub pa sor bzhag lha mi'i theg
NK071(du)002:4924: pa zhes dge ba bcus 'dod pa'i lha dang mir
NK071(du)002:4925: 'phen zhing bsam gtan dang gzugs med kyis khams gong
NK071(du)002:4926: ma sgrub pa'o // log par rtog pa ni mu
NK071(du)002:4927: stegs byed de lta ba log pa'i grangs kyis de'i
NK071(du)002:4928: dbye ba bsam gyis mi khyab kyang bsdu na /
NK071(du)002:4929: rtag lta sde bzhi chad par lta ba dang bcas pas tir ti ka sde lngar grags te /
NK071(du)002:4931: dbang phyug rtag par smra ba rig pa can dang /
NK071(du)002:4932: khyab 'jug rtag par smra ba khyab 'jug pa dang
NK071(du)002:4933: gtso bo rtag par smra ba grangs can pa dang
NK071(du)002:4934: / rdul phran rtag par smra ba bye brag pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4935: chad par lta ba ni rgyang 'phen pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4936: yang dag pa'i don phyogs tsam rtogs pa ni nyan
NK071(du)002:4937: thos dang rang sangs rgyas gnyis te bdag med gcig
NK071(du)002:4938: dang phyed dang gnyis rtogs shing 'khor ba las grol
NK071(du)002:4939: ba'o // gnas lugs kyi don mthar thug par yang
NK071(du)002:4940: dag pa mnyam pa nyid ma rtogs pa ni mtshan
NK071(du)002:4941: nyid kyi theg pa chen po ste rgyu sems can
NK071(du)002:4942: gyis tshogs gnyis bsgrubs pas 'bras bu bskal pa grangs
NK071(du)002:4943: med pa du ma nas sangs rgyas gdod 'grub par
NK071(du)002:4944: 'dod cing lta ba bdag gnyis kyi stong pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:4945: nyid du thag chod kyang chos thams cad ye nas
NK071(du)002:4946: sangs rgyas par mnyam pa'i don ma mthong ba'o //
NK071(du)002:4947: gtsang sbra dang dka' thub gtso bor byed pas sgo
NK071(du)002:4948: gsum gyi nyes spyod 'dul ba ni bya spyod rgyud
NK071(du)002:4949: de sems bskyed tsam la brten nas lha sgrub pa
NK071(du)002:4950: dang dka' thub dang smyung gnas tsam la brten nas
NK071(du)002:4952: rigs gtad dang rjes gnang tsam la brten nas lha
NK071(du)002:4953: sgrub pa ste gsum du yod do dgongs pa ni
NK071(du)002:4954: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de a b+ai pra ya'i sgra
NK071(du)002:4955: las sems kyi dgongs pa la 'jug cing sems rtse
NK071(du)002:4956: gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gtso bas lha sgrub pa'o
NK071(du)002:4957: // sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba gsal por ston
NK071(du)002:4958: pa dang ni rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud de bskyed
NK071(du)002:4959: rim gtso bor ston pa pha'i rgyud dang rdzogs rim
NK071(du)002:4960: gtso bor ston pa ma'i rgyud dang //
NK071(du)002:4961: zung 'jug gtso bor ston pa gnyis su med pa'i rgyud do //
NK071(du)002:4962: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:4963: don rmad du byung ba ni rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK071(du)002:4964: sems dang ye shes rang snang bar ston pa sgyu
NK071(du)002:4965: 'phrul chen po ste kun gyi spyod yul ma yin
NK071(du)002:4966: pa'i ngo bo nyid rang bzhin dang thabs khyad par
NK071(du)002:4967: can gyis gsang ba ste dbye na sems dang ye
NK071(du)002:4968: shes gnyis med du ston pa bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug
NK071(du)002:4970: sems gtso bor ston pa sems klong ye grol gyi rdzogs pa chen po /
NK071(du)002:4971: ye shes gtso bor ston pa 'od gsal chos nyid kyi rdzogs pa chen po'o /
NK071(du)002:4972: de ltar theg pa so so'i tshul rnams ni gtan la dbab par bya ba'i don no //
NK071(du)002:4973: gnyis pa don de gang gi dbyings na gnas tshul bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4974: theg pa de dag gi don rnams brjod byed kyi
NK071(du)002:4975: gzhung la gnas shing gzhung yang yi ge sil bu'i
NK071(du)002:4976: khong na gnas pas sgra dang tha snyad btags pa
NK071(du)002:4977: las ming du tshogs pa'i spyi la /
NK071(du)002:4978: brten nas tshig gi shwa lo ka dang rab tu
NK071(du)002:4979: byed pa dang bstan bcos sam rgyud sde so so'i
NK071(du)002:4980: lus grub cing gzhung des rang rang gi brjod bya'i
NK071(du)002:4981: don rab tu mtshon te gnas so //
NK071(du)002:4982: gsum pa don de ma nor ba gang gis ston pa ni /
NK071(du)002:4983: de ltar gzhung tshig so so'i khong nas rang rang
NK071(du)002:4984: gi brjod bya'i don 'byin pa dang khyad par rgyud
NK071(du)002:4985: tshig so so'i khung nas chos thams cad ye nas
NK071(du)002:4986: sangs rgyas pa la sogs pa'i don rnams gab cing
NK071(du)002:4987: tha mal pa'i spyod yul du bsgrag tu mi rung
NK071(du)002:4988: ba'i gsang ba zab mo rnams brda' la sogs pas
NK071(du)002:4989: sbas pa'i don rnams mngon sum du 'byin pa ni
NK071(du)002:4990: / rgyud kyi don phyin ci ma log par ston
NK071(du)002:4991: pa rdo rje'i slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas pas
NK071(du)002:4993: gnyis par rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don bye brag tu bshad pa gsum /
NK071(du)002:4994: snying po'i zab don dngos bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:4995: de bzhan las khyad par 'phags tshul /
NK071(du)002:4996: gang la gdams pa'i snod bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:4997: dang po la gsum mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:5000: dang po la gsum las thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5001: phung po khams dang skye mched kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:5002: thams cad ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5003: du sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin te 'gro ba kun
NK071(du)002:5004: ye nas de ltar gnas pa ni gzhi lhun gyis
NK071(du)002:5005: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rang chas su ldan pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:5006: bzhin te de ltar rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)002:5007: dkyil 'khor gyis / ye nas yin pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5008: la ni yin pa shes pa'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK071(du)002:5010: gnyis pa shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5011: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i dkyil 'khor rtog
NK071(du)002:5012: tshogs nyon mongs su snang ba thams cad thabs kyis
NK071(du)002:5013: zin pa'i dkyil 'khor las byung ba ste /
NK071(du)002:5014: de nyid ma spangs rang sar dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5015: yin pas thugs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste dkyil
NK071(du)002:5016: 'khor thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5017: gsum pa gnyis med 'od gsal gyi rim pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5018: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa na
NK071(du)002:5019: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa sku dang ye shes
NK071(du)002:5020: kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5021: gsang ba'i thig le rmad du byung ba ste rkyen
NK071(du)002:5022: bla ma'i man ngag gis nyams su blangs na sku
NK071(du)002:5023: gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:5024: 'khor thams cad 'byung ba'i dbyings yin no //
NK071(du)002:5025: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:5028: gsang ba 'od gsal gyi rim pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5029: dang po la gnyis las lta bas thag bcad pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5030: phyi 'byung ba lngar snang ba'i gzugs brnyan ni med
NK071(du)002:5031: bzhin snang ba'i chos nyid rang bzhin gyi rnam par
NK071(du)002:5032: dag pa'i gnas lugs shes rab kyi pha rol tu
NK071(du)002:5033: phyin ma stong pa nyid gzugs su snang ba ste
NK071(du)002:5034: gdod ma nas ngo bo nyid med pa'i rigs chos
NK071(du)002:5035: nyid kyi rol pa'am yum du gnas so //
NK071(du)002:5036: phung po lnga la chen po zhes rigs kyi yab
NK071(du)002:5037: lnga'i de bzhin nyid gzugs stong pa'i rang bzhin te
NK071(du)002:5038: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:5039: rig pa byang chub kyi sems gzhi dang rtsa ba
NK071(du)002:5040: med pa'i rang bzhin ye nas rnam par rtog pa
NK071(du)002:5041: yul la mi rtog pa ni rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5042: kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi tshogs so //
NK071(du)002:5043: de'ang rig pa gsal ba dang stong pa gnyis su
NK071(du)002:5044: med pa'i dbyings brjod du med pa ni bgrang ba
NK071(du)002:5045: las 'das pa'i ye shes kun gyi 'byung gnas yin
NK071(du)002:5046: pas kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi tshogs zhes
NK071(du)002:5048: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po dang gzugs la sogs
NK071(du)002:5049: pa'i yul 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus mig gi
NK071(du)002:5050: rnam par shes pa la sogs pa'i rig pa rnams
NK071(du)002:5051: kyang sems dpa' dang sems ma dang sgo ba'i bar
NK071(du)002:5052: du rnam par dag la de dag gi rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5053: yang snang la ngo bo med par lta bar bya'o
NK071(du)002:5054: // gnyis pa sgom pas nyams su blang ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5055: snang srid kyi chos thams cad snang dus nyid nas
NK071(du)002:5056: ngo bo med pa kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5057: la / dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin zhen med
NK071(du)002:5058: pa'i blo spros pa dang bral ba'i ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)002:5059: bdag nyid chen po kun tu bzang po yab yum
NK071(du)002:5060: gyi lhag pa yi dgongs pa zab mo yin te
NK071(du)002:5061: la / / de nyid kyi ngang la me long
NK071(du)002:5062: lta bu la sogs pa thugs kyi ye shes lngas
NK071(du)002:5063: la / / lta zhing / de'ang phyi yul gyi
NK071(du)002:5064: rnam pa ma 'gags par snang ba ni me long
NK071(du)002:5066: de'i ngo bo stong pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:5067: der 'dzin med pa ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:5068: gzugs sgra la sogs pa so sor snang ba ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:5069: dgag sgrub la sogs pa'i nyon mongs grol ba ni bya ba 'grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK071(du)002:5070: yang na dug lnga shar dus ngos zin pa tsam
NK071(du)002:5071: gyis ma spangs gnas su dag pa ni ye shes
NK071(du)002:5072: lnga'o // yang sems rtse gcig mnyam par bzhag pa'i
NK071(du)002:5073: tshe ngo bo stong pa nyid ni chos dbyings ye
NK071(du)002:5074: lnga'o // shes so // rig pa'i gsal dwangs ma 'gags pa ni me long ye shes /
NK071(du)002:5075: gnyis 'dzin med pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK071(du)002:5076: snang yul ma 'gags pa sor rtog ye shes /
NK071(du)002:5077: gzung 'dzin grol ba bya grub ye shes so /
NK071(du)002:5078: gnyis pa nang rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:5079: bde stong gi don la sgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5080: yab yum gyi dwangs ma dkar dmar gyi snying po
NK071(du)002:5081: thig le rdo rje dang pad+ma'i rtser phan tshun 'dres
NK071(du)002:5082: shing mnyam par sbyor bas thob pa'i /
NK071(du)002:5083: bde ba dang stong pa'i ye shes mchog tu gsang ba'i rol mo yis /
NK071(du)002:5084: mkha' gsang gi dkyil 'khor du spyan drangs pa'i lha
NK071(du)002:5085: rnams mchod cing rlung gis gyen du drangs te 'khor
NK071(du)002:5086: lo bzhi'i rtsa dang lus thams cad na rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5087: gyis gnas pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor dang rang
NK071(du)002:5088: gi sems nyid bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyis
NK071(du)002:5089: rab tu dgyes pa chen por gyur pa la bde
NK071(du)002:5090: stong gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa 'bul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:5092: de ltar zag pa med pa'i mchod pa phul ba'i bsod nams kyis /
NK071(du)002:5093: gnas skabs rig 'dzin gsum dang grub pa chen po
NK071(du)002:5094: brgyad thob cing mthar thug lhun gyis grub pa'i rig
NK071(du)002:5095: 'dzin gyi zhing ye shes kyi sgyu ma sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:5097: lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang bzhin bkod pa tshad
NK071(du)002:5098: med pa'i rol mo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas
NK071(du)002:5099: shing mchog chos sku'i zhing khams kun tu bzang po'i
NK071(du)002:5100: gzhi la mthar phyin pa nyid 'thob bo //
NK071(du)002:5101: gsum pa gsang ba 'od gsal gyi rim pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:5102: dang po gzhi 'od gsal gyi rang bzhin ngos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5103: 'khor lo bzhi dang khyad par snying ga na gnas
NK071(du)002:5104: pa 'od gsal gsang ba'i thig le sku dang ye
NK071(du)002:5105: shes kyi dkyil 'khor ni lhun gyis grub pa'i de
NK071(du)002:5106: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings 'og min stug pa bkod pa'i
NK071(du)002:5107: rang bzhin du gnas pa de ye nas sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:5108: kun gyi dngos por lhun gyis grub pas sku gsum
NK071(du)002:5109: rang la gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)002:5110: gnyis pa lam ye shes kyi snang ba ngos bzung ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5111: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor bsgoms pas ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:5112: gyi snang yul 'od dang thig le la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:5113: mthong ba ni / phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon par
NK071(du)002:5114: rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:5115: sku dang gsung dang yon tan dang phrin las dang
NK071(du)002:5117: ma lus pa'i bdag nyid kyi zhal mthong ba yin pas /
NK071(du)002:5118: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sangs rgyas la
NK071(du)002:5119: ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur ba de nyid chos
NK071(du)002:5120: thams cad kyi mchog nyid kyi dam pa yin te
NK071(du)002:5121: gnas lugs mthar thug gi don sgom pa yin pa'i
NK071(du)002:5122: phyir ro // de ltar sgom pa'i tshe rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5123: gyi dkyil 'khor dang ting nge 'dzin bskyed pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:5124: 'khor la gnas pa des rang snang 'od gsal gyi
NK071(du)002:5126: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa ye shes chen po'i
NK071(du)002:5127: dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pas lam gong nas
NK071(du)002:5128: gong gi yon tan rdzogs par mngon du byed do
NK071(du)002:5129: // khyad par rang snang rigs lnga'i zhing du gyur
NK071(du)002:5130: pa de'i tshe phyi dang nang gi rtsa gnas 'khor
NK071(du)002:5131: lo thams cad na ye shes kyi rang bzhin rig
NK071(du)002:5132: pa'i rgyan du lha so so'i dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK071(du)002:5133: pa thogs te yon tan brgya phrag bcu la sogs
NK071(du)002:5134: // pas mdzes so // de nas de dag gi
NK071(du)002:5135: 'dzin pa thams cad zad pa na sa dang lam
NK071(du)002:5136: gyi rang bzhin ye nas dag pa'i chos nyid zad
NK071(du)002:5138: 'bras bu longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyiil 'khor chos sku'i
NK071(du)002:5139: dkyil 'khor dang gnyis su med par mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)002:5140: bas / thugs rje sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa lhun grub chen por yongs kyis 'byung zhing /
NK071(du)002:5141: de'i mthus phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i 'jig rten drug gi
NK071(du)002:5142: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa 'dul ba'i mgon du gyur
NK071(du)002:5143: pa ste / thub pa drug la sogs pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:5144: bzhin du snang bas sems can sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK071(du)002:5145: dkyil 'khor thams cad 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las sgrol
NK071(du)002:5146: ba'i phrin las phun sum tshogs par mdzad pa yis
NK071(du)002:5147: gang la gang 'dul du snang yang /
NK071(du)002:5148: snang dus nyid nas bsgral bar bya ba'i sems can
NK071(du)002:5149: rang mtshan pa dang sgrol bar byed pa'i sprul pa
NK071(du)002:5150: bden pa med par gdul bya dang 'dul byed kyi
NK071(du)002:5151: dkyil 'khor gzugs brnyan dang sprul pa lta bur spyod
NK071(du)002:5152: pa'o // gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5153: chos thams cad ye nas sku dang ye shes su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa la /
NK071(du)002:5154: de ltar shes par byed pa'i thos pa dang de'i
NK071(du)002:5155: don sems kyis dpyod pa'i bsam pa dang de thog
NK071(du)002:5156: tu sgom par byed pa'i rang bzhin thabs bskyed pa
NK071(du)002:5157: dang shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)002:5158: ba'i don gyis / bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu rang byung
NK071(du)002:5159: gi ye shes gdul bya'i don la thugs rje chen
NK071(du)002:5160: pos kun nas dam par mdzad pa'i phrin las dang
NK071(du)002:5161: bcas pa lhun gyis grub pa 'thob bo //
NK071(du)002:5162: de ltar bu'i tshul phun sum tshogs pa 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)002:5163: bslu ba med pa'i chos su zhal gyis bzhes shing
NK071(du)002:5164: lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis su med par bsgoms pa'i 'bras
NK071(du)002:5165: bu sangs rgyas grub pa'i rang bzhin las 'da' bar
NK071(du)002:5166: mi mdzad pa'i dam tshig gi mchog tu bstan pa
NK071(du)002:5167: yin no // gnyis pa de gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:5168: sgrub pa po gang zag gi che ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5169: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig theg pa 'di la mos par gyur pa tsam yang /
NK071(du)002:5170: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)002:5171: rang rang bzhugs pa'i phyogs dang dus ma lus pa kun nas dus dang rnam pa thams cad du /
NK071(du)002:5172: gsang chen don gyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams
NK071(du)002:5173: cad rgyud la bsnyen pa ste myur du 'thob pa
NK071(du)002:5174: yi / rang bzhin rmad du byung ba'i gsang ba la nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:5175: gnyis pa sgrub thabs lam gyi che ba la bzhi las /
NK071(du)002:5176: lam kun gyi 'bras bu yin pa'i che ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5177: dus kyi yun bskal pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing gi rdul phra ba snyed du /
NK071(du)002:5178: rgyu'i theg pa sna tshogs la shin tu sbyangs te
NK071(du)002:5179: de la rab tu gnas par byas shing brtson pa
NK071(du)002:5180: dang / gsang sngags kyi theg pa'i sgo nas phyi
NK071(du)002:5181: nang gi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa bsnyen cing bsgrub
NK071(du)002:5182: pa de thams cad kyi don du gnyer bya yi
NK071(du)002:5183: dang / / 'bras bu gsang chen a ti yo
NK071(du)002:5184: ga'i theg pa 'di yin te sangs rgyas pa la
NK071(du)002:5185: thams cad lam 'di la rag lus pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:5186: dang / / // gnyis pa rgyal ba kun gyi gshegs shul yin par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5187: s+n+rel gzhi dang steng 'og la sogs pa'i 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK071(du)002:5188: sngar 'das pa dang da ltar byung nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa yi /
NK071(du)002:5189: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyang /
NK071(du)002:5190: lam 'di la bsnyen nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs
NK071(du)002:5191: te dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad la bgrod
NK071(du)002:5192: lam gcig po 'di las gzhan med pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:5193: // gsum pa rnal 'byor pa kun gyi lam yin par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5194: sngar dang da ltar byung ba'i rnal 'byor pa kun
NK071(du)002:5195: dang ma 'ongs pa na 'byung ba'i rig 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)002:5197: lam 'di yis lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin sangs
NK071(du)002:5198: rgyas kyis 'grub par 'gyur te dus gsum gyi sangs
NK071(du)002:5199: rgyas thams cad kyi lam la tha dad med pa'i
NK071(du)002:5200: phyir ro // bzhi pa rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5201: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i tshul 'di
NK071(du)002:5202: ni theg pa 'og ma la ma grags pa'i gsang
NK071(du)002:5203: chen 'bras bu mngon du byed nges pa yi man
NK071(du)002:5204: ngag / tshe 'di nyid la 'bras bu'i ngo bo
NK071(du)002:5205: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor lam du byas
NK071(du)002:5206: pas gzhan nas sgrub ma dgos par rang chas su
NK071(du)002:5207: grub pa'i sangs rgyas nye lam 'dis mngon du gyur
NK071(du)002:5208: ngag / pa yin no // gsum pa de las
NK071(du)002:5209: mchog tu gyur pa'i lam gzhan med par bstan pa
NK071(du)002:5210: ngag / pa yin no // ni / phyogs bcu
NK071(du)002:5211: dus bzhi'i rgyal ba snga phyir gshegs shing da ltar
NK071(du)002:5212: bzhugs pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus thams cad la /
NK071(du)002:5213: a ti'i theg pa ye grol lhun gyis rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:5214: 'di las gzhan pa'i nye lam gsang ba'i nges don
NK071(du)002:5216: gzhan du btsal kyang rgyal bas de las zab pa'i
NK071(du)002:5217: chos nam yang mi brnyes so ste mi rnyed pa'i
NK071(du)002:5218: don to // gsum pa gang la gdams pa'i snod bstan pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:5219: skal bzang sbyin pa'i snod ni /
NK071(du)002:5220: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba phyag rgya chen po'i
NK071(du)002:5221: mchog rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud 'di nyid
NK071(du)002:5222: / gang zag mang du thos pa'i tshig gi rim
NK071(du)002:5223: pa la mkhas shing de'i don bsam byung gi shes
NK071(du)002:5224: rab kyis dpyad pas don la mkhas pa de nyid
NK071(du)002:5225: bsgom pa la yang dang yang du legs par rab
NK071(du)002:5226: / tu sbyangs pa'i / shes rab kyi mig dang ldan pa rnams kyis zungs shig /
NK071(du)002:5227: de las kyang rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i snod
NK071(du)002:5228: dang ldan pas zab mo'i don rlabs po che la
NK071(du)002:5229: mi skrag cing sems kyi ngang tshul dge zhing bzang
NK071(du)002:5230: la dad pa brtan pa de la chos 'di gtad
NK071(du)002:5231: par bya zhing / rang gi lus dang longs spyod
NK071(du)002:5232: thams cad bla ma dang chos kyi phyogs su gtong
NK071(du)002:5233: nus pa la yongs su rdzogs par sbyin no //
NK071(du)002:5234: gnyis pa skal med la mi sbyin par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5235: sbyin par bya ba'i snod las gzhan du bstan yang mi go ba dang /
NK071(du)002:5236: go yang phyin ci log tu spyod cing sdom pa
NK071(du)002:5237: dang dam tshig 'chal ba bsnyen sgrub tshogs gnyis las
NK071(du)002:5238: g.yel ba basnganga zhing skrag pa skye ba rnams la
NK071(du)002:5239: dus nam yang sbyin par mi bya ste nyes pa
NK071(du)002:5240: chen pos gdung bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:5241: yang dag pa'i don la rmongs par gyur pa la
NK071(du)002:5242: mi shes shing skal pa med pa dang sgo gsum
NK071(du)002:5243: 'phyar ba ma bsdams ma zhi bas sdig pa byed
NK071(du)002:5244: cing gsang ba sgrogs pa sogs pa gal te sbyin
NK071(du)002:5245: na / mkha' 'gro dang dam can gyi chad pas dus min par ni srog zad nas /
NK071(du)002:5246: tshe'i dus byed cing phyi ma la tsha dmyal mun
NK071(du)002:5247: pa mi zad pa 'khrigs pa rnams su dmyal ba'i
NK071(du)002:5248: mes bsreg pa dang grang dmyal gyi bu yug la
NK071(du)002:5249: sogs pas sbreb pa la yun ring du gnas dgos
NK071(du)002:5250: so // gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5251: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)002:5252: kun tu bzang po nyid kyis rang snang du bkod
NK071(du)002:5253: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du brjod
NK071(du)002:5254: do // mchog tu gsang ba'i snying po rdzogs pa
NK071(du)002:5255: chen po'i gdams ngag tshe 'di nyid du grol bar
NK071(du)002:5256: byed par de kho na nyid nges pa las theg
NK071(du)002:5257: pa 'og ma rnams la shin tu gsang ba man
NK071(du)002:5258: ngag gi snying po'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5260: // don gsum pa 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin la bstod pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:5265: lam bskyed rdzogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas
NK071(du)002:5266: 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la bstod
NK071(du)002:5267: pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:5268: dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen po'i glu 'di blangs
NK071(du)002:5270: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang bcas pa la spyir bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5271: dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug yab yum la bye brag tu bstod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5273: dang po sku rdo rje rigs kyi dkyil 'khor chos
NK071(du)002:5274: kyi dbyings su sku lnga rdzogs pas zhes glu'i mgo
NK071(du)002:5275: 'dren pa dang / bla ma rong bas de la
NK071(du)002:5276: +amo zhes pa ni glu'i yan lag thams cad rdzogs
NK071(du)002:5277: 'dren pa dang / pa ste / yi ge +amo
NK071(du)002:5278: ni rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po dang tha mi
NK071(du)002:5279: dad pas glu len pa'i mkhan po yin no //
NK071(du)002:5280: de bzhin du tshangs pa dbyangs kyis 'dren pa yin pas glu'i dbyangs yin no //
NK071(du)002:5281: don chen po ston pa'i tshig yin pas glu'i tshig yin no //
NK071(du)002:5282: de'i mtho dman gsal bar byed pas glu'i rgyan yin no //
NK071(du)002:5283: yi ge +amo gyis drangs na glu dang tshig thams
NK071(du)002:5284: cad gsang sngags bden pa'i ngag tu byin gyis rlob
NK071(du)002:5285: par byed pa yin pas glu byin gyi rlob pa
NK071(du)002:5287: sku de yang phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun gyi sangs
NK071(du)002:5288: rgyas thams cad kyi sku rdo rje gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:5289: pa'i rang bzhin du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:5291: rang snang dag pa'i ye shes me long lta bu
NK071(du)002:5292: la sogs pa'i rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK071(du)002:5293: dkyil 'khor sku'i thugs rnam par dag pa'i theg le
NK071(du)002:5294: che ste gnyis su med pa'i don to //
NK071(du)002:5295: de lta bu'i rang snang de'ang bsod nams phun sum
NK071(du)002:5296: tshogs pa'i ngo bo snang la rang bzhin med pa'i
NK071(du)002:5297: dkyil 'khor ni sku lnga ste rigs lnga'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:5298: mtha' dbus khyab pas sku yi tshogs so //
NK071(du)002:5299: de'i ngo bo snang stong gnyis su med pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:5300: bzhin ni sku'i gsung brjod bral don gyi thig le
NK071(du)002:5301: yon tan phun sum tshogs pa kun tu rdzogs de
NK071(du)002:5302: la dgyes pas ho zhes so //
NK071(du)002:5303: gnyis pa gsung pad+ma rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du so
NK071(du)002:5304: sor rtog pa'i ye shes ye nas rnam par dag
NK071(du)002:5305: pa'i gsung lnga rdzogs shing lhun gyis grub pas zhes
NK071(du)002:5306: so // 'od dpag med kyi dkyil 'khor de yang
NK071(du)002:5307: snang stong dbyer med pas rdo rje bsod nams dang
NK071(du)002:5308: ye shes kyi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'ii thig
NK071(du)002:5309: so // le che / mi phyed pa'i rdo rje
NK071(du)002:5310: so sor rtogs pa la sogs pa'i ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:5311: dkyil 'khor ldan pa ni gsung gi thugs so //
NK071(du)002:5312: gnyis su med pa'i rdo rje ye shes kyi rang
NK071(du)002:5313: sgra chen po mtha' yas pa mnga' ba ni gsung
NK071(du)002:5314: gi gsung ngo // don gyi rdo rje rang snang
NK071(du)002:5315: bas rgyal po thig le che ste gsung gi sku
NK071(du)002:5316: yin pas de la dgyes te ho zhes so //
NK071(du)002:5317: gsum pa thugs sangs rgyas rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)002:5318: me long lta bu'i ye shes la bstod pa ni
NK071(du)002:5319: / thugs lnga rdzogs pas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:5320: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che ste rnam par
NK071(du)002:5321: / snang mdzad do // de nyid la yon tan
NK071(du)002:5322: phrin las ma lus pa kun tu rdzogs pa ni
NK071(du)002:5324: yon tan phun sum tshogs pa rnams ma btsal bar
NK071(du)002:5325: ye nas lhun rdzogs su gnas pa rang bzhin kun
NK071(du)002:5326: tu bzang po'i ngang ni thugs kyi gsung ngo //
NK071(du)002:5327: de'i tshe ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang snang du
NK071(du)002:5328: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen po ni rang bzhin gyis dag
NK071(du)002:5329: pas thig le che ste thugs kyi sku'o //
NK071(du)002:5330: lhun gyis grub pas ho zhes so //
NK071(du)002:5331: bzhi pa yon tan rin chen rigs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5332: du mnyam nyid ye shes kyi sgo nas bstod pa
NK071(du)002:5333: ni / yon tan phun sum tshogs pa lnga lhun
NK071(du)002:5334: gyis grub pas zhing khams phun sum tshogs pa chos
NK071(du)002:5335: kyi dbyings mtshan ma thams cad mi dmigs shing thabs
NK071(du)002:5336: shes kyi sgyu 'phrul lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:5338: gzhal yas khang dang lha'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas pa
NK071(du)002:5339: rgyan gyi bye brag kun nas 'od zer sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:5340: spro ba ni yon tan gyi sku'i /
NK071(du)002:5341: ye shes mtha' yas pa kun nas lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:5342: cing dbyer med mnyam pa'i ngang du thim pa ni
NK071(du)002:5343: brda 'am rang bzhin te yon tan gyi gsung ngo
NK071(du)002:5344: // ting nge 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul dang mngon par
NK071(du)002:5345: shes pa la sogs pa sna tshogs kyi gter yid
NK071(du)002:5346: bzhin gyi nor bu ltar dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i sku
NK071(du)002:5347: gsung thugs chen po mnga' ba ni yon tan gyi
NK071(du)002:5348: // thugs te / ngo mtshar che ho zhes so //
NK071(du)002:5349: lnga pa phrin las kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)002:5350: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi sgo nas bstod
NK071(du)002:5351: pa ni / phrin las lnga lhun gyis grub pas
NK071(du)002:5352: phyogs bcu'i snod bcud 'jig rten zhing gi rdul phra
NK071(du)002:5353: pa ni / ba snyed du / rgyal ba'i don
NK071(du)002:5354: phrin las rnam pa bzhi po rnams kyi grangs rdul
NK071(du)002:5355: phran snyed pa ni mdzad pa rang gi ngo bo
NK071(du)002:5356: yin te phrin las kyi sku'o //
NK071(du)002:5357: gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul pa'i grangs rdul phran
NK071(du)002:5358: dang mnyam pa bsam yas kyis 'dul ba ni sprul
NK071(du)002:5359: pa 'phro ba ste phrin las kyi gsung ngo /
NK071(du)002:5360: sprul pa de dag gis zhing de dag tu skad
NK071(du)002:5361: cig yud tsam la khyab nas 'bad rtsol med par
NK071(du)002:5362: 'gro ba'i don lhun gyis grub pa ni chos kyi
NK071(du)002:5363: sku las ma g.yos bzhin rtsol med du grub pa'i
NK071(du)002:5365: de la ngo mtshar bas ho zhes so //
NK071(du)002:5366: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug yab yum la bye brag tu bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5367: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis rdzogs pas phyogs bcu
NK071(du)002:5368: dus bzhi dang rang snang gi rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5369: thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin ni sku gsung
NK071(du)002:5370: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo yin la
NK071(du)002:5371: / de dag gi sku gsung thugs kyi byed pa
NK071(du)002:5372: po'i bdag nyid che ste kun tu bzang po dang
NK071(du)002:5373: / / sku gsung thugs kyis bya ba mo'i yul
NK071(du)002:5374: kun la khyab pa ni kun tu bzang mo ste
NK071(du)002:5375: / / / yab yum gnyis su med pa'ii rang
NK071(du)002:5376: bzhin de ni 'khor 'das thams cad sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)002:5377: kyi ngo bo ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i chos nyid
NK071(du)002:5378: thig le che gzhi lam 'bras bu'i kun tu bzang
NK071(du)002:5379: po yab yum ni sangs rgyas dang sems can kun
NK071(du)002:5380: gyi gdod ma'i mgon por lhun gyis grub pas ho
NK071(du)002:5381: / / / zhes so // gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5382: zhes lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing rang snang dag
NK071(du)002:5383: pa'i 'khor la zhu ba po med par ched du
NK071(du)002:5384: bsgrags so // 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po sku
NK071(du)002:5385: dang ye shes kyi de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)002:5386: las mnyes pa'i mchod pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o
NK071(du)002:5388: spyi don gnyis pa khro bo mngon par 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:5389: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba'i tshul bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:5390: lam ji ltar bsgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag rgya cher bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:5391: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la bstod pa'i tshul brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5393: khro bo mngon par 'byung ba'i tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5394: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5396: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas phyogs bcu
NK071(du)002:5397: dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK071(du)002:5398: nyid chen po dpal kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:5399: thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i ngo bo
NK071(du)002:5400: nyid kyis chos sku spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang
NK071(du)002:5401: las ma g.yos bzhin du lhun stug po bkod pa'i
NK071(du)002:5402: zhing du rang snang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ye shar
NK071(du)002:5403: du bkod pa'i mngon par 'du mdzad de sprul pa
NK071(du)002:5404: sku'i khro bo 'byung ba'i 'char gzhir bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5406: gdul bya las kyi khro bo'i 'byung tshul dang /
NK071(du)002:5407: 'dul byed ye shes kyi khro bos btul tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:5412: 'char gzhi longs sku dang de las shar ba sprul
NK071(du)002:5413: sku'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de dgos pa'am
NK071(du)002:5414: rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir zhe na /
