NK071(du)002:5416: rgyu gang gis bskyed pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5418: de'ang sprul sku'i khro bos 'dul ba la longs sku'i khro bo dgos la /
NK071(du)002:5419: longs sku'i khro bos mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul rang snang
NK071(du)002:5420: du ston pa ji 'dra na sprul sku'i khro bos
NK071(du)002:5421: gdul bya'i 'jig rten du ston pas chu dang zla
NK071(du)002:5422: gzugs bzhin 'brel pa grub pa de'i phyir ma dag
NK071(du)002:5423: par snang ba nyid 'dul bar ston pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5424: skabs 'di'i gdul bya dang 'dul byed bzang ngan gyis
NK071(du)002:5425: bskyed pa'i rgyu 'bras dang bzang ngan du snang yang
NK071(du)002:5426: don la bzang ngan med de ngo bo'i 'char tshul
NK071(du)002:5427: de ltar snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:5428: des na 'di dang mdo gnyis 'char gzhi dang 'char byed du 'brel lo //
NK071(du)002:5429: rnam pa de 'dra bas dus gcig pa'ang ma dgos
NK071(du)002:5430: te 'char byed 'char gzhi dang dus gcig kyang 'char
NK071(du)002:5431: gzhi 'char byed dang gcig pa'i nges pa med de
NK071(du)002:5432: zla ba dang zla'i dus bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:5433: 'on te gcig pa'ang mi 'gal bar rung ste de ltar byin gyis rlob nus pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:5435: nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa'i gang zag gi bdag
NK071(du)002:5436: tu rang gi sems rmongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa
NK071(du)002:5437: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa 'dzin pa la
NK071(du)002:5439: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba brda tsam
NK071(du)002:5440: blos brtags pa tsam yin pa la de ltar ma
NK071(du)002:5441: shes par bden bden grub grub por mngon par zhen
NK071(du)002:5442: pa kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas /
NK071(du)002:5443: gzung yul la bdag gir zhen pas 'khor bar 'khyams
NK071(du)002:5444: shing srid pa'i rgyu byed de sdug bsngal gyis 'khor
NK071(du)002:5445: mor gdung la yang dag pa'i lam 'khor ba las
NK071(du)002:5446: nges par 'byin pa'i shes rab zab mo dang bral
NK071(du)002:5447: ba dag ni srid pa'i 'du byed pa sbyi'i rgyu
NK071(du)002:5448: yin la de'i steng du don zab mo rgyud lung
NK071(du)002:5449: gi khung na gab pa'i rang bzhin rtogs par dka'
NK071(du)002:5450: ba rang bzhin gyis gsang ba ma rtogs par sbyor
NK071(du)002:5451: sgrol gyi thabs la sogs pa sbas pa'i gsang ba
NK071(du)002:5452: spyod pa barlanga po rang 'gal ba la mngon par
NK071(du)002:5454: rgyu dge sdig dang 'bras bu bde sdug gi 'brel
NK071(du)002:5455: ba la rmongs pas gsang ba zab mo rnams kyi
NK071(du)002:5456: sgra ci lta bar spyod cing phyin ci log gi
NK071(du)002:5457: lam la zhugs pa r+au trar skye ba'i rgyu ste
NK071(du)002:5458: thar pa nag po lta bu'o //
NK071(du)002:5460: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK071(du)002:5461: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la 'tshe ba'o //
NK071(du)002:5462: dang po la'ang gnyis las dmyal bar skye ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5463: sngon zhe sdang la sogs pas kun nas bslangs ba'i
NK071(du)002:5464: las bsags te dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa ni
NK071(du)002:5465: / srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mo ste des bar do med par rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'phangs nas /
NK071(du)002:5466: bar mtshams med pa'i rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal ba mnar med par skad cig la skyes so //
NK071(du)002:5467: de nyid du bskal chen du mar sdug bsngal la spyod do //
NK071(du)002:5468: de rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal drag pos gdungs
NK071(du)002:5469: pa dang las cung zad bsrabs te de las thar
NK071(du)002:5471: grang dmyal gyi gnas dag mthong nas 'di bas shin
NK071(du)002:5472: tu grang ba'i gnas pha gir skyes shing sdug bsngal
NK071(du)002:5473: myong yang ci ma rung snyam pa'i mod la der
NK071(du)002:5474: skyes te / gangs dang bu yug la sogs pas
NK071(du)002:5475: rab tu sbrebs pa ste shin tu grang ba dang
NK071(du)002:5476: skyes te / / lus kyang pad+ma ltar bzhi tshal
NK071(du)002:5477: dang brgyad tshal la sogs par gas pa'i sdug bsngal
NK071(du)002:5478: drag po bzod bka' ba btud mar 'byung ba dag
NK071(du)002:5479: gis rab tu gdung ba de lta bu'i sdug bsngal
NK071(du)002:5480: rab tu tsha ba mnar med la sogs pa ste
NK071(du)002:5481: rab tu tsha ba dang tsha ba dang ngu 'bod
NK071(du)002:5482: chen po dang ngu 'bod dang bsdus 'joms dang thig
NK071(du)002:5483: nag dang yang sos te brgyad dang /
NK071(du)002:5484: shin tu grang ba pad+ma chen po ltar gas pa
NK071(du)002:5485: la sogs pa ste pad+ma ltar gas pa ut+pala ltar
NK071(du)002:5486: gas pa kyi hud zer ba so tham tham pa
NK071(du)002:5487: a chu zer ba chu bur rdol ba can chu
NK071(du)002:5488: bur can te brgyad po dag tu /
NK071(du)002:5489: phan tshun zung re re zhing skye res kyis 'jig
NK071(du)002:5490: rten de 'jig par brtsams pa na 'jig rten gyi
NK071(du)002:5491: khams gzhan du brgyud cing bskal pa chen po stong
NK071(du)002:5492: phrag bcu gnyis su tsha grang gi sdug bsngal dpag
NK071(du)002:5494: gnyis pa yi dwags su skyes pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5495: de nas dmyal ba'i rnam par smin pa de dag zad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5496: yi dwags su skyes nas ltogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5497: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis rab tu nyen pa spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa can dang /
NK071(du)002:5498: phyi rol 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams yid du mi
NK071(du)002:5499: 'ong ba chu gtsang la rnag khrag la sogs par
NK071(du)002:5500: mthong ba'i phyi'i sgrib pa can dang /
NK071(du)002:5501: bza' btung dang por mi rnyed cing rnyed kyang mgrin
NK071(du)002:5502: par mi chud chud na'ang nang khrol la me 'bar
NK071(du)002:5503: te lus phyi nang kun tu me 'bar ba'i phyir
NK071(du)002:5504: na longs spyod kyi dngos po rnams gdug cing rtsub
NK071(du)002:5505: pa'i dngos po sna tshogs su skad cig la gyur
NK071(du)002:5506: pa me lce'i 'khor lo can dang /
NK071(du)002:5507: skom pa'i tshe rgya mtsho dang chu klung chen po
NK071(du)002:5508: dang bkres pa'i tshe bza' ba'i bye brag dang gnas
NK071(du)002:5509: dang yo byad yid du 'ong ba dag pa longs
NK071(du)002:5510: spyod par 'dod nas bltas shing de'i drung du phyin
NK071(du)002:5511: pa'i tshe yongs te lhag rol lam rjes shul tsam
NK071(du)002:5513: rus gzeb la pags pas g.yogs pa tsam las sha
NK071(du)002:5514: khrag gi mdangs med par shin tu rid cing bskams
NK071(du)002:5515: pa dang / lus dang yan lag mi 'tsham par ri rab dang 'jag ma tsam dang /
NK071(du)002:5516: dbang po ma tshang zhing skyon chags pa mgo ri
NK071(du)002:5517: tsam la kha khab mig tsam pa la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:5518: rnam par mi 'tshams par gyur par bskal pa chen
NK071(du)002:5519: po drug tu gcig nas gcig tu brgyud cing skyes
NK071(du)002:5520: so // gnyis pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la ji ltar 'tshe ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5521: de nas yi dwags su skyes pa'i las kyi sgrib
NK071(du)002:5522: pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa de khad kyis
NK071(du)002:5523: bsrabs te rags pa de zad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5524: phra ba'i rgyu dang sngon gyi skye ba la khro
NK071(du)002:5525: bo mgo dang phyag du ma yod pa bsgoms shing
NK071(du)002:5526: rang mtshan du zhen nas phra men la sogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:5527: 'khor yid la byas te drag sngags rtsub mo rnams
NK071(du)002:5528: bzlas shing / dngos po bzhi la spyod pa la
NK071(du)002:5529: sogs pa'i las kyi srid pas r+au tra'i rgyud du
NK071(du)002:5530: bzlas shing / 'tshams sbyar nas / ngo bo yi
NK071(du)002:5531: dwags kyi 'gro bas bsdus shing cha lugs srin po
NK071(du)002:5532: chen po mtshon cha dang mgo thod thogs pa sems
NK071(du)002:5533: rab tu gdug pa can khro zhing gtum po 'jigs
NK071(du)002:5534: su rung ba ste rdzu 'phrul ni lus gcig la'ang
NK071(du)002:5536: de yang stag dang seng ge la sogs pa'i mgo mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5537: lha dang lha ma yin la sogs pa'i lus brgya
NK071(du)002:5538: la ma he lta bu'i mgo bo gcig pa dang
NK071(du)002:5539: / glang po che dang chu srin la sogs pa'i lus sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5540: lus gcig la yan lag rab tu mang po dang /
NK071(du)002:5541: yan lag de dag kyang kha dog dang rnam pa mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5542: de dag gis mda' dang mdung thung la sogs pa gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thogs pa /
NK071(du)002:5543: ma mo dang sha za dang mkha' 'gro la sogs pa'i 'khor rab tu mang po dang ldan pa /
NK071(du)002:5544: yan lag sprul du byung zhing lus la gshogs pa
NK071(du)002:5545: thogs pa la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i gzugs sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:5546: dang / ra la ra la ru lu ru lu
NK071(du)002:5547: la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i nga ro sgra sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:5548: dang / sgrogs pa'o // de'i byed las ni 'jigs pa'i gzugs dang mi snyan pa'i nga ro dang /
NK071(du)002:5549: mi zhim pa'i dri dang rims nad gtong ba'i kha
NK071(du)002:5550: rlang kyis 'tshubs pas 'gro ba thams cad skyi bung
NK071(du)002:5552: phyogs thams cad rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag gi mun pas khebs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5553: grang ba dang tsha ba'ii dbugs kyis phyogs bcu kun tu stong khams thams cad 'khrugs par byed pa /
NK071(du)002:5554: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa las gyur pa'i nad
NK071(du)002:5555: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi 'gro ba la 'debs par byed
NK071(du)002:5556: pa / sems myos shing lus dang dran pa nyams par byed pa'i mthus /
NK071(du)002:5557: dga' bo dang 'jog po la sogs pa klu'i ris dang /
NK071(du)002:5558: thag bzang ris la sogs pa lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK071(du)002:5559: dbang po dang khyab 'jug la sogs pa 'dod pa'i lha'i ris dang /
NK071(du)002:5560: bsam gtan dang po'i tshangs pa'i ris dang /
NK071(du)002:5561: tshangs pa kun 'khor dang tshangs chen dang /
NK071(du)002:5562: gnyis pa'i 'od chung dang tshad med 'od dang /
NK071(du)002:5564: gsum pa'i dge chung tshad med dge dang dge rgyas dang /
NK071(du)002:5565: bzhi pa'i sprin med dang bsod nams skyes dang 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK071(du)002:5566: gnyis pa 'dul byed ye shes kyi khro bos btul tshul la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:5567: dang po gdul bya gzigs tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5568: r+au tra de sngon theg pa chen por sems bskyed
NK071(du)002:5569: cing dbang mnos te dge ba'i bshes gshen bsten pa'i
NK071(du)002:5570: bsod nams kyi stobs kyis che btsun dang gdul zhing
NK071(du)002:5571: du gyur pa dpal chen po he ru ka thams
NK071(du)002:5572: cad mkhyen pas 'dul ba'i dus la bab par gzigs
NK071(du)002:5573: nas thabs la mkhas pa dang thugs rjes 'dul bar
NK071(du)002:5574: bya bar gyur te gdul ba'i dus la bab par
NK071(du)002:5575: dgongs so // gnyis pa btul ba dngos rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:5576: cho 'phrul bzhis dregs pa can zil gyis mnan pa /
NK071(du)002:5577: phrin las drag pos gdug pa can tshar bcad pa /
NK071(du)002:5578: thugs rjes rjes su bzung nas bka' la btags pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:5580: dang po rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5581: gdul bya las kyi khro bo snang ba de nas
NK071(du)002:5582: 'dul byed ye shes kyi khro bo bstan pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:5583: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi chos sku ni che
NK071(du)002:5584: ba'i rdo rje gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin rgya
NK071(du)002:5585: chad phyogs lhung med par bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK071(du)002:5586: bas te snang stong gnyis med nam mkha' lta bu'i
NK071(du)002:5587: ngang las rang snang khro bo'i longs sku 'byung ste
NK071(du)002:5589: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i zhing na srid pa
NK071(du)002:5590: gsum gyi bdag po dregs pa r+au tra 'dul ba'i
NK071(du)002:5591: nga rgyal chen po'i zhe sdang la sogs pa'i snyem
NK071(du)002:5592: pa thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi brjid ston
NK071(du)002:5593: pa'i phyir / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid chen po /
NK071(du)002:5594: bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po gdul bya 'dul
NK071(du)002:5595: ba'i thabs la dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i rgyal
NK071(du)002:5596: po he ru'i ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po
NK071(du)002:5598: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po ye shes rang snang
NK071(du)002:5599: ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te gnas
NK071(du)002:5600: so // gnyis pa de las cho 'phrul ji ltar spros pa'i tshul la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:5601: dang po dbyings gang las spros pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5602: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas /
NK071(du)002:5603: ye shes kyi khro mo dbang phyug chen mo gdangs
NK071(du)002:5604: kyi yum bya ba mo kun tu bzang mo rang
NK071(du)002:5605: snang du mngon du phyung ste /
NK071(du)002:5606: hi hi zhes yab la dgyes pa'i sku'i gzi mdangs
NK071(du)002:5607: kyis gsang ba'i pad+ma bstan pas byed pa po kun
NK071(du)002:5608: tu bzang po yang ha ha zhes rin chen dang
NK071(du)002:5609: pad+ma bde bas rgyas par mdzad nas /
NK071(du)002:5610: yab yum gnyis su med par 'khril te rol pa'i
NK071(du)002:5611: dgyes pas pad+mara nor bu thim par mdzad nas rol
NK071(du)002:5612: lo // gnyis pa tshul ji ltar spros pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5613: yab kyi byang chub sems kyi sprin yum gyi mkhar bab pa las byung ba ni rgyu'o //
NK071(du)002:5614: de'i tshe h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha
NK071(du)002:5615: dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata ha la ha la
NK071(du)002:5616: ha la h+aum zhes pa ni rkyen te sku dang
NK071(du)002:5617: gsung dang thugs kyi bdag nyid sna tshogs rdo rje
NK071(du)002:5618: khro bo 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis ma rung ba'i
NK071(du)002:5619: rnam 'gyur gsum dang ldan pa'i gdug pa can gyi
NK071(du)002:5620: lus ngag yid gsum dum bur gyis shig pa'o zhes
NK071(du)002:5621: brjod pas / nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa'i 'jig rten
NK071(du)002:5622: drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa thams cad go
NK071(du)002:5623: 'tshams med par khyab par kun tu bzang mo yum
NK071(du)002:5624: gyi mkha' dbyings las rigs lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:5625: gyi tshogs che chung stong gsum gyi 'jig rten tsam
NK071(du)002:5626: brjod pas / pa la / grangs phyogs bcu'i 'jig
NK071(du)002:5627: rten gyi khams thams cad kyi rdul phra mo snyed
NK071(du)002:5628: tsam 'thon par 'gyur nas gang bar gyur to //
NK071(du)002:5629: gsum pa spros pa'i ltas ni /
NK071(du)002:5630: de ltar khro bo'i sprin gyis nam mkha'i khams kun
NK071(du)002:5631: gsal bas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad
NK071(du)002:5632: kyis dang ri gling thams cad chung ngur g.yos /
NK071(du)002:5634: chen por kun tu rab tu g.yos so //
NK071(du)002:5635: 'brug la sogs pa'i sgra skad chung ngur 'ur 'ur /
NK071(du)002:5638: lha'i rnga bo che la sogs pa rol mo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:5639: rnams ma brdung kyang rang sgra chung ngur chem chem
NK071(du)002:5641: cher por kun tu rab tu chem chem mo //
NK071(du)002:5642: ri dang sa rdo la sogs par rags pa'i dngos
NK071(du)002:5643: po 'dus pa rnams ma gyes tsam du chung ngur
NK071(du)002:5644: shig shig / 'bring du rab tu shig shig /
NK071(du)002:5645: chen por kun tu rab tu shig shig go /
NK071(du)002:5646: rgya mtsho la sogs pa'i rba rlabs chung ngur gtor gtor /
NK071(du)002:5648: chen por kun tu gtor gtor ro //
NK071(du)002:5649: chung 'bring che gsum ni sa 'og steng sa bla gsum bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5650: de ltar lnga po la gsum gsum gyis ltas chen po bco lnga zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)002:5651: de ni snod ltar phyi la sbyar ba yin zhing /
NK071(du)002:5653: bcud ltar nang du sbyar na g.yo ba g.yum 'gro ba'i sems so //
NK071(du)002:5655: chem pa gsum gzung ba dang 'dzin pa dang gnyis bcas so //
NK071(du)002:5656: shig pa gsum dug gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5657: 'thor pa gsum spang gnyen 'dzin pa dang bcas pa ste bco lnga dag par byas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5658: ye shes ltar gsang bar sbyar na rang snang 'od lnga'i snang ba ni g.yos pa gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5659: ye shes kyi gzhal med khang phyogs bcur gsal ba ni 'ur ba gsum mo /
NK071(du)002:5660: rten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor ni chem pa gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5661: snang ba mi 'dra ba'i bkod pa du ma ba ni shig pa gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5662: dkyil 'khor gyi 'phro 'du dang rol pa ni 'thor ba gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5663: yang gsang bla med ltar sbyar na snang yul bzang ngan bar ma gsum ni g.yos pa gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5664: shes pa dgag sgrub par ma gsum ni 'ur ba gsum mo //
NK071(du)002:5665: de nyid rang grol kun tu bzang po thabs shes
NK071(du)002:5666: zung 'brel gsum du shar bas chem pa gsum mo
NK071(du)002:5667: // de'i tshe spros pa dang bral ba'i ye shes
NK071(du)002:5668: bde gsal mi rtog pa gsum du shar ba ni
NK071(du)002:5670: rang bzhin rtogs pas spang gnyen 'dzin pa gsum zhig pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5671: 'thor ba gsum ste 'khor ba chos nyid du grol ba'i ltas chen po bco lnga'o //
NK071(du)002:5672: de dag bstan pas de'i tshe 'jig rten drug gi
NK071(du)002:5673: phyogs bcu'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten
NK071(du)002:5674: gyi khams thams cad na gnas pa'i gtso bo rang
NK071(du)002:5675: rang gi gnas ris na dbang che ba dang /
NK071(du)002:5676: 'od dang gzi brjid che ba dang /
NK071(du)002:5677: stobs dang nus mthu che ba'i lha dbang phyug chen
NK071(du)002:5678: po dang tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:5679: thams cad lus 'gyed cing gzi brjid chung bar gyur
NK071(du)002:5680: pas brgyal ngag cung zad kyang smra bar mi nus
NK071(du)002:5682: sems skrag cing spa bkong la dran pa nyams pas kun tu brgyal bar 'gyur to //
NK071(du)002:5683: gnyis pa phrin las drag pos gdug pa can tshar bcad pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)002:5684: gtso bo ye shes kyi dkyiil 'khor bkod pa /
NK071(du)002:5685: dregs pa pho rgyud dngos su bsgral ba /
NK071(du)002:5686: mo rgyud sbyor bas dgyes pa /
NK071(du)002:5689: dang po gtso bo che mchog tu bzhugs pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:5690: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po kun tu bzang po nyid /
NK071(du)002:5691: 'jigs byed chen po shin tu rngam pa'i cha lugs
NK071(du)002:5692: skyi bung zhes byed pa'i rnam pa ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:5693: gzi mdangs nyi ma 'bum bas kyang 'bar ba chen
NK071(du)002:5694: po'i 'od 'phro khrag 'thung che mchog he ru ka
NK071(du)002:5695: sku mchog smug nag la rnam 'gyur cir yang 'gyur
NK071(du)002:5696: ba dbu dang phyag dang zhabs grangs mtha' yas pa
NK071(du)002:5697: stong khams kyi rdul snyed mnga' ba'i phyag na mtshon
NK071(du)002:5698: cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa de rnam par thar pa'i
NK071(du)002:5699: dbu gsum dang pha rol tu phyin pa'i phyag drug
NK071(du)002:5700: dang rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa'i zhabs bzhir gyur te
NK071(du)002:5701: / 'khor ba ma spang gnas su dag pa'i dur
NK071(du)002:5702: khrod chen por dgyes nas 'dod chags gnas su dag
NK071(du)002:5703: pa'i phyir khrag gi rgya mtsho'i klong dkyil na /
NK071(du)002:5704: zhe sdang ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i brdar keng
NK071(du)002:5705: rus chen po'i tshogs spungs shing brtsigs pa'i ri rab
NK071(du)002:5706: kyi steng na gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:5707: ye shes kyi me ri me dpung 'bar ba chen
NK071(du)002:5708: po'i klong gi dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:5709: na lha dbang phyug chen po ste ma h+aa de
NK071(du)002:5710: ba dang / dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa
NK071(du)002:5711: chen po u ma de ba ste khyo shugs gi
NK071(du)002:5712: gdan la g.yon brkyang g.yas bskums su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5713: gnyis pa 'khor rigs bzhir bkod tshul ni gong du
NK071(du)002:5714: spros pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin phung gi
NK071(du)002:5716: rigs lnga'am bzhi'i rang bzhin las la la ste me
NK071(du)002:5717: long lta bu'i ye shes kyi rigs rnams ni dpal
NK071(du)002:5718: khrag 'thung chen po badz+ra he ru kar gyur te
NK071(du)002:5719: 'khor lo'i rtsibs shar phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5720: la la ste mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:5721: rigs rnams ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po
NK071(du)002:5722: che ste rat+na he ru kar gyur te 'khor lo'i
NK071(du)002:5723: rtsibs lho phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5724: la la ste so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:5725: rigs rnams ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+ma he
NK071(du)002:5726: ru kar gyur te 'khor lo'i rtsibs nub phyogs su
NK071(du)002:5727: bzhugs so // la la ste bya ba grub pa'i
NK071(du)002:5728: ye shes kyi rigs rnams ni dpal khrag 'thung chen
NK071(du)002:5729: po kun tu las su ste karma he ru kar
NK071(du)002:5730: gyur te 'khor lo'i rtsibs byang phyogs su bzhugs so
NK071(du)002:5731: bzhugs so // // khro bo'i rigs bzhi po de
NK071(du)002:5732: dag kun kyang 'jigs byed chen po'i cha lugs dur
NK071(du)002:5733: khrod kyi chas brgyad dang h+aum dang phata la sogs
NK071(du)002:5734: pa rngam pa'i nga ro dang ye shes kyi me
NK071(du)002:5736: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod cing sku gsum mtshon pa'ii
NK071(du)002:5737: dbu gsum dang rgyud drug dbyings su sgrol ba'i phyag
NK071(du)002:5738: drug dang phrin las bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing
NK071(du)002:5739: skye 'gag bzhi gnas su sgrol ba'i phyir zhabs bzhis
NK071(du)002:5740: / phyin ci log bzhi dang bdud bzhi gnon pa'i brdar shar du dri za dang /
NK071(du)002:5743: lhor gshiin rje dang la sogs pa ste ma rung
NK071(du)002:5744: ba'i gdug pa can gyi rigs ji snyed pa bsdus
NK071(du)002:5745: te de dag so so'i khyo shug gis gdan byas
NK071(du)002:5746: pa la g.yon brkyang g.yon bskums su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5747: he ru ka rigs lnga'i btsun mo khrag 'thung chen
NK071(du)002:5748: mo'i tshogs bud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri ma la sogs
NK071(du)002:5749: pa rnams kyang khro bo so so'i sku la 'khyud
NK071(du)002:5750: cing 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:5751: gnyis pa pho rgyud dngos su bsgral ba la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:5752: dang po dregs pa can gyi nga rgyal gyis gtum
NK071(du)002:5753: rngams bsgrags pa ni de nas gdan du bsnol ba'i
NK071(du)002:5754: dregs pa chen po r+au tra la sogs pa dbang
NK071(du)002:5755: phyug chen po pho brgyud nyi shu rtsa brgyad po
NK071(du)002:5756: rnams kyis gdug cing gtum pa'i sems kyis khros te
NK071(du)002:5757: lus gdan du bting yang gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen
NK071(du)002:5759: tshig mthun par mgrin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ro //
NK071(du)002:5760: mi snyan pa'i barlanga po'i gtum tshig drag po ngag tu smras pa /
NK071(du)002:5761: nged rnams rkang pa'i 'og nas thong thong khyed cag
NK071(du)002:5762: snying rje'i bdag po 'gro ba la phan 'dogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:5763: gzugs brnyan ma yin nam ci de ltar byed dam
NK071(du)002:5764: zhes 'dzer zhing / shin tu gdug pa'i sems kyis khros nas brgal ba'i phyir rngam mo //
NK071(du)002:5765: gnyis pa thugs rjes mngon spyod drag pos dngos su bsgral ba la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:5766: dang po 'jigs gzugs rngam pa'i sprin spros pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5767: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po che
NK071(du)002:5768: mchog he ru ka nyid phyir he ru ka dgu
NK071(du)002:5769: klong rngam pa'i zhal du gsol ba dang nang du
NK071(du)002:5770: snyoms 'jug dgu brnyes pa'i rtags su dbu dgu dang
NK071(du)002:5771: phyir sgrol ging bco brgyad kyis gdug pa can sgrol
NK071(du)002:5772: ba dang / nang du stong pa nyid bco brgyad
NK071(du)002:5773: kyi brdar phyag bco brgyad dang phyir tshad med pa
NK071(du)002:5774: bzhi dang phrin las bzhis sems can gyi don mdzad
NK071(du)002:5775: cing nang du rnam par thar pa brgyad brnyes pa'i
NK071(du)002:5776: rtags su zhabs brgyad du gnas par sprul nas /
NK071(du)002:5777: gdug pa can la rngam pa'i skad kyis thabs la
NK071(du)002:5778: mkhas pa'i thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs kyis gdul bya'i
NK071(du)002:5779: snang ngor shin tu khros par bstan nas /
NK071(du)002:5780: h+aum h+aum h+aum ni lus ngag yid gsum bsdus shig
NK071(du)002:5781: pa'o ha ha ha ni dgod pa ste dug gsum
NK071(du)002:5782: zhal du gsol bar rngam pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5783: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi ni sha khrag rus
NK071(du)002:5784: pa gsum la rol pa'o zhes brjod nas 'dar zhing
NK071(du)002:5785: dngas te las su rung bar byas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5786: gnyis pa bsgral ba dngos ni /
NK071(du)002:5787: khro ba'i tshogs de dag gis dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa /
NK071(du)002:5788: gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag gi don snying
NK071(du)002:5789: phyung pa ni rnam shes kyi tshogs la bdag tu
NK071(du)002:5790: 'dzin pa'i ngo bo rtsad nas bcad pa dang mig
NK071(du)002:5791: la sogs pa'i dbang po kun phyung ba ni yul
NK071(du)002:5793: rgyu ma la sogs pa'i nang khrol kun drangs ba
NK071(du)002:5794: ni gzung 'dzin gyi rten lus su zhen pa spangs
NK071(du)002:5795: ba'o // mgo la sogs pa'i yan lag kun bcad
NK071(du)002:5796: cing gtubs nas srid par 'du byed pa bshig pa'o
NK071(du)002:5797: ba'o // // sha kun zos pas gti mug dag par mdzad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5798: khrag kun 'thung nas 'dod chags dag par byas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5799: rus pa kun 'chos nas zhe sdang dag par byas so //
NK071(du)002:5800: gsum pa mo brgyud sbyor pas dgyes pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:5802: sbyor ba chen po'i rol pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5804: dang po snod kyi 'jig rten bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5805: de nas h+aum h+aum h+aum ni dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyis bsdus shig pa'o //
NK071(du)002:5806: b+h+yo ni ma mo rnams so //
NK071(du)002:5808: a ra li mkha' 'gro ma'am pho nya mo'o /
NK071(du)002:5810: dza dza ni shog shog gam khug cig pa'o zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:5811: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha' dbyings kyi
NK071(du)002:5812: mthas gtugs pa dang bcas pa thams cad yungs 'bru
NK071(du)002:5813: gcig tsam du chud par bsdus so //
NK071(du)002:5814: gnyis pa bcud kyi sems can bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5815: de nas mthu che ba'i 'byung po phal pa'i rigs
NK071(du)002:5816: ma lus pa'i rgyal po gnas 'jog dang ser skya
NK071(du)002:5817: dang gnod sbyin la sogs pa lha dang lha ma
NK071(du)002:5818: yin gyi blon po chen po bka' nyan pa rnams
NK071(du)002:5819: yin la / de'i yang rgyal po ni dregs pa
NK071(du)002:5820: chen po dang tshangs pa la sogs pa'i nyi shu
NK071(du)002:5821: brgyad yin pas na de dag so so'i chung ma
NK071(du)002:5822: ni 'byung po phal pa'i rigs thams cad kyi rje
NK071(du)002:5823: mo rna brnyen chen mo la sogs pa yin la
NK071(du)002:5824: de'i yang rje mo dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa
NK071(du)002:5825: yin la / brgyad do // 'di dag thun mong
NK071(du)002:5826: gi lugs kyis 'jig rten par byed kyang thun mong
NK071(du)002:5827: ma yin pas 'jig rten las 'das par bstan cing
NK071(du)002:5828: yin la / brgyad do // / shin tu thun
NK071(du)002:5829: mong ma yin pas rtsa gnas 'khor lo'i nang na
NK071(du)002:5830: yod par sangs rgyas pa'i tshe de ltar snang bar
NK071(du)002:5831: 'dod pas de'i rjes su 'brang ba yin la /
NK071(du)002:5832: 'dir rigs byed kyi gtam dang sbyar te bstan na
NK071(du)002:5833: go sla bas de ltar bshad na khyo'i ming las
NK071(du)002:5834: chung ma la grags par zad de /
NK071(du)002:5835: dur khrod kyi dregs pa dbang phyug chen po'i chung ma srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5836: tshangs pa'i chung ma tshangs ma dang /
NK071(du)002:5837: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bdag po dbang phyug chen po'i chung ma 'khrug mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5838: brgya byin gyi chung ma dbang mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5839: khyab 'jug gi chung ma 'jug sred mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5840: gzhon nu gdong drug gi chung ma gzhon nu mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5841: 'jug sred kyi chung ma dmar mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5842: nyi ma'i chung ma bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5843: zla ba'i chung ma zhi ba mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5844: be con te spen pa'i chung ma be con mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5845: srin po lang+ka mgrin bcu'i chung ma srin mo dang //
NK071(du)002:5846: lha ma yin dang dam tshig nyams pa rnams za
NK071(du)002:5847: bar byed pa'i lha'i dmag dpon ma h+aa k+aa la'i
NK071(du)002:5848: chung ma za ba mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5849: dga' byed dbang phyug gi chung ma dga' ba mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5850: lha stobs bzang gi chung ma ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK071(du)002:5851: dri za tam bu ra'i chung ma gcig pur spyod ma dang /
NK071(du)002:5852: 'dod lha ka ma de ba'i chung ma yid 'phrog ma dang /
NK071(du)002:5853: nor sgrub cing byad gtod ba'i nor srung gi chung ma grub mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5854: rlung lha'i chung ma rlung mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5855: bdud gsod byed chung ma gsod byed mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5856: me lha'i chung ma me mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5857: sa bdag phag chen gyi chung ma phag mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5858: gshin rje'i chung ma rgan byed mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5859: tshogs bdag gi chung ma sna chen mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5860: chu lha'i chung ma chu lha mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5861: nag po rnam 'jigs chen po'i chung ma nag mo chen mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5862: srin po da sha g+r+ai ba'i chung ma ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5863: srin po sum pa ka ra bum sna'i chung ma 'bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5864: ra ma na 'bod sgrogs te gsus po che'i chung
NK071(du)002:5865: ma gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:5866: / phyi'i las byed pa'i bran dang de'i yang bran dang /
NK071(du)002:5867: nang gi las sgrub pa'i g.yog dang de'i yang g.yog
NK071(du)002:5868: la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i 'khor zhing gi rdul
NK071(du)002:5869: snyed kyi grangs thams cad kyang bsdus so //
NK071(du)002:5870: gnyis pa sbyor ba chen po'i rol pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:5871: dang po rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5872: dbang du bsdus pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK071(du)002:5873: pa chen po 'gro ba'i dpal khrag 'thung chen pos
NK071(du)002:5875: yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen po'i tshogs 'bar bar snang bar byas nas /
NK071(du)002:5876: yab yum de dag kun kyang dgyes pas gnyis su
NK071(du)002:5877: med par rol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rang snang
NK071(du)002:5878: nam mkha'i dbyings kun tu khyab par 'byung ba zhes
NK071(du)002:5879: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs te
NK071(du)002:5880: / gnyis pa rkyen rig pa chen po'i gsang sngags bsgrags pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5881: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di skad ces phyung ngo //
NK071(du)002:5883: badz+ra pra be sha ni rdo rje gzhung par bya ba'o //
NK071(du)002:5884: a la la hohni shin tu ngo mtshar che ba'o //
NK071(du)002:5885: gsum pa 'bras bu gnyis su med par sbyar ba ni zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:5886: 'byung mo'i rgyal mo rnams he ru ka'i tshogs la shin tu chags pas yid g.yos nas /
NK071(du)002:5887: rang rang gi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor bsdud pa ste 'dzum zhing rgyas pa ste 'byed par gyur nas /
NK071(du)002:5888: he ru ka'i sku la sbyor ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5889: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du /
NK071(du)002:5890: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje'i sku la /
NK071(du)002:5891: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK071(du)002:5898: ser nag chen mo ste brgyad po rnams 'khril lo //
NK071(du)002:5899: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po de bzhin gshegs pa che mchog he ru ka'i sku la /
NK071(du)002:5904: gzhon nu mo ste shar gyi lnga rnams 'khril lo /
NK071(du)002:5905: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po che'i sku la /
NK071(du)002:5910: srin mo ste lho'i lnga rnams 'khril lo //
NK071(du)002:5911: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+ma'i sku la /
NK071(du)002:5916: rlung mo ste lho'i lnga rnams 'khril lo //
NK071(du)002:5917: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las kyi sku la /
NK071(du)002:5922: chu lha mo ste byang gi lnga rnams 'khril lo //
NK071(du)002:5923: bzhi pa 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor spro ba'i tshul la lnga las /
NK071(du)002:5924: dang po spro ba'i sbyor ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5925: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po khrag
NK071(du)002:5926: 'thung rigs lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis
NK071(du)002:5927: h+aum zhes brjod pas dbang mo rnams kyi pad+ma'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:5928: 'khor gyi tshogs de dag khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i rdo
NK071(du)002:5929: rje la bsdus nas phan tshun phyag zhabs bsnol zhing
NK071(du)002:5930: stod smad shin tu bcum par byas pas bde ba
NK071(du)002:5932: gnyis pa ma mo spros pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5933: de nas dgyes te ha zhes brjod pas rgyu yab
NK071(du)002:5934: yum gyi byang chub sems kyi sprin las thugs rnam
NK071(du)002:5935: par dag pa zhi ba'i las mdzad pa dkar mo'i
NK071(du)002:5936: tshogs dang / yon tan gyi tshogs sdud pas rkun mo'i tshogs dbang gi las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5937: spangs blang gnyis su med pa'i rmongs mo'i tshogs sems
NK071(du)002:5938: gyii dran pa nyams par byed pas drag po'i las
NK071(du)002:5939: mdzad pa dang / mi mthun pa'i phyogs rdul du
NK071(du)002:5940: rlog pas thal byed mo'i tshogs drag po'i las mdzad
NK071(du)002:5941: mdzad pa dang / pa dang / yon tan gyi
NK071(du)002:5942: gang bas spos mo'i tshogs rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa
NK071(du)002:5943: mdzad pa dang / pa dang / dang / 'thab
NK071(du)002:5944: cing 'khrug pas gtum mo'i tshogs drag po'i las mdzad
NK071(du)002:5945: mdzad pa dang / pa dang / dang / pa
NK071(du)002:5946: dang / gang yang grub pas sme sha can gyi
NK071(du)002:5947: tshogs las thams cad mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5948: tshe dang yo byad 'phel ba ma tshogs ma'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:5949: rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa rnams zhing dbyug dang mda'
NK071(du)002:5950: gzhu la sogs pa rang rang gi lag cha dang
NK071(du)002:5951: / ngo mtshar ba'i 'od zer dang rgyan du chas
NK071(du)002:5952: nas dbang phyug ma rnams kyi mkha' las 'thon te
NK071(du)002:5954: lo'i rtsibs mchan gyi shar lho'i phyogs nas g.yas skor
NK071(du)002:5955: du 'khor bar 'jigs pa'i gzugs dang rang rang gi
NK071(du)002:5956: lag cha dang bcas nas 'khod do //
NK071(du)002:5957: de'ang rtsibs mchan bzhi dang gru chad bzhi la'o //
NK071(du)002:5958: gsum pa phra men ma spro ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5959: de nas shin tu dgyes nas he zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:5960: zil gyis gnon pas seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5961: dpa' gtum che ba stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs drag po'i las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5962: phung po'i bdud 'joms shing thabs la mkhas pa wa
NK071(du)002:5963: gdong chen mo'i tshogs drag po'i las mdzad pa dang
NK071(du)002:5964: / bslu ba'i bdud 'joms shing me la tshe la
NK071(du)002:5965: mkhas pa khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs las thams cad
NK071(du)002:5966: / mdzad pa dang / mig rno bas bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs rgyas pa'i las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5967: 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms shing srog dang bral ba'i
NK071(du)002:5968: ro la spyod pas kang ka'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:5969: zhi ba'i las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5970: thams cad mi spong ba kh+aa gdong chen mo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:5971: 'khor ba mi spong ba chos nyid du dag pas
NK071(du)002:5972: dbang gi las mdzad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:5973: mtshan mo mthong ba 'ug pa'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:5974: 'khor ba spyan gyis gzigs pa zhi ba'i las mdzad
NK071(du)002:5976: lag pa khar bsnol ba la sogs pa rang rang
NK071(du)002:5977: gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar ba'i 'od zer dang
NK071(du)002:5978: rgyan du chas nas 'thon par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:5979: 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba chen po'i 'khor lo'i phyi
NK071(du)002:5980: rol khyams nang ma'i phyogs bzhir mche ba can bzhi
NK071(du)002:5981: dang mtshams bzhir gshog pa can bzhi shar phyogs nas
NK071(du)002:5982: 'khor bar rngam pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod do //
NK071(du)002:5983: bzhi pa sgo ma rnams spros pa ni /
NK071(du)002:5984: de nas shin tu dgyes pas ye shes kyi snang
NK071(du)002:5985: ba chen pos phyogs bcu'i zhing ma lus par khyab
NK071(du)002:5987: tshad med pa bzhis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing phyin
NK071(du)002:5988: ci log bzhi dang bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i brdar rdo
NK071(du)002:5989: rje sring 'gro rta gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:5990: rdo rje gdong mo phag gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:5991: rdo rje 'jig rten ma dred gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:5992: rdo rje ro langs spyang gdong ma'i tshogs rnams lcags
NK071(du)002:5993: kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril bu ste rang rang
NK071(du)002:5995: ngo mtshar du ma chas nas 'thon par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:5996: 'thon nas kyang 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgor bzhir
NK071(du)002:5997: gdug pa can la shin tu rngam pa'i gzugs kyis
NK071(du)002:5998: gnas so // lnga pa 'khor rnams rang rang gi gnas su btang ba ni /
NK071(du)002:5999: de nas yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa dgyes pa
NK071(du)002:6000: chen po'i sprin las phyogs bcu ma lus pa nas
NK071(du)002:6002: thams cad snying rjes rngams shing khros nas sku la
NK071(du)002:6003: 'khril ba dang slas su bkod pa'i ma mo thams
NK071(du)002:6004: cad kyang sngon gang nas 'ongs pa bzhin rang rang
NK071(du)002:6005: gi gnas ga la ba der yud tsam gyis phyin
NK071(du)002:6007: gsum pa thugs rjes rjes su bzung nas bka' la btags pa'i tshul la bzhi /
NK071(du)002:6008: gnas spar te dkyil 'khor mthong ba'i tshul bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:6009: stong khams thams cad mnyam du btul ba /
NK071(du)002:6010: dregs pa can gyis 'bangs su khas blang ba /
NK071(du)002:6011: dbang bskur te bka' bsgo ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6013: dang po rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par bzhag nas gsang sngags brjod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6014: de nas bcom ldan 'das rjes su bzung ba'i tshul
NK071(du)002:6015: gyis dgyes pa chen po 'gro ba'i dpal khrag 'thung
NK071(du)002:6016: chen po rigs lnga po de dag kun kyang chos
NK071(du)002:6017: kyi dbyings las rang byung gi thugs rje chen po
NK071(du)002:6018: gdul bya'i nad gso bas bdud rtsi 'byung ba zhes
NK071(du)002:6019: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NK071(du)002:6020: / de dag gi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK071(du)002:6021: badz+ra ma h+aa a mri ta ni rdo rje bdud rtsi chen po'o //
NK071(du)002:6022: ma h+aa kro d+ha ni khro bo chen po'o //
NK071(du)002:6023: am am am ni lan gsum du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6024: gnyis pa slar yang dregs pa can phyung ste khrus byas pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6026: sngar sha zos shing zhal du bstabs pa'i dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad /
NK071(du)002:6027: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen po rigs lnga po
NK071(du)002:6028: de dag gi 'og sgo'i bsnams khung nas bton te
NK071(du)002:6029: / dri chen la sogs pa'i mi gtsang ba'i 'dam
NK071(du)002:6030: gyi rgya mtshor chud pa las de dag par bya
NK071(du)002:6031: ba'i phyir khro bo so so'i bsnams khung nas khro
NK071(du)002:6032: bo'i u tsush+ma kro d+ha phyung nas mi gtsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:6033: 'dam kun 'thung te dregs pa can de dag dran
NK071(du)002:6034: pa slar rnyed par byas nas /
NK071(du)002:6035: gsum pa 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhal bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6036: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin gyi tshogs rigs lnga
NK071(du)002:6037: po yum dang bcas pa de dag thams cad kyang
NK071(du)002:6038: ye shes lnga dang phrin las bzhi'i dbye bas re
NK071(du)002:6039: re zhing dam pa rigs brgyar mtshon pa'i brdar dbu
NK071(du)002:6041: phyag stong brgyad brgya pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6043: sku ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba chen po'i klong gi dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par mthong ngo //
NK071(du)002:6044: de ni sangs rgyas bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK071(du)002:6045: ting nge 'dzin du bden pa mthong bar byas pa'o
NK071(du)002:6046: // gnyis pa stong khams mnyam du btul ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6047: 'og min du rang snang ye shes kyi cho 'phrul
NK071(du)002:6048: rang bkod pa de'i dus su gdul bya'i 'jig rten
NK071(du)002:6049: drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum po kun tu
NK071(du)002:6050: gnas pa'i dregs pa'i dbang phyug thams cad so so
NK071(du)002:6051: gang la gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs kyi
NK071(du)002:6052: rol pa sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab par steng
NK071(du)002:6053: 'og gi 'jig rten so sor snang bas gdul bya
NK071(du)002:6054: de dag snga phyi med par dus gcig tu btul
NK071(du)002:6055: lo // 'dis ni rang snang lhun stug po bkod
NK071(du)002:6056: par snang ba ji 'dra ba gzhan snang phyogs bcur
NK071(du)002:6058: gsum pa dregs pa can gyis 'bangs su khas blangs pa la bzhi las /
NK071(du)002:6059: dang po 'bangs su dam bcas te dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du phul ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6060: cho 'phrul bkod pa de nas dregs pa can de
NK071(du)002:6061: dag skrag cing lus shin tu 'dar zhing sems bred
NK071(du)002:6062: pas rab tu dpa' zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK071(du)002:6065: sems 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na /
NK071(du)002:6066: rang rang gi mgo dang lus ni tshal pa brgyar 'gas shing /
NK071(du)002:6067: snying yang tshal pa stong du 'gas shing gtub par gyur cig /
NK071(du)002:6068: lus kyang rul cing myags la dmod pa'i mes 'tshig nas tshe 'dir brlag pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6069: phyi mar dmyal bar ltung nas 'o dod chen po 'bod par shog cig /
NK071(du)002:6070: ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor nas /
NK071(du)002:6071: rang rang gi lus khro bo'i rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du bzhag go /
NK071(du)002:6072: gnyis pa 'khor phul te gus pas gtsug gis mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6073: dregs pa can thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu yang smras pa /
NK071(du)002:6074: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis brang chung ma dang /
NK071(du)002:6075: ma dang bu mo dang sring mo rnams /
NK071(du)002:6076: khro bo'i tshogs kyis longs spyod kyi dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol //
NK071(du)002:6077: gdug pa can 'joms pa'i dpa' bo rjes su 'dzin
NK071(du)002:6078: pa'i lha skyabs kyi dam par gyur pa'i rjes bzhes
NK071(du)002:6079: su gsol / bdag cag so so 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)002:6080: zhal mthong ba'i khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po 'di'i /
NK071(du)002:6081: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa rnams la yang /
NK071(du)002:6082: gtsug gi yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'od 'bar ba bskur pa ltar /
NK071(du)002:6083: yid g.yo sgyu med cing mchog tu gus pa dang ldan pa'i /
NK071(du)002:6084: sems kyis mchod nas su blos blangs nas rtag tu spyi bo yi /
NK071(du)002:6085: gtsug tu bzhag ste bkur sti dang rim gro che bar bgyi zhing /
NK071(du)002:6086: dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan 'chang ba de yi dgos pa phrin las bzhi'i ci sgrub yang rung /
NK071(du)002:6087: re ba ma lus pa rdzogs par bdag bcag gis bsgrub par bagyi'o //
NK071(du)002:6088: gsum pa dam bcas te las kyi sdong grogs byed pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6089: gal te dpa' bo'i spyan snga 'dir /
NK071(du)002:6090: bdag cag rnams kyis khas blangs dam bcas pa'i tshig
NK071(du)002:6091: smras pa bzhin du bdag cag gis ma bsgrubs na
NK071(du)002:6092: / bdag cag rnams kyi mgo dang lus dang snying
NK071(du)002:6093: rnams tshal par bkas shing dmod pa'i mtshon gyis gtubs
NK071(du)002:6094: te dum bur gyur nas rul bar mchi'o //
NK071(du)002:6096: bzhi pa dbang mo rnams 'bangs su 'ong nas bka' nyan pa 'phrin las zhu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6097: de nas dregs pa can de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)002:6099: bu mo'i tshogs thams cad sngar bkye ba las slar
NK071(du)002:6100: yang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du skad cig yud tsam
NK071(du)002:6101: gyis 'ong nas / de dag thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu smras pa /
NK071(du)002:6102: bdag cag 'khor gyi tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad kun /
NK071(du)002:6103: bgegs dpung 'joms pa'i dpa' bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi nas /
NK071(du)002:6104: dpa' bo chen pos bdag cag rnams la /
NK071(du)002:6105: zhi ba dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po
NK071(du)002:6106: gang byed sngar rang rang gi las la spyod pa
NK071(du)002:6107: bzhin du 'di ltar gyis shig pa'i las kyi dngos
NK071(du)002:6108: grub bka' bsgo ba stsal du gsol /
NK071(du)002:6110: bzhi pa dbang bskur te bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6111: de nas bcom ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka
NK071(du)002:6112: 'gro ba la dgyes pa chen pos de dag gi
NK071(du)002:6113: lag tu rdo rje byin nas rdo rje mi'i srin
NK071(du)002:6114: mo zhes pa la sogs pa rang rang gi ming
NK071(du)002:6115: gis dbang bskur te 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyi
NK071(du)002:6116: rol ste phyi khyams dag tu bkod do //
NK071(du)002:6117: rol pa'i ye shes mchog tu gsang ba'i snying po
NK071(du)002:6118: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i de kho na nyid nges
NK071(du)002:6119: pa las lhun stug po bkod par khro bo rang
NK071(du)002:6120: bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rang snang mtha' dbus
NK071(du)002:6121: med par rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bco lnga
NK071(du)002:6123: spyi don gnyis pa lam ji ltar sgrub pa thabs
NK071(du)002:6124: kyi yan lag rgya cher bshad pa la lnga ste
NK071(du)002:6125: / thugs brgyud bskul ba gsung gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor dmigs pa'i rten gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK071(du)002:6126: de la mchod pa ji ltar bya ba'i tshul /
NK071(du)002:6127: dam tshig dang ldan pas 'grub pa dam tshig gi rim pa /
NK071(du)002:6128: dam tshig can gyis phrin las ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul lo //
NK071(du)002:6130: gsang sngags 'byung ba'i tshul mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:6131: ji ltar phyung ba'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:6132: ltas khyad par can gyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6133: dang po ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bkod pa
NK071(du)002:6134: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro
NK071(du)002:6135: bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs chen po gong du bstan
NK071(du)002:6136: pa 'di dag dam tshig chen pos gsung gis grub
NK071(du)002:6138: rang snang bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa khro bo
NK071(du)002:6139: khrag 'thung chen po rang rang gi btsun mo dang
NK071(du)002:6140: bcas pa'i tshogs de dag gi sku dang gsung dang
NK071(du)002:6141: thugs rdo rje rang byung gi ye shes gsang sngags
NK071(du)002:6142: kyi rang sgrar rang shar ba 'brug stong ldir ba
NK071(du)002:6143: tsam gyi nga ro rngam pa las gsung gi dkyil
NK071(du)002:6144: 'khor sngags kyi tshogs 'di dag rang shar du phyung
NK071(du)002:6147: ye shes pa spyan drangs pa'i sngags /
NK071(du)002:6148: dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa /
NK071(du)002:6149: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags /
NK071(du)002:6150: phrin las kyi don du gtor ma sbyin pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)002:6152: dang po gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa las yab kyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6153: bkra shis pa dang sngags byin gyis rlabs pa'o sarba
NK071(du)002:6154: ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa ma h+aa
NK071(du)002:6155: chen po sh+r+ai dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung ma
NK071(du)002:6156: h+aa tsan+da gtum po chen po sarba dush+t+aa n+ta ka
NK071(du)002:6157: sdang ba thams cad mthar byed pa ste de dag
NK071(du)002:6158: rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bcom ldan 'das la 'bod pa'o
NK071(du)002:6162: h+aum h+aum h+aum ni gdug pa can gyi lus ngag yid gsum bsdud pa phata dum bur gtong ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6163: de dag phrin las kyi sngags so //
NK071(du)002:6164: ni sngags byin gyis rlob pa badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK071(du)002:6165: he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da rdo rje chen po
NK071(du)002:6166: dpal khrag 'thung gtum po chen po sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka
NK071(du)002:6167: sdang ba thams cad mthar byed pa ste rtsa ba'i
NK071(du)002:6168: sngags dang / ha na da ha pa tsa rgyob cig /
NK071(du)002:6171: h+aum h+aum h+aum phata gdug pa can gyis lus ngag
NK071(du)002:6172: yid gsum bsdus la choms shig ces phrin las kyi
NK071(du)002:6173: sngags so / sngags byin gyis rlob pa rat+na ma
NK071(du)002:6174: h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da rin po
NK071(du)002:6175: che chen po dpal khrag 'thung gtum po chen po
NK071(du)002:6176: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka sdang ba thams cad mthar byed pa
NK071(du)002:6178: ha na da ha pa tsa rgyob cig sregs shig
NK071(du)002:6179: tshos shig h+aum h+aum h+aum phata sdang ba'i lus ngag
NK071(du)002:6180: yid gsum bsdus la choms shig ces phrin las kyi
NK071(du)002:6181: sngags so // sngags byin gyis rlob pa pad+ma ma
NK071(du)002:6182: h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da pad+ma chen
NK071(du)002:6183: po dpal khrag 'thung gtum po chen po sarba dush+t+aan+ta
NK071(du)002:6184: ka sdang ba thams cad mthar byed pa ste rtsa
NK071(du)002:6185: sngags dang ha na da ha pa tsa rgyob cig
NK071(du)002:6186: sregs shig tshos shig h+aum h+aum h+aum phata sdang ba'i
NK071(du)002:6187: lus ngag yid gsum bsdus la choms shig ces las
NK071(du)002:6188: sngags so // sngags so // bkra shis pa dang sngags byin gyis rlob pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6189: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK071(du)002:6190: las chen po dpal khrag 'thung gtum po chen po
NK071(du)002:6191: / sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka sdang ba thams cad mthar byed pa ste rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK071(du)002:6192: ha na da ha pa tsa rgyob cig sregs shig tshos shig /
NK071(du)002:6193: h+aum h+aum h+aum phata sdang ba'i lus ngag yid gsum
NK071(du)002:6194: bsdus la choms shig ces phrin las kyi sngags so
NK071(du)002:6196: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa
NK071(du)002:6197: r+ai de bzhin gshegs pa'i khro mo dbang phyug ma
NK071(du)002:6198: sarba dush+t+aana h+aum phata sdang ba kun bsdus la choms
NK071(du)002:6199: shig / ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro
NK071(du)002:6200: d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata rdo rje
NK071(du)002:6201: gzung ma khro mo dbang phyug gi 'bar ba chen
NK071(du)002:6202: mo gdug pa can bsdus la gtor shig /
NK071(du)002:6203: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai bi da ma h+aum phata /
NK071(du)002:6204: rin chen nyi ma'i khro mo dbang phyug ma chen
NK071(du)002:6205: mo rnam par 'joms ma gdug pa can gtor cig
NK071(du)002:6206: / h+r+ai shwat+ta sa man+ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+he
NK071(du)002:6207: shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h+aum phata kun tu rgod pa'i
NK071(du)002:6208: khro mo dbang phyug chen mo zo zhig gtor cig
NK071(du)002:6209: / / sarba a mo g+ha ma h+aa kro d+he
NK071(du)002:6210: shwa r+ai bi sh+w+aa h+aum phata thams cad don yod
NK071(du)002:6211: pa'i khro mo dbang phyug sna tshogs ma gdug pa
NK071(du)002:6212: / / can gtor cig / gnyis pa ma mo brgyad kyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6215: badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha chom kun ma'o badz+ra pra mo ha rab tu rmongs ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6216: badz+ra bet+ta l+ai ha ro langs ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6217: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha gtum mo'o //
NK071(du)002:6218: badz+ra puk+ka s+ai ha spos ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6219: badz+ra g+ha sma r+ai ha sme sha can no //
NK071(du)002:6220: badz+ra sme sha n+ai ha ni dur khrod ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6221: ha brgyad ni de dag gi sa bon no //
NK071(du)002:6222: badz+ra ko'u ri dzahzhesa pa dang sbyar na phrin las dang sgrub pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6223: dzahbasala na mnyes pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)002:6224: gsum pa phra men ma brgyad kyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6225: badz+ra sed+ha mu kh+aa he seng gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6226: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+aa he stag gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6227: badz+ra srid+g+ha la mu kh+aa he wa gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6228: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+aa he sbyang gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6229: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+aa he bya rgod gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6230: badz+ra kang+ka mu kh+aa he dur bya'i gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6231: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+aa he bya rog gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6232: badz+ra u l+au ka mu kh+aa he 'ug pa'i gdong can ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6233: he brgyad ni de dag gi sa bon no //
NK071(du)002:6234: phrin las kyi sngags kyang snga ma bzhin no //
NK071(du)002:6235: bzhi pa sgo ma bzhi'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6236: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah'aphagasa pa'i gzi brjid de rta mgo can no //
NK071(du)002:6238: don yod pa ste phag gi gdong can no //
NK071(du)002:6239: badz+ra lo ka bam 'jig rten snang byed ma ste dred gdong ma'o //
NK071(du)002:6240: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hohthala bar byed ma ste spyang gdong can no //
NK071(du)002:6241: mtha' rten gyi dzahh+aum bam hohbazhi ni de dag gi sa bon no /
NK071(du)002:6242: lnga pa dbang phyug ma rnams kyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6243: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)002:6244: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)002:6245: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)002:6246: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)002:6248: de la b+ha gi ni sring mo /
NK071(du)002:6249: b+har ya chung ma de dag gi sgra bsdus te b+h+yo zhes sa bon du byas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6250: las sgrub pa'i tshe ma nu rak+sha si b+h+yo /
NK071(du)002:6251: dgra bo ma r+aa ya h+aum phatah ces pa la sogs pa so sor sngags dang sbyar ro //
NK071(du)002:6252: gnyis pa ye shes pa spyan drangs pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6253: ru lu ru lu h+aum khro bo 'chol ba'i dkyil
NK071(du)002:6254: 'khor 'dod pa ste de'ang sngon las kyi srin po'i
NK071(du)002:6255: gdug pa'i glu dpal chen pos byin gyis brlabs pa'o
NK071(du)002:6256: // e h+ye hi tshur spyon tshur spyon +aa na ya gnas 'dir /
NK071(du)002:6257: dzahh+aum bam hohni tshad med bzhis sems can gyi don la bskul ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6258: ram ni dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa spyan
NK071(du)002:6259: drangs pa'i me ri 'dab 'byor tsam du bzhugs pa'o
NK071(du)002:6260: // bla ma rong pa ni rig pa'i me tog
NK071(du)002:6261: dor ba ste bdag dang lha rang bzhin dbyer med
NK071(du)002:6262: du rtogs nas gnyis su med pa la phyogs pa'o
NK071(du)002:6263: // zhes 'chad do // gsum pa dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdabs pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6264: gdul bya las kyi khro bo ma rungs pa 'dul
NK071(du)002:6265: ba la ye shes kyi rang bzhin shin tu khros
NK071(du)002:6266: pas gdul bya'i rgyud zhi bar mdzad pa /
NK071(du)002:6267: thugs rje ngang gis khro bor sprul pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6268: 'gro ba'i dpal chen po rab tu rngam pa'i tshogs /
NK071(du)002:6269: sku gsung thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin 'bar ba'i byin rlabs ya mtshan rmad po che /
NK071(du)002:6270: dus da lta nyid du ni bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub ma lus pa stsol cig /
NK071(du)002:6271: bzhi pa rigs pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6272: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum rdo rje khro bo dam tshig la 'dus shig /
NK071(du)002:6273: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam rdo rje khro bo dam tshig la nos shig /
NK071(du)002:6274: badz+ra kro d+h+aa sa ma ya phata rdo rje khro bo dam tshig spros shig /
NK071(du)002:6275: badz+ra kro d+h+aa sa ma ya hohrdo rje khro bo dam tshig yin no //
NK071(du)002:6276: lnga pa phrin las don du gtor ma sbyin pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)002:6277: a ba b+h+ram sha'i skad gyis /
NK071(du)002:6278: a li u li bza' ba dang btung ba t+aa
NK071(du)002:6279: li ta p+aa li de dag gi yan lag go
NK071(du)002:6280: / damsh+t+aa go n+aa roo drii mche ba can rdo rje drag po'i tshogs /
NK071(du)002:6281: kham ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa hi ho zhal 'bar ba rnal 'byor pa'i tshogs gsol cig /
NK071(du)002:6282: de dag gong gi zhal du gsol snyam nas /
NK071(du)002:6283: h+aum ha he phata lha sum cu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)002:6284: gsum pa ltas khyad par can gyis mjug bsdu ba ni de skad ces brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:6285: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad snod ma
NK071(du)002:6286: dag pa'i dngos po dang bcud kyi sgrib pa'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:6287: las lus kyi mi dge ba rnams tshig /
NK071(du)002:6288: ngag gi mi dge ba rnams rab tu tshig /
NK071(du)002:6289: yid kyi mi dge ba rnams kun tu tshig go /
NK071(du)002:6290: snang ba snod kyi 'jig rten ye shes kyi snang
NK071(du)002:6291: bar 'bar zhing gdul bya'i sgo gsum la sku'i ye
NK071(du)002:6292: shes 'bar / gsung gi ye shes rab tu 'bar /
NK071(du)002:6293: thugs kyi ye shes kun tu 'bar ro //
NK071(du)002:6294: de'i tshe snang srid snod bcud nam mkha'i mtha' gtug
NK071(du)002:6295: pa thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor rigs lnga'i
NK071(du)002:6296: rang bzhin gyi tshogs kyis nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad
NK071(du)002:6297: sku'i dkyil 'khor gyis gang de dag las gsang sngags
NK071(du)002:6298: kyi rang sgra 'brug stong tsam gyis khyab par rab
NK071(du)002:6299: tu gang ba thams cad kyang thugs rje chen po'i
NK071(du)002:6300: sprul pa dang / 'od dang gzi brjid kyis gsal
NK071(du)002:6301: la chos skus khyab pa'i thugs kyi rang bzhin gnyis
NK071(du)002:6302: su med pas kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK071(du)002:6303: yang dkyil 'khor gsum gyis nam mkha' dang sa gzhi
NK071(du)002:6304: dang bar snang gsum du gang rab tu gang kun
NK071(du)002:6305: tu gang ngo // yang rang snang lhun stug po
NK071(du)002:6306: bkod par 'od dang gzi brjid dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:6307: bkod pas gang rab tu gang kun tu gang ba'o
NK071(du)002:6308: tu gang ngo // // gsung mchog tu gsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:6309: snying po ye shes kyi rang sgra'i de kho na
NK071(du)002:6310: nyid nges pa las ye shes kyi khro bo'i tshogs
NK071(du)002:6311: chen po'i gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)002:6312: pa'i dkyil 'khor mtha' dbus med par spros pa'i le'u
NK071(du)002:6315: // don gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rten gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:6316: dkyil 'khor 'byung ba'i rgyu spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:6317: dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:6318: ngo mtshar gyi ltas snang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6320: gsung gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:6321: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro
NK071(du)002:6322: bo'i dkyil 'khor gsung sngags dang bcas pa de dag
NK071(du)002:6323: gi rnam pa gsal bar byed pa na dmigs pa'i
NK071(du)002:6324: rten dgos pas phyi rabs kyi gdul bya la phan
NK071(du)002:6325: pa'i don du gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i
NK071(du)002:6326: phyir ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)002:6331: dang po gzhal yas khang dngos ni //
NK071(du)002:6332: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i phyir phyi nang med par
NK071(du)002:6333: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong pho brang gi 'og gzhi
NK071(du)002:6334: lte ba mu khyud dang bcas pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs
NK071(du)002:6335: bzhi pa ni rigs lnga'i rang bzhin gyi barda'o //
NK071(du)002:6336: de'ang tshad med pa bzhi dang bden pa bzhi mtshon
NK071(du)002:6337: pa'i phyir gru chad bzhis ni rnams par brgyan pa'o
NK071(du)002:6338: // de'i steng du ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang
NK071(du)002:6339: yon tan rgyas pa'i brdar gru bzhi pa rnam par
NK071(du)002:6340: thar pa bzhi'i mtshon byed du sgo khyud bzhi dang
NK071(du)002:6341: ldan pa'i dbus su sku lnga'i rang bzhin mtshon pa'i
NK071(du)002:6342: brdar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad dang bcas pas
NK071(du)002:6343: // mdzes pa'o // des mtshon te rnam thar brgyad
NK071(du)002:6344: kyi rta babs dang bden pa gnyis kyi don mtshon
NK071(du)002:6345: pa ye shes 'bar ba'i bar khyams phyi nang gnyis
NK071(du)002:6346: kyis mdzes shing b+han+d+ha'i rtsig pa chen pos lhun mtho
NK071(du)002:6347: // mdzes pa'o // ba'o // gnyis pa de mdzes par byed pa'i rgyan ni /
NK071(du)002:6348: phal cher gong dang mtshungs shing khyad par du thod
NK071(du)002:6349: pa skam rlon gyi rtsig pa la sbrul nag gi
NK071(du)002:6350: chun pos dkris shing thod pa sbrul gyi zar tshags
NK071(du)002:6351: dang nyi zla'i mthong khung dang tshangs pa'i gdung dang
NK071(du)002:6352: mchog chen gyi ka ba dang rus sbal gyi ka
NK071(du)002:6353: gdan dang zhing gi lcam dang mchog phran gyi gral
NK071(du)002:6354: ba dang g.yang bzhi'i thog g.yam dang rgyu ma'i d+r+wa
NK071(du)002:6355: ba dang don snying gi d+r+wa phyed dang sgo bzhi
NK071(du)002:6356: rus bal gyi ma them dang /
NK071(du)002:6357: chu srin gyi ya them dang /
NK071(du)002:6358: sbrul nag gi skyes bu dang zhing chen gyi sgo
NK071(du)002:6359: glegs la sogs pa sna tshogs pas brgyan zhing nyi
NK071(du)002:6360: ma dang zla ba gza' skar gyis brjid cing /
NK071(du)002:6361: me dpung 'bar ba'i rtse las me'i tsha tsha phyogs
NK071(du)002:6362: bcur 'phro ba'i phreng ba mang po dang 'od zer
NK071(du)002:6364: gsum pa gdan gyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)002:6365: 'gro ba zil gyis gnon pa khyu mchog dang gzi
NK071(du)002:6366: brjid che ba ma he dang gdug pa che ba
NK071(du)002:6367: gzig dang dpal rtul che ba stag dang /
NK071(du)002:6368: rang bzhin gyis gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni btegs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6369: srog chags 'di dag kyang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i mtshon byed du rang snang ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6370: de ci ltar yin zhe na bla ma rong pas //
NK071(du)002:6371: khyung mchog ni lce 'bar ba'i 'jigs pa dang bral ba dang /
NK071(du)002:6372: khyus 'gro zil gyis gnon pas 'jigs byed khyung mchog zhes bya ste thugs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:6373: ma he ni gzi brjid che bas brjid pa'i ma he zhes bya ste sku'i phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:6374: gzig ni gdug pa che bas mi gtong ba'i phyir
NK071(du)002:6375: gzung dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK071(du)002:6376: gyi phyag rgya'o // stag ni dpal rtul che bas
NK071(du)002:6377: thugs rje chen po'i mtshan nyid pad+ma rig sa kyi
NK071(du)002:6378: gyi phyag rgya'o // phyag rgya'o // dom ni gtum pa'i phyir las kyi rigs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)002:6380: de'i steng du dregs pa'i dbang phyug lha chen po la sogs pa khyo shug zung du bsnol ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6381: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:6385: dang po sku mdog dang zhal phyag gi rnam pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6386: gti mug gnas su dag pas gtso bo smug nag
NK071(du)002:6387: zhe sdang dag pas badz+ra he ru ka sngon nag
NK071(du)002:6388: nga rgyal dag pas rat+na he ru ka ser nag
NK071(du)002:6389: dang / 'dod chags dag pas pad+ma he ru ka
NK071(du)002:6390: dmar nag phrag dog dag pas karma he ru ka
NK071(du)002:6391: ljang nag ste rtsa zhal dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6392: dbus dang shar nub byang gi he ru ka bzhi'i g.yas dkar zhing /
NK071(du)002:6393: lho'i g.yas sngon po dbus dang lho byang gi g.yon dmar zhing /
NK071(du)002:6394: shar dang nub kyi g.yon ser po gdul bya gdug
NK071(du)002:6395: pa can gyi snang ngor rab tu 'jigs pa'i sku
NK071(du)002:6396: / dug gsum dag cing sku gsum mnga' ba'i phyir
NK071(du)002:6397: thams cad kyang dbu gsum pa ye shes la dbang
NK071(du)002:6398: bsgyur zhing pha rol tu phyin pa drug gis 'gro
NK071(du)002:6399: ba drug sgrol ba'i phyir phyag drug rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK071(du)002:6400: rkang pa bzhi brnyes shing bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i brdar
NK071(du)002:6402: gnyis pa rgyan chas dang gsung gi nga ro ni /
NK071(du)002:6403: theg pa chen po'i don la mnga' brnyes pa'i mtshon
NK071(du)002:6404: byed du glang chen gyi ko rlon gyi stod g.yog
NK071(du)002:6405: dregs pa dbang du sdud pa zhing gi g.yang gzhi
NK071(du)002:6406: gzung 'dzin gyi mtha' las grol ba stag spags kyi
NK071(du)002:6407: sham thabs te bgo ba'i gos ni sna tshogs gyon
NK071(du)002:6408: zhing / sbrul rgyal rigs dkar po'i dbu rgyan rje'u
NK071(du)002:6409: rigs ser po'i snyan cha dang mgul chun bram ze'i
NK071(du)002:6410: rigs dmar po'i do shal dang dpung rgyan gdol po'i
NK071(du)002:6411: rigs nag po'i phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu dang thod
NK071(du)002:6412: phreng yang mi mgo skam po'i dbu rgyan rnying pa'i
NK071(du)002:6413: se ral kha rlon pa lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi
NK071(du)002:6414: do shal dang nyi ma dang zla ba'i chas phrag
NK071(du)002:6415: pa g.yas g.yon nas 'od 'gyed pa ste thabs dang
NK071(du)002:6416: shes rab kyi snang ba'i barda'o //
NK071(du)002:6417: de dag gis mtshon nas mkhur tshos su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK071(du)002:6418: ol ko zhag gi zo ris smin mtshams thal chen gyi tshom bu dang dpal gyi chas brgyad do //
NK071(du)002:6419: gsung gi nga ro rngam pa'i sgra skad chen po
NK071(du)002:6420: 'jigs par sgrogs pa 'brug stong ldir ba tsam mo
NK071(du)002:6421: // gsum pa phyag mtshan dang btsun mo'i sbyor tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:6422: sangs rgyas gsang ba g.yas g.yon gyi dang po gnyis na rdo rje dang 'khor lo //
NK071(du)002:6423: bar pa na ral gri dang dung chen /
NK071(du)002:6424: tha ma gnyis na dgra sta dang thong gshol la
NK071(du)002:6425: sogs kyi sgra dbyug tho tri shul be con la
NK071(du)002:6427: rong pa ni g.yas dang po rang rang gi phyag mtshan /
NK071(du)002:6428: g.yon dang po b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba gzhan rnams rim pa bzhin sbyor bar bzhed kyang /
NK071(du)002:6429: 'dir sgyu 'phrul rdo rje dang mthun par sbyar na /
NK071(du)002:6430: rdo rje'i g.yon tha ma dang las kyi g.yon tha
NK071(du)002:6431: ma na stong gi 'jig rten 'khor yug bcas pa
NK071(du)002:6433: badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas dang po rdo rje rtse
NK071(du)002:6434: dgu pa rigs lnga ka'i g.yas bar ma rdo rje
NK071(du)002:6435: rtse lnga pa g.yon bar ma dung chen te thod
NK071(du)002:6436: pa lcang lo med pa khrag gis gang ba dang
NK071(du)002:6437: / karma he ru ka'i g.yas dang po la ral
NK071(du)002:6438: gri de bzhin gshegs pa'i g.yon dang po dang rin
NK071(du)002:6439: po che'i g.yon tha ma gnyis na dgra s+t+wa las
NK071(du)002:6440: kyii g.yon dang po na gshol la sogs pa ste
NK071(du)002:6441: bud+d+ha'i g.yas dang po na 'khor lo //
NK071(du)002:6443: pad+ma las kyi g.yas tha ma na kha t+w+aam ka riin po che'i g.yon dang po na rgyu zhags /
NK071(du)002:6444: pad+ma'i g.yon dang po na dril bu tha ma na
NK071(du)002:6445: rnga chung thams cad kyi g.yas tha ma na ti
NK071(du)002:6446: ra ste zhing dbyug gdengs pa bcas rang rang gi
NK071(du)002:6448: rang rang gi rigs kyi btsun mo zhal gcig phyag
NK071(du)002:6449: gnyis ma 'jigs pa'i tshogs g.yas yab la 'khyud cing
NK071(du)002:6450: g.yon thod khrag gtso bo'i zhal du stob pa dang
NK071(du)002:6451: 'khril ba'o // gnyis pa 'khor gyi bkod pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6452: dang po khro mo nyi shu'i bkod pa las /
NK071(du)002:6453: gnas kyi ma mo brgyad ni rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK071(du)002:6454: 'khor ba bskyed pa'i gnas yin la de rnams gnas
NK071(du)002:6455: su dag par byed pa'i phyir gnas kyi phyag rgya
NK071(du)002:6456: dang de la koo'u r+ai dkar mo zhing dbyug dang
NK071(du)002:6457: b+han dmar / tso'u r+ai ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa //
NK071(du)002:6458: pra mo ha dmar mo phyag gnyis chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba /
NK071(du)002:6459: be ta l+ai nag mo rdo rje 'phyar zhing b+han dmar thugs dkar 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6460: puk+ka s+ai dmar ser byis pa'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK071(du)002:6461: kasma r+ai ljang nag dung dmar dkrugs cing gsol ba /
NK071(du)002:6462: sme sha n+ai mthing nag byis pa'i snying zab /
NK071(du)002:6463: tsan+da l+ai ser skya bam gyi mgo lus 'dral ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6464: yul gyi phra men brgyad ni /
NK071(du)002:6465: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyi yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya yid kyi yul chos /
NK071(du)002:6466: nyon mongs pa can gyi yul kun gzhi /
NK071(du)002:6467: kun gzhi'i yul phyi nang gi chos thams cad gnas su dag pas yul gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK071(du)002:6468: de'ang seng ha ser mo lag pas ro bsnol nas khas thad du 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6469: b+y+aa g+h+ri dmar mo ro la mig 'bru tshugs su blta ba /
NK071(du)002:6470: sri la nag mo zhing la bdag pa /
NK071(du)002:6471: shwa na mthing ga ro'i lto ba 'dral ba /
NK071(du)002:6472: gri d+ha dmar mo ro'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK071(du)002:6473: kang ka ser mo zhing chen phrag la khur ba /
NK071(du)002:6474: kha kha nag mo b+han+d+ha dang gri gug thogs pa /
NK071(du)002:6475: hu lu mthing ga lcags kyu 'debs pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6476: yang phyin ci log gi bdud bzhi 'joms shing ye
NK071(du)002:6477: shes bzhi yis rgyas 'debs pa'i rta gdong dkar mo
NK071(du)002:6479: phag gdong nag mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6480: dred gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6481: spyang gdong ljang gu dril chen 'dzin pa ste sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgyas rab tu mdzes shing /
NK071(du)002:6482: gnyis pa dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad gyi bkod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6483: slas chung ma dang byi mo mdza' mo dang g.yog gi las byed pa'i bran mo'i tshogs /
NK071(du)002:6484: bcu phrag gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes par bskor ba /
NK071(du)002:6485: de dag rang rang gi stan ro'i gdan dang thod rlon pa la sogs pa'i lag cha dang /
NK071(du)002:6486: phrin las ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas so //
NK071(du)002:6487: ji ltar gnas na srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang ba /
NK071(du)002:6488: tshangs pa dkar ser pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6489: 'khrug mo dkar ljang tri sh+aul 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6490: gtogs 'dod sngon mo 'khor lo thogs pa /
NK071(du)002:6491: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6492: dbang mo dkar mo rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6493: rdo rje ser mo tsan+dana 'thung ba /
NK071(du)002:6495: zla ba dkar mo pun+da r+ai ka /
NK071(du)002:6496: be con ljang gu dbyug tho /
NK071(du)002:6497: srin mo dmar nag dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK071(du)002:6498: za ba ljang nag ro'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK071(du)002:6499: dga' ba dmar mo gri gug /
NK071(du)002:6501: gcig pur spyod ma spu gri /
NK071(du)002:6503: grub mo dkar mo bum pa /
NK071(du)002:6504: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan /
NK071(du)002:6505: gsod byed dkar mo ral gri /
NK071(du)002:6506: mi mo dmar mo gsal shing /
NK071(du)002:6507: phag mo nag mo mche zhags /
NK071(du)002:6508: rgan byed nag mo zhing za ba /
NK071(du)002:6509: sna 'phyang dkar mo thod khrag 'thung ba //
NK071(du)002:6510: chu lha dmar mo sbrul zhags 'dzin pa /
NK071(du)002:6511: nag mo chen mo lcags kyu /
NK071(du)002:6515: le'u 'di ni bri ba dang sgom pa spyi'i don
NK071(du)002:6516: du smos kyi gcig kho na'i phyogs su byed pa
NK071(du)002:6517: ma yin no // gsum pa ngo mtshar gyi ltas snang ba ni zhes brjod pas /
NK071(du)002:6518: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du ye
NK071(du)002:6519: shes kyi khro bo me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:6520: zhing gi rdul snyed nam mkha'i dbyings dang chos kyis
NK071(du)002:6521: khyab pa kun tu sku gsung thugs kyi snang ba
NK071(du)002:6523: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po dkyil 'khor gyi de
NK071(du)002:6524: kho na nyid nges pa las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:6525: gyi rnam dbye bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o
NK071(du)002:6527: // // don gsum pa der mchod pa ji ltar bya ba'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:6533: de nas bcom ldan 'das mchod sprin gyi rol pas
NK071(du)002:6534: dgyes pa chen pos phyi nang gsang ba'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:6535: gyis mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen po 'di dag ched
NK071(du)002:6536: du brjod do // gnyis pa la gsum /
NK071(du)002:6537: sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:6538: dam rdzas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK071(du)002:6539: de'i phan yon dngos grub 'grub pa'i tshul brjod pas //
NK071(du)002:6542: de la rgyal ba mchod pa dang sems can la sbyin pa bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:6543: bsod nams kyi tshogs yin la de dag gi nang nas mchod dam pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6544: sems nyid ye nas dag pa mchod bya dang mchod
NK071(du)002:6545: byed med pa don gyi mchod pa ste mchod pa'i
NK071(du)002:6546: phyag rgya chen po yin pas na /
NK071(du)002:6547: thog mar bdag nyid kyis 'khor ba'i gnas 'dir ma
NK071(du)002:6548: rig pa'i log par rtog pas dngos po dang mtshan
NK071(du)002:6549: mar goms pa'i phyin ci log spros pa'i mtha' brgyad
NK071(du)002:6550: dang gzung 'dzin du zhen pa'i blo gdod nas skye
NK071(du)002:6551: ba med pa'i ngang du bsgral te phyi nang gi
NK071(du)002:6552: chos thams cad nam mkha'i rang bzhin du bsgom ste
NK071(du)002:6553: de nas bsgral ba'i yul dang sgrol byed bdag nyid
NK071(du)002:6554: gnyis su med pa'i blo yis ni /
NK071(du)002:6555: shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ngang las thabs snying rje chen pos bsgral bar bya ste /
NK071(du)002:6556: zhing bcu lta bu'i sems can blo ngan srid pa'i
NK071(du)002:6557: 'jig rten 'og mar brgyud ba 'di dag snying re
NK071(du)002:6558: rje snyam du byams pa dang snying rje tshad med
NK071(du)002:6559: pa bsgoms nas bdag nyid sgyu ma dang yul mig
NK071(du)002:6560: yor gyi tshul tsam du shes par byas te /
NK071(du)002:6561: kun rdzob tu snang yang don dam par gnyis su med par rtogs pas bsgral bar bya'o //
NK071(du)002:6562: gnyis pa sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6563: bdag dang yum lhar bskyed pa'i gsang bar dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:6564: spyan drangs la yab yum gnyis su med par 'khril
NK071(du)002:6565: ba'i bde ba byang chub kyi sems kyi mchod rdzas
NK071(du)002:6566: chen po rdo rje pad+ma mnyam par sbyor ba las
NK071(du)002:6568: bdag nyid mnyes pas de bzhin gshegs pa kun mnyes par bya'o /
NK071(du)002:6569: gnyis pa dam rdzas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6570: dang po dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6571: bdag gzhan 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i
NK071(du)002:6572: rdzas chen po bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dag
NK071(du)002:6573: / bdag gi phung po khams dang skye mched ye
NK071(du)002:6574: nas dkyil 'khor du gnas pa ting nge 'dzin zab
NK071(du)002:6576: bdag dang mnyam pa'i ye shes lha'i tshogs la 'bul lo //
NK071(du)002:6577: gnyis pa 'dod yon mchod pa gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6578: dam rdzas ni sha la sogs pa'i bza' ba dang
NK071(du)002:6579: shing thog la sogs pa'i bca' ba dang ja dang
NK071(du)002:6580: rgun chang la sogs pa'i btung ba dang li chu
NK071(du)002:6581: dang za ber la sogs pa'i bgo ba dang /
NK071(du)002:6582: gzhan yang lha dang mi'i longs spyod 'dod yon lnga
NK071(du)002:6583: dang ldan pa thams cad kun ji ltar 'bul tshul
NK071(du)002:6584: ni / mchod yul ye shes kyi lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:6585: du gsal ba la ni mchod rdzas 'dod yon gyi
NK071(du)002:6586: lha'i dkyil 'khor thim pa'i tshul gyis dbul zhing bdag
NK071(du)002:6587: yab tu shes pa la rdzas yum du rol pas
NK071(du)002:6589: gsum pa de'i phan yon la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6590: dang po thun mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6591: phyogs bcu dus bzhir sems can gyi don la gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)002:6592: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi yon tan rmad po
NK071(du)002:6593: che thams cad kyang sems goms pa las gzhan nas
NK071(du)002:6594: yod pa zhig 'dir 'ongs ba ma yin te /
NK071(du)002:6595: sems nyid goms pas mngon du gyur pa kho nar nges na /
NK071(du)002:6596: thun mong gi dngos grub lha srin bran du khol
NK071(du)002:6597: ba dang zhi rgyas dbang drag la sogs pa 'grub
NK071(du)002:6599: gnyis pa mchog gi dngos grub ni /
NK071(du)002:6600: rnal 'byor pa rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba rnams kyis /
NK071(du)002:6601: mtshan bcas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po me long
NK071(du)002:6602: nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bu'i bskyed rim rdzogs par
NK071(du)002:6603: 'gyur zhing / mtshan med rdzogs pa chen po bya
NK071(du)002:6604: rtsol med pa'i ngang nas gsal la yid gnyis med
NK071(du)002:6606: med pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po phrin las dang bcas
NK071(du)002:6608: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6610: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod sprin rgya mtsho'i mnyes pa'i
NK071(du)002:6611: mchod pa chen pos phyi nang gi 'jig rten drug
NK071(du)002:6612: gi phyogs bcu thams cad khyab par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:6613: ye shes gsang ba'i snying po kun la khyab pa'i
NK071(du)002:6614: de kho na nyid nges pa las bla na med
NK071(du)002:6615: pa'i yo byad kyis rgyal ba mchod cing sems can
NK071(du)002:6616: la sbyin pa dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bco
NK071(du)002:6618: don bzhi pa dam tshig dang ldan pas grub pa dam tshig gi rim pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:6624: de nas bcom ldan 'das dam tshig chen po'i rang
NK071(du)002:6625: bzhin la dgyes pa chen pos gsang sngags 'chang ba'i
NK071(du)002:6626: rnal 'byor pa rnams 'bras bu myur du grub cing
NK071(du)002:6627: log par mi ltung bas smos pa don yod par
NK071(du)002:6628: bya ba'i phyir gsang chen rgyal ba'i dam tshig chen
NK071(du)002:6629: po 'di ched du brjod par mdzad do //
NK071(du)002:6631: dam tshig chen po'i ngo bo spyir bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6632: sgrub srung gi rnam bzhag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6634: dang po gsang ba'i gzhan las 'phags pa'i tshul ni /
NK071(du)002:6635: gang zag gang zhig gsang chen bla na med pa'
NK071(du)002:6636: theg pa 'dir zhugs te don phyin ci ma log
NK071(du)002:6637: par rab tu nges pa ste nyams su blang na
NK071(du)002:6638: / 'dod chags la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa dug
NK071(du)002:6639: lnga dang de'i bskyed pa'i las rnams kun la spyad
NK071(du)002:6640: / kyang / sgyu ma'i sprul pas spyad pa ltar
NK071(du)002:6641: las de nyid byas pa ltar snang la de'i sgrib
NK071(du)002:6642: pa dang bag chags mi gsog pa'i steng du bsod
NK071(du)002:6643: nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur
NK071(du)002:6644: / kyang / te / spyod pa de nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:6645: ngo bo la so sor thar pa'i tshul khrims dang
NK071(du)002:6646: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang gsang sngags kyi
NK071(du)002:6647: dam tshig rnams phun sum tshogs pa'i don tshang zhing
NK071(du)002:6649: gnyis pa gsang ba'i dam tshig tu 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6650: gsang chen bla na med pa mchog gi dam tshig tu /
NK071(du)002:6651: nyes spyod 'dul ba'i dbang gis rnam par bzhag pa'i tshul khrims so sor thar pa'i sdom pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6652: des mtshon nas byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang
NK071(du)002:6653: gsang sngags phyi pa gsum nang pa dang bcas pa
NK071(du)002:6654: ji snyed pa'i sdom pa bsam yas pa /
NK071(du)002:6655: ma lus pa'i yon tan kun ldan du 'dus shing
NK071(du)002:6656: 'og ma'i skyon gyi phyogs phra mo tsam du yang
NK071(du)002:6657: med pas rnam par dag pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6658: gsum pa rtsa ba'i tshig chen po'i rnam par bzhag pa la bzhi las //
NK071(du)002:6659: dang po srog gcad pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6660: don dam par chos yod pa rtag pa'i mtha' dang
NK071(du)002:6661: med pa chad pa'i mtha' dang mtha' gnyis dang bral
NK071(du)002:6662: ba'i dbu ma tsam du yang mi dmigs shing /
NK071(du)002:6663: kun rdzob tu bdag nyid sgyu ma dang sems can
NK071(du)002:6664: mig yor lta bu'i tshul gyis sgrol ba ltar snang
NK071(du)002:6665: ba / snang dus de nyid na sems can rang
NK071(du)002:6666: mtshan du ma grub pas srog bden pa med cing
NK071(du)002:6667: srog rang bzhin ma grub pas srog kyang rmi lam
NK071(du)002:6668: dang 'dra bas bcad du med la /
NK071(du)002:6669: srog dang srog ldan gyi skyes bu ltar snang ba
NK071(du)002:6670: yang rang sems 'khrul ba'i log rtog tsam las don
NK071(du)002:6671: gnyis su grub pa med do //
NK071(du)002:6674: sangs rgyas bstan pa gnod byed dang //
NK071(du)002:6675: bla ma dmod brtson ma rung dang //
NK071(du)002:6676: rtag tu sems can gnod brtson pa //
NK071(du)002:6677: mkhas pas bsgrims te gsad par bya //
NK071(du)002:6679: byang chub spyod 'phel sems can bde //
NK071(du)002:6680: lha mnyes bdag gi dam bskangs shing //
NK071(du)002:6681: las ngan bar chad sdug yun thung /
NK071(du)002:6683: gnyis pa ma byin par blang ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6684: chos thams cad don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi
NK071(du)002:6685: bden pa gnyis ka rang bzhin dbyer med pas don
NK071(du)002:6687: tha snyad tsam du'ang 'phrul dag'i lha rnams rang rang
NK071(du)002:6688: gis sprul pa'i longs spyod la len pa'i tshul te
NK071(du)002:6689: gzhan du snang ba'i rdzas dang len pa po bdag
NK071(du)002:6690: nyid don la tha dad min pa'i rang bzhin shes
NK071(du)002:6691: nas / rang snang gi rdzas la rang gis len
NK071(du)002:6692: pa'i tshul gyis ma byin par len dus de nyid
NK071(du)002:6693: na'ang blang bya'i yul sems can gzhan dang des bdag
NK071(du)002:6694: tu bzung ba'i rdzas rang mtshan pa ma byin pa
NK071(du)002:6696: blangs pa yang med de blang bya'i yul blang rgyu'i
NK071(du)002:6697: rdzas len pa po rnams kyis mtshon pa'i chos thams
NK071(du)002:6698: cad ye nas rnam par dag pa nam mkha'i lta
NK071(du)002:6699: bu'i de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings yin pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)002:6700: // blang ba'i dgos pa yang phyung po de dag
NK071(du)002:6701: gi tshogs rdzogs la bkren pa de dag gi 'dod
NK071(du)002:6704: 'jungs pa rnams la nor blangs la //
NK071(du)002:6705: sems can bkren la sbyin par bya //
NK071(du)002:6706: de phyir mi yi bdag po dang //
NK071(du)002:6707: phyug po rnams kyi nor dbrog go /
NK071(du)002:6709: gsum pa brdzun du smra ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6710: gzhan don du 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod na ji
NK071(du)002:6711: ltar phan pa de ltar smras kyang nyes pa med
NK071(du)002:6712: de / 'di ltar 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK071(du)002:6713: rnams ni sgyu ma dang rmi lam lta bu dang
NK071(du)002:6714: de / / de dag so so'i ming dang tshig
NK071(du)002:6715: tu btags pa de yang so so'i rtog pas glo
NK071(du)002:6716: bur du btags pa'i phyir brdzun zhing /
NK071(du)002:6717: de ltar rtogs na gtong bya'i yul brdzun pa nyid
NK071(du)002:6718: la ni gtong byed bdag kyang brdzun pas ngag tu
NK071(du)002:6719: yod med la sogs pa'i brdzun spyod pa de'i tshe
NK071(du)002:6720: / brdzun zhes ming tsam btags tsam du yang yod
NK071(du)002:6721: pa ma yin te sgra de nyid phyi nang gang
NK071(du)002:6723: de'i ngo bo grags stong skye med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:6726: sems can rnams la phan spyod pas //
NK071(du)002:6727: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK071(du)002:6728: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK071(du)002:6729: brdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK071(du)002:6731: bzhi pa mi tshangs par spyad pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6732: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gang du'ang ma chags
NK071(du)002:6733: pa dngos po dang mtshan mar grub pa cung zad
NK071(du)002:6734: kyang med pa'i gnas lugs stong pa nyid la blos
NK071(du)002:6735: de ltar rtogs pa ni chags pa dang ste shes
NK071(du)002:6736: rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ngang nas /
NK071(du)002:6737: yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i ye shes la chags
NK071(du)002:6738: pa nyid na tha mar rang ka ba'i chags pa
NK071(du)002:6739: med pa / de ni bde stong gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:6740: pa'i ye shes tshangs par spyod pa mchog gi rgyal
NK071(du)002:6741: med pa / po ste / shin tu rnam par
NK071(du)002:6742: dag pa'i chags pa chen po pad+ma'i rigs sems can
NK071(du)002:6743: la thugs rje 'byung ba'i ngang tshul yin no //
NK071(du)002:6746: sangs rgyas rnams ni mnyes bya dang //
NK071(du)002:6747: dam tshig rnams ni bsrung ba dang //
NK071(du)002:6748: gsang sngags rig par bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK071(du)002:6749: gzhan gyi bud med brten par bya //
