NK071(du)002:6751: gnyis pa bsgrub srung gi rnam bzhag bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)002:6752: ngo bo nges tshig dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)002:6753: phan yon nyes dmigs dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)002:6754: rang bzhin dbye ba dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)002:6755: phan yon chen po bshad pa'o /
NK071(du)002:6760: dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK071(du)002:6761: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi bla na med pa'i
NK071(du)002:6762: dkon mchog gsum mi spangs pa dang chos dang dam
NK071(du)002:6763: tshig gis 'brel ba'i bla ma rnams dang khyad par
NK071(du)002:6764: gsang sngags kyi rdo rje'i bla ma bkur pa ste
NK071(du)002:6765: de'ang dbang bskur brgyud bshad pa gdams pa bstan pa
NK071(du)002:6766: ni bka' drin sum ldan ste de las yul gnyan
NK071(du)002:6768: re re'am gnyis ldan lta bu la dbang dang bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6769: man ngag gsum ni snga ma snga ma las gnyan no //
NK071(du)002:6770: dkyil 'khor gang du zhugs pa'i lha rnams kyi rgyu
NK071(du)002:6771: ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags la sogs pa yan
NK071(du)002:6772: lag lnga'i sgo nas bzlas pa dang dam tshig chos
NK071(du)002:6773: las phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi'i sgo nas lha
NK071(du)002:6774: so so'i phyag rgya 'chang ba rnams rgyun mi gcad
NK071(du)002:6775: pa dang / yang dag pa'i lam theg pa chen
NK071(du)002:6776: po nyid du zhugs pa'i gang zag rnams la byams
NK071(du)002:6777: pa dang / pa dang / gab pa dang sbas
NK071(du)002:6778: pa'i lta spyod gsang ba'i don rnams phyir snod du
NK071(du)002:6779: ma gyur pa la smra bar mi bya'o //
NK071(du)002:6780: 'di dag ni dam tshig gi rtsa ba lnga po rnams te /
NK071(du)002:6781: dang po gsum sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang phyi ma
NK071(du)002:6782: gnyis de dag gi thugs dang 'gal ba srung ba'i
NK071(du)002:6783: dam tshig gi mchog yin no //
NK071(du)002:6784: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6785: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK071(du)002:6786: gtii mug gang du'ang mi rtog pa dang 'dod chags
NK071(du)002:6787: bde ba chen po dang zhe sdang gsal ba chen
NK071(du)002:6788: po dang / nga rgyal dregs pa chen po dang
NK071(du)002:6789: phrag dog khro ba chen po rnams ni gzhi ye
NK071(du)002:6790: nas dag cing thabs kyis lam du 'gyur ba la
NK071(du)002:6791: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su 'char ba'i rang
NK071(du)002:6792: bzhin yin pas nam yang mi spang ngo //
NK071(du)002:6793: dang du blang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK071(du)002:6794: dkar rtsi byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK071(du)002:6795: dmar rtsi pad+ma rak+ta dang dri chen dang dri chu dang sha chen gyi dwangs ma rnams /
NK071(du)002:6796: kha cig rtsog par 'dzin pas de dang thun mong
NK071(du)002:6797: blo spang byar shes pa ni dam rdzas kyis dag
NK071(du)002:6798: pa'i snod yin pas de nyid du mi dor ro
NK071(du)002:6799: // de dag ni rtsa ba'i grogs sam thabs su
NK071(du)002:6800: byung bas na yan lag rnams pa bcu yi dam
NK071(du)002:6801: // tshig ste / rang dgar spyad na tha mal
NK071(du)002:6802: ba bzhin 'gyur bas ye nas dag pa gsum dang
NK071(du)002:6803: mnyam pa bzhir gnas pa'i don rtogs pas rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:6804: shes par byas la rang rang gi thabs kyis zin
NK071(du)002:6806: gnyis pa nges tshig la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6808: bsrung zhing sgrub pa'i dam tshig rnam pa lnga /
NK071(du)002:6809: gsang sngags sgrub pa'i rtsa ba yin te /
NK071(du)002:6810: ljon shing gi rtsa ba ltar bsrung na dngos grub 'byung zhing /
NK071(du)002:6811: nyams na mngon par byang chub pa'i rigs med par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:6812: yan lag gi nges tshig ni /
NK071(du)002:6813: mi spang ba dang mi 'dor ba'i dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis ni /
NK071(du)002:6814: rtsa ba sgrub pa'i grogs su dgos pas yan lag
NK071(du)002:6815: gi dam tshig ces bya ste de dag kyang rtsa
NK071(du)002:6816: ba dang gnyan mi gnyan dgos pa'i dbang gis mnyan
NK071(du)002:6817: pas na / de las shin tu 'da' daka'o //
NK071(du)002:6818: gnyis pa phan yon nyes dmigs dang bcas pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6819: dam tshig la gnas pa'i phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:6820: chos thams cad ye nas sku dang ye shes su
NK071(du)002:6821: sangs rgyas mnyam pa'i don la lam thabs dang shes
NK071(du)002:6822: rab zab mos mnyam par sbyor ba yi rang bzhin
NK071(du)002:6823: no // mnyam pa'i dam tshig chen po de nyid la gnas na /
NK071(du)002:6824: 'bras bu sku gsum 'du 'bral med par mnyam pa
NK071(du)002:6825: nyid kyi yon tan lhun rdzogs chen po rdzogs pa'i
NK071(du)002:6826: sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur bas na dam tshig bsrung
NK071(du)002:6827: bar bya'o // de las 'das na sangs rgyas thob pa ma yin no //
NK071(du)002:6828: dper na rgyal po'i khrims la gnas pas bde ba
NK071(du)002:6829: 'byung zhing 'das pas chad pa 'byung ba bzhin no
NK071(du)002:6830: // gnyis pa nyams pa'i nyes dmigs la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6831: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa la'ang nyams sgrib gzhan la gnod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6832: rtsa ba nyams pa'i gang zag bslab sdom 'chal ba dag /
NK071(du)002:6833: dam tshig gso ba'i thabs la nye bar mi brtson pa de dang /
NK071(du)002:6834: skad cig tsam yang mi 'grogs shing yud tsam cig tu'ang phan tshun gtam smra bar ma byed cig /
NK071(du)002:6835: ci'i phyir zhe na tshe 'dir nad dang gnod pa
NK071(du)002:6836: la sogs pa mi 'dod pa'i rkyen sna tshogs 'byung
NK071(du)002:6837: zhing phyi mar de dang mnyam du dmyal bar 'gro
NK071(du)002:6838: dgos pas dam tshig nyams pa las gyur pa'i nyes
NK071(du)002:6839: pa brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK071(du)002:6840: gnyis pa nyams pa'i nyes pa rang la 'byung ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6841: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams par gyur na /
NK071(du)002:6842: char phab than pa 'byung ba'am mthu btang na rang
NK071(du)002:6843: la log pa ltar gang sgrub pa thams cad de
NK071(du)002:6845: kun gyi yid du mi 'ong ba dang /
NK071(du)002:6847: nad dang gdon dang 'tshe ba dang tshe thung ba
NK071(du)002:6848: la sogs pa mi 'dod pa thams cad 'byung zhing
NK071(du)002:6849: / phyi mar dmyal bar ltung nas bskal pa du
NK071(du)002:6850: mar sdug bsngal ba la sogs pa rang gi yid
NK071(du)002:6851: du mi 'ong pa sna tshogs pa'i rang bzhin rgyu
NK071(du)002:6852: dam tshig nyams pas bskyed pa'i gnas skabs dang mthar
NK071(du)002:6853: thug gi 'bras bu sdug bsngal du ma mi 'dod
NK071(du)002:6854: bzhin du rang dbang med par 'du bar byed do
NK071(du)002:6855: / // gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig nyam pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6856: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na /
NK071(du)002:6857: tshe 'dir bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub gang yang
NK071(du)002:6858: med cing phyi ma ngan song gsum du ltung ngo
NK071(du)002:6859: // gsum pa rang bzhin dang dbye ba bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6860: dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni /
NK071(du)002:6861: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams ni sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che ste /
NK071(du)002:6862: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid dam pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:6863: gnyis pa dbye ba la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:6864: rnam grangs kyi dbye ba dang /
NK071(du)002:6865: bsam gyis mi khyab par dbye ba'o //
NK071(du)002:6868: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po la ni /
NK071(du)002:6869: bla med mi spong ba lta bu gcig la'ang rtsa
NK071(du)002:6870: ba thabs dang shes rab gnyis dang de gnyis la
NK071(du)002:6871: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum ste drug dang /
NK071(du)002:6872: de re re la'ang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK071(du)002:6873: las lnga lnga ste bsngomasa pas bcu phrag gsum rtsa
NK071(du)002:6874: ba'i thabs shes gnyis bsnan pas sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)002:6875: de ltar lnga ka la phye bas brgya drug cu'o
NK071(du)002:6876: // yan lag gi dam tshig dbye ba ni yan
NK071(du)002:6877: lag gi dam tshig lnga yan lag gi dam tshig
NK071(du)002:6879: 'dod chags mi spang ba lta bu gcig la'ang thabs
NK071(du)002:6880: dang shes rab las thabs la ye shes lnga dang
NK071(du)002:6881: yul lnga shes rab la ye shes lnga dang yul
NK071(du)002:6882: lnga ste bcu phrag gnyis su dbye bas nyi shu
NK071(du)002:6883: yod do // de ltar nyi shu tshan pa bcu la nyis bargya'o //
NK071(du)002:6885: yan lag gi dam tshig ni /
NK071(du)002:6886: yan lag nyi shur dbye bar bya ste /
NK071(du)002:6887: gcig la'ang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi yan lag rnam pa lnga /
NK071(du)002:6888: sku gsum thugs kyi dngos gzhi gsum yang de nyid du zhig ste yan lag gi gzhi med /
NK071(du)002:6889: rtsa ba thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyang thabs shes rab dang ldan /
NK071(du)002:6890: shes rab thabs dang ldan pas rtsa ba gnyis po
NK071(du)002:6891: zhig ste yan lag bzhir 'gyur bas de yang sku
NK071(du)002:6892: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'ii cha shas su
NK071(du)002:6893: 'gyur bas rtsa ba'i 'phro gzhi med de yan lag
NK071(du)002:6894: dang cha shas nyi shu nyi shu 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:6895: mdor na rtsa ba'i dbye ba'i skabs su ni rtsa
NK071(du)002:6896: ba dang bcas pa snying po dang bcas pa yon
NK071(du)002:6897: tan dang bcas pa yan lag dang nyid lag dang
NK071(du)002:6899: yan lag gi dbye ba'i skabs su ni /
NK071(du)002:6900: rtsa ba med pa snying po med pa 'phro gzhi
NK071(du)002:6901: med pa yan lag dang cha shas tsam du zad
NK071(du)002:6902: ces yongs grags dbus lugs pa'i ltar bshad do //
NK071(du)002:6903: gnyis pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbye ba la gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:6904: dang po chos can bsam gyis mi khyab pas dam
NK071(du)002:6905: tshig bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni rtsa ba dang
NK071(du)002:6906: yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag ni ngo mtshar
NK071(du)002:6907: rmad po che yin te 'gro ba'i khams rnams ye
NK071(du)002:6908: shes chen por 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)002:6909: de'ang sems can mtha' yas pa ltar de re re
NK071(du)002:6910: la ltos pa'i dam tshig sum brgya drug cu'ang de
NK071(du)002:6911: snyed 'gyur bas mtha' yas so zhes bstan pa ni
NK071(du)002:6912: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK071(du)002:6913: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ji snyed yod pa /
NK071(du)002:6914: de dag gi rnam par rtog pa ji snyed pa
NK071(du)002:6915: 'dul ba'i phyir rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK071(du)002:6916: tshig kyang de snyed du spro bas nam mkha'i dbyings
NK071(du)002:6917: dang chos kyi dbyings ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o
NK071(du)002:6918: // gnyis pa chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pas dam tshig bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6919: de ltar chos can rnam grangs kyi dam tshig bstan
NK071(du)002:6920: pa las gzhan yang snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)002:6921: thams cad ye nas blang dor med pas spang blang
NK071(du)002:6922: srung mtshams las 'das pa rgyal mchog kun tu bzang
NK071(du)002:6923: po bya rtsol med pa mchog gi rol par chos
NK071(du)002:6924: thams cad ma lus par 'dus shing gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:6926: gang gis kyang bcos shing rtsol sgrub med pa'i rang
NK071(du)002:6927: bzhin te ma lus pa'i dam tshig thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:6928: snying po'i mchog dam pa 'grub cing /
NK071(du)002:6929: de la sogs pa bsam brjod dmigs pa'i yul las
NK071(du)002:6930: 'das pas dam tshig gi ngo bo mtha' yas pa'i
NK071(du)002:6931: mchog rdzogs pa chen po don gyi gnas lugs su
NK071(du)002:6932: gnas pa'o // de lta bu'i dam tshig tu dam
NK071(du)002:6933: tshig thams cad ma sgrub kyang ngang gis 'du ba'i
NK071(du)002:6934: gnas pa'o // yon tan ni / nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK071(du)002:6935: nor bu rin chen rnyed pa'i mi //
NK071(du)002:6936: 'jig rten so nam mi dgos bzhin //
NK071(du)002:6937: ma sgom sems kyi don rtogs na //
NK071(du)002:6938: yon tan ma lus lhun gyis grub //
NK071(du)002:6939: de las mi 'da' dam tshig yin //
NK071(du)002:6941: bzhi pa phan yon chen po rgya cher bshad pa la lnga las /
NK071(du)002:6942: dang po 'jig rten pas bstod cing bskur ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6943: rgyal ba'i rigs kyi mchog gsang sngags 'dzin cing dam tshig la gnas pa de /
NK071(du)002:6944: tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs pa 'jig rten
NK071(du)002:6945: pa'i gtso bo dang de dag gi 'khor gyis bstod
NK071(du)002:6946: cing bkur sti dang phu dud byed par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)002:6947: // gnyis pa 'phags pas byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK071(du)002:6948: lha dang mi'i skye dgu rnams kyi nang nas dam
NK071(du)002:6949: pa'i mchog gtso bo sangs rgyas rnams dang de'i thugs
NK071(du)002:6950: sras kyi dam pa byang chub sems dpa' yis ni
NK071(du)002:6951: / rim pa bzhin sras kyi thu bo dang spun
NK071(du)002:6952: gyi dwangs mar dgongs shing sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK071(du)002:6953: phrin las bcas pas byin gyis rlob pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6954: gsum pa rgyal ba'i spyod yul thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:6955: dam tshig la gnas pa de nyid bde bar gshegs
NK071(du)002:6956: pa nyid kyi spyod yul sar chud pa sa la
NK071(du)002:6957: gnas pas yongs su smin pa'i rig 'dzin gsum la
NK071(du)002:6958: zhugs pa'i mthar / chos thams cad la 'jigs pa
NK071(du)002:6959: med pa'i mchog kun tu bzang por sbyor zhing thob
NK071(du)002:6960: zhugs pa'i mthar / par byed do // sar chud
NK071(du)002:6961: pa'i rig 'dzin ni dkyil dkyil 'khor du zhugs te
NK071(du)002:6962: bskyed rdzogs dang por nos pa dag go /
NK071(du)002:6963: sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)002:6964: rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin thob nas de la rgyun du gnas pa'o //
NK071(du)002:6966: thob pa de las kyang stobs cher gyur te rnam
NK071(du)002:6967: smin tshe dbang phyag rgya thob nas lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)002:6968: pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor zhing thob par byed pa'o
NK071(du)002:6969: // bzhi pa sdom pa dang dam tshig gi yon tan 'dus pa'i phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:6970: bla na med pa'i dam tshig gi nang du chos
NK071(du)002:6971: thams cad kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid
NK071(du)002:6972: nam mkha' lta bu dang sems can 'dul ba'i thabs
NK071(du)002:6973: theg pa mtha' dag gi don dang /
NK071(du)002:6974: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK071(du)002:6975: dpa' dang rig pa 'dzin pa la sogs pa ji
NK071(du)002:6976: snyed pa de dag gi sdom pa bsam yas kyi
NK071(du)002:6978: ma lus pa kun yar ldan gyi tshul bre mig
NK071(du)002:6979: tu phul ltar 'dus nas rnam par dag cing lhun
NK071(du)002:6981: lnga pa nyams kyang gsor rung ba'i phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:6982: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa
NK071(du)002:6983: na nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims rdza be'u chag pa
NK071(du)002:6984: ltar gsor mi rung ba ma yin gyi dbang nod
NK071(du)002:6985: pa dang bshags pa la sogs pa'i tshogs bskangs bas
NK071(du)002:6986: snga ma bzhin sor chud cing rdzogs pa dang /
NK071(du)002:6987: de la sogs pa phan yon mtha' yas pa'i mchog gsang sngags la yod do //
NK071(du)002:6988: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:6990: rang snang gi de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshogs nyid de
NK071(du)002:6991: bzhin gshegs pa kun tu bzang po dkyil 'khor gyi
NK071(du)002:6992: mnga' bdag de nyid la 'dud par gyur to //
NK071(du)002:6993: dam tshig gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK071(du)002:6994: nges pa las rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK071(du)002:6995: tshig gi don bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o
NK071(du)002:6997: // // don lnga pa dam tshig can gyis phrin las ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:7002: dam tshig gi rim pa bshad pa de nas dam tshig can gyis phrin las sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)002:7003: de bzhin gshegs pa bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi
NK071(du)002:7004: dgyes pa chen po nyid ye nas rang bzhin lhun
NK071(du)002:7005: gyis grub pa'i dam tshig phrin las su byin gyis
NK071(du)002:7006: rlob pa zhes bya ba ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
NK071(du)002:7007: par zhugs nas las thams cad 'grub pa'i ched du
NK071(du)002:7010: phrin las bzhi'i rim pa spyir bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:7011: las kyi rjes su bka' bsgo zhing bro gar gyi
NK071(du)002:7012: phan yon bye brag tu bshad pa las bzhi sgrub
NK071(du)002:7013: pa'i gnas dang / ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par ro //
NK071(du)002:7020: dang po bsreg pa me'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7021: drag po'i thab khung gru gsum e yi rnam pa
NK071(du)002:7022: can mtshan nya da rnams tshang ba'i tshogs kyi dbus
NK071(du)002:7023: su lha so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi mchog /
NK071(du)002:7024: dam tshig pa bskyed la ye shes pa bcug ste
NK071(du)002:7025: gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin drag po'i me dpung
NK071(du)002:7026: 'bar ba'i me lha gtum chen rngam pa'i cha byad
NK071(du)002:7027: can la / sngags mkhan bsgrub bya la rab tu
NK071(du)002:7028: khros pa'i yid kyis drag po'i mchod pa dang bsreg
NK071(du)002:7029: rdzas sbyin par bya ba na tshogs gnyis las grub
NK071(du)002:7030: pa'i sangs rgyas bsod nams brgya'i mtshan gyis brgyan pa'i
NK071(du)002:7031: sku yang 'jig rten phal pa rnams lta ci smos
NK071(du)002:7032: can la / pa'o // gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7033: lang+ka'i rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na nywa sha bu
NK071(du)002:7034: ram til nag sbrang rtsi 'bras he zas lnga de'i
NK071(du)002:7035: gseb tu bsgrub bya'i dri ma rkang rjes kyi sa
NK071(du)002:7037: bsgrub bya'i mtshan ma la dpral bar ming snying gar
NK071(du)002:7038: rus mdoms su bla btags gang yod dang m+aa ra
NK071(du)002:7039: ya phatahdu bcas par bri bar bya zhing tha ma
NK071(du)002:7040: 'gug byed kyi yi ge dzas bskor ba gro ga'am
NK071(du)002:7041: ras sam shog bu la bris te de'i nang du
NK071(du)002:7042: gzhug pa'am mdun rgyab gang rung du glan par bya'o
NK071(du)002:7043: // de la bsgrub bya sngags dang ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)002:7044: phyag rgya gsum gyis bkug nas lcags la sogs pa
NK071(du)002:7045: rdo rje phur bu badz+ra k+ai la yar bskyed pas
NK071(du)002:7046: snying ga la sogs pa'i gnas su gdab ste /
NK071(du)002:7047: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du byas par bsam nas
NK071(du)002:7048: karma he ru ka'i tshogs sam snga ma'i thab khung
NK071(du)002:7049: du drag po'i lha bskyed pa'i tshogs la 'bul zhing
NK071(du)002:7050: sbyin sreg bya'o // gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7051: e tshogs kyi ste drag po'i dkyil 'khor mchog gi
NK071(du)002:7052: khor yug tu rnal 'byor pa des gung srin gnyis
NK071(du)002:7053: mthe bos mnan mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba bkan pa'i
NK071(du)002:7054: mathe'u chung gnyis lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams
NK071(du)002:7055: nas / phyag rgya de ltar bcings par gyur pas
NK071(du)002:7056: lus bskyod nas rdo rje'i 'gros kyis gom pa phyogs
NK071(du)002:7057: bcur g.yo bas h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK071(du)002:7058: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK071(du)002:7060: skad cig yud la brlag mdzad de //
NK071(du)002:7061: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK071(du)002:7062: m+aa ra ya phatahcesa brjod cing ling+ga'i steng du rkang
NK071(du)002:7063: bro brdungs pas bsgrub bya rdul du song bar bsam
NK071(du)002:7064: mo // des ni gang dmigs de nyid dran pa
NK071(du)002:7065: myos nas snying gas te lus tshig cing dngos po
NK071(du)002:7067: kha cig sngar gyi sbyin sreg gi las zin pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7068: sa gzhi bsrungs la de'i steng du rnal 'byor pho
NK071(du)002:7069: mo rnams gral gru gsum du byas te me dpung
NK071(du)002:7070: gi dbus su karma he ru ka'i rnam par bskyed
NK071(du)002:7071: la thams cad srin lag sbrel te dbus su ling+ga
NK071(du)002:7072: bzhag pa'i mthar bro brdungs zhes zer ro //
NK071(du)002:7073: de'ang bsreg mnan bro gsum po 'di gang rung re
NK071(du)002:7074: res kyang las 'grub la gsum ka tshang na mchog
NK071(du)002:7075: tu 'grub po // gnyis pa dbang gi las la'ang gsum las /
NK071(du)002:7076: dang po bsreg pa me'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7077: bam gyi rnam pa thab khung zla gam mtshan nyid
NK071(du)002:7078: tshang ba'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog ste thab kyi
NK071(du)002:7079: mtshan nyid dang lha'i dkyil 'khor gnyis ka la 'jug
NK071(du)002:7080: cing de'i nang du thab kyi me dang /
NK071(du)002:7081: me lha rab tu 'bar ba dbang gi cha byad
NK071(du)002:7082: can gzi brjid che zhing sku bong gi lhun chen
NK071(du)002:7084: sngags mkhan bsgrub bya la rjes su chags pa'i yid
NK071(du)002:7085: kyis dbang dang mthun pa'i rdzas me la mchod sbyin
NK071(du)002:7086: bya bas / rdo rje gsung ste snang ba mtha' yas lta bu yang dbang du 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:7087: gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7088: bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga bsgrub bya'i gos dang dri mar bcas pa la /
NK071(du)002:7089: mtshan ma gzugs byas pa'i nang du shog bu la
NK071(du)002:7090: sogs pa'i byang bu la ming rus mtshan gsum du
NK071(du)002:7091: bcas pa bris la gzhug par bya zhing /
NK071(du)002:7092: rdo rje chags pa pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i zangs la sogs pa'i phur bas gdab pa'i //
NK071(du)002:7093: ling+ga de nyid chags pa'i tshogs pad+ma he ru ka
NK071(du)002:7094: 'khor bcas sam thab kyi lha la thim par 'bul
NK071(du)002:7095: lo // gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7096: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor thab khung gi mtha' 'am dbang gi dkyil 'khor du /
NK071(du)002:7097: rnal 'byor pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel te bsdams nas bro byas na /
NK071(du)002:7098: 'gro ba thams cad 'gug par 'gyur ba'i rdo rje
NK071(du)002:7099: pad+ma dang dbang chen mdzes pa'ang phyi bzhin 'brang na
NK071(du)002:7100: / mi'i 'gro ba phal pa rnams lta smos kyang
NK071(du)002:7101: ci dgos te yid la ci 'dod pa de bzhin
NK071(du)002:7103: gsum pa rgyas pa'i las la'ang gsum las //
NK071(du)002:7104: dang po bsreg pa me yi las ni /
NK071(du)002:7105: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog thab gru bzhi bar /
NK071(du)002:7106: me dang me lha gnyis po 'od zer 'bar ba
NK071(du)002:7107: nyid nang du 'du bas longs spyod sdud cing phyir
NK071(du)002:7108: 'phro ba'i gzi brjid chen pos re ba skor bar
NK071(du)002:7109: bsam la / sngags mkhan dga' zhing spro ba'i yid
NK071(du)002:7110: kyis rgyas pa'i mchod sbyin bya bas tshe dang dpal
NK071(du)002:7111: dang 'byor ba la sogs pa yon tan nam mkha'i
NK071(du)002:7113: gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7114: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga gang rung gi gseb tu 'bru dang rin chen la sogs pa bsres la /
NK071(du)002:7115: nor bu gser dngul mu tig rta glang la sogs
NK071(du)002:7116: pa gang rgyas shing 'phel bar 'dod pa de'i gzugs
NK071(du)002:7117: kyi mtshan ma mir spel bris pa dang bcas pa
NK071(du)002:7118: byas te 'dod pa'i yon tan gang dgos 'byung ba
NK071(du)002:7119: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i gter du
NK071(du)002:7120: brtag nas / nga rgyal dga' 'phro'i rang bzhin rat+na
NK071(du)002:7121: k+ai la ya dngos grub kyi char 'beb par bskyed
NK071(du)002:7122: la gser la sogs pa'i phur pas gdab cing /
NK071(du)002:7123: yon tan rdo rje lta bu'i gzi brjid chen po
NK071(du)002:7124: 'phel bar 'gyur ba'i rat+na he ru ka'i tshogs sam
NK071(du)002:7125: rgyas pa'i me thab tu dbul lo //
NK071(du)002:7126: gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7127: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor thab khung gi mtha' 'am rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK071(du)002:7128: rnal 'byor ba lu gu rgyud du sbrel cing bsdams
NK071(du)002:7129: pa phyogs bcur bskyod nas bro brdungs pa'i 'od zer
NK071(du)002:7130: gyis longs spyod kyi sprin phung dang dpal dang gzi
NK071(du)002:7131: brjid 'bar ba'i rnam 'phrul chen po rang gi gnas
NK071(du)002:7132: der char du 'bab pa'i ting nge 'dzin spro zhing
NK071(du)002:7133: des sems can gyi dbul ba bsal bar bsam na
NK071(du)002:7134: / yon tan 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi
NK071(du)002:7135: nor bu'i nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur zhing bsam pa
NK071(du)002:7137: bzhi pa zhi ba'i las la'ang gsum las /
NK071(du)002:7138: dang po bsreg pa me'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7139: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog thab khung zlum
NK071(du)002:7140: po'i nang du me dang me lha gnyis ka 'od
NK071(du)002:7141: gsal ba'i gzi brjid 'tsher ba zhi ba'i rnam par
NK071(du)002:7142: bskyed la / sngags mkhan rab tu dang ba'i yid
NK071(du)002:7143: kyis nad dang gnod pa dang 'jigs pa zhi ba'i
NK071(du)002:7144: mchod sbyin bya bas shin tu ma rungs ba'i gtum
NK071(du)002:7145: chen rngam pa bdud dang ru tra la sogs pa'ang
NK071(du)002:7146: sems rab tu zhi ba byang chub kyi sems su
NK071(du)002:7148: gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7149: bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga la /
NK071(du)002:7150: gang zhi bar 'dod pa de'i gos dang dri ma
NK071(du)002:7151: la sogs pa bsres nas sngar bzhin ling+ga byas te
NK071(du)002:7152: // de nyid lus gtum ngag rngam sems 'khrug pa'i
NK071(du)002:7153: rnam pa can dgra bgegs la sogs pa gang yin
NK071(du)002:7154: pa de'i ngo bor brtag cing /
NK071(du)002:7155: lhan ner gsal ba bud+d+ha k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i dngul la sogs pa'i phur bus gdab nas /
NK071(du)002:7156: dpal dang gzi brjid 'bar ba lhan ne'i tshogs bud+d+ha
NK071(du)002:7157: he ru ka 'khor bcas sam zhi ba'i me lha
NK071(du)002:7158: la dbul lo // gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni /
NK071(du)002:7159: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' nyid du /
NK071(du)002:7160: rnal 'byor pa rnams lu gu rgyud du sbrel te bsdams nas bro byas na /
NK071(du)002:7161: pha rol khro ba'i me 'bar ba yang zhi bas lhan ne'i byin gyis rlabs pas khyab nas /
NK071(du)002:7162: sdig pa dang gdug sems thams cad yid la cung
NK071(du)002:7163: zad kyang mi 'gyu bas g.yo ba med par byed
NK071(du)002:7164: pa'o // de ltar e wam m+aa y+aa bzhi ni
NK071(du)002:7165: yi ge'i dbyibs kyis thab khung gi dbyibs mtshon par
NK071(du)002:7166: pa'o // byed pa'o // bla ma rong pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7167: dbang gi dkyil 'khor yi ge bam gyi rnam par bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7168: zhi ba ya'i rnam par bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7169: dbyibs dang kha dog gi rnam pas mi mthun yang yi ge sgra'i don dang sbyar na /
NK071(du)002:7170: bam ban d+ha na sdud pa'am bcing bar ya ba
NK071(du)002:7171: ti ni zhi ba ste 'di'i dbang du gsung pa
NK071(du)002:7172: yin par mngon no zhes bzhed do //
NK071(du)002:7173: gnyis pa las kyi rjes su bka' bsgo zhing bro
NK071(du)002:7174: gar gyi phan yon bshad pa la gnyis dam can
NK071(du)002:7176: bro gar gyi phan yon bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7178: dang po las la bsgo ba'i tshul brjod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7179: de ltar phrin las bzhi po gang yang rung ba'i
NK071(du)002:7180: rjes thogs su tshogs kyi 'khor lo la longs spyad
NK071(du)002:7181: de bza' btung gi lhag ma bsdus la rdo rje
NK071(du)002:7182: slob dpon gyi kha phrus byin gyis brlabs te dpal
NK071(du)002:7183: chen po'i dkyil 'khor du 'dus pa'i slas lha chen
NK071(du)002:7184: po rnams kyi chung ma dang byi mo mdza' na
NK071(du)002:7185: mo dang las byed pa'i bran mo'i tshogs /
NK071(du)002:7186: lhag ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa rnams la sbyin te
NK071(du)002:7187: za lam gom pa bdun cu'i sar bskyal zhing sngon
NK071(du)002:7188: dpal chen po'i spyan sngar khas blangs pa'i rang rang
NK071(du)002:7189: gi dam tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags nas /
NK071(du)002:7190: zhi ba la sogs pa gang 'dod pa'i las de byed par bsgo bar bya'o //
NK071(du)002:7191: gnyis pa ji ltar bsgo ba dngos ni sngon dregs
NK071(du)002:7192: pa'i dbang phyug rnams btul ba'i tshe dpal chen po
NK071(du)002:7193: he ru ka / shin tu gdug cing gtum bag
NK071(du)002:7194: can mdzad de 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi
NK071(du)002:7195: dregs pa ma lus pa rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'i
NK071(du)002:7196: he ru ka / // dbang phyug dang byin rlabs rmad po che mnga' bas /
NK071(du)002:7197: lha dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad dbang du bsdus nas /
NK071(du)002:7198: de dag gi 'khor chung ma dang bu mo dang
NK071(du)002:7199: pha ma dang phu nu ma lus pa rnams longs
NK071(du)002:7200: spyod pa'i phyir dbang phyug dang slas su byin gyis
NK071(du)002:7202: 'gug pa dang bcing ba dang gsod pa la sogs
NK071(du)002:7203: pa so so'i las rnams dpal chen pos rang rang
NK071(du)002:7205: sngon ji ltar dam bcas shing khas blangs pa bzhin
NK071(du)002:7206: skad cig kyang ma thogs par las kyi 'bras bu
NK071(du)002:7207: myur du mngon par phyung bar mdzod cig /
NK071(du)002:7208: rang rang gis dam bcas pa bzhin du ma byas na /
NK071(du)002:7209: sngon ji ltar dam bcas shing so sos mna' bor ba'i /
NK071(du)002:7210: sdom pa dam bcas pa de las 'da' bar 'gyur la /
NK071(du)002:7211: gal te dam tshig de las 'das par gyur na /
NK071(du)002:7212: khyed cag gi mgo lus dang snying yang tshal pa bdun du /
NK071(du)002:7213: yak+sha me dbal gyi khro bos dum bur gtubs par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:7214: rgyu mtshan de bas na rnal 'byor pa sngags 'chang bdag gis /
NK071(du)002:7215: las ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du byos shig /
NK071(du)002:7216: gal te las de mngon du ma byas na /
NK071(du)002:7217: rang rang gis mna' bor zhing khas blangs pa'i /
NK071(du)002:7218: dmod pa bzhi rul myags tshig nas rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:7219: des na rnal 'byor pa dam tshig la gnas par gyur pa'i /
NK071(du)002:7220: phrin las ci 'dod pa rnams yongs su bya ba dang /
NK071(du)002:7221: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi 'khor rnams kyang rang gi bu gcig pa bzhin du skyongs shig dang /
NK071(du)002:7222: de'i mthus khyed cag phra men ma yang mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'gyur bas /
NK071(du)002:7223: rnal 'byor pas ji ltar bcol ba'i las rnams mngon du byos /
NK071(du)002:7225: gnyis pa bro gar gyi phan yon la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:7226: don ngos bzung ba dang de rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7228: khro bo sgrub pa'i phrin las kyi gtso bo ni bro gar 'di yin no //
NK071(du)002:7230: gtso bo lnga'i bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:7231: khrag 'thung chen po bud+d+ha he ru ka la sogs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa'i /
NK071(du)002:7232: bro gar las bzhi'i skabs su bstan pa ltar glu tshig gi nga ro chen pos ni /
NK071(du)002:7233: zhi rgyas la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub
NK071(du)002:7234: thams cad dang mchog gi dngos grub thams cad ci
NK071(du)002:7235: 'dod par / phrin las thams cad dang dngos grub thams cad 'grub par byed pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:7236: gnyis pa gnas kyi ma mo brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni //
NK071(du)002:7237: goo r+ai'i sgra las mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs
NK071(du)002:7238: pa'i phyogs ma bzhi'i bro gar dang glu tshig chen
NK071(du)002:7239: mos ni / skye 'gro dbang du 'du bar 'dod na dbang du 'du bar byed cing /
NK071(du)002:7240: tshe dang yo byad la sogs pa 'phel bar 'dod na 'phel bar byed do //
NK071(du)002:7241: spos mo chen mo puk+ka s+ai la sogs pa'i mtshams
NK071(du)002:7242: ma bzhi'i bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni
NK071(du)002:7243: / dgra bgegs la sogs pa lhan ner zhi bar 'dod na zhi zhing lhan ner byed la //
NK071(du)002:7244: sems rmugs shing mi gsal bar byed par 'dod na rmugs par byed do //
NK071(du)002:7245: gsum pa yul gyi phra men brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:7246: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i phyogs ma bzhi'i /
NK071(du)002:7247: bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK071(du)002:7248: dgra bgegs thams cad kun gyi lus srog la za bar byed cing /
NK071(du)002:7249: rdul phra rab kyi cha shas tsam yang med par byed do //
NK071(du)002:7250: bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i mtshams ma bzhi'i bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK071(du)002:7251: gdug pa can thams cad kyi nang khrol dang don snying ma lus pa 'byin par byed cing /
NK071(du)002:7252: de dag gi srog la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa kun la rab tu nyams par byed do //
NK071(du)002:7253: bzhi pa dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK071(du)002:7254: slas dang byi mo dang bran mo'i tshogs kyis /
NK071(du)002:7255: bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK071(du)002:7256: pho nya dgra la rbad cing mngag gzhug las la gtang bar bya ba ste /
NK071(du)002:7257: phyir 'gal byed cham la 'bebs pa'i las thams cad
NK071(du)002:7258: dang nang du dngos grub yid bzhin 'grub pa'i las
NK071(du)002:7259: thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK071(du)002:7260: gsum pa las bzhi sgrub pa'i gnas dang ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par ni /
NK071(du)002:7261: ljon pa ste nags tshal dang ni lcug phran gyi tshal skyed shing gi ra ba dang /
NK071(du)002:7262: shing sdong gcig gi drung dang ni mes reg drung
NK071(du)002:7263: ste nags mes tshig pa'i gnas rnams su zhi ba
NK071(du)002:7264: dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po rnams bsgrub
NK071(du)002:7265: pa'i phyir du dang bas dang dga' bas dang chags
NK071(du)002:7266: pas dang / khros pas k+aa li ste thabs kyi phrin las bzhi po rab tu bsgrub par bya'o //
NK071(du)002:7267: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:7269: gtso bo de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la 'khor gyi
NK071(du)002:7270: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i
NK071(du)002:7271: don rtogs pa ste lung nod pa'i tshul gyis sbyong
NK071(du)002:7272: bar gyur to // rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK071(du)002:7273: ye shes kyi de kho na nyid nges pa las
NK071(du)002:7274: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa chen po ye nas lhun
NK071(du)002:7275: gyis grub pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhir gnas pa
NK071(du)002:7276: de nyid gdul bya'i don du byin gyis rlob pa
NK071(du)002:7277: zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7279: // spyi don gsum pa 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la bstod pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK071(du)002:7280: bstod tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7281: bstod pa dngos rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7283: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi mdzad pa rdzogs pa de
NK071(du)002:7284: nas rang snang gi sku dang ye shes la bstod
NK071(du)002:7285: pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i khrag
NK071(du)002:7286: 'thung rigs lnga'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis shin
NK071(du)002:7287: tu rngam pa'i mdangs kyis dgyes pa'i glu 'di blangs
NK071(du)002:7289: rigs dang rigs kyi bdag po la bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7290: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7291: dang po la gnyis rigs lnga la spyir bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7292: dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bye brag tu bstod pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7294: dang po sku'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni //
NK071(du)002:7295: h'uzhesa pa ni khro bo'i glu rnams re re zhing
NK071(du)002:7296: sku lnga ye shes lnga ldan du mtshon zhing mgo
NK071(du)002:7297: 'dren pa'o // de'ang sku ni bdud dang ru tra
NK071(du)002:7298: la sogs pa dregs pa can rnams 'dul bar byed
NK071(du)002:7299: pas gtum po chen po dus kyi mtha'i me chen
NK071(du)002:7301: me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa'i sku las ye
NK071(du)002:7302: shes kyi 'od zer nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid
NK071(du)002:7303: phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa ltar phyogs bcur 'phro zhing
NK071(du)002:7304: / gdug pa can la sdig pas khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin du 'khyug pa //
NK071(du)002:7305: mche ba zangs yag rno dkar bzhis ma rungs pa
NK071(du)002:7306: rnams za bar byed pa'i 'jigs byed che ho ni
NK071(du)002:7307: ngo mtshar ba'i gad mo ste 'og ma rnams la
NK071(du)002:7308: yang sbyar ro // gnyis pa gsung gi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni //
NK071(du)002:7309: h+aum khro bo'i gsung rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug sgra stong dus gcig la ldir ba lta bu'i //
NK071(du)002:7310: gtum chen dang drag shul ri rab 'bum dus gcig tu bsnyil ba'i sgra skad dang mnyam pa /
NK071(du)002:7311: a la dang ha la'i gad brgyangs chen por dgod
NK071(du)002:7312: cing dbugs kyi shug las spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung chen
NK071(du)002:7313: pos gdug pa can rnams 'jigs pas g.yeng bar byed
NK071(du)002:7314: pa ni dus mtha'i rlung bas kyang che'o ho //
NK071(du)002:7315: gsum pa thugs kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7316: h'u khro bo ma rig pa'i tshogs 'joms pa'i shes
NK071(du)002:7317: rab kyi snang ba mtha' yas pa'i 'od po che
NK071(du)002:7318: / ye shes lnga yi dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal bas /
NK071(du)002:7319: dug lnga 'bar ba'i ngo bo ye shes su gnas
NK071(du)002:7320: pas nyon mongs rang mtshan gyi rtsal kun tu 'joms
NK071(du)002:7322: sprul sku la ltos nas ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis dang /
NK071(du)002:7323: longs sku la ltos nas me long lta bu la
NK071(du)002:7324: sogs pa sna tshogs pa'i ye shes rnams ngo bo
NK071(du)002:7325: gnyis su med pa'i thig le che ste chos nyid
NK071(du)002:7326: don gyi ye shes su ro gcig pa'o ho //
NK071(du)002:7327: bzhi pa yon tan gyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7328: h+aum gdug pa can 'dul ba'i yon tan mnga' bas
NK071(du)002:7329: na khro bo'i rgyal po sprul pa sna tshogs su
NK071(du)002:7331: de las 'phros pa'i khro bo'i dkyiil 'khor gyi char chen po 'bebs shing /
NK071(du)002:7332: gang la gang 'dul gyi dkyil 'khor yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i gter las /
NK071(du)002:7333: sprul pa sna tshogs pa khros pa'i gzugs su nam
NK071(du)002:7334: mkhar khyab par 'byung ba thams cad kyang gnas lugs
NK071(du)002:7335: thig le chen po gcig go ho //
NK071(du)002:7336: lnga pa phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7337: h+aum phung po la sogs pa'i bdud kun gyi ni stobs 'joms pas na bdud chen po yin la /
NK071(du)002:7338: bdud kyi dbang po rnams kyang gdul bar byed pa'i
NK071(du)002:7339: bdud de las dang nyon mongs pa'i bdud rnams 'joms
NK071(du)002:7340: shing / bdud dang gshin rje la sogs pa 'jigs
NK071(du)002:7341: pa'i tshogs kyang rab tu 'jigs shing skrag par byed
NK071(du)002:7342: shing / pa / 'jigs byed chen po he ru
NK071(du)002:7343: ka rnams ni rang bzhin spros pa'i mtha' dang bral
NK071(du)002:7345: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bye brag tu bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7346: h'u che mchog yab yum gyi sku ni skye shi
NK071(du)002:7347: 'pho 'gyur med pas rdo rje brag chen rab tu
NK071(du)002:7348: sra ba chen po mtshan dpes 'bar zhing /
NK071(du)002:7349: gsung dang yon tan ni ye shes rdo rje yi
NK071(du)002:7350: chu bo che gdul bya'i tshogs sdud cing smin pa'i
NK071(du)002:7351: bdag nyid chen po yin la /
NK071(du)002:7352: thugs ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i rdo rje ye shes
NK071(du)002:7353: kyi me 'od gsal ba ste shes bya'i yul ma
NK071(du)002:7354: lus pa mngon du gyur cing thugs rjes 'od zer
NK071(du)002:7355: kun tu 'bar ba che ste 'gro ba'i ma rig
NK071(du)002:7356: pa'i mun pa thams cad sel bar byed pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7357: phrin las lhun gyis grub pa dang gdul bya la
NK071(du)002:7358: khyab pas rdo rje rlung ste bdud dang mu stegs
NK071(du)002:7359: la sogs pa 'thor zhing las bzhi'i don rnams rdzogs
NK071(du)002:7360: pa chen por lhun gyis grub par byed pas rlung
NK071(du)002:7361: chen po'o ho // gnyis pa rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)002:7362: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7363: h+aum gtum chen dus mtha'i zhes pa nas 'jigs byed
NK071(du)002:7364: chen po thig le che ho'i bar te he ru
NK071(du)002:7365: ka rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor la so sor bstod pa'o
NK071(du)002:7366: // rten gzhal yas khang la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7367: rdo rje brag chen keng rus kyi ri rab chu bo rak+ta'i rgya mtsho /
NK071(du)002:7368: me ye shes kyi me ri /
NK071(du)002:7369: rlung 'og gzhi rlung gi dkyil 'khor la sbyar te bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7370: zhes ched du glu blangs so //
NK071(du)002:7371: 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po sku dang ye shes
NK071(du)002:7372: kyi de nyid nges pa las rang snang ye shes
NK071(du)002:7373: kyi khro bo la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu
NK071(du)002:7375: spyi don gsum pa rgyud dam par gdams nas rjes 'jug la gtad pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK071(du)002:7380: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK071(du)002:7381: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK071(du)002:7382: kun tu bzang pos rang snang lhun stug po bkod
NK071(du)002:7383: pa'i rigs lnga sems dpa' brgyad la sogs pa'i de
NK071(du)002:7384: bzhin gshegs pa nyid la gsang sngags kyi rgyal po
NK071(du)002:7385: 'di nyid mi nub cing 'gro ba la phan gdags
NK071(du)002:7386: pa'i phyir brtan par bzung ba 'di ched du brjod
NK071(du)002:7387: cing khyad par du rig pa'i sems dpa' gsang bdag
NK071(du)002:7390: lam kun gyi 'bras bur gdams pa dang /
NK071(du)002:7391: gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7393: gdams bya rgyud kyi rang bzhiin dang /
NK071(du)002:7394: gang la gdams pa snod kyi che ba'o //
NK071(du)002:7396: dang po 'bras bu rgyud dngos bstan pa ni //
NK071(du)002:7397: rang snang gi thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK071(du)002:7398: pa'i rang bzhin yab yum du snang ba rnams la
NK071(du)002:7399: kye kye zhes bos nas snang srid 'khor 'das kyi
NK071(du)002:7400: chos phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di dag
NK071(du)002:7401: / de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga yab yum sems
NK071(du)002:7402: dpa' dang bcas pa zhi khro gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)002:7403: du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du
NK071(du)002:7404: gnas pa ni gzhi gsang ba'i snying po ste des
NK071(du)002:7405: mtshon nas lam dang 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po
NK071(du)002:7407: gnyis pa lam gzhan de'i rkang stegs su bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7408: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems kyi spros pa la 'chel ba yis /
NK071(du)002:7409: phyi nang bdag gzhan la sogs pa'i rnam par rtog
NK071(du)002:7410: pa mi bzad pa'i zhags pas so sor zin pa'i
NK071(du)002:7411: sems can gyi dbang po'i rim pa dang sbyar te
NK071(du)002:7412: theg pa so so'i sa rnams dang lam gyi khyad
NK071(du)002:7414: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam ste
NK071(du)002:7415: yin gyi lam tshang la ma nor ba dngos ma
NK071(du)002:7416: yin te de dag gi mthar thug 'dir 'jug dgos
NK071(du)002:7417: pa'i phyir ro // gsum pa rnam grangs du ma gsungs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7418: de ltar na gsang ba'i snying po kho na gsung bas chog mod /
NK071(du)002:7419: theg pa'i rnam grangs mtho dman mang po bstan ci dgos zhe na /
NK071(du)002:7420: sems can rnams ni dbang po'i rim pa sna tshogs
NK071(du)002:7421: su gnas pas gang la gang 'tshams kyis so sor
NK071(du)002:7422: bstan te / 'di nyid dang po nas go ba'am /
NK071(du)002:7423: phrad par shin tu dka' bas sngon 'agro'am stegs su
NK071(du)002:7424: bstan te phyis 'di dang 'phrad cing spyad par bya
NK071(du)002:7425: ba'i phyir spang ba dang rtogs pa'i ye shes ngo
NK071(du)002:7426: mtshar ba rab 'byams mnga' ba'i ston pa kun tu
NK071(du)002:7428: rang byung gi thugs rje sprul pa'i sku 'jig rten
NK071(du)002:7429: du snang bas gsungs pa'i chos thams cad kyang sems
NK071(du)002:7430: can gyi don du mi 'gyur zhes bya ba ni
NK071(du)002:7431: cung zad cig kyang yong ste rnam pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:7433: gnyis pa gang la gdams pa snod kyi che ba
NK071(du)002:7434: ni phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK071(du)002:7435: cad kyi / sku gsung thugs yon tan phun sum
NK071(du)002:7436: tshogs pa'i phyag rgya dam pa gzhi lam 'bras bu'i
NK071(du)002:7437: gsang chen chos thams cad kyi snying po 'di /
NK071(du)002:7438: phyin ci ma log par rang gis rtogs nas gzhan la smra bar gang byed pa /
NK071(du)002:7439: gang zag de nyid ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)002:7440: nga yin zhing de la phan pa dang nus pa'i
NK071(du)002:7441: dbang yang ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pa yin no
NK071(du)002:7442: // gnyis pa gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)002:7444: de 'dzin pa'i gang zag dam par lung bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7446: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la /
NK071(du)002:7447: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba mthar thug pa rgyud
NK071(du)002:7448: kyi don 'di las gzhan cung zad kyang mi mnga'
NK071(du)002:7449: bas mchog dam par zungs shig ces pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7450: de'i don yang chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa
NK071(du)002:7451: nyid gsang ba'i snying por sangs rgyas pa ni gzhi'i
NK071(du)002:7452: rgyud de rgyal ba thams cad kyis gtan la dbab
NK071(du)002:7454: de nyid ston pa gzhung gi tshogs la'ang don zab
NK071(du)002:7455: mo yod par rtag pa'i mthar sgro 'dogs pa dang
NK071(du)002:7456: med pa chad pa'i mthar skur pa 'debs pa dang
NK071(du)002:7457: gnyis ka dang gnyis min gyi spros pa thams cad
NK071(du)002:7459: blo'i yul las 'das pas gsang ba'i snying po chos
NK071(du)002:7460: thams cad kyi de kho na nyid de chos nyid
NK071(du)002:7461: bsam brjod med pa nges pa'i dbyings nas brjod pa'i
NK071(du)002:7462: don du ston pas phyung ba'o //
NK071(du)002:7463: gnyis pa de 'dzin pa'i gang zag dam par lung bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7464: rgyud 'di 'dzin cing ston pa'i gang zag de ni
NK071(du)002:7465: gzhan la ston pa rig pa'i skyes bu dang rang
NK071(du)002:7466: nyid sangs rgyas pa nges par lung bstan te /
NK071(du)002:7467: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras po ni
NK071(du)002:7468: dam pa thugs kyi gsang ba las skyes pa yin
NK071(du)002:7469: pas / sa rab rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa la gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)002:7470: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)002:7472: rang snang 'od gsal du bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)002:7473: pa rigs lnga til gyi gong bu ji snyed kyis
NK071(du)002:7474: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' dbus khyab pa de dag
NK071(du)002:7475: thams cad gnyis su mi dmigs shing ngo bo dbyer
NK071(du)002:7476: med pas dgyes nas dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa'i
NK071(du)002:7477: ngang gzhi rdzogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin dus
NK071(du)002:7478: bzhi chos nyid kyi 'khor lor mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK071(du)002:7479: dbyings // snang zhing bkod pa thams cad ston pa
NK071(du)002:7480: nyid kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK071(du)002:7481: 'khor lo'i rang bzhin lhun stug po bkod pa'i rgyan
NK071(du)002:7482: nyid du 'pho 'gyur med par bzhugs so //
NK071(du)002:7483: spyi don gsum pa yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don la gsum las /
NK071(du)002:7484: dang po rgyud gang gi khongs su gtogs pa ni
NK071(du)002:7485: brjod bya gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa bden
NK071(du)002:7486: pa gnyis dbyer med pa'i don ye nas sangs rgyas
NK071(du)002:7487: par ston pas brjod byed tshig gi rgyud la'ang de
NK071(du)002:7488: dang mthun par btags pas 'phags pa 'jig rten dang
NK071(du)002:7489: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs
NK071(du)002:7490: kyi rgyud thams cad la rtog pa zhes brjod pas
NK071(du)002:7491: de dag thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:7492: rtog pa'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul
NK071(du)002:7493: d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i khongs su gtogs
NK071(du)002:7494: so // gnyis pa le lag gang yin pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7495: de las 'di ni rgyu mtshan nyid dang 'bras bu
NK071(du)002:7496: gsang sngags kyi rgyud thams cad kyi 'phro gzhi dang
NK071(du)002:7497: 'byung khungs yin pas lung gi spyi de nyid de
NK071(du)002:7498: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo
NK071(du)002:7499: rje'i gsang ba yin la mchog tu 'phags shing rab
NK071(du)002:7500: tu zab la rgya che ba'i gnas ston pa'i phyir
NK071(du)002:7501: gsang ba'i snying po gzhi lam 'bras bu de kho
NK071(du)002:7502: na nyid rnam par nges pa'o //
NK071(du)002:7503: gsum pa 'bras bu mchog tu bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)002:7504: de nyid las thams cad ma lus par 'phros te
NK071(du)002:7505: chos kyi dkyil 'khor lo bskor ba de dag gi
NK071(du)002:7506: 'bras bu'i mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud zhing khams gsang ba'i
NK071(du)002:7507: snying po ye shes kyi rang snang de kho na
NK071(du)002:7508: nyid nges pa las mdzad pa rdzogs nas dgongs pa
NK071(du)002:7509: la bzhugs pas mnyes pa dang rgyud mi nub par
NK071(du)002:7510: gtad pas 'khor gyis yongs su gzung ba'i le'u ste
NK071(du)002:7513: // shin tu rtogs dka' rgyud don rdo rje'i tshig /
NK071(du)002:7514: kun mkhyen bla ma'i snyan brgyud man ngag bzhin //
NK071(du)002:7515: gsal bar bstan la nongs pa ci mchis pa //
NK071(du)002:7516: dbyings phyug mkha' 'gros bzod pa bzhes par mdzod //
NK071(du)002:7517: ces rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa
NK071(du)002:7518: ba'i rgyud kyi mchan 'grel 'di ni kun mkhyen chos
NK071(du)002:7519: kyi rgyal po rgyal ba klong chen pa'i 'grel pa
NK071(du)002:7520: ji lta ba bzhin grub pa'i slob dpon o rgyan
NK071(du)002:7521: bstan 'dzin nor bu'i thugs kyi cha shas las skyes
NK071(du)002:7522: pa sprang ban gzhan phan snang bas mkhas pa'i 'byung
NK071(du)002:7523: gnas grub pa'i gdan sa rdzogs chen sh+r+ai seng gi
NK071(du)002:7524: chos sder sbyar bas 'od gsal snying po'i bstan pa
NK071(du)002:7525: la bya ba byed nus par shog cig //
NK071(du)002:7527: rang snang mi 'gyur 'og min chen po ru //
NK071(du)002:7528: sna tshogs zhi dang khro bo'i rol gar gyis //
NK071(du)002:7529: nam mkha'i mtha' klas 'gro ba sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK071(du)002:7530: gsang chen bla med chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK071(du)002:7531: rgyud dang theg pa'i rim pa grangs mang po //
NK071(du)002:7532: kun gyi mthar thug 'od gsal rdzogs pa che'i //
NK071(du)002:7533: gzhi dang lam dang mthar phyin 'bras bu'i don //
NK071(du)002:7534: gtan la 'bebs pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud //
NK071(du)002:7535: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan stong pa nyid //
NK071(du)002:7536: bde chen 'gyur med ye shes kyis rol pa'i //
NK071(du)002:7537: gnas gsum dpa' bo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams kyi //
NK071(du)002:7538: thugs kyi thig le rgyud rgyal 'di kho na //
NK071(du)002:7539: zab pa'i don 'dus yang zab phul du byung //
NK071(du)002:7540: rgya che'i rgyud lung rgya cher gtan la 'bebs //
NK071(du)002:7541: rig 'dzin dgongs rgyud rig stong gsal ston pa'i //
NK071(du)002:7542: rgyud rgyal 'di ni rgyal ba dngos dang 'dra //
NK071(du)002:7543: kun khyab gdod ma'i gzhi la byang chub pa'i //
NK071(du)002:7544: mi yi lus la sangs rgyas dgongs pa can //
NK071(du)002:7545: klong chen chos kyi rgyal po'i legs bshad ni //
NK071(du)002:7546: rig 'dzin snyan brgyud gdams ngag lugs su byas //
NK071(du)002:7547: de phyir 'di ni kun mkhyen bla ma yi //
NK071(du)002:7548: gzhung lugs ji bzhin snying po yongs bsdus shing //
NK071(du)002:7549: blo mchog ldan pa'i 'jug ngogs zla med pa //
NK071(du)002:7550: rgyud don gsal byed 'chad pa'i skyes bu bzhin //
NK071(du)002:7551: 'di na tshig rgyud grangs med spel ba'i 'phrul //
NK071(du)002:7552: gsang chen rgyal ba'i mchod sdong 'di bsgrubs pas //
NK071(du)002:7553: 'od gsal snying po'i bstan pa rgyas pa dang //
NK071(du)002:7554: 'gro kun gdod ma'i gzhi ru grol bar shog /
NK071(du)002:7555: ces pa 'adi'ang 'jigs med mdo sngags bstan 'dzin gyis
NK071(du)002:7556: gsang ba'i snying po'i mchan 'grel spar du sgrub pa'i
NK071(du)002:7557: tshe / spar byang smon tshig tu gzhan phan snang
NK071(du)002:7558: bas bris brgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che phyogs
NK071(du)002:7559: dus gnas skabs thams cad du dar zhing rgyas la
